NK109(dze)001:1: // rdzogs pa chen po mu tig phreng rgyud gsal byed pan chen bi ma las mdzad pa bzhugs so ///
NK109(dze)001:4: rat+na mu sa la pra ka ri na ya /
NK109(dze)001:6: mu tig rin po che gsal bar 'byed pa zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:7: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK109(dze)001:8: dpal ldan bla ma mkha' 'gro ma //
NK109(dze)001:9: rgyud kyi ston pa 'gro ba'i bla //
NK109(dze)001:10: gong ma'i brgyud pa byin rlabs ldan //
NK109(dze)001:12: rdzogs pa chen po mngon gsum lam //
NK109(dze)001:13: gsang ba'i rgyud rgyal nges phye nas //
NK109(dze)001:14: dbang po'i yul du mthong don du //
NK109(dze)001:15: dgos don man ngag bdag gis dbye //
NK109(dze)001:16: gal te 'khrul pa'i blo nyes sam //
NK109(dze)001:17: 'dod tshig rtags su bkod pa dang //
NK109(dze)001:18: mi shes yid kyis dpyad pa rnams //
NK109(dze)001:19: mkhas pa rnams la bzod par mdzod //
NK109(dze)001:20: de la yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnam
NK109(dze)001:21: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan gyis
NK109(dze)001:23: chos nyid mngon gsum gyi dgongs pa las dus thams cad du mi 'da' ba nyid kyis /
NK109(dze)001:24: gdul bya'i rigs mi 'dra ba tha dad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:25: de nyid 'dul bar byed pa'i sku yang tha dad par sprul te /
NK109(dze)001:26: brjod bya tshig gi bye brag kyang tha dad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:27: khyad par gyi gdul bya blo mchog tu gyur pa rnams la dgongs pas /
NK109(dze)001:28: tshe 'di nyid la zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po mi snang par sangs rgya ba'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:29: rang rig khyab pa mngon gsum gyi gnad la dgongs nas dbang po la rno brtul med cing /
NK109(dze)001:30: las la bzang ngan med par nyid kyi sgor zhugs
NK109(dze)001:31: so lcog la sa rnam pa gsum du mi brgyud
NK109(dze)001:32: par bstan pa'i / gsang ba'i rgyud khyad par mchog tu nges par bsdus nas bstan pa'i bka'/
NK109(dze)001:33: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa cig char du bstan pa /
NK109(dze)001:34: mngon gsum gnad kyis ma thog tu grol bar byed
NK109(dze)001:35: pa'i rgyud mu tig 'phreng ba'i rgyud chen po gsungs
NK109(dze)001:36: te / de'i dgongs pa tshig la lhad med cing
NK109(dze)001:37: don la 'khrul pa med par bstan pa la gnyis
NK109(dze)001:38: te / te / dbang po mchog gis cig char
NK109(dze)001:39: du rtogs par bya ba'i phyir rgyud kyi mtshan bstan
NK109(dze)001:40: pas khams gsum dong nas sprugs par bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:41: te / te / / gdul bya thun mong pa rnams rim gyis rtogs nas /
NK109(dze)001:42: khams gsum rang rgyud du mi ldog par bya ba'i phyir rgyud kyi gzhung bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:43: de la mtshan bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:44: grub mtha' 'dod rgyal ba nyams par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:45: rdzogs pa chen po mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pas theg brgyad blo'i chos grol lugs bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:46: rgyud mtshan nges pa rang gi 'dod pa'i khong 'grel
NK109(dze)001:47: ba la brten nas gsang ba'i rgyud 'di la 'jug
NK109(dze)001:49: de la grub mtha' 'dod rgyal ba rnams nyams par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:50: rdzogs pa chen po mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pas
NK109(dze)001:51: theg brgyad blo'i chos las grol lugs bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:52: / de yang grub mtha' 'dod rgyal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:53: so so'i skye bo la ltos pas phyi rol phyin
NK109(dze)001:54: ci log tu lta ba rnams 'byung ba bzhi don
NK109(dze)001:56: bag la nyal rgyun gcod par 'dod pa'i mi dang /
NK109(dze)001:57: 'byung ba rtags pa rang bzhin can rkyen dang bcas par 'dod pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:58: 'byung ba bye brag yan lag dang bcas pa'i mu las ma 'das pas na /
NK109(dze)001:59: chos nyid la phyin ci log tu gyur pas mu mtha' dang bcas pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:60: sems can dmyal ba'i skye gnas su 'khrid pa la 'di las lhag pa'i chos gzhan med de /
NK109(dze)001:61: de ltar kyang bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:62: khams gsum mu dang bcas pa'i phyin ci log /'dod khams mu mthar gnas nas ni //
NK109(dze)001:63: 'byung ba'i thems kyis gtim pa'i srog chags kyis //
NK109(dze)001:64: mi 'dra'i lus ni skye ba 'bum phrag brgyad //
NK109(dze)001:65: de nas yi dwags drag po'i skye gnas te //
NK109(dze)001:66: de 'og dman pa'i lus dang rme sha can //
NK109(dze)001:67: sdig lus 'khor bas yang ni mu matha'o //
NK109(dze)001:69: yang de dag la ltos pas /
NK109(dze)001:70: nyan thos bye brag pas gang zag la 'byung ba zhes bcings pa'i bdag med la /
NK109(dze)001:71: chos kyi khams phyogs gcig tsam zhig gal te yod pa'i mu ste /
NK109(dze)001:72: cha med pa'i rdul phra rab kyi phung po khams
NK109(dze)001:73: dang bcas pas bcings ba zhig 'phags pa rnams kyi
NK109(dze)001:74: spyod yul du ma gyur pa gcig yod par 'dod
NK109(dze)001:77: de ltar kyang rdo rje rtse mo rnam par rol pa las /
NK109(dze)001:78: gal te chos kyi bdag nyid cha //
NK109(dze)001:80: lus can mtha' yi bye brag tha dad du //
NK109(dze)001:81: rnal 'byor spyod las khyad par log snang bas //
NK109(dze)001:82: byang chub gnas su 'di nyid ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:84: yang mdo sde bas gang zag la bdag med par mthun pa la /
NK109(dze)001:85: chos kyi cha yi bdag de yang /
NK109(dze)001:89: de yang mthar gyis 'phra ba'i mu la ltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:90: gzugs kyi khams su skye bar yang /
NK109(dze)001:92: gang zhig smra bar byed pa'i mdo sde pas //
NK109(dze)001:93: 'phra ba'i gzugs la ltas pa yis //
NK109(dze)001:94: rags pa'i khams la de bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:98: rang rgyal dang bse ru ltar gnas pa'i spyod pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:99: bsgom rten 'brel lugs 'a byung du bsgoms pas /
NK109(dze)001:100: shes bya'i gzhi lnga'i matha'i rtog pa las grol bar ltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:101: chos thams cad bdag gam bdag gis stong par lta
NK109(dze)001:102: ba'i mu la ltas pas bdag tu rtog pa dag
NK109(dze)001:103: pa ste / de nyid kyi mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:104: lha min gyis skye ba khyad par can du skye ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:105: de ltar kyang bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:106: stong pa bdag med mu la gnas bcas nas //
NK109(dze)001:107: shes bya mtha' yi dri ma rtog pas sel //
NK109(dze)001:108: lha min khams gsum las ni 'dod srid do //
NK109(dze)001:110: yang de nyid las ltos pas ni 'khor gnas pa'i rang rgyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:111: 'gro ba'i gnas mtshungs par ldan pas khyad par rten pas /
NK109(dze)001:112: lta spyod khyad par gyi 'jug pa la brten pas /
NK109(dze)001:113: bsgoms pa rten 'brel lugs ldog la bsgoms pa'i mus /
NK109(dze)001:114: mi sdug pa'i rang bzhin brgyad rgyud la skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:115: spyod pa'i 'jug pa la rten nas lta ba'i don
NK109(dze)001:116: ya dang bcas pas rgyud la skye bar 'dod pa
NK109(dze)001:117: ni / lha min kha 'thor ba'i skye gnas su skye ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:118: yang bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:119: gang zhig tshogs la gnas pa'i stong blo can //
NK109(dze)001:120: skye mched lugs kyis rang gi rgyud rtan pas /
NK109(dze)001:121: kha 'thor lus te 'jug pa'i las kyis so //
NK109(dze)001:125: de yang sems tsam rnam bden pas don dam pa rnam par rig tsam la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:126: phyi rol don yod pa'i mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:127: rnam par shes pa mtha' yas pa'i skye gnas su skyes pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:128: de ltar kyang ut+pa las rab tu mdzes pa'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:129: gang gi phyi rol don rnams rig rtsal nyid //
NK109(dze)001:130: rnam shes mtha' yas 'khor ba'i mthar lhung nas //
NK109(dze)001:131: pre mtha' 'jug pa'i lus su gyur ta re //
NK109(dze)001:133: de la ltos pas rnam rdzun pas phyi rol don med par /
NK109(dze)001:135: dri med la rang rig rgyun chags su gnas pa'i mus /
NK109(dze)001:136: ci yang med pa'i skye mched du skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:137: de ltar kyang gser gyi snying po'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:138: gang zhig rnam par rdzun pas bslus pa'i gzugs can nyid //
NK109(dze)001:139: stong pa rang rig rgyun la bcas pas na //
NK109(dze)001:140: ci yang med pa'i yid kyi lus can rnams //
NK109(dze)001:143: dbu ma rang rgyud pa snang pa rten 'brel gcig dang du ma bkag pas /
NK109(dze)001:144: stong pa'i rang rgyud du 'dod pas /
NK109(dze)001:145: 'od gsal gyi skye gnas su skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:146: de ltar kyang bkod pa chen po las /
NK109(dze)001:147: stong pa gzhan bkag 'dod pa'i blo can rnams //
NK109(dze)001:148: 'od gsal gzugs kyi khams su 'jug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:150: de la ltos pas dbu ma thal 'gyur ba /
NK109(dze)001:151: khas len med pa'i stong pa'i spyod yul du 'dod pas /
NK109(dze)001:152: gzugs med pa'i khams phal par skye ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:153: de ltar kyang de nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:154: gang gis gzhan 'dod bkag nas khas mi len //
NK109(dze)001:155: gzugs med khams kyi 'bras bu 'byin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:157: de ltar rgyu'i theg pa sum brgya /
NK109(dze)001:158: rtag chad bdag dang bcas pa'i mu las gzhan du gyur pa /
NK109(dze)001:161: stong pa'i mu la gnas pas khams gsum las mi grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:162: de dag las khyad par du gyur pa 'bras bu
NK109(dze)001:163: gsang sngags kyi theg pa stong par smra ba ni
NK109(dze)001:164: / phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud kyi theg pa gsum las /
NK109(dze)001:166: kri ya bas bsrung pa chang la sogs pa gcig bsrung pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:168: dmigs pa gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:169: lha drug rje khol gyi rnam pa ltar lta ba'i mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:170: gnas tha ma'i lha rigs rnams su skye ste /
NK109(dze)001:171: de ltar yang rdo rje snying po mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:172: gang zhig smyung bar gnas nas zas dkar za //
NK109(dze)001:173: gos gsum rje dang lha la lha //
NK109(dze)001:174: gnas gtsang rigs kyi lha'i skye gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:176: de la ltos pas u pa ya /
NK109(dze)001:177: lta spyod ya 'khyal ba'i mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:178: 'og min gyi lha yi gnas su skye ste /
NK109(dze)001:179: yang mkha' 'gro brtse ba'i snying po'i rgyud las //
NK109(dze)001:180: gang la lta spyod nyid la sa zin med //
NK109(dze)001:181: snying rje skyo ba'i bdag nyid sems rangs pa //
NK109(dze)001:182: 'og min lha yi gnas su skye ba kho na'o //
NK109(dze)001:184: de la ltos pas yo ga bas /
NK109(dze)001:185: mngon par byang chub pa lnga las bskyed nas /
NK109(dze)001:186: dal rgyal mchog nas zhugs pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:187: bdag dang lha spun grogs po ltar ltas pa'i mus
NK109(dze)001:188: bdag tu bcings pas gzugs kyi khams lha'i gnas su
NK109(dze)001:189: skye ba ste / yang de nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:190: gang zhig cho ga 'dus pa'i yan lag las //
NK109(dze)001:191: lha dang bdag gnyis bzung dang 'dzin gyur pas //
NK109(dze)001:193: gzugs kyi khams su gnas nas gzhan du 'khor //
NK109(dze)001:195: de la ltos pas ma h+aa yo ga bas /
NK109(dze)001:196: 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum la rim gyis pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:197: gcig char du 'jug pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:198: phrin las bzhi'i las kyi khyad par mngon par rtogs pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:199: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob kyi rnam pa la /
NK109(dze)001:200: 'di ltar phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang du blta ba'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:201: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad lha dang dal lha mo'i du blta ba'i mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:202: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha'i gnas su skye ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:203: de ltar kyang shel gyi khang bu brtsegs pa'i rgyud las //
NK109(dze)001:204: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med 'dod pa yang //
NK109(dze)001:205: dngos la stong pa'i rgyas 'debs gzugs la rjes 'gro bas /
NK109(dze)001:206: gzhan las sprul pa'i lha yi skye gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:208: de la ltos pas a nu ba dbyings dang ye
NK109(dze)001:209: shes las gcig char ba dang rim gyis dang mthar
NK109(dze)001:210: chags dang / thod rgal du zhugs pa'i mu dang /
NK109(dze)001:211: zung 'jug la rnam par lta bas chu la nya ldang lta bu'i mu la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:212: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched du skye ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:213: rdo rje dur khrod kyi rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:214: gnyis 'jug khyad par 'jug pa'i las kyis kyang /
NK109(dze)001:215: rnam pa'i bden pas sa ya bde gnas phyir /
NK109(dze)001:216: gang dag stong pa'i bden pas khyad par med phyir yang /
NK109(dze)001:217: rnam par shes tsam nyid du 'khor bar nges par gnas /
NK109(dze)001:219: de ltar na dngos por smra ba mu stegs rtag chad nas /
NK109(dze)001:220: sems tsam pa yan chad kyang khams gsum las mi grol la //
NK109(dze)001:221: de yang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa rnams ni rang
NK109(dze)001:222: rang gi lta spyod kyi 'dod pa mthar phyin na
NK109(dze)001:224: 'dod pa tshad du ma phyin na ngan song gsum gyi skye gnas su skye'o //
NK109(dze)001:225: stong par smra ba'i theg pa sngags dang /
NK109(dze)001:226: pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa gnyis kyang /
NK109(dze)001:227: khams gsum las mi grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:229: rim rtsol blo yi theg pa brgyad //
NK109(dze)001:230: khams su 'khrid par byed pa'i dam pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:231: yid dpyod blo yi chos de tshig la zhen //
NK109(dze)001:232: yang dag don gyi bden pa med pas lam gyi rtogs //
NK109(dze)001:235: de dag las khyad par du gyur pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ste /
NK109(dze)001:236: klong sde lta sgom spyod gsum la zhen pas kyang /
NK109(dze)001:237: chos nyid mngon sum dang 'gal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:238: sems sde sems yin la las pas /
NK109(dze)001:239: chos nyid mngon gsum la mnyam byed du las pas yang dag par ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:240: de dag las khyad par du gyur pa man ngag gi sde ste /
NK109(dze)001:241: de la yang bye brag pa rnams kyang don rang thog tu mi phebs so //
NK109(dze)001:242: de dag las khyad par mu las grol te rig pa phebs pa 'di nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:243: de yang chos ma yin pa'i mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:244: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i lam nyid yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:245: theg brgyad blo'i chos las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:246: yid dpyod tshig la 'dzin pa rang log ste /
NK109(dze)001:247: chos nyid rang ngo la gnas pas rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:248: de yang tshig gi mtha' las grol bas dpyod du ma song la /
NK109(dze)001:249: gsal ba'i mtha' las grol bas ris can ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:250: stong pa'i mtha' las grol bas phyam ma chad /
NK109(dze)001:251: yod pa'i mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:253: med pa'i mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:254: yid dpyod kyi skyon med par /
NK109(dze)001:255: yin pa'i mtha' las grol bas 'di 'dra gcig tu nges pa med /
NK109(dze)001:256: min pa'i mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:257: rtog dpyod blo'i chos las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:258: de ltar na snang srid 'khor 'das yod med thams cad yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:259: spang blang las 'das pa'i tig zhes bya /
NK109(dze)001:260: chos dang chos ma yin pa'i mthar 'dzin pa yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:261: bdag dang bdag ma yin pa'i rnam rtog dang bral ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:262: chos dang chos nyid kyi mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:263: lta sgom spyod pa la rag ma lus pas /
NK109(dze)001:264: rang gi rang bzhin gyis gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:265: khams gsum dus gcig la grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:266: rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:267: dbang po la rno brtul med pas /
NK109(dze)001:268: mngon gsum gnad kyis grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:269: thos bsam rag ma lus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:270: de'i phyir na mngon gsum mthong ba'i gnad la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:271: mthong snang chos kyi shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:272: bsgom mi dgos pas goms stobs la rag ma lus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:273: chos nyid kyi snang ba mthong ba'i gnad gyis /
NK109(dze)001:275: dge ba dag rnam smin la mi ltos pas na /
NK109(dze)001:276: mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:277: khyad par chen po'i lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:278: de yang snang ba'i tig ka yin pas 'khrul snang zhing khams su 'char /
NK109(dze)001:279: stong pa'i tig ka yin pas da lta gtan la phebs so //
NK109(dze)001:280: snang stong dbyer med pa'i tig ka yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:281: dus thams cad du chos nyid kyi 'phreng pa las
NK109(dze)001:282: ma 'das pas bgrang bya yul gyi rtog pa chod
NK109(dze)001:283: / chos dang chos ma yin pa tig la phebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:284: bdag gzhan matha'i dri ma las te /
NK109(dze)001:285: dus thams cad du nyams su myong pa rang thog na gsal ba'i 'phreng ba la ga nas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:286: de lta bu'i rgyud de sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad la khyab par gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:287: sangs rgyas dang sems can khyad med pas /
NK109(dze)001:288: lam gyi bcos su med pas /
NK109(dze)001:289: rang rig rang sa nas gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:290: de ltar na breng chags pas rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:291: da ni rgyu mtshan nges par rang 'dod pa khong 'brel la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:292: gsang ba'i rgyud 'di la 'jug ngo shes par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:293: mtshan rang gi ngo bo bstan pa de nyid mtshan
NK109(dze)001:294: bstan pa tsam la brten nas gzhung don bde blag
NK109(dze)001:296: de la mtshan rang gi ngo bo bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK109(dze)001:297: yi ge brda' sbyor gyi man ngag la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:298: snang brtags thams cad sgra don 'brel par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:299: dang / 'khor 'das ltar snang gi man ngag la brten nas thams cad brdar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:300: don chos nyid mngon gsum la brten nas skal ba can khams gsum du mi brgyud par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:301: de la yi ge brda' sbyor gyi man ngag la
NK109(dze)001:302: brten nas snang brtags thams cad sgra don 'brel bar
NK109(dze)001:303: bstan pa ni / sgra'i ngo bo brjod bya'i mthar
NK109(dze)001:304: thug pa nges tshig grags pas na sgra yin pas
NK109(dze)001:305: de nyid kyi don mtshon la /
NK109(dze)001:306: brjod pas na sgra yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:307: de nyid don mtshon la gnas pas na sgra yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:311: 'byung ba gnad la 'bebs pa'i las nye par mtshon pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:313: yi ge brda' sbyor gyi sgras yi ge'i 'brel du
NK109(dze)001:314: ma la brten nas chos nyid kyi don mtshon pa'o
NK109(dze)001:315: // brjod pa rang gzhan gyi sgras sems rigs kyi rtsas ston pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:316: gnas pa rang srog gi sgras lus sems kyi 'brel 'tshol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:317: bkod pa 'brel sbyor gyi sgras tshig gi mtha' sdud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:318: rang gzhan 'dug stong gi sgras chos nyid kyi lam 'tshol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:319: de la yi ge 'brel sbyor gyi sgra ni /
NK109(dze)001:320: bkod pa'i yi ge skad rigs mi 'dra ba so so'i yi ger bris pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:321: gnas pa'i yi ge so so'i rtsa rnams kyi nang
NK109(dze)001:322: nas rtsa gnas kyi yi ge sus kyang byas pa
NK109(dze)001:323: med par spus bris pa tsam la rdzas su ma
NK109(dze)001:324: grub pa / la las ni 'gro ba so so rang gi lus bskyed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:328: la las ni 'gro ba'i 'byung ba so so'i rten dang /
NK109(dze)001:333: gsad cing gtan du brlag pa'i las byed /
NK109(dze)001:337: la las ni phung po dang khams dang skye mched dang /
NK109(dze)001:338: dbang po dang yul gyi 'brel gcod cing sbyong /
NK109(dze)001:339: la las ni khrag dang chu ser dang /
NK109(dze)001:340: sha dang rus pa'i 'phel 'grib kyi las nye bas byed do //
NK109(dze)001:341: la las ni blo dang shes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:348: de la 'di ni bkod pa'i yi ge'i sgra don te /
NK109(dze)001:349: de yang sgra dang skad gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:351: yi ge 'di dag rgya'i skad lo tsa bas rang 'thad du bstan pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:352: rgya'i skad dang mi mthun pas /
NK109(dze)001:353: sgra don la dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:354: la la nas don rang 'thad du yod pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:355: rgya gar skad dang mthun pas bod skad du mtshams sbyar ba yang yod do //
NK109(dze)001:356: de la chos nyid rtag pa yin pas ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:357: 'gyur ba med pa'i ye shes de phyogs gang du
NK109(dze)001:358: yang ma byung pas ngo bo stong rig gsal bar
NK109(dze)001:359: gcig la / rgya gang du yang ma chad pas /
NK109(dze)001:360: thams cad kyi dngos gzhir byung pas ta yin la /
NK109(dze)001:361: de yang thog mtha' gang dang yang ma 'dres pas /
NK109(dze)001:362: de nyid ring por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:363: de'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang 'gyur med dag pa'i
NK109(dze)001:364: 'od lnga rang gsal bas gu gu 'od mtshon par
NK109(dze)001:365: byung ba'o // de nyid mtho ris ngan song na
NK109(dze)001:366: yod kyang mi 'gyur bas sa zhes pas ni t+ais
NK109(dze)001:368: de la rgyan gyi yi ge sar byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:369: gang zag bu tha ba'i tshe na yang /
NK109(dze)001:370: de nyid las 'gyur ba med pa sta zhes /
NK109(dze)001:371: rtag pa kun grol gyi yi ger byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:372: skad kyi dbang du byas na mu tig zhes sgra rang sor bzhag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:373: de lta bu'i chos yang dag pa nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:374: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gang shar yang /
NK109(dze)001:375: de nyid las 'gyur ba med pas sa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:377: rang rig pa'i ye shes 'char byed kyi sgo ma 'gags pas rgyan gyi yi ger yin la /
NK109(dze)001:378: de ltar kyang ma rig pa gsum gyis sgribs pas rba yin /
NK109(dze)001:379: skad ltar na thams cad ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:380: de ltar ma rig pa gsum las ma 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)001:381: rig pa de la skye ba yod ma myong pas
NK109(dze)001:382: / da lta skye ba la mi gnas /
NK109(dze)001:384: khams gsum 'khor ba'i ming med pas +aahzhesa ring por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:385: de yang 'di nyid a la lnga yod pa las
NK109(dze)001:386: a glang po'i sna zhes bya ste skye med mtshon
NK109(dze)001:387: pa'o // de nyid las ma bcos na chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:388: mnyam pa'i las dus gsum du g.yos pa med pas
NK109(dze)001:389: pa'o // / ma zhes ring por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:390: de ltar skye med mnyam pa nyid dus gsum du gsal 'grib med pas /
NK109(dze)001:391: sno ra dbyings gcig tu 'dus par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:392: de ltar gnas pa'i chos nyid la sku gsum rang
NK109(dze)001:393: shar te dag pa rang grol du byung bas k+aa
NK109(dze)001:395: skad ltar byas na thang log tu 'gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:397: de lta bu'i sku gsum las so so'i 'char sga ma 'gags pas ra yin la /
NK109(dze)001:398: de la ngos bzung gang du yang ma grub pas
NK109(dze)001:399: ye nas stong pas rang chad pas da zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:400: ba / de yang 'gro ba'i lus la gnas b+y+aa ring por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:401: de ltar lus la gnas pa'i chos nyid de lus ji srid du gnas pa'i rin la /
NK109(dze)001:402: rtag par bzhugs pas ta yin la /
NK109(dze)001:403: de yang 'bras bu sku gsum gyi lus su grol nas na yin la /
NK109(dze)001:404: de ltar rtag pa'i chos nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:405: ye shes lnga'i 'char sgo ma 'gags pas tra zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:406: de yang lus kyi sgo dgu las mi gsan 'char bas na zhes thung bar byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:407: de nyid thog ma'i gzhi la rang log pas m+aa zhes ring por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:408: zhes yi ge brda' sbyor gyi man ngag la rten
NK109(dze)001:409: nas snang brtags thams cad sgra don 'brel bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:410: nas / 'khor 'das brdar snang gi man ngag brten nas thams cad brdar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:411: brda ni spyir na chos thams cad brdas brtags pas na /
NK109(dze)001:412: brda' nyid la rang bzhin ni /
NK109(dze)001:413: ngo bo gang du yang grub pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:414: snang grags kyi chos thams cad sgyu ma rmi lam /
NK109(dze)001:415: rmi lam gyi rnam pa ltar shes pas gang la
NK109(dze)001:416: yang zhen pa'i blo mi skye bas na chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:417: bu thog tu ma grol bas zhes bya ba nas
NK109(dze)001:418: / bod skad du zhes brdas brtags pas /
NK109(dze)001:419: gang du 'dzin pa'i blo mi skye ba'i skye med don gyi ngo bo mi zin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:420: de la chos dang chos ma yin pa rnams brda' tsam mam /
NK109(dze)001:422: tshig tsam las ma 'das pas na /
NK109(dze)001:423: gang yang ma yin pa'i ngo bo mngon gsum du snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:424: don chig chod du grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:425: khams gsum dus gcig la lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:426: 'khor 'das brdar snang gi man ngag la brten nas thams cad brdar bstan pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:427: mtshan don chos nyid mngon gsum la brten nas skal
NK109(dze)001:428: ba can khams gsum du mi brgyud par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:429: ni / mu zhes lus kyi gnad la brten nas chos nyid mngon gsum du 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:430: de yang lus dbang dang 'brel bas /
NK109(dze)001:431: dad pa dang ldan pa'i gang zag thog ma gzhi
NK109(dze)001:432: ma smin pa smin par byed pas na 'di'i le'u
NK109(dze)001:433: bzhi pa nas phyag rgya chen po mngon pas shes
NK109(dze)001:434: pa la sogs pa dbang bskur ba'i mu ni /
NK109(dze)001:435: bskur rgyud yod pa spros bcas kyi dbang dang /
NK109(dze)001:436: bskur rgyu yod pa dang med pa phyed ma spros med kyi dbang dang /
NK109(dze)001:437: bskur rgyu med pa shin tu spros med kyi dbang dang /
NK109(dze)001:438: bskur rgyu las 'das pa rab tu spros pa med pa'i dbang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:440: smin pa grol bar byed pa bla ma'i man ngag gis tig la 'bebs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:441: 'di'i le'u brgyad pa las gnas lugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa la sogs pas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:442: de ltar nyams su blangs pa las grol lugs gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:443: nyams yar 'phel du grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:444: 'bad med du grol pa gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:445: nyams yar 'phel du grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:447: lu gu rgyud ni grangs mang la sogs pas bstan /
NK109(dze)001:450: lcags kyi lcags rnams la sogs pas bstan pas na /
NK109(dze)001:452: de yang stong pa'i mu las grol pas gsal ba'i tig ka 'od du gnas te /
NK109(dze)001:453: chos nyid kyi rang gdangs so //
NK109(dze)001:454: de nyid kyi mu las 'das pas gsal stong gang du yang mi 'byed do //
NK109(dze)001:455: de ltar mu tig ni mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pa'i lta ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:456: yod med rtag chad kyi rang bzhin gyis mtha' las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:457: rig pa nyid la gang gis kyang ma gos pas na /
NK109(dze)001:458: snang ba'i dus na rang snang bas gzhan ltos kyi chos las grol la /
NK109(dze)001:459: gnas pa'i tshe na rang gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:460: bcas bcos blo'i rtog pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:461: grol ba'i dus na rang grol bas gnyen po gzhan la ma ltos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:462: de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:463: dben pa rin po che gser gling du phyin pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:464: sa rdo'i bag med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:465: rnal 'byor pa des 'gro nyal 'dug sdod bya ba ci dang ci byed kyang /
NK109(dze)001:466: chos nyid mngon gsum gyi ngang las ma g.yos pas /
NK109(dze)001:467: yid dpyod dang tshig tu rtog pa las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:468: de nyid kyi gzungs las 'das pa med pas 'phreng ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:469: rgyud ni rang rgyud rnam par dag pa dri ma med pa nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:470: mngon gsum gnad kyis zin pas /
NK109(dze)001:471: lu gu rgyud 'phel dang bcas te snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:472: de la goms pas brtson 'grus rab 'di nyid la zag bcas mi snang sangs rgya /
NK109(dze)001:473: 'bring po chos nyid kyi bar ma do la sangs rgya /
NK109(dze)001:474: tha ma rang gzhan sprul sku'i zhing khams su dbugs phyung nas sangs rgya'o /
NK109(dze)001:475: de'i phyir na don khams gsum du mi brgyud pas don zab mo don gyi chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:476: zhes mtshan don chos nyid mngon gsum la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:477: skal ba can khams gsum du mi brgyud par bstan
NK109(dze)001:478: nas / de nas mtshan bstan pa tsam la brten
NK109(dze)001:479: nas gzhung don bde blag tu rtogs par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:480: nas / ni / de yang gsang ba'i rgyud 'di la /
NK109(dze)001:481: le'u brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:483: mu zhes pa bsdus pa'i don gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:484: ston pa rang gi 'khor 'du ba'i don du gzhi
NK109(dze)001:485: snang gi rig pa mngon gsum du bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:486: / sdud pa pos rang gi 'khor gyis rtogs par
NK109(dze)001:487: bya ba'i phyir thun mong gi gleng gzhi brjod bya
NK109(dze)001:488: rang gi ngo bo dang bcas te bstan pa gnyis
NK109(dze)001:489: / las / de la 'di skad bdag gis bstan pa'i zhes pa la sogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:490: rang ngo rnam dag gi gnad yod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:491: bdag gis thos pa la sogs pa theg pa thun mong ba la brgyad du phye bas /
NK109(dze)001:492: gdul bya gang zag rnams kyis rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:493: de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi gnas lugs la thun mong snang thabs su byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:494: de gnyis zung du zhugs pas 'khrul pa rang dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:495: le'u gnyis pa 'khrul pa gzhi la bzlog pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:496: dper na mu tig dkar dmar gyi 'phreng ba rab tu spel legs pa /
NK109(dze)001:498: rig pa nyid mngon gsum du snang pas 'khrul pa rang dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:499: de nyid las yon tan gyi 'phel sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung yang /
NK109(dze)001:501: dang po zhu ba sngon du 'gro bas ye shes rang gi ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:502: sdud pa pos rgyud 'di khyad par legs par bsgrubs pas /
NK109(dze)001:503: chos nyid la byan tshud par 'gyur pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:504: gnyis pa de ltar byan tshud pas 'khrul pa ldog tshul bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:505: ye shes rang ngo shes pas de nyid las gzhan du brjod du med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:506: gsum pa de ltar log pa'i ye shes ngos bzung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:507: rang gi rig pa las ma rtogs pa'i chos logs pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:508: bzhi ba de ltar ngos zin pa'i 'khrul ba de la bzla ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:509: 'khor 'das thams cad rang byung ye shes su bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:510: de yang gdul bya skal ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis bde blag tu rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:511: dang po la yan lag gi don brgyad /
NK109(dze)001:512: gnyis pa la drug gsum pa la bcu /
NK109(dze)001:513: de ltar nyer dgus mu tig 'phreng ba brgyus pa ltar bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:514: yang le'u gsum pa 'khrul pa bdas su brda' ba'i
NK109(dze)001:515: le'u mu tig gi 'phreng ba rnam par bkod par
NK109(dze)001:516: ni bsdus pa'i don lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:517: de dag nyid kyis zhu ba sngon du 'gro ba 'khrul pa nyid kyi rang bzhin bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:518: 'khrul pa ye shes su 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:519: gnyis pa de'i snang ba de nyid rang ma 'khrul bar bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:520: snang sems gnyis med du grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:521: gsum pa 'khrul pa nyid kyi don rtogs na thams
NK109(dze)001:522: cad rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas yin par bstan pas
NK109(dze)001:523: / rang byung gi ye shes spang blang las 'das par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:524: bzhi pa de ltar don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK109(dze)001:525: snang ba thams cad la gnas lugs kyi rgyas thebs
NK109(dze)001:527: gang ltar spyad kyang chos nyid las 'das pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:528: lnga pa de'i phyir na rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NK109(dze)001:529: bla ma'i gdams ngag 'brel par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:530: rig pa'i ngo bo kun la khyab kyang de nyid rang bzhin gdams ngag gis grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:531: de la yan lag gi don ni 'phreng ba brgyus pa'i rnam pa ltar bshad na /
NK109(dze)001:536: lnga pa la drug ste sum cus mu tig 'phreng ba brgyus legs ba ltar ba stan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:537: le'u bzhi pa la 'bad med rang grol du bstan
NK109(dze)001:538: pa'i mu tig gi 'phreng ba rnam dkar bkod pa
NK109(dze)001:539: ni bsdus pa'i don dgu ste /
NK109(dze)001:540: dang pos chos nyid kyi rgyan du thams cad 'dus par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:541: rig pa'i che ba ngos zin /
NK109(dze)001:542: gnyis pa de nyid las ye shes kyi byung tshul bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:543: 'khrul ma myong pa'i ye shes ngos zin /
NK109(dze)001:544: gsum pa de la rgyun du spyod pa'i thabs bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:545: goms pa rang rgyud la shar /
NK109(dze)001:546: bzhi pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di dag kyang rang 'byung du bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:547: thams cad rang 'byung ye shes kyi rol pa ngos zin /
NK109(dze)001:548: lnga pa 'khrul pa de yang rkyen kha nas bzlog par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:549: ye shes ma bu'i snang ba ngo sprad /
NK109(dze)001:550: drug pa de ltar log pa nyid zhing khams su skyel bar bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:551: ye shes dag pa'i snang ba rang ngo shes /
NK109(dze)001:552: bdun pa rta mgrin la sogs pa'i khro bo de
NK109(dze)001:553: dag kyang rgyal ba bslang ba'i don 'di ltar snang
NK109(dze)001:554: ba thams cad rang grol du bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:555: rdzogs pa chen po spang blang las 'das pa'i lta bas zin /
NK109(dze)001:556: brgyad pa mkha' 'gro ma la sogs pas zhu ba
NK109(dze)001:557: sngon du 'gro zhing rjes su yi rang ba dang
NK109(dze)001:558: bcas pas / snod bcud kyi 'jig rten 'di ltar grol lugs bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:559: rang bzhin rnam dag gi lta ba gzhi la skyol /
NK109(dze)001:560: dgu pa de ltar sems dang po yang grol na
NK109(dze)001:561: bcud kyi sems can cis ma grol bar bstan pas
NK109(dze)001:562: / 'gro ba rnams rang 'byung gi ye shes las ma 'das /
NK109(dze)001:563: de yang yan lag 'phreng bas mdzes par spras pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:572: dgu pa la bzhi ste bzhi bcu rtsa gcig gis
NK109(dze)001:573: rgyud kyi le'u mu tig gi 'phreng ba brgyus pa
NK109(dze)001:574: ltar bshad pa'o // le'u lnga pa gnas lugs la
NK109(dze)001:575: 'khrul pa rang rdzogs su bstan pa'i le'u mu tig
NK109(dze)001:576: gi 'phreng ba rnam par bkod pa ni bsdus pa'i
NK109(dze)001:577: ltar bshad pa'o // don gnyis te / dri ba mdor bstan pas rang don gyi the tshom bsal /
NK109(dze)001:578: lan rgyas par bshad pas rang bzhin gyi don mngon
NK109(dze)001:579: par rtogs pa'i de'i yan lag gi 'phreng bas mdzes
NK109(dze)001:580: par spras na / lan la drug de'i nyid lag gis spras na /
NK109(dze)001:581: de la drug yod pa'i bsdus don dang po la drug gnyis pa la gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:583: de'i bzhi pa la drug de'i lnga pa la bcu ste /
NK109(dze)001:586: sum cu rtsa bzhi pa le'u lnga pa'i mu tig gi phreng bas mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:587: le'u drug pa sems can gyi snang thabs bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)001:588: mu tig gi 'phreng ba rnam par bkod pa ni
NK109(dze)001:590: dang po dri ba dang bcas pas dgongs pa ngo bo nyid kyi gnas lugs bstan pa /
NK109(dze)001:591: rang bzhin gnas thabs kyi snang ba ngos zin /
NK109(dze)001:592: gnyis pa ngo bo nyid de la 'ching byed kyi dri ma gang yin par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:593: ye shes dang nyon mongs pa'i tshad zin /
NK109(dze)001:594: gsum pa sems can la gzhi lam 'bras bu ji ltar tshad bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:595: rig pa nyid rtsol ba las 'das par ngo shes /
NK109(dze)001:596: de dag gi yan lag gi 'phreng bas mdzes par spras na /
NK109(dze)001:599: de'i nying lag gis mdzes par spras na /
NK109(dze)001:602: bsdus don gnyis pa la gsum /
NK109(dze)001:603: de'i nying lag dang po la lnga /
NK109(dze)001:604: gnyis pa la drug gsum pa la yang drug ste /
NK109(dze)001:605: de ltar sum cu rtsa dgus le'u drug pa'i 'phreng ba mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:606: le'u bdun pa 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang
NK109(dze)001:607: la rdzogs par bstan pa'i mu tig gi 'phreng ba
NK109(dze)001:610: dang po rig pa'i ngo bo de nyid 'khor ba'i chos du ma ltar byung ba bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:611: byas bcos ci dang ci byas pa chos nyid du rang grol bar shes /
NK109(dze)001:612: gnyis pa de yang sbyor ba'i lus dang sems la tshang bar bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:613: gzhan nas btsal mi dgos par thag chod /
NK109(dze)001:614: gsum pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad
NK109(dze)001:615: rnal 'byor pa'i lus dang sems la tshang bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:616: pas / thams cad rang grol chen po gcig gi 'khor lo las ma 'das par rtsal 'byongs /
NK109(dze)001:617: bzhi pa dkon mchog gsum rang gi lus dang sems la tshang par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:618: mchod par bya ba'i yul gzhan na med par yid ches /
NK109(dze)001:619: lnga pa dkar po'i chos de dag rang gi lta ba'i ngo la ji ltar gnas bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:620: las dge sdig gi shan phyes /
NK109(dze)001:621: drug pa sems dang ye shes kyi dbye ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:622: kun gzhi dang chos sku gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:623: 'byung ba dwangs snyigs su dbye ba bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:624: nyams su blang bya dang blang bya ma yin pa nye bar rtogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:625: de dag la yan lag gis rnam par spras na /
NK109(dze)001:626: dang po la drug gnyis pa la gsum /
NK109(dze)001:631: sum cu rtsa gsum gyis le'u bdun pa'i don mu
NK109(dze)001:632: tig gi 'phreng bas rnam par spras pa ltar bstan
NK109(dze)001:633: pa'o // le'u brgyad pa rgyud rnam par bsdoms te
NK109(dze)001:634: bstan pa'i mu tig gi 'phreng ba rnam par bkod
NK109(dze)001:635: pa'o // na / bsdus pa'i don bzhi ste /
NK109(dze)001:636: dang po thabs kyi rgyud kyi don bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:637: 'khor ba las tshegs med par grol bar ngo shes /
NK109(dze)001:638: gnyis pa rang gzhan gyi rgyud kyi don bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:639: 'khor 'das gnyis med du ngo mnyam par thag chod /
NK109(dze)001:640: gsum pa tshig gi rgyud kyi don bstan pas blos brtags pa'i spros pa chod /
NK109(dze)001:643: rnal 'byor pa'i lam ye shes kyi cha rkyen dang gros byas par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:644: de la yan lag gi rgyas par bshad na /
NK109(dze)001:646: gnyis pa la drug gsum pa la yang drug bzhi pa la yang gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:647: nyer gnyis kyis le'u brgyad pa'i mu tig gi 'phreng bas mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:648: de ltar gsang ba'i rgyud 'di la le'u brgyad du byung bas ni mu zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:649: de ltar le'u brgyad pa bsdus pa'i don sum cu rtsa gcig gis spras pas ni tig ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:650: de yang yan lag dang rang nying lag gis shin tu rgyas par spras na /
NK109(dze)001:651: nyis brgya dang sum cu rtsa dgus le'u brgyad pa'i rnam par bcad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:652: rin po che'i 'phreng ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:653: de ltar na mu tig ni khyad par gyi don te /
NK109(dze)001:654: rgyal po gcig la mu tig gi phung po gcig yod na /
NK109(dze)001:655: 'jig rten 'di'i 'dod pa'i don yongs su rdzogs pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:656: gsang ba'i rgyud ni 'dzin pa'i 'gro ba skal pa yod pa las /
NK109(dze)001:657: sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu tshegs med par 'byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:658: de ltar yang a ti bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:659: 'gro ba mchog tu gyur pa'i mis //
NK109(dze)001:662: klags pa nyid kyis sangs rgyas zhing //
NK109(dze)001:663: mdzes shing nyams dang ldan par skye /
NK109(dze)001:665: yang yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che yod pa'i mis /
NK109(dze)001:666: nyi ma dang zla ba gzas zin pa'i tshe rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags nas /
NK109(dze)001:667: mchod pa lnga phul nas gsol ba btab nas /
NK109(dze)001:668: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ji ltar 'dod pa 'byung ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:669: rgyud 'di bla ma'i man ngag gis bkrol nas /
NK109(dze)001:670: brtson 'grus dang bcas par thang bcad de nyams su blangs na /
NK109(dze)001:671: brtson 'grus rab 'di nyid la 'khrul pa'i snang ba nub nas ye shes dag pa'i snang ba 'char /
NK109(dze)001:672: 'bring la chos nyid kyi bar ma do la 'char /
NK109(dze)001:673: tha mas rang bzhin sprul pa sku'i zhing khams su dbugs phyung nas de nyid la shar nas /
NK109(dze)001:674: mi lo lnga brgya na chos nyid ka dag gi klong du yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK109(dze)001:675: de ltar yang +aa ti bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:676: gang gis mu tig 'phreng ba'i rgyud //
NK109(dze)001:677: bla ma'i man ngag gis bkrol nas //
NK109(dze)001:678: goms pa rgyud la brten pas ni //
NK109(dze)001:679: khams gsum dag tu mi ldog go /
NK109(dze)001:680: gal te goms par ma gyur na //
NK109(dze)001:682: chos nyid bden pa'i stobs kyis kyang //
NK109(dze)001:683: ka nas dag pa'i rig mthong ngo //
NK109(dze)001:686: ri rab kyi zom na yod pa'i gnod sbyin gyi phug ces bya ba na /
NK109(dze)001:687: rin po che 'bar ba yon tan mngon par 'byung ba zhes 'phreng ba yod de /
NK109(dze)001:688: de khrus byas nas sus bgrangs pa'i tshe /
NK109(dze)001:689: gser gyi dong rtse lnga brgya lnga brgya 'byung pa gcig yod pas /
NK109(dze)001:690: de la lha rnams kyis brkus shing 'phrog par bltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:691: 'phreng ba de nyid shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten na /
NK109(dze)001:692: gser gyi 'khor lo rnam par dag pa'i nam mkha' zhes bya ba la 'phar bas /
NK109(dze)001:693: de'i tshe nam mkha' de nyid gser gyi bye ma
NK109(dze)001:694: sna tshogs su 'phros pa zhes bya ba'i char babs
NK109(dze)001:695: pas / phyi'i rgya mtsho na gnas pa'i klu'i rgyal
NK109(dze)001:696: po rnams kyi gtsug gi nor bu'i 'od nyams shing
NK109(dze)001:697: yon tan stong par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:698: de ltar na bcom ldan 'das bya rgod kyi phung
NK109(dze)001:699: po'i ri la theg pa sna tshogs kyi chos kyi
NK109(dze)001:700: gsung rnam par dag pa'i sgra sgrogs pa'i tshe /
NK109(dze)001:701: nam mkha' nas mu tig gi 'phreng ba rnam par spras pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:702: zhes lan gsum du grags pas /
NK109(dze)001:703: de'i bcom ldan 'das kyi 'khor brgya stong bye ba
NK109(dze)001:704: phrag khrig dpag tu med pa rnams kyis mi skye
NK109(dze)001:705: ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK109(dze)001:706: de yang rgyu gang las byung zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:707: de'i tshe 'og min gyi gnas na rgyud kyi rgyal
NK109(dze)001:708: po 'dis sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung rnam par dag
NK109(dze)001:709: pas yongs su spras pa'i byin gyis rlabs las byung
NK109(dze)001:710: pa'o // de ltar yang bkod pa chen po las //
NK109(dze)001:711: gang gis mu tig 'phreng ba'i rgyud //
NK109(dze)001:712: 'gro ba phal pa sus kyang ni /
NK109(dze)001:713: rna bar lan gsum thos pas kyang //
NK109(dze)001:714: skye med chos la longs spyod do //
NK109(dze)001:721: rgyud du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK109(dze)001:722: ngo bo ni bar ma chad cing tshig don rnam par chod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:723: nges tshig ni gnas pas rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:725: thabs dang shes rab tu 'brel bas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:727: rgyud rang ngo bo'i dbye ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:732: tshig gi rgyud dang gsum mo //
NK109(dze)001:733: thabs kyi rgyud la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:734: mtshon bya thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:735: mtshon byed thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:736: de ltar yang 'di'i le'u brgyad pa nas //
NK109(dze)001:737: mtshon bya dang ni mtshon byed do //
NK109(dze)001:739: mtshon bya'i rgyud la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:742: yang de nyid nas khyab pa rnam pa gnyis yin te zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:743: rang bzhin gyi rgyud gsum ste /
NK109(dze)001:744: gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:745: snying po rang bzhin gyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:746: bcud rang bzhin gyi rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:747: de ltar yang gzhi dang snying gi bcud nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:749: de yang bsdu na tshig gi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:753: de ltar yang don rgyud dang ni tshig rgyud do zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:754: de la tshig gi rgyud la bco brgyad yod kyang brgyad du bsdus te /
NK109(dze)001:756: yan lag gi rgyud gnyis dang /
NK109(dze)001:757: lung rig gsal ba'i rgyud gnyis dang /
NK109(dze)001:758: man ngag gi rgyud bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:760: dgongs pa rang gnas kyi rgyud gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:761: 'jug pa rang grol gyi rgyud gnyis dang /
NK109(dze)001:762: mkhas pa cho ga'i rgyud dang brgyad du 'dus so //
NK109(dze)001:763: rtsa ba ni rdzogs pa rang byung dang yi ge med pa gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:764: bshad pa ni rang shar rang grol gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:765: yan lag ni rin po che spungs pa dang sku gdung 'bar ba gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:766: lung rigs gsal ba'i gnyis ni sgra thal 'gyur dang /
NK109(dze)001:773: dgongs pa rang gnas gsum ni /
NK109(dze)001:776: nyi zla kha sbyor dang gsum mo //
NK109(dze)001:777: 'jug pa rang grol gnyis ni seng ge rtsal rdzogs dang /
NK109(dze)001:779: mkhas pa cho ga'i rgyud ni dpal nag mo 'khros pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:781: thabs khyad par dang thun mong las /
NK109(dze)001:784: rang bzhin ni gzhi gnas lugs dang /
NK109(dze)001:786: bcud rigs pas na rgyud du 'thad do /
NK109(dze)001:787: tshig ni spras pas na rgyud du 'thad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:788: rgyun du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK109(dze)001:790: me tog la sogs rang 'byung rang grol du rtogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:791: zhes de dag rnams bstan par bya /
NK109(dze)001:793: zhes mtshan bstan pa tsam la brten nas gzhung don bde blag tu rtogs par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:794: de dag gis ni rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:795: da ni rgyud de nyid kyi brjod bya'i don bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:796: don gyi ngo bo rig pa ye shes la dbang
NK109(dze)001:797: mi za ba'i phyir phyag btsal ba bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:798: / bcom ldan 'das zhes pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:800: sdud pa pos drin lan gyi tshul du btsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:801: rtogs pa'i bdag nyid rang gzhung du btsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:802: sdud pa po'i dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)001:803: ston pa'i yon tan la dmigs te /
NK109(dze)001:804: ston pa nyid la 'jig rten dga' ba de la zhen pa med pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK109(dze)001:805: phung po lnga'i rdos pa rang rgyud du med par /
NK109(dze)001:806: de dag rnams rang snang rang grol du yod pas /
NK109(dze)001:808: rtog pa rnam pa tha dad pa la 'dzin pa'i nyon mongs pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:810: ye nas skye ma myong ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:811: da lta skye ba la mi gnas pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:812: phyis skye mi srid pa'i dgongs pa la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:815: de las mang ba'am nyung ba'i gzhom bya med dam zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:816: spyir 'gro ba rnams kyi skye ba bzhi'i khungs stongs
NK109(dze)001:817: par bya ba la gzigs la nang du sems can
NK109(dze)001:818: gyi skye rgas na 'chi bzhi las grol ba la
NK109(dze)001:819: gzigs la / gsang ba sku bzhi'i 'bras bur dril ba la gzigs pas so //
NK109(dze)001:820: de yang bdud bzhi po de 'joms la /
NK109(dze)001:821: gzhom bya'i yul gzhan med dam zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:822: gzugs kyi phung po rdul phra rab du ma 'tshogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:824: sems kyi khang bu bshig pas 'khor 'das dpyis 'byin pa'i man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:825: lus sems kyi 'brel chad de shing dang bya lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:826: tshor ba'i phung po bde sdug btang snyoms lus sems gnyis ka 'ching ba'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:827: skye ba snga phyi 'tshams 'byed pa snang shes mi bden pa'i man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:828: skye ba snga phyi mi bden pas sems kyi ltos zad pa /
NK109(dze)001:829: mkha' la mkha' thim pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:830: 'du shes kyi phung po rnam par rig rtsal gyis shes pa'i rten byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:831: rig pa lu gu rgyud bcings pa'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:832: chos nyid mngon gsum mthong ba rang grol gyi man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:833: brda' la byang ba'i skyes bu la zla ba bstan pa lta bu'o /
NK109(dze)001:834: 'du byed kyi phung po nyon mongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:835: nye ba'i nyon mongs pas yul dang shes pas 'ching ba'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:836: rnam shes rang grol gyi man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:837: mkha' la mdud pa bor ba lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:838: rnam shes kyi phung po yul yul can du 'dzin pas /
NK109(dze)001:839: rdzogs pa chen po thig le nyag gcig spros pa'i mtha' las grol ba bcings pa'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:840: mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:841: ba mo dang reg pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:842: de ltar na phung po lnga la tshod du 'dzin pa dang zhen pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:845: skye mched du 'khor mi srid pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:846: de nyid la dmigs nas phyag rtsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:847: bdag gis kyang man ngag lnga'i don rtogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:848: de yang phyi 'byung ba lnga'i bcings pa las grol /
NK109(dze)001:849: nang dbang po lnga'i 'du mched las grol /
NK109(dze)001:850: gsang ba rigs lnga'i skur smin pa la dgos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:851: de yang gti mug dge dang mi dge lung du
NK109(dze)001:852: ma bstan pas shes rab gcod par byed pa la
NK109(dze)001:853: bcings pa'i bdud / chos nyid yin pa la bdag
NK109(dze)001:854: tu med pa'i man ngag la brten nas bcom pas
NK109(dze)001:855: bcings pa'i bdud / / gzu bo'i blo can lha khang du phyin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:856: zhe sdang rag pa yan lag dang bcas pas rnam
NK109(dze)001:857: par mi rtog pa'i bsam gtan la bcings pa'i bdud
NK109(dze)001:858: / rang grol chen po 'gyur ba med pa'i man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:859: sbrul mdud rang grol ba lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:860: 'dod chags yul mthar thug dang bcas zhen pas /
NK109(dze)001:861: snang ba dag pa'i ye shes la bcings pa'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:862: 'gyu ba rang dag stong pa kun lam gyi man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:863: bar snang gi ser bu lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:864: nga rgyal min mnyam la bdag tu 'dzin pas /
NK109(dze)001:865: chos nyid nyams skye ba'i yon tan la bcings pa'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:866: ye med sems kyi spyibs 'byin pa'i man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:867: grong khyer dgras bcom pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:868: phrag dog rjes tha dad pa la rtogs pa dang bcas pas /
NK109(dze)001:869: rang sems mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' dang bral ba la bcings pa'i bdud /
NK109(dze)001:870: sems kyi yul dbyung ba stong pa kun sangs kyi man ngag la brten nas bcom pas /
NK109(dze)001:871: khyim stong gi rkun po lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:872: de lta lnga yang phyir yul lnga'i 'dzin pa sangs song pa la dgongs /
NK109(dze)001:873: nang du rlung lnga zad pa la dgongs /
NK109(dze)001:874: gsang ba ye shes lnga mngon du shar ba 'bras bu la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:875: de yang bzhi po de bdud du 'gro ba ci zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:876: phung po lngas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi ye shes la bar du bcad nas /
NK109(dze)001:877: lugs med pa la snang du ma gtub pas bdud yin la /
NK109(dze)001:878: nyon mongs pa lngas sku gsum lam du snang ba la bar du bcad pas /
NK109(dze)001:879: phyis 'bras bu re ba bdud yin /
NK109(dze)001:880: lha'i bu 'jig rten gyi 'dod pa dga' ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:887: gnyen 'dun la chags pas thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa la bar du bcad nas /
NK109(dze)001:888: lo les g.yengs te ma gos pa'i stobs ma rnyed pas bdud do //
NK109(dze)001:889: 'chi bdag lus sems kyi rten nyams par byed pas /
NK109(dze)001:890: bsgom bsgrub rnal 'byor gyi spyod pa la bar du
NK109(dze)001:891: bcad pas goms pa'i stobs sam gegs ma snyed pas
NK109(dze)001:892: bdud do // de ltar bcom pa la dmigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:893: ston pa'i yon tan bdag gis len par byed pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:894: de ltar gdul bya ma 'ongs pa rnams la nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:895: de'i phyir na bcom zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:897: ston pa de nyid gzugs phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan /
NK109(dze)001:898: dpe byad brgyad cus spras pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:899: sku'i zhabs kyi 'khor lo la sogs te mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis spras pas /
NK109(dze)001:900: 'jig rten pa las khyad par du gyur pa'i gzugs dang ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:901: de nyid kyi rang don chos nyid mngon gsum du
NK109(dze)001:902: rtogs pas bdag gi dpal stong pa nyid la thugs
NK109(dze)001:903: ldan dang / rnam pa thams cad pa mkhyen nyid
NK109(dze)001:904: kyi ye shes kyi rnam par 'phrul pa'i thugs rje
NK109(dze)001:905: ldan dang / gsum / gdul bya'i yul gsum la shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:906: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal dang ldan pas /
NK109(dze)001:907: 'gro ba'i don rdzogs par mdzad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:908: de nyid grags pa dang ldan te /
NK109(dze)001:909: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK109(dze)001:910: bar du mdzad pa sum cu rtsa drug mthar phyung /
NK109(dze)001:911: tha ma mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pas /
NK109(dze)001:912: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phun sum
NK109(dze)001:913: tshogs pa dang ldan pa de yang ye shes phun
NK109(dze)001:914: su tshogs pa dang ldan te stong pa nyid la
NK109(dze)001:915: thugs 'byongs pas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mkhyen
NK109(dze)001:916: la / gsal ba ris med du thugs su chud pas /
NK109(dze)001:917: me long lta bu'i ye shes mkhyen /
NK109(dze)001:918: thugs mnyam par las ma g.yos pas /
NK109(dze)001:919: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mkhyen la /
NK109(dze)001:920: 'gro ba tha dad pa'i bsam pa thugs su chud
NK109(dze)001:921: pas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su thugs su
NK109(dze)001:922: chud mkhyen pa'o // 'gro ba'i don la nan tan
NK109(dze)001:923: du mdzad pas bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes
NK109(dze)001:924: su mkhyen pas longs sku'i dus na mtshan nyid 'dzin
NK109(dze)001:925: pa'i ye shes lnga dang ldan /
NK109(dze)001:926: chos sku'i dus na gzhi gnas kyi ye shes gsum /
NK109(dze)001:927: sprul sku'i dus na shes bya'i ye shes gnyis dang ldan pa'i dbang phyug phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:928: 'jig rten du bdud rnams bcom la 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ma lus par mkhyen no //
NK109(dze)001:929: brtson 'grus ni go cha'i brtson 'grus kyis byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed /
NK109(dze)001:930: lhur blangs pa'i brtson 'grus kyis bar du bskal pa grangs med par tshogs bsags /
NK109(dze)001:931: dpung gi brtson 'grus kyis bdud la sogs pa'i bar chod rnams bsal nas sangs rgyas so //
NK109(dze)001:932: de ltar drug dang ldan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:933: phyir 'gro ba rigs drug la gzigs la /
NK109(dze)001:934: nang du skye mched drug la gzigs la /
NK109(dze)001:935: gsang bar ye shes drug gi mkhyen pa rdzogs pas drug dang ldan pa kho na'o //
NK109(dze)001:936: de nyid sems kyi blo'i rtog pa las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:937: byas pa med pa'i thugs rje rang shugs su byung
NK109(dze)001:938: bas rig pa ni 'jig rten gyi rig pa'i gnas
NK109(dze)001:939: lnga phyin ci ma log pa mkhyen yang /
NK109(dze)001:940: 'gro ba rnams kyi gdul bya'i zhing dag 'das pa'i rig pa mngon gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:941: shes pa'i cha gnyis ka mkhyen pas /
NK109(dze)001:943: bdag nyid ni de lta bu'i rig pa nyid /
NK109(dze)001:944: rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa la sogs pa'i dri ma /
NK109(dze)001:945: 'khrul pa de ma yin la der 'dzin pa mi mnga' bas /
NK109(dze)001:946: chos nyid stong pa kun khyab pa'i rig pa nyid rang snang ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK109(dze)001:947: zhes sdud pa pos mngon 'byung du btsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:948: sdud pa po'i phyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig pa ma lus pa /
NK109(dze)001:949: ston pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan la dmigs pas byang /
NK109(dze)001:950: nang du ston pa'i yon tan gyis shes rab rnam par dag pa skyes pas rtogs pa'i gdeng rnyed /
NK109(dze)001:951: gsang bar ston pa'i gsung bdud rtsi lta bu chos nyid mngon gsum gyi gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)001:952: rig pa nyid mngon gsum du mthong bas /
NK109(dze)001:953: khams gsum du mi ldog pa 'dis thos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:954: ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi gdul bya 'di nyid la mos pa rnams kyis kyang de ltar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:955: rtogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi btsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:957: ston pa'i byin rlabs kyis de ltar rtogs pas chos
NK109(dze)001:958: nyid mngon sum gyi gnad kyis ma rig pa la
NK109(dze)001:959: sogs pa bcom / rig pa lu gu rgyud mngon sum du ldan /
NK109(dze)001:960: 'khrul ba sa chu me rlung gi snang ba las 'das /
NK109(dze)001:961: chos thams cad rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo las ma 'das par ngo shes /
NK109(dze)001:962: de lta bu'i rig pa nyid sangs rgyas kyi bdag nyid yin par yid ches /
NK109(dze)001:963: don de nyid la snga ma nas 'khrul ma myong bar thad chod /
NK109(dze)001:964: de lta bu'i sdud pa po la 'dod pa gang yang mi mnga' ba nyid yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:965: rang rig pa 'dus ma byas pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo zhes phyag btsal ba bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:966: da ni bsdus don gnyis pa rgyud 'byung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:967: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:968: ston pa rang gi 'khor 'dus pa'i yan lag tu
NK109(dze)001:969: gzhi snang gi rig pa mngon sum du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:970: dang / sdud po rang gi 'khor gyis rtogs par
NK109(dze)001:971: bya ba'i phyir thun mong gi gleng gzhi brjod bya
NK109(dze)001:972: rang gi ngo bo dang bcas te bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:973: ston pas 'khor 'du ba'i yan lag gzhi snang gi
NK109(dze)001:974: rig pa mngon sum du bstan pa la nang don
NK109(dze)001:975: gnyis las / dang po gzhung mtshan gyis mtshams sbyar
NK109(dze)001:976: bas chos nyid kyi don dgongs pa'i gnad bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:977: gnyis las / ni / de yang gang zag dad pa dang ldan pas /
NK109(dze)001:979: 'das pa'i chos nyid dang du len pa gcig gis dad pa rab dang ldan zhing /
NK109(dze)001:981: bla ma sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes su mthong ba gal che'o //
NK109(dze)001:982: de lta bu'i gang zag ni /
NK109(dze)001:984: gang zag blo'i rim pa yis /
NK109(dze)001:986: de lta bu'i 'dod pa dang ldan pa'i slob ma la /
NK109(dze)001:987: dad pa dang shes rab yod kyang /
NK109(dze)001:988: bla ma tshad med dang ldan pa /
NK109(dze)001:989: gsang ba'i rgyud la mkhas pa /
NK109(dze)001:990: thos pa che zhing khong yangs pa /
NK109(dze)001:991: mdzad spyod mi dang 'dra ba la /
NK109(dze)001:992: dgongs pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa dgongs te /
NK109(dze)001:993: de ltar kyang 'di'i le'u gsum pa nas /
NK109(dze)001:994: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba /
NK109(dze)001:996: de lta bu'i bla la lo gsum gyi sngon du dbang bskur bar zhu zhes zhu ba phul la /
NK109(dze)001:997: bla mas kyang de'i dus su /
NK109(dze)001:998: phyi spros bcas kyi dbang bskur rgyu dang bcas pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:999: nang spros med kyi dbang bskur rgyu yod pa dang med pa phyed ma dang /
NK109(dze)001:1000: gsang ba shin tu spros pa med pa'i dbang brdas bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1001: yongs su rdzogs pa rab tu spros pa med par
NK109(dze)001:1002: lus gnad dang 'dug stangs la rten nas bskur rgyu
NK109(dze)001:1003: med pa rnams / bla mas ci rigs par bskur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1005: sems la rang dbang du bskur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1006: 'di'i le'u bzhi pa nas stong gsum thams cad dal la zhes pa la sogs pas so //
NK109(dze)001:1007: de ltar skal ldan gyis gzhi ma smin pa dbang bskur nas smin par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:1008: dbang brtan pa'i don du dam tshig bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1009: yang de nyid las bsrung rgyud med pa'i dam tshig
NK109(dze)001:1010: 'da' bar 'dod pa dam tshig la zhen pas so
NK109(dze)001:1011: // de ltar dam tshig dang ldan pa de la
NK109(dze)001:1012: smin pa grol bar byed pa bla ma'i gdams ngag
NK109(dze)001:1015: de la sngon du 'gro ba la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:1016: 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pas lus ngag yid kyi spyod pa byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1017: 'khor ba ru shan phyed nas blo ldog pa'i gnas bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1018: lus ngag yid sor 'jug pa rnal du 'beb pa'i cho gas /
NK109(dze)001:1019: 'gro ba'i don rdzogs pa'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:1020: gnyis pa 'khor 'dus ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1022: sdig pa las dang rnam smin /
NK109(dze)001:1023: 'jig rten snod dang bcud kyang dang /
NK109(dze)001:1024: ces pa la sogs pas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1027: yan lag ma bskyod ye phyin pas ces pa'i tshig drug gis bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1029: da ni dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes rnal 'byor pa'i rgyud la rten pa las /
NK109(dze)001:1030: dang po lus ngag gi gnad gzir bas ye shes dngos su snang bar bya ba'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:1032: snod rnam pa gsum la brten nas mngon sum rang thog tu dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1033: de ltar mngon sum la ma gos par byas pas snang ba bzhi ji ltar 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:1034: gong ma'i gdams ngag pa la yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:1035: mtha' rten gyi man ngag dang bzhi'o //
NK109(dze)001:1036: lus ngag yid kyi gnad ni sngon du rig pa'i ye shes gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1037: rig pa'i ye shes mngon du snang par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:1038: lus kyi gnad du bzhugs stangs chos sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:1040: sprul sku'i bzhugs stangs gsum las mi 'da' bar bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:1041: dper na sbrul gyi rkang lag gcus pas mngon pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:1042: de ltar kyang 'di'i le'u brgyad pa nas //
NK109(dze)001:1043: lus kyi gnad ni rnam pa gsum /
NK109(dze)001:1044: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan /
NK109(dze)001:1045: de nas brjod du med pa'i don rgyud la rten
NK109(dze)001:1046: par bya ba'i phyir ngag gi gnad gzir nas chos
NK109(dze)001:1047: nyid brjod du med pa la gnas par bya ba
NK109(dze)001:1049: brjod cing smra bsam yul med pas /
NK109(dze)001:1051: yid kyi gnad du gtad sa'i 'ben dang mi 'bral bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1053: yid ches gsum gyis rab tu bstan /
NK109(dze)001:1055: de nas gnyis pa de ltar gnad gzir nas /
NK109(dze)001:1056: gnad rnam pa gsum la brten nas mngon gsum rang thog tu dbab pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1057: de yang 'char sgo'i gnad la brten nas sgron ma yul gyi snang ba bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:1059: sgo ni de nyid ma 'gul dang /
NK109(dze)001:1061: de ltar shar ba de yul gang la gtad pas ma gos pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1063: nam mkha' nyid kyang 'gul ba min //
NK109(dze)001:1065: de ltar nam mkha' la snang ba'i rig pa de ji lta bur snang na /
NK109(dze)001:1067: dper na gser gyi lu gu rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:1069: 'brel chags so zhes pas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1070: de ltar nyams su blangs pa la snang ba bzhi las /
NK109(dze)001:1071: chos nyid mngon gsum snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1073: de yang zab mo'i don du 'du shes zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:1074: de nas nyams gong 'phel gyi snang bas chos nyid ma bu 'brel ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1076: lu gu rgyud ni grangs mang bas //
NK109(dze)001:1077: cha shas sku ni bsam mi khyab //
NK109(dze)001:1079: de ltar goms pas rig pa nyid tshad 'phel gyi snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1083: de las ltos pa'i nyams stong pas chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1085: sgra dang dri ro mya ngan 'das /
NK109(dze)001:1087: mtha' rten gyi man ngag ni /
NK109(dze)001:1089: sgo ni de nyid ma 'gul dang /
NK109(dze)001:1091: snang ba thams cad sdod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1094: gcig dang gnyis kyi grangs zad pas //
NK109(dze)001:1095: thig le zla dang bral pa nyid /
NK109(dze)001:1097: de yang 'jug pa sgra'i yi ge la brten nas chos nyid kyi don mtshon pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1098: log pas 'khor ba las log pa'i shes rab kyis 'khor 'das gnyis dus gcig la chod pas /
NK109(dze)001:1099: mngon gsum mthong tsam la brten nas grol /
NK109(dze)001:1100: shes bya gnas lugs su gnas pas mngon gsum rang thog na gsal /
NK109(dze)001:1101: sngar gyi bden thog tu gshegs pas slar mi ldog pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1102: de yang dngos po'i gshis yin pas chos nyid mthong /
NK109(dze)001:1103: rtog pa tha dad pa bshig pas rig pa rang ngo na gnas /
NK109(dze)001:1104: chos nyid shin tu rnam par dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1106: rtogs pa'i shugs kyis 'khor ba'i mtha' chod /
NK109(dze)001:1107: gong ma'i shul du gshegs pas mngon gsum la yid dpyod kyi tshig med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1108: de lta bu'i chos nyid mngon gsum dus thams cad du rtag par bzhugs pas lha zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1109: da ni nang don gnyis pa ston pas rang gis
NK109(dze)001:1110: 'khor 'du ba'i yan lag tu gzhi snang gi rig
NK109(dze)001:1111: pa mngon gsum du bstan pa dngos ni /
NK109(dze)001:1112: 'di skad bdag gis bstan pa'i dus gcig na /
NK109(dze)001:1113: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1114: 'di zhes bya ba ni ston pa dpal kun tu
NK109(dze)001:1115: bzang pos chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK109(dze)001:1116: / gnyug ma gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin las bzhengs nas /
NK109(dze)001:1117: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dpag tu med pa thugs
NK109(dze)001:1118: kyi dal las spros te zhal 'dzum par mdzad pas
NK109(dze)001:1119: / sangs rgyas thams cad mngon par 'byung ba zhes
NK109(dze)001:1120: bya ba'i zhing khams su zhal gyi sgo nas 'od
NK109(dze)001:1121: zer dkar dmar dpag tu med pa 'phros pa las
NK109(dze)001:1122: / / chos kyi sgo mo brgya stong bye ba phrag khrig dpag tu med pa rnams 'phros te /
NK109(dze)001:1123: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnams su rab tu snang bar byas so //
NK109(dze)001:1124: de nas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i bdag nyid dpal drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen po /
NK109(dze)001:1125: snying po khyad par gyi ston pa bzhengs te /
NK109(dze)001:1126: gzhi dang snying po me tog gis rgyan pa'i zhing khams 'dir /
NK109(dze)001:1127: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ma rig pa la sogs
NK109(dze)001:1128: pa'i 'khrul pas bdag tu rtog pa dang bcas par
NK109(dze)001:1129: ma bsgom pa'i / gnas chos kyi dbyings spros pa med pa'i yul chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK109(dze)001:1130: rnam dag stug po bkod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1131: 'og min gyi gnas la sogs pa so sor shar ro //
NK109(dze)001:1132: gnas de lta bur 'dir ston pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:1133: phyi yul las 'khrul pa de ma yin la der 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1134: nang sems las 'khrul pa yid dpyod snyam byed dang /
NK109(dze)001:1135: yul sems tha dad pas 'khrul pa chos dang gang
NK109(dze)001:1136: zag gi rtog pa du ma dang gzhi gnas lugs
NK109(dze)001:1137: las 'khrul pa ma 'khrul bar gtan la 'bebs par
NK109(dze)001:1138: byed pa rnams med pa'i rdo rje 'chang /
NK109(dze)001:1139: phyi nang gi chos thams cad bdag tu med par rig pa dang gnyis su med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1142: de 'di'i dus 'khor phun sum tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:1143: de'i tshe rags pa sa rdo ri brag gi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:1144: phra ba rdul 'phra rab cha dang /
NK109(dze)001:1147: sems dang sems kyi rtog pas bsdus pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:1148: de las byung tshor gyi rtog pa yid kyi 'du
NK109(dze)001:1149: byed kyi rgyal po rgyu bdag nyid gcig gi ma
NK109(dze)001:1150: rig pas / snyam byed yul la bdag tu rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1151: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa zla sdud par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1152: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:1153: yul du ma la 'jug pas snang ba'i rigs mi
NK109(dze)001:1154: 'dra ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams su 'byed
NK109(dze)001:1155: pa'i rig pa ngo bo las ma g.yos kyang /
NK109(dze)001:1156: phyi yul la snang ba'i rtog pa bdag 'dzin du ma ltar byung ba rnams dang /
NK109(dze)001:1157: de las khyad par bdag dang bcas pa las lhun
NK109(dze)001:1158: grub rin po che'i lus sna tshogs su 'khrul pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1159: bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa las sems can
NK109(dze)001:1160: gyi sems sna tshogs su snang ba zhes bya ba'i
NK109(dze)001:1161: 'khor yod de / lhun grub rin po che'i skyon yon tan du mthong pa de dag las /
NK109(dze)001:1167: yul du snang ba'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK109(dze)001:1168: 'byung ba rlung la brten nas phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK109(dze)001:1170: lus la brten nas nang bcud kyi 'jig rten stong
NK109(dze)001:1171: gsum gyi stong chen po grangs med dpag tu med
NK109(dze)001:1173: de dag rnams la sangs rgyas kyi gsung yan lag drug dang ldan pa'i skad kyis bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:1174: kye ma 'di ltar rang shes rig gi rgyal po rang snang ba'i 'khor /
NK109(dze)001:1175: brtags pa 'khrul pa'i bdag nyid chen po shar pa rnams nyon cig zhes bos /
NK109(dze)001:1176: de'i tshe ston pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:1177: de ltar 'khrul pa'i snang ba de dag chos nyid ka nas dag pa /
NK109(dze)001:1178: dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba /
NK109(dze)001:1179: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams su rig pa nyid gzhi
NK109(dze)001:1180: la bzlog pa'i thabs thun mong ma yin pa bla
NK109(dze)001:1181: ma'i gdams ngag la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:1182: mchog gi dngos grub thob par byed pa rdo rje 'chang bdag nyid ces /
NK109(dze)001:1183: 'khrul pa yul tha dad du shar ba'i ngos nas ngas bstan gyis /
NK109(dze)001:1184: zhes pa 'di nyid kyi dal du zhugs pa rnams /
NK109(dze)001:1185: khams gsum du mi ldog pa'i thabs gsang ba'i rgyud
NK109(dze)001:1186: kyi rgyal po 'di bstan gyis gdul bya ma 'ongs
NK109(dze)001:1191: sems gdung ba dang gsum gyis nyon cig /
NK109(dze)001:1193: de'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams de nyid du
NK109(dze)001:1194: 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams khams gsum las grol ba'i snying
NK109(dze)001:1195: po can zhes bya ba'i chos la bzod pa thob
NK109(dze)001:1196: bo // de yang dus phun sum tshogs pa ji tsam na zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:1198: thams cad du 'byung pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:1199: chos thams cad bdag tu med pa rtogs pa'i dus 'khrul pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1200: ma 'khrul par 'dzin pa med pa'i sngon rol ka
NK109(dze)001:1201: dag gzhi rig pa las 'di ltar lus med pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1202: rig pa gang du yang ma phye ba'i dus /
NK109(dze)001:1203: de nyid las gzhan du brjod du med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1205: ston pas rang gi 'khor 'du ba'i yan lag tu
NK109(dze)001:1206: gzhi snang gi rig pa mngon gsum du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:1207: bstan nas / da ni gnyis pa sdud pa pos rang gi 'khor gyis rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:1208: thun mong gi gleng gzhi brjod bya rang gi ngo bo dang bcas te bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1209: nang don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po thun mong gi gleng gzhi dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1210: de nas zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1211: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ston pas gsungs pas /
NK109(dze)001:1212: de nas sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po lag
NK109(dze)001:1213: na rdo rje yis rig pa mngon sum gyi don
NK109(dze)001:1215: rang gi chos skye ba med pa'i don rtogs /
NK109(dze)001:1217: gzhan don du sems can gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i don go /
NK109(dze)001:1218: sdud pa pos khong du chud nas kho rang gi
NK109(dze)001:1219: 'khor gyi nang du 'di skad bdag gis thos pa
NK109(dze)001:1220: dus gcig na / zhes smras so //
NK109(dze)001:1222: sdud pa po rang gi 'khor la rtog pa tha dad par skyes te /
NK109(dze)001:1223: la la ni 'di zhes gang yin snyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1224: la la ni skad ji lta bu zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1225: la la ni bdag ces pa su yin snyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1226: la la ni thos pas ni gang su zhig la thos snyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1227: dus ni ji tsam na thos snyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1228: grangs ni gcig ma yin pa gzhan ma yin nam
NK109(dze)001:1229: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i rtog pa tha dad
NK109(dze)001:1231: sdud pa pos 'khor gyi rtog pa rnams thugs su shar nas 'di zhes bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1232: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1233: dngos po gshis kyi gnas cha yis ma ba sgos pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1234: thugs tsi ta gnyis yin zhes pas /
NK109(dze)001:1236: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sangs rgyas thams cad
NK109(dze)001:1237: kyi mnga' bdag dpal rdo rje 'chang chen po yin
NK109(dze)001:1238: no / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1239: ngo bo'i 'khor rig pa rdo rje rnon po la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1240: nang snang ba'i 'khor dkar ba la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1241: phyi yul gyi 'khor de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs pa la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1242: de'i snang ba'i 'khor yul la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1243: khyad par chos kyi 'khor byang chub sems dpa' la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1244: 'jig rten gzugs snang gi lha dang zhes pa lags pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1245: gi zhes 'brel pa mtshon pa'i tshig tu byung ba'i //
NK109(dze)001:1246: de ltar gtso 'khor ldan pa la bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1247: ston pa nyid kyi lha tshangs pa'i skad kyis 'khor
NK109(dze)001:1248: rnams la nye ring med par gsal zhing yangs par
NK109(dze)001:1250: de yang gsang sngags kyi bstan pa thabs /
NK109(dze)001:1251: gcol bas ni thabs zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1255: bstan pa bzhi dus 'dzom pas dus zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1256: de khyad par du bstan pa gsang pa'i rgyud 'di
NK109(dze)001:1257: gcig pu la 'tshogs shing 'dus pas gcig na zhes
NK109(dze)001:1258: pas / gzhan gnyis la sogs pa'i sgro 'dogs chod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1259: de yang sdud pa po rtogs pa che bas dus gcig tu gsang pa'i rgyud gzhan kyang thos la /
NK109(dze)001:1260: de yang thos lugs rna ba'i dbang po phyin ci
NK109(dze)001:1261: ma log pas sgro skur dang bral bar thos pa'o
NK109(dze)001:1262: // de yang thos pa rgya che bas chos kyi rnam grangs dpag tu med pa thos /
NK109(dze)001:1264: de yang cha yis zhes pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1265: ma 'khrul pa'i rig pa nyid ka dag tu gnas pas gnas zhes yin la /
NK109(dze)001:1266: de nyid gang sus kyang ma bsgom pas phun sum tshogs pa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:1267: snang ba so sor rang dag pa'i gzhal zhes tshad med /
NK109(dze)001:1268: de yang rtog pa tha dad pa'i 'di nyid mthong nas sems mtha' yas su khyer na /
NK109(dze)001:1270: khang zhes pa phyi dang nang med pa /
NK109(dze)001:1271: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa steng 'og phyogs mtshams so so na gsal ba /
NK109(dze)001:1272: rang bzhin rnam par dag pas na dam pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1273: de nas dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK109(dze)001:1274: shes bya rang gi mtshan nyid /
NK109(dze)001:1275: sangs rgyas dang sems can gang gis kyang bcas bcos med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1276: de yang sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen pa ye shes dang sbyar na thugs /
NK109(dze)001:1277: gdul bya gang zag gi rgyud dang sbyar na 'gro ba so so rang rang gi rtsi tog dkyol /
NK109(dze)001:1278: rtsa thams cad 'dus pa rtsa rnams kyi nang na gnas /
NK109(dze)001:1283: thig le rgyu bas na 'khor zhes bya la /
NK109(dze)001:1284: na ni 'gro ba'i lus la smos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1285: gnyis pa dkon mchog gsum gyi don mdor bstan pa rang gi ngo bo'i 'khor bstan pa na /
NK109(dze)001:1286: de'i nang na rig pa ni shes rig gis khyab pa /
NK109(dze)001:1288: rnon po ni snang ba gcod pa'i shes pa /
NK109(dze)001:1289: sku ni snang zhing rang gzhan med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1290: yang rig pa ni rang gi ngo bo /
NK109(dze)001:1291: rdo rje ni 'dus ma byas pa /
NK109(dze)001:1292: lu gu rgyud ni 'brel pa chags shing rgyun du gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1294: rang snang ni rang gzhan gyi snang ba yid kyi rtog pa ma zhugs pa /
NK109(dze)001:1295: gi sku dang zhes pa ni 'brel zhing dag pa'i chos /
NK109(dze)001:1296: rig pa ni bsgom pa yul gyi gnad /
NK109(dze)001:1297: cog bzhag gi ni rlung bdag rang sar dengs pas 'gyu ba rgyun chad pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:1298: sku ni spros pa dang bral pa /
NK109(dze)001:1299: rig pa ni yul kun la snang ba /
NK109(dze)001:1300: theg pa med pa'i zhes pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1301: yul shes gnyis med du gcod pa /
NK109(dze)001:1302: sku dang ni rang bzhin rnam dag gi gzugs su gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1303: rig pa ni gcer grol du byung pa /
NK109(dze)001:1304: cir snang gi ni snang ba nyid snang thog tu grol ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:1305: sku dang ni rang bzhin bstan pa /
NK109(dze)001:1306: rig pa drug po de dag thad kyang rig pa
NK109(dze)001:1307: ka nas dag pa la 'khrul pa yod ma myong
NK109(dze)001:1308: pas ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum sku gsum
NK109(dze)001:1309: / dbyer med pa las ma g.yos te /
NK109(dze)001:1310: de yang ngo bo ka dag pa'i ye shes lhun
NK109(dze)001:1311: grub gyi yon tan rdzogs tshul du byung bas gzhi
NK109(dze)001:1312: las byung ba'i 'khor zhes bya la /
NK109(dze)001:1313: bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni brjod du med pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)001:1314: zhes nang don gnyis pa dkon mchog gsum gyi don
NK109(dze)001:1315: mdor bstan pa rang gi ngo bo'i 'khor bstan nas
NK109(dze)001:1316: / da ni nang don gsum pa de'i rang bzhin gyi 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1317: dkar ba dang zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1318: de yang dkar ba dang ni rig pa dri ma gang yang med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1319: dmar ba dang ni rig pa la ma brtsal rdzogs pa'i ye shes lnga lhug par 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1320: ser ba dang ni rig pa la yon tan rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1321: ljang khu ni rig pa nyid la phrin las thogs pa med par 'byung ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:1322: mthing ka ni rig nyid mi 'gyur pa la sogs
NK109(dze)001:1323: te ni kha dog nyer lnga la sogs pa rig
NK109(dze)001:1327: 'di dag kyang rig pa las byung pas 'khor du 'gro bas na /
NK109(dze)001:1328: sems can gyi bsam pas bcam na mi khyab pa dang thabs gcig tu ba zhugs so //
NK109(dze)001:1329: zhes pa de'i rang bzhin gyi 'khor bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1330: da ni don bzhi pas phyi yul gyi 'khor ni 'di lta ste /
NK109(dze)001:1331: zhes pa la sogs pa gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:1332: 'di dag ni nyid las ma zhan pa'i 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1334: da ni nang don lnga pa 'dzin byed 'khrul pa'i 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1335: rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo las 'jig rten pa
NK109(dze)001:1336: ltar byung pa mdor bstan pa ste 'og nas rgyas
NK109(dze)001:1337: par ston no // de yang ma rig gsum po
NK109(dze)001:1338: ni ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes lags pa
NK109(dze)001:1340: ma dag pa'i sems sems pa sna tshogs su 'gyu ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1342: yid drug ni rigs drug las byung /
NK109(dze)001:1343: nyon mongs pa lnga ni ye shes lnga las byung /
NK109(dze)001:1344: phyi yul la 'dzin pa rnams ni /
NK109(dze)001:1345: rig pa'i snang ba las byung /
NK109(dze)001:1346: nang sems su rtog pa rnams ni bsam gtan las byung /
NK109(dze)001:1347: mi dge ba bcu rnams ni ma dag pa'i bsam pa las byung /
NK109(dze)001:1349: rig pa nyid 'jig rten pa ltar kyang snang bas na /
NK109(dze)001:1350: gong ltar yang spyad kyang me tog skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1351: zhes pa lnga pa 'dzin byed 'khrul pa'i 'khor bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1352: da ni rang don drug pa de'i snang ba'i 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1353: de'i snang ba'i 'khor ni 'di ltar zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:1354: de dag gi 'og gi dbang po la sogs pa'i mdor bstan /
NK109(dze)001:1355: yul ni snod kyi 'jig rten rigs las 'byung ngo 'og nas ston /
NK109(dze)001:1356: shes pa dang ni bcud kyi sems can /
NK109(dze)001:1357: dran nas dang ni yid drug gi 'dzin pa /
NK109(dze)001:1358: mthong byed dang ni mig gis gzugs mthong /
NK109(dze)001:1359: nyan byed rna bas sgra thos /
NK109(dze)001:1362: gzugs dang snang stong dbyer med /
NK109(dze)001:1364: dri dang zhen pa rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:1365: rang dang thob pa bde ba nyid du grol /
NK109(dze)001:1367: thugs rje gzhi snang du grol /
NK109(dze)001:1368: chos la sogs pa dang ni /
NK109(dze)001:1369: 'byed med yul dag tu grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1370: zhes drug pa de'i snang ba'i 'khor bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1371: da ni bdun pa khyad par chos kyi 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1372: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ni /
NK109(dze)001:1373: 'og gi rig pa dang ye shes dkon mchog gsum gyi don mdor bstan du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1374: 'jig pa ni lta ba ngan pa rnams gsang ba'i rgyud 'dis 'jig tshogs su lta ba dang ni /
NK109(dze)001:1375: phyi rol rtag chad du lta ba rnams rig pa'i rgyan du shar ba 'og nas ston /
NK109(dze)001:1377: chos dang gang zag rang grol du shes pa nyid las byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:1378: rang rgyal ba'i dge 'dun rten 'brel rang dwangs su grol /
NK109(dze)001:1380: don dam kun rdzob gcer grol du rtogs /
NK109(dze)001:1381: nyan thos la sogs pa 'di dag ni grub mtha'
NK109(dze)001:1382: 'dod rgyal ba ltar na blo brteg gis shes so
NK109(dze)001:1383: // kri ya la sogs pa'i gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:1384: zhes bdun pa khyad par gyi 'khor bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1385: da ni nang don brgyad pa 'jig rten gzugs snang gi 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1386: lha dang zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1387: de yang ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la /
NK109(dze)001:1388: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'khor sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpag tu med pas bskor /
NK109(dze)001:1389: de dag gi rig pa'i ye shes rigs drug ltar byung ba'i mdor bstan du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1390: de yang lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang /
NK109(dze)001:1391: lha ma yin gyi rgyal po thag bzang ris dang /
NK109(dze)001:1392: de la sogs pa mi'i gtso bo sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1393: byol song gi seng ge rab bstan dang /
NK109(dze)001:1394: yi dwags kyi kha 'bar ma dang /
NK109(dze)001:1395: dmyal ba'i chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK109(dze)001:1396: dri za'i rgyal po zur phud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1397: nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po gser mig can dang /
NK109(dze)001:1398: mi'am ci'i rgyal po ljon pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1399: tshangs pa la sogs pa 'khor brgya stong bye ba
NK109(dze)001:1400: phrag khrig dpag tu med pa rnams kyis yongs su
NK109(dze)001:1401: bskor ba'o // de yang 'das pa dang 'jig rten pa rnams dang thabs gcig tu ni /
NK109(dze)001:1402: chos thams cad kyi 'dun pa rab tu gsal ba zhes bya ba la ro gcig par bzhugs so //
NK109(dze)001:1404: zhes mu tig 'phreng ba'i rgyud gsang ba ni mtshan gyi skabs su bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1406: gleng pa ni gang glengs na gsang ba'i rgyud gzhung tshig dang yi ger bcad pa gleng la /
NK109(dze)001:1407: su dang gleng na sdud pa po lag na rdo
NK109(dze)001:1408: rje la sogs pa'i 'khor dpag tu med pa dang
NK109(dze)001:1410: tshul lam thabs ji ltar gleng na /
NK109(dze)001:1411: tshig don 'brel pa bya ngang ma'i mthun ltar gleng /
NK109(dze)001:1412: de ltar gleng pa la dgongs pa ci yod na
NK109(dze)001:1413: 'di nyid la mos pa'i 'gro ba rnams khams gsum
NK109(dze)001:1414: du mi ldog pa'i dgongs pa yod //
