NK109(dze)001:1416: mtshan la brten nas gzhung 'byung pas na gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:1417: 'di la brten nas rgyud le'u brgyad kyi bdag nyid du byung bas na gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1418: le'u ni gzhung gi tshig don nges pa'i dum bu nges par ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1419: dang po ni sngun ma'am gong ma zhes pa ste
NK109(dze)001:1420: grangs kyi gzhi mtshon par byed pa gcig zhes pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1421: tshig go / le'u dang po'i mu tig 'phreng ba brgyus pa ltar bstan pa rdzogs so ///
NK109(dze)001:1423: // thatha sra swah da ni le'u gnyis pa 'khrul pa
NK109(dze)001:1424: gzhi la lhag pa'i le'u mu tig gsal bar phye
NK109(dze)001:1425: na / le'u 'di la bsdus pa'i don bzhis bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1426: dang po zhu ba sngon du 'gro ba ye shes rang gi ngo bo bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1427: gnyis pa la 'khrul ba'i ldog tshul bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1428: gsum pa de ltar log pa'i ye shes ngos bzung bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1429: bzhi pa de nyid la bzla ba bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1430: bsdus pa'i don dang po zhu ba sngon du 'gro
NK109(dze)001:1431: ba ye shes rang gi ngo bo bstan pa la
NK109(dze)001:1432: nang don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:1433: zhu ba sna gtad kyi bskul bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1434: de nas bcom ldan 'das zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1435: de nas ni le'u dang po bshad pa'i 'og tu'o //
NK109(dze)001:1436: 'khrul pa la ma 'khrul bar ngo 'dzin pa'i log rtog bcom /
NK109(dze)001:1438: skyon sna tshogs pa dang ldan pas 'khrul pa'i gzhi byas /
NK109(dze)001:1439: ka dag brjod gzhi las 'das kyang /
NK109(dze)001:1440: lhun grub yon tan las skyon 'khrul pa ni rig pa nyid ma 'khrul ba zhes 'dod pa las /
NK109(dze)001:1441: de nyid rang 'khrul bar song pas /
NK109(dze)001:1442: 'khor 'das thams cad pa'i mnga' bdag tu med byung bas te /
NK109(dze)001:1443: de la gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:1444: rnal 'byor gyi lam du byung la /
NK109(dze)001:1445: gdul bya'i dbang du byas nas 'bras bu zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:1446: gdul byas las dag pa rnams kyi ston par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1447: gsang ba'i bdag po la sogs pa ni sdud pa po'i ming gis zhus pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:1449: zhes ngo bo'i sgo nas bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:1451: gzugs med pa la sogs pa khams gsum gyi sems
NK109(dze)001:1452: can 'di dag rnams zhes ji ltar 'khrul pa ldog
NK109(dze)001:1453: na ji ltar pa lags zhes bris pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1454: bdag cag gsang ba'i bdag po la sogs pa rnams la ston pas bka' stsol cig /
NK109(dze)001:1455: ces dang po zhu bar sna gtad cing bskul ba bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1456: da ni gnyis pa lan du gnas lugs la 'khrul pa glo bur du byung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1457: de nas bcom ldan 'das zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1458: zhus pa'i de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' des /
NK109(dze)001:1459: 'khor dpag tu med pa'i nang nas nye ba rigs
NK109(dze)001:1460: gsum gyi mkha' 'gro de las kyang nye ba'i 'khor
NK109(dze)001:1461: / lag na rdo rje la bka' stsal pa /
NK109(dze)001:1462: bstsal lugs ji ltar stsal zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:1463: 'o ma las mar byung ba bzhin du bsdu ba'i don du stsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:1464: nges pa'i snying po yin pas kye ma zhes bya /
NK109(dze)001:1465: rna ba'i dbang po'i sgo sol la nyon cig gzhan la /
NK109(dze)001:1466: gsang ba'i bdag po khyod yin pas ngas bstan zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1467: dang po ni rtogs sangs rgyas zhes bya bar yang med la /
NK109(dze)001:1468: ma rtogs sems can du yang med pa'i ngo bo ka nas dag pas 'khrul pa'i ming med /
NK109(dze)001:1469: rang bzhin la lhun gyi grub pas 'khrul ma myong
NK109(dze)001:1470: zhes bya bar yang grub pa med pa'i gzhi de
NK109(dze)001:1471: la / gnas pa yin pas 'pho ba med brjod bya tsam du med pas /
NK109(dze)001:1472: smra bsam gyi yul du ma gyur /
NK109(dze)001:1473: kun gyi byung ba yin pas sna tshogs su snang la /
NK109(dze)001:1474: 'di 'dra zhes gang du yang ma grub pas gtan la dbab bya'i yul du ma gyur pas /
NK109(dze)001:1475: 'khrul pa med kyang dper na nyi ma'i ngo bo la sprin pas gos pa med kyang /
NK109(dze)001:1476: glo bur du sgrib pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:1477: sems can gyi blo'i rnam par rtog pa rtsal du yang 'khrul pa 'dra byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:1478: yang dag par 'khrul ba dang ma 'khrul gang du yang grub pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:1479: zhes gnyis pa lan du gnas lugs la 'khrul ba glo bur du byung bar bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1480: de ni nang don gsum pa bla ma'i gdam ngag gis 'khrul pa bzlog par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1481: de yang la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1482: de yang snang ba thams cad rang snang yin pa'i gnad kyis 'khrul pa rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:1483: grol pa thams cad rang grol yin pa'i gnad kyis ma 'khrul pa yang rang dag pa'i /
NK109(dze)001:1484: rig pa ye shes kyi gdam ngag mngon gsum gnad kyi rtsi dam pa'i gdams pas /
NK109(dze)001:1485: don ma bu phrad pa ltar thebs pa ni chang dang ra ro ba 'dra gyur na /
NK109(dze)001:1486: rig pa nyid ye nas 'khrul ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)001:1487: da lta 'khrul pa la mi gnas /
NK109(dze)001:1488: da lta ma gnas pas phyis 'khrul mi srid pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:1489: dang po'i gzhi ka dag la bzlog pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1490: nam mkha' la nam mkha' thim pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:1491: zhes gsungs pa bla ma'i gdam ngag gis 'khrul pa ldog par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1492: da ni don bzhi pa de ji ltar rtogs pa dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1493: rang rig la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1494: rang ni gnas pa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:1495: gnas pa'i don de rig pas de las ye shes zhes bya /
NK109(dze)001:1496: de nyid blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas rtogs par dka' ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:1497: de nyid gzhi yin pas kun gyi 'gro ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:1499: rig pa nyid bcud du 'brel bas /
NK109(dze)001:1501: sgron ma bzhi rang la 'char bas ye tog ste /
NK109(dze)001:1502: kun gyi mi gnas 'char ba can zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1503: de nyid rang gi ngo bo la 'khrul pa ltar byung yang /
NK109(dze)001:1504: chos nyid mngon gsum gyi gnad la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:1505: gdar sha rang grol gang yang ma spangs par gcad pa'i thabs /
NK109(dze)001:1506: lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:1507: ma gos stobs kyis khams gsum las grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1508: zhes pa de ji ltar rtogs pa dngos bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1509: da ni nang don lnga pa de rtogs par byed
NK109(dze)001:1510: pa'i thabs la goms par bya ba bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:1511: ma rig ces pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:1512: de yang ma rig pa gsum ye shes gsum du rang dag la song bas /
NK109(dze)001:1513: ye shes rang ngo na gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:1514: 'khor ba zhes khams gsum gyii chos rang grol du ngos su brdas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1515: de gang las byung zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:1516: rig pa mngon gsum lu gu rgyud dbyings la gtad de rtag tu ltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1517: rang rig rang grol du song bas /
NK109(dze)001:1519: mngon gsum gyi rang gnad kyis thebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:1520: gcer gyis ltas tshad chos nyid kyi snang ba sna tshogs su rang grol ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:1521: gang shar rig pa'i klong 'gags pa med par rang shar /
NK109(dze)001:1522: gtad med phyogs med du grol ba nyid rlung 'khor 'das gnyis skyal ba la chos nyid zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1523: de yang gang gis 'grub zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:1524: rang gi rigs ni ngo bo ka nas dag pa dang po'i snga so ma bcos pa /
NK109(dze)001:1525: phyis so ma bsgyur bar bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1526: ma rig pa dang rig pa gnyis rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:1527: chos nyid mngon gsum rtsad nas gcod pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:1529: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes gsum gyi snang ba sgron
NK109(dze)001:1530: ma bzhir rang gi mig nas 'char ba yin pas
NK109(dze)001:1531: de ltar rab chos nyid mngon gsum pa zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:1532: // de nyid yid dpyod ma yin pas ye nas dag ste /
NK109(dze)001:1533: 'khrul pa'i rtog pa chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba
NK109(dze)001:1534: la thog ma'i gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs las log
NK109(dze)001:1536: lam du ni nyid kyi bar ma do la mtshan
NK109(dze)001:1537: nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga'i snang ba ru rig
NK109(dze)001:1539: 'bring po bar ma do la sangs rgyas pa'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:1540: zhes lnga pa rtogs par byed pa'i thabs la goms par bya ba bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1541: da ni drug pa de nyid kyi dgag bya bkag
NK109(dze)001:1542: pas ye shes rang gi ngo bo gsal bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:1543: pa ni sems ni zhes pas bstan te sems kyi
NK109(dze)001:1544: khang bu gtibs pas gzhi stong pa'i man ngag dang
NK109(dze)001:1545: / rtsad bcad pas byung ba ngo shes pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:1546: ro myong pas mtshan nyid gtan phebs pa'i man ngag gis /
NK109(dze)001:1547: sems dang ye shes dbye ba ye shes kyi klong du 'gro ba'i man ngag ni /
NK109(dze)001:1549: yang ma rig pa'i byung ba brtsal ba'i man ngag gis 'khrul pa gzhi la ldog /
NK109(dze)001:1550: byung sa lugs ldog pas rang ngo la gtan la phebs /
NK109(dze)001:1551: phugs ded pas snang ba rang dag ste lu gu rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:1552: 'dab 'byor du skye ba'i man ngag kyang blo brdeg gi gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:1553: sgo lnga ni sgron ma la gtad pa'i gnad kyis
NK109(dze)001:1554: mthong ba yul gyi rgyun bcad pa'i man ngag dang
NK109(dze)001:1555: / rna ba'i sgo rlung gi rang sgra la gtad pas 'gyu ba rgyun chad pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:1556: sna'i sgo 'gyu tshad ye shes kyi rlung gi grangs bzung bas /
NK109(dze)001:1557: las rlung rtog pa'i rgyun 'gags pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:1558: lce'i sgyur byed yi ge'i sgra don gyis bsgyur bas /
NK109(dze)001:1559: 'byung ba dus kyi nad 'pho ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:1560: lus kyi sgo gnas ba rtsa'i gnad stems pas bde chen gyii lus rgyas pa'i man ngag gis /
NK109(dze)001:1561: rtog pa las kyi rlung rgyun bcad de ye shes su gsal bar 'gyur ba na /
NK109(dze)001:1562: blo brdeg gi gnad dang sbyar ro //
NK109(dze)001:1563: rig pa 'char bar byed pa'i mthong /
NK109(dze)001:1564: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu gar phye bas /
NK109(dze)001:1566: rig pa gsal ba gnyis dbyer med du gyur nas /
NK109(dze)001:1567: ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang bar 'gyur ba'i man ngag kyang blo brdeg gis gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:1568: de dag gi gnad la brten nas 'khrul ba'i snang ba yul phyung bas /
NK109(dze)001:1569: ka dag pa'i rig pa rang las 'das pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:1570: de ltar skyes pas glo bur bas drin sad pa'i yid rang dwangs su song bas /
NK109(dze)001:1573: chos sku'i ngang las 'gro sa med do //
NK109(dze)001:1574: de nyid kyi nyams rgyud la skyes pas 'khor ba'i rtog pa thams cad spyi bas phyung ste /
NK109(dze)001:1575: 'khor ba nyid ma grub par shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:1576: de nyid rang rdzogs su bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1579: sems chos sku gsum du gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:1580: zhes drug pa de nyid kyi dgag bya bkag pas ye shes rang gi ngo bo bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1581: da ni bdun pa de nyid kyang 'bad rtsol med par rang log grol bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1582: stong pa ni gzhi rtsa ba med pa'i ye shes /
NK109(dze)001:1583: de yang dngos po las log pas rang rgyud du ma song /
NK109(dze)001:1584: de la bdag dang rang rig can du med pas
NK109(dze)001:1585: 'od lnga'i gsal bas mdzes par byas pa ni stong
NK109(dze)001:1587: dug lnga zhes bya ba ni 'gro ba rnams 'ching bar byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:1588: 'di la gnad chen po gnyis kyis sbyor du bya ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:1589: dug lnga sman du bsgyur bas ye shes rang sar grol ba'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:1590: rnam rtog ye shes su bsgyur pas 'gyu ba rang sar grol ba'i gnad gnyis kyis /
NK109(dze)001:1591: 'bras bu gcig char du thob pas /
NK109(dze)001:1592: mig gnyis kyi mdor sgron ma nyid phyung pas dug nyid sman gyi ngang du grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:1593: khams gsum dus gcig tu sprugs pas blo rdeg gsang ba'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1594: mun pa ni 'khor ba de'i rgyu ni ma rig
NK109(dze)001:1595: pa de zad par byed pa la 'khor 'das bsres
NK109(dze)001:1596: par byed pa / sems kyi khong bu gzhig pa'i gnad kyis sgron ma nyid /
NK109(dze)001:1597: dngos su snang bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1599: med pa'i don snang ba dang bcas pa /
NK109(dze)001:1600: de'i rgyu ni ma rig pa las bag chags kyis bsdus pa /
NK109(dze)001:1601: de yang ye nas rgyu med du rtogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1602: snang ba yul gyi gnad kyis chos zad pas /
NK109(dze)001:1603: mthong snang ye shes kyi grogs su 'char ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:1604: de ltar shar bas gsal ba 'od lngas khyab bas /
NK109(dze)001:1605: phyi rol gyi snang ba longs sku khro bo 'bar ba'i cha lugs can /
NK109(dze)001:1606: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i ngang du so so ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:1607: tha mi dad pa nyid du 'gyur ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1608: bem po sa chu me rlung lags pa gzugs kyis sdud pa rnams /
NK109(dze)001:1609: phyi yul gyi gnad la brten na sa rang sar grol ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:1610: rig pa ni shes bya nang gi snang ba la rten nas /
NK109(dze)001:1611: gnyis med du khong du sangs pas /
NK109(dze)001:1613: de yang 'khrul ba rang dag pa'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1614: don gyi ye shes ni lu gu rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:1615: gzhi ni gsang ba'i rig pa rang dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1617: zhes bdun pa de dag kyang 'bad rtsol med par rang log par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1618: da ni brgyad pa de dag gi 'jug bsdu ba
NK109(dze)001:1619: don dam kun rdzob las 'das par bsdu ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1620: pa ni / don dam pa'i chos nyid spros bral sgra blo las 'das par bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1621: de yang snang brtags gcig tu bsre ba stong pa
NK109(dze)001:1622: 'bad med kyi gnad kyis 'khor 'das lto bzlog pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1624: kun rdzob sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:1625: tshogs drug rang sar log pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1626: de gnyis su med pa chos nyid las bcos su med pa las byu ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1627: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don dang po
NK109(dze)001:1628: zhu ba sngon du 'gro ba ye shes rang gi
NK109(dze)001:1629: ngo bo bstan pa la brgyad du byas nas bstan
NK109(dze)001:1630: to // da ni bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:1631: pa'i ldog tshul bstan pa las nang don drug gis
NK109(dze)001:1632: bstan pa'i dang po rgyu rkyen med pa'i ye shes
NK109(dze)001:1633: to // bstan pa ni / e ma ni de
NK109(dze)001:1634: ltar gnad kyi gdams pa ste de dag la brten
NK109(dze)001:1635: to // bstan pa ni / nas / khams gsum dus gcig la grol ba ngo mtshar che'o //
NK109(dze)001:1637: pad+ma rigs kyi gsung rnam par dag pa las byung
NK109(dze)001:1638: ba'i khro bo rta'i mgrin pa yod pa 'khor ba
NK109(dze)001:1639: las rgyal ba chen po khyod nyon cig tses bos
NK109(dze)001:1640: nas / sems ni bsam pa du ma'i 'khrul 'khor /
NK109(dze)001:1641: gnas ni kun gzhi zhabs med pa de nyid bsam
NK109(dze)001:1642: pas ma rnyed pa'i ye shes kun snang la brten
NK109(dze)001:1643: nas grol ba'i // de la gzhi gnas kyi ye
NK109(dze)001:1644: shes ni yin no zhes sngon byung du rta mgrin
NK109(dze)001:1645: la gdams la rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas
NK109(dze)001:1646: nas grol ba'i // slob ma la'o // phyi rkyen gyi snang ba ni blo yis ma bsgyur /
NK109(dze)001:1648: shes pa rang ngo na bzhag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1649: de yang phyi snang bas ma bcos pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1650: yul med gcig char du grol ba zhes bya'o /
NK109(dze)001:1651: zhes nang don dang po rgyu rkyen med pa'i ye shes bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1652: da ni gnyis pa rig pa'i ngo bo yid dang
NK109(dze)001:1653: bral bas 'khrul pa'i ldog pa ngos bzung ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1655: rgyu ma rig pa gsum la rkyen dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1656: ma dag pa'i yul sna tshogs /
NK109(dze)001:1658: ngo bo ka dag pa'i gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:1659: rig pa rang dag tu bstan pas lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)001:1660: btson du bzung ba'i gnad kyis 'khrul pa thams cad
NK109(dze)001:1662: dran pa ni glo bur gyi rtog pa sna tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:1664: rig pa nyid mkha' la ston pas /
NK109(dze)001:1665: yid kyi byung tshor 'gag pas yid med pa ste
NK109(dze)001:1666: nang ye shes kyi yul gyi dbyings nyams kyi snang
NK109(dze)001:1667: ba / 'khor sku dang ye shes su 'char ba de nyid du rig pa tshad la phebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:1668: 'dzin pa tha dad pa'i rnam par rtog pa las
NK109(dze)001:1669: grol bas rang gi rgyud rig pa nyid du gsal
NK109(dze)001:1670: bas rdzogs pa chen po bya bral klong chen gyi
NK109(dze)001:1671: lta ba ye shes pa thog na gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1672: de la yid dran pa'i snang ba ji snyed pa /
NK109(dze)001:1673: de la bdag tu bzung pas 'khrul pa chen po'i
NK109(dze)001:1674: rang rgyud 'ching ba'i rgyu yin pas snang ba rang
NK109(dze)001:1675: sar bzhag pas chos nyid zad pa dang dus mnyam
NK109(dze)001:1676: pa'o // zhes gnyis pa rig pa'i ngo bo yod
NK109(dze)001:1677: pa dang bral bas 'khrul pa'i rtog pa ngos bzung
NK109(dze)001:1678: pa'o // ba bstan nas / da ni gsum pa
NK109(dze)001:1679: 'khrul pa de nyid rtog pa yul gang la log
NK109(dze)001:1681: dran pa ni mig gi phyed btsum la sogs pa bya byed dang bral ba /
NK109(dze)001:1682: sangs pa'i ni de nyid dang bral te rab sor nyam ka la bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1684: de yang 'khrul pa'i de nyid lta stangs gsum la brten nas bzlog par bya'o /
NK109(dze)001:1685: zhes gsum pa 'khrul pa de nyid yul gang la zlog pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1686: da ni bzhi pa yul la snang ba de nyid
NK109(dze)001:1687: la 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul ngos bzung ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1688: pa ni / phyi rol du chos nyid yul gyi snang ba rang grol shar nas /
NK109(dze)001:1689: dran bsam rang rig tu gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:1690: dngos po ji snyed pa thams cad sems snang sna tshogs snang ba dngos po rang dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1691: rig pa nyid ma bcos pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1692: de nyid du ma shes na snang ba 'khrul pa
NK109(dze)001:1693: de ma yin la der 'dzin pa'i rgyu lta sgom
NK109(dze)001:1695: ma rig pa'i rgyu ye shes lnga la bdag tu 'dzin pa yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:1696: thams cad rang snang rang grol du shes pa ni gnad yin no //
NK109(dze)001:1697: zhes bzhi pa yul la snang ba de nyid las
NK109(dze)001:1698: 'khrul ba dang ma 'khrul ba ngos bzung ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1699: nas / da ni lnga pa 'khrul pa nyid mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1700: bsam pa ni rlung rnam par 'phros pas sems kyi 'gyu ba /
NK109(dze)001:1703: da lta'i rnams slong bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1704: de dag med pa'i rang rig pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1705: don gyi mig gis gzigs stangs de nyid /
NK109(dze)001:1706: chos sku'i gzigs stangs su gyen la bzlog par byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1707: khams gsum 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:1708: zhes lnga pa 'khrul pa nyid mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin du bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1709: da ni nang don drug pa 'khrul ba nyid ma 'khrul ye shes su bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1710: lu gu zhes spel legs pa'i snang ba la rgyud kyi ni sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin /
NK109(dze)001:1711: snang ba la ni chos nyid mngon gsum la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:1712: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1713: de yang yul nam mkha' la rig pa stong pa su bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:1714: de'i tshe yid 'gyu ba'i rlung dang bral te /
NK109(dze)001:1715: 'dzin pa yul la brten pa'i rtogs par gzhan gyi spros pa ji snyed pa /
NK109(dze)001:1716: dga' ba la mngon par zhen pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1717: mi dga' ba la mngon par zhen pa de nyid 'khrul pa'i bdag tu 'dzin pa yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:1718: de yang 'di ltar snang ba la 'jal byed kyi shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:1719: de rtogs par byed pa'i rang gi ngo bo 'jal byed kyi tshad mas brtags pas /
NK109(dze)001:1720: shes rab kyi bdag nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang du gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:1721: phyi nang gnyis kyi shes pa rang dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1722: phyi nang gnyis ka la brtags te don rang gi
NK109(dze)001:1723: rig pa nyid la lta ba ma log na las
NK109(dze)001:1725: zhes drug pa 'khrul pa nyid ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes su bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1726: da ni bdun pa 'khor 'das gnyis kyi rtsa ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1729: de gnyis kun kyi rtsa ba na 'khor ba'i rtsa ba dran pa'i yid /
NK109(dze)001:1730: 'das pa'i rig pa yul dag pa la snang ba gnyis las ma 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1731: zhes de dag gis ni spyi don gnyis pa 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:1732: pa'i ldog tshul bstan pa la bdun du byas nas
NK109(dze)001:1733: bstan to // da ni spyi don gsum pa de
NK109(dze)001:1734: ltar log pa'i ye shes ngos bzung ba la nang
NK109(dze)001:1735: don bcus bstan pa'i dang po dbyings rig 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)001:1736: med pa'i don las ma yengs par lta ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1737: bstan to // pa ni / kye ma nyon cig
NK109(dze)001:1738: gshin rje'i rgyal po ni sku'i rigs kyi khro bo
NK109(dze)001:1739: sdud pa po khyod la bstan par bya zhes pa'o
NK109(dze)001:1740: bstan to // pa ni / // rang rig pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1741: ye shes 'od lnga rang gdal dang bcas pa so
NK109(dze)001:1743: de nyid la rang gis rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:1744: gong na med pas rgyal po ka nas dag pas ngo bo nyid ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1746: lu gu rgyud ngo bo sku /
NK109(dze)001:1747: de la goms pas rig pa tshad la phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1748: de las yul rig gi gnad /
NK109(dze)001:1749: yengs pa med pas nyams su len pa las ma 'da' ba /
NK109(dze)001:1752: rtags pa ni nyams rgyud la rten pa chen po
NK109(dze)001:1753: ni yar 'phel ba la bstan par bya ba nyid
NK109(dze)001:1754: do zhes nang don dang po dbyings rig 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)001:1755: med pa'i don la ma yengs par lta ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1756: nas / da ni gnyis pa dran pa snang byed
NK109(dze)001:1757: kyi blo rig pa'i ngang du grol bar bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:1758: nas / ni / dran byed ni yid rang byung
NK109(dze)001:1759: gi ye shes su bsgyur ba'i man ngag gis 'khor
NK109(dze)001:1761: blo la snang ba ni tshogs drug rang bzhag gi
NK109(dze)001:1762: man ngag dang sbyar ba rnams ni rig pa'i ngang
NK109(dze)001:1763: du grol bas / 'khor 'das ming med pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:1764: de yang gang las byung na rig pa'i rgyal po /
NK109(dze)001:1765: lu gu rgyud dang ma bral na /
NK109(dze)001:1766: de'i sku'i snang ba grangs med pa snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:1767: gzigs stangs gsum gyis ltos zhes gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1768: de la rtag tu ltas pas de mi 'gyur ba
NK109(dze)001:1769: ni rdo rje lu gu rgyud rang rig pa 'gyur
NK109(dze)001:1770: ba med pa de las ye shes lnga'i snang ba
NK109(dze)001:1773: sku lnga'i rang ngo rkyang pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1776: tshom bu'i snang ba mi 'gyur bas rig par grol ba'i rtags so /
NK109(dze)001:1777: de yang ye nas rang la gsal bas spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid zhes bya la /
NK109(dze)001:1778: phyi'i yul na ka la 'phyo bas dbyings rig zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1779: zhes gnyis pa snang ba dran byed kyi blo rig pa'i ngang du grol bar bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1780: da ni gsum pa de stong pa nyid spros pa
NK109(dze)001:1781: dang bral bar bstan pa ni chos nyid ni lu
NK109(dze)001:1782: gu rgyud / stong pa ni dngos po las log pa /
NK109(dze)001:1783: rang don ni de las ma g.yos pa gnas pa ni sems bstan pa /
NK109(dze)001:1784: stong pa nyid kyi ni dngos po las 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1785: ye shes dbang po dang spyod yul du byung ba'o
NK109(dze)001:1786: // de yang rig pa'i ngo bo ni 'gyur yang
NK109(dze)001:1787: de las cha shas kyi sku'i snang ba bsam gyis
NK109(dze)001:1788: mi khyab pa rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i dus
NK109(dze)001:1789: // na snang ba'o // de ltar nang ba'i chos de la ye nas skye ba med pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1790: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1791: zhes gsum pa de la yang stong pa nyid spros pa dang bral bar bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1792: da ni bzhi ba dran pa med pa'i ye shes chos las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1793: de yang chos sku skye ba med pa las gzugs can ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1794: longs sku la skye ba med par 'gro 'ong du ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1795: sprul sku la skye ba med pas dus thams cad pa ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1796: gsum gyis chos nyid skye ba med pa zhes bya bar gtan la dbab tu btub bo //
NK109(dze)001:1797: bsam pa ni sems kyi rtog pa las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:1798: yul dngos po la bdag tu mi 'dzin pas /
NK109(dze)001:1799: rig pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud phyi sku ltar
NK109(dze)001:1800: snang zhing nang du 'od lnga ltar 'byung pas 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:1801: pa'i snang ba zad par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1802: de'i rang bzhin chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1803: yid dang ye nas bral ba dran byed du med /
NK109(dze)001:1804: sems las 'das pas bsam pa'i chos rtogs pa tha dad pa las 'das so //
NK109(dze)001:1805: zhes bzhi pa dran pa med pa'i ye shes chos las 'das par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:1806: da ni nang don lnga pa chos nyid skye med
NK109(dze)001:1807: kyis rnam par rtog pa'i mdud pa las grol bar
NK109(dze)001:1808: bstan pa ni / chos nyid spros pa dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)001:1809: dbyings ni phyi nang gnyis med kyi nyams de yang
NK109(dze)001:1810: de nyid las ma g.yos shing rgya ma chad par
NK109(dze)001:1811: rang byung pas / yid kyi rtog pa gzhan du ma yengs pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1813: rtog med kyi ngang gis rang gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1814: bdag dang bcas pa'i mdud pa rang ka ma rang bzhag pas grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:1816: lus ngag gi bya byed rgyun chad pas /
NK109(dze)001:1818: 'khrul pa'i ye shes snang ba rtags chos nyid du shar ba de /
NK109(dze)001:1819: chos nyid kyi bar do chos nyid ma'i snang pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1822: zhes lnga pa chos nyid skye ba med pas rnam
NK109(dze)001:1823: par rtog pa'i mdud pa las grol bar bstan nas
NK109(dze)001:1824: / da ni nang don drug pa bar snang la
NK109(dze)001:1825: rang byung gi ye shes 'du 'bral med par shar
NK109(dze)001:1827: de'i tshe rang byung gi ye shes bdag med pas gzung 'dzin las 'das so //
NK109(dze)001:1828: de'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud rang grol du shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:1829: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung zad pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1831: da ni nang don bdun pa de nyid kyi snang ba rang bzhin med par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1832: de ltar shar ba de la gces spras kyi 'dzin
NK109(dze)001:1833: pa med na rang gi snang ba rnam par dag
NK109(dze)001:1834: pa ni / bzung bas ma zin te snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK109(dze)001:1835: chu nang gi zla ba dang 'dra ba nyid du snang ba kun 'char ro /
NK109(dze)001:1837: da ni nang don brgyad pa shes rab kyi rtsal
NK109(dze)001:1838: gyis de'i don rtsol bsgrub dang bral bar bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:1839: ni / thogs pa med pa ni phyi nang gnyis la rtsod rtogs pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:1840: rang grol ni shes rab kyi rtsal che chung gi bye brag go /
NK109(dze)001:1841: de yang dper na khyung chen gshogs pa rgyas pa
NK109(dze)001:1842: nam mkhar ngam grog dang g.yang sa thams cad bcad
NK109(dze)001:1843: nas lding pa bzhin du gshogs pa'i rtsol bsgrub med
NK109(dze)001:1844: pa ltar / rang sems spro ba dang bsdu ba
NK109(dze)001:1845: byas par rang sar bzhag pas grol ba rdzogs pa
NK109(dze)001:1846: chen po'i gnad chen po'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1848: da ni nang don dgu pa de'i don yul la
NK109(dze)001:1849: snang yang dran pa las 'das par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:1850: / de yang rig pa nyid kyi ngo bo bzung
NK109(dze)001:1851: bar dka' yang ye shes kyi rtsal dal bas 'grub
NK109(dze)001:1852: / ste / mngon gsum mthong ba'i gnad kyis de
NK109(dze)001:1853: la tshig gi spro ba med pa yin mnyam gyi
NK109(dze)001:1854: / ste / mtha' chod / yul las bsdu ba med pas min mnyam gyi mtha' chod /
NK109(dze)001:1855: de nyid shugs kyi ngang du grol bas yin min gang yang mtha' la ma gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1856: lu gu rgyud du snang ba de ka chos sku'i
NK109(dze)001:1857: rang gi snang ba ni phyi rol gyi yul thad
NK109(dze)001:1858: kar rtsal du snang ba las /
NK109(dze)001:1859: ma rtogs pa gang yang med do //
NK109(dze)001:1860: de'i phyir na dngos po las grol ba'i rig pa dran byed yid las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1861: zhes nang don dgu pa bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1862: da ni nang don bcu pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba de ye nas med par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1863: phyi rol mtshan mar song pa la bdag 'dzin blo'i rtog pa thams cad kun /
NK109(dze)001:1864: ye nas skye ba med par shes pas rig pa nyid chos sku rang grol du thos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1865: zhes de dag gis ni spyi don gsum pa de
NK109(dze)001:1866: ltar log pa'i ye shes ngos bzung pa la bcur
NK109(dze)001:1868: da ni spyi don bzhi pa de nyid la bzla
NK109(dze)001:1869: ba na don lngas bstan pa'i dang po snod kyi
NK109(dze)001:1870: 'jig rten la rig pa'i ngo bo snang bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:1871: pa ni / e ma zhes rang la rang ngo mtshar ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:1872: rig pa'i ye shes de kun la khyab kyang /
NK109(dze)001:1873: bla ma'i lung med pa la snang ba med pas na /
NK109(dze)001:1874: phyi rol sa chu me rlung bem po'i snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:1875: rang byung gi ye shes mi bsgrib ste /
NK109(dze)001:1876: brtan g.yo kun la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1878: da ni nang don gnyis pa stong pa phyam chad kyi lta ba las grol bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1879: dngos po las log pas stong pa'i chos nyid blo'i
NK109(dze)001:1880: spyod yul du med pas de la blos bsgom mi
NK109(dze)001:1881: dgos pas / tshig gi stong pa nyid la rang
NK109(dze)001:1882: gsal dang bcas pa'i rig pa mi gnas so zhes
NK109(dze)001:1884: da ni nang don gsum pa sems kyi dran byed de nyid blo las 'das pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1885: sgo lnga'i yul mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i dngos po /
NK109(dze)001:1886: rang dag pas mig gzugs la 'dzin pa la sogs
NK109(dze)001:1887: pa'i chos la nga 'dzin med rang grol ba nyid
NK109(dze)001:1888: mi gnas so // zhes nang don gsum pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:1889: da ni nang don bzhi pa tshig dang yi ge'i chos las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1890: rig pa'i ye shes de shes rab kyi spyod yul
NK109(dze)001:1891: ma yin pas thos bsam las 'das pa'i shes rab
NK109(dze)001:1892: / mngon sum chen po rang las byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:1893: de nyid tshig dang yi ge las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:1894: bka' sde snod rnam pa gsum gyi chos la nga
NK109(dze)001:1895: rtogs pa rang byung gi ye shes mi gnas so
NK109(dze)001:1897: da ni nang don lnga pa de nyid kyi ngo
NK109(dze)001:1898: bo la dge sdig las 'das pa bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:1899: / thugs rje kun khyab tu snang ba'i nga ye
NK109(dze)001:1900: nas grol ba'i chos nyid la las dge bas skyabs
NK109(dze)001:1901: / su med la / sdig pas gos su med pas na /
NK109(dze)001:1902: dge sdig gnyis ka rnam par sel zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:1903: de'i phyir na 'khor ba snang shes kyi chos la
NK109(dze)001:1904: nga rig pa ye sangs rgyas pa nyid mi gnas
NK109(dze)001:1905: so // zhes de dag gis ni bsdus don tha ma la lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:1906: le'u gzhung de la bsdus pa'i don bzhi pa la nang don sum cur byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1907: zhes mu la sogs pas mtshan gyi skabs su bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1908: le'u ni gzhung gi don du ma bu nges pa /
NK109(dze)001:1909: gnyis pa ni gcig las gzhan du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1910: le'u gnyis pa'i mu tig gsal bar phye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:1914: na/&&& da ni le'u gsum pa'i mu tig gsal bar dbye ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:1915: le'u gsum pa 'khrul pa des su bsdus pa'i le'u la bsdus pa'i don lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:1916: bsdus pa'i don dang po de dag gi zhu ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK109(dze)001:1917: 'khrul pa nyid kyi rang bzhin bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1918: gnyis pa snang ba'i de nyid ma 'khrul bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:1919: gsum pa 'khrul pa'i de nyid kyi don rtogs na
NK109(dze)001:1920: thams cad rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs yin pa
NK109(dze)001:1922: bzhi pa de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas snang
NK109(dze)001:1923: ba thams cad la gnas lugs kyis rgyas thebs par
NK109(dze)001:1924: bstan pa dang / lnga pa de'i phyir rgyud kyi
NK109(dze)001:1925: rgyal po 'di bla ma'i gdams ngag dang 'brel bar
NK109(dze)001:1926: bstan pa dang / bstan pa'o // bsdus pa'i don
NK109(dze)001:1927: dang po la nang don bzhi pa bstan pa'i dang
NK109(dze)001:1928: bstan pa dang / bstan pa'o // po / gsang
NK109(dze)001:1929: sngags kyi sri zhu khyad par can gyis rig pa'i
NK109(dze)001:1930: lung gis rig pa ji ltar ma 'khrul bar zhus
NK109(dze)001:1932: de nas ni de gnyis las so //
NK109(dze)001:1933: khro bo ni gdul dka' ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1934: rta mgrin ni rkang thang gi tshogs 'dul ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1935: 'di ni tshig skad ni gdung pa'i sgo nas /
NK109(dze)001:1938: kye kye zhes zhu bar snang gtad cing bskul ba ste gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:1940: da ni nang don gnyis pa lan du sngags kyi
NK109(dze)001:1941: sgra dang bcas pa 'a khrul pa'i rang bzhin de
NK109(dze)001:1942: chos kyi sku dang dbyer med par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:1943: / zhus pa'i de nas ston pa rdo rje 'chang
NK109(dze)001:1944: chen po des ma zhugs pa ni bzhengs pa mi
NK109(dze)001:1945: mnga' ba gdan las ni langs te /
NK109(dze)001:1947: zhes chos thams cad stong pa nyid kyi ngang du 'du ba zhes bya ba'i sgra brjod nas /
NK109(dze)001:1948: gnas de nyid du 'dus pa'i tshogs la bka' stsal pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:1949: bsdu ba'i don du brtsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:1950: chos thams cad rig pa la 'dus pa'o zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:1951: kye kye nyon cig dad pas 'dus pa'i 'khor 'jig
NK109(dze)001:1952: rten pa dang 'das pa rnams la nyan par rna
NK109(dze)001:1954: bstan pa gzhan las khyad par du rgyud 'di che bas /
NK109(dze)001:1955: mun pa las snang ba ston par byed pa'i sgron ma 'bar ba'i 'od dang 'dra ba 'di /
NK109(dze)001:1956: rgyud kyi don chos kyi sku'i dgongs pa dang dbyer
NK109(dze)001:1957: med pas na dam pa nyid du zungs shig ces
NK109(dze)001:1958: gdams pa'o // nang don gnyis pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1959: da ni nang don gsum pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba
NK109(dze)001:1960: 'di dag rang gzhan gyi snang ba ngo bo nyid
NK109(dze)001:1962: rnal 'byor pas lam du rang rig pa phyi'i yul nam mkha' stong pa la gtad /
NK109(dze)001:1963: de nyid kyi spyod lam nirgyuna tu rtenapa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1964: thabs bla ma'i gdams ngag sku de la rgyun du
NK109(dze)001:1965: gnas pa las mi 'gyur ba de ltar byas pa
NK109(dze)001:1966: las shes par rtogs tshad thun mong ma yin pa
NK109(dze)001:1967: rgyud la skye'o // de skyes pas dbyings dag pa 'gag pa med par shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:1968: byas bcos ci dang ci byas pa thams cad /
NK109(dze)001:1969: chos nyid kyi rol par 'char ro //
NK109(dze)001:1970: de'i ngang la gnas pas blo dman pa la gsang
NK109(dze)001:1971: ba'i ye shes de rang la 'gyur ba med pas
NK109(dze)001:1972: las / rang bzhin gyi snang so 'di ltar grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:1973: dbang po la ma 'gag par gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:1974: de yang ngo bo ka dag nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:1975: sku gsum ltar rang gi mi gnas 'aphro'o //
NK109(dze)001:1976: rtsol bsgrub kyi mtha' bcad pa /
NK109(dze)001:1977: bya ba lus byed pa sems gnyis las rab tu 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:1978: stong pa nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid kyi yul la gzigs stangs gsum gyis bltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:1979: snang ba bzhi'i don mkhyen pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:1980: de'i thugs rje'i go ma 'gags par shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:1981: rtags byang chub sems kyi sgron ma'i ye shes ni
NK109(dze)001:1982: 'od kyi thig ler rang gi mig nas gsal lo
NK109(dze)001:1984: da ni nang don bzhi ba de dag gi don
NK109(dze)001:1985: 'jug bsdu ba sgron ma nyid kyi snang ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:1986: pa ni / de dag thams cad kyang rig pa
NK109(dze)001:1987: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku la chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:1988: rnam par dag pa gsal ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:1989: sgron ma dbyings rnam par dag pa nyid kyi snang
NK109(dze)001:1990: ba ni dbyings rig pa 'du 'bral med pa yin
NK109(dze)001:1991: pas / de la rtag tu ma gos par byas pas khams gsum du ldog mi srid do //
NK109(dze)001:1992: de dag gi bsdus pa'i don dang po la bzhir byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:1993: da ni bsdus don gnyis pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba de nyid ma 'khrul bar bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)001:1994: nang don bzhis bstan pa'i dang po 'khrul snang de
NK109(dze)001:1995: nyid sangs rgyas kyi snang ba dang khyad med du
NK109(dze)001:1996: bstan pa ni / de nas ni 'khrul snang yul
NK109(dze)001:1997: la snang bas snang ba de'i gong dag pa dang
NK109(dze)001:1998: ma dag pa gnyis su 'byed pas /
NK109(dze)001:1999: snang tshad tsam cig yin pa ni rig pa'i snang
NK109(dze)001:2000: ba tha dad pa'i spros pa dang bral bas gang
NK109(dze)001:2001: yang min no // gsang ba'i phyir rtogs par dka'/
NK109(dze)001:2002: lta ba'i don gyi spyi'i rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:2003: 'gro ba rnams la stab pas mos pa'i snying la byin rlabs 'jug par byed pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)001:2006: da ni gnyis pa don dam kun rdzob kyi snang
NK109(dze)001:2007: ba de la sku lhar snang zhing rig pa gcig
NK109(dze)001:2009: gzhal bya las 'das pas don rig pa dam pa gdam ngag ye shes mkhyen pa'i cha /
NK109(dze)001:2010: lnga grangs te me long lta bu la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:2011: snang ba kha dog de yang brtags pa tsam du
NK109(dze)001:2013: rdzob sgrib par byed pa ye shes ma spangs par gnas su dag pa /
NK109(dze)001:2014: sna tshogs ming gi bye brag de yang lu gu
NK109(dze)001:2015: rgyud ar la gtad pas de nyid sku lhar snang
NK109(dze)001:2016: zhing ngo bo rig par don dam kun rdzob dbyer
NK109(dze)001:2017: med du 'adu'o // zhes nang don gnyis pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2018: da ni nang don gsum pa 'byung ba las grol
NK109(dze)001:2019: ba'i rig pa yul la sngon du snang ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:2020: pa ni / 'phra rag la sogs pa'i tshig drug gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2021: da ni nang don bzhi pa bla ma'i man ngag
NK109(dze)001:2022: gis thams cad brjod du med pa'i sa la phyin
NK109(dze)001:2024: man ngag rin po che ni sngon du 'gro ba rnam pa drug gis gzhi sbyang pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2025: dngos gzhi bzhis gnad du gzud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2026: de yang mig gi ngo bo ma chod pas /
NK109(dze)001:2028: man ngag 'dir rab tu zab par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2029: de ltar byas pas phyi nang du rgyu ba'i rlung byang /
NK109(dze)001:2030: rig pa skur chub pa'i sa /
NK109(dze)001:2031: sku gsum dbyer med pa las /
NK109(dze)001:2032: pha rol na chos nyid zad pas zhes bya ba la phyin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2034: de'i don brjod du med pas tshig gis gtan la mi phebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2035: yul la mngon gsum du yod pa'i phyir skur snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2036: zhes de dag gis ni le'u gsum pa'i bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa la gzhir byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:2037: da ni le'u gsum pa'i bsdus pa'i don gsum pa
NK109(dze)001:2038: 'khrul pa'i de nyid rtogs na rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK109(dze)001:2039: gnas lugs yin par bstan pa la nang don bcu
NK109(dze)001:2040: gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:2041: 'khor 'das gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2042: kye kye gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:2043: 'khor ba'i chos snang ba snang thog tu grol bas snang du shes /
NK109(dze)001:2044: shes pa 'gyus thog tu grol ba'i don rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2045: 'gyu ba rang dag tu shes pas na /
NK109(dze)001:2046: 'khor ba nyid rang sar grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:2048: zhes bya ba yod pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:2050: da ni nang don gnyis pa dug lnga dang ye shes gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2051: nyon lus la mongs sems te /
NK109(dze)001:2052: de ltar lus sems 'ching ba dug lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:2053: 'dod chags 'dod chags kyis grol bas spang la me
NK109(dze)001:2054: mched pa lta bu zhe sdang de nyid kyis grol
NK109(dze)001:2055: bas chu ngogs su rdo bor ba lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2056: gti mug de nyid kyis grol ba mun pa'i smag sangs pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2057: nga rgyal de nyid kyis grol ba rgyas po'i gnya' las bkrol ba lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2058: phrag dog de nyid kyi grol ba ri gsum gyi rtser phyin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:2059: de ltar rtogs na ye shes lnga rang grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2060: de ltar rtogs pas mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga dang /
NK109(dze)001:2061: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes ming du yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:2063: da ni nang don gsum pa bde sdug gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2066: de gnyis la bde ba skye bar byed pa'i rgyud sdug bsngal yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2067: don rang snang cog bzhag tu rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2068: de nyid rang bde bar grol bas rdzogs pa chen
NK109(dze)001:2069: po'i gnad yin pas gzhan nas brtsal du med do
NK109(dze)001:2071: da ni nang don bzhi pa skyon yon gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2072: skyon gyi mtha' med na yon tan brtsal du mi snyegs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2073: de chos nyid du shes pas na /
NK109(dze)001:2074: de la gtang bzhag med par rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2075: skyon nyid rang gis rang grol ba'i phyir yon tan chen po brtsal mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)001:2077: da ni lnga pa 'khrul ba dang ma 'khrul ba gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2078: 'khrul ba nyid kyi don rig pa ye nas 'khrul ma myong par shes na /
NK109(dze)001:2079: de nyid rang thog tu grol bas 'khrul pa med pa'i rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:2080: zhes gzhan nas brtsal mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)001:2082: da ni drug pa 'byung ba'i dwangs snyigs gnyis med bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2083: 'byung ba sa'i mtshan nyid bstan zhing bskyed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2085: chu brlan zhi nga sdud pa //
NK109(dze)001:2087: nam mkha' yang zhing skabs 'byed pa lnga nyid kyi don sa sra ba med pa'i brtan pa /
NK109(dze)001:2088: chu gsher pa med pa'i khyab pa /
NK109(dze)001:2089: me tsha ba med pa'i smin pa /
NK109(dze)001:2090: rlung yang ba med pa'i 'degs pa /
NK109(dze)001:2091: nam mkha' yang pa med par gsal bar rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2092: sa chen po las ser po /
NK109(dze)001:2093: chu chen po la dkar po /
NK109(dze)001:2096: nam mkha'i las mthing ga ste /
NK109(dze)001:2097: 'od lnga nyid du dwangs ma ye nas babs kyi shes bya la grub bo //
NK109(dze)001:2099: da ni nang don bdun pa ma rig pa gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2100: ma rig pa nyid kyi rtsal 'khor ba rang dag tu chod na /
NK109(dze)001:2101: rig pa'i sku nyidade las gzhan du brtsal du med pas /
NK109(dze)001:2104: da ni nang don brgyad pa sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2105: sems can nyid kyi don ye sangs rgyas par shes na /
NK109(dze)001:2106: sangs rgyas pas de nyid kyang gang nas kyang ma brtsal bar rang la rnyed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2108: da ni nang don dgu pa snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:2109: 'od gnyis gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2110: 'di ltar sna tshogs snang ba'i don dbang po la sogs pa rang grol du rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2111: rang rig pa'i rang bzhin dag pa'i 'od snang /
NK109(dze)001:2112: gzhan nas ma brtsal pa rang rnyed do //
NK109(dze)001:2114: de ni nang don bcu pa rtog pa dang mi rtog pa gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2115: rtog pa nyid kyi rjes 'dzin med rang dag tu chod na /
NK109(dze)001:2116: 'khrul pa'i bdag tu 'dzin pa zad pas de nyid rang grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2118: da ni nang don bcu gcig stong gsal gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2119: stong pa snang ba'i don dngos med zang thal du rtogs na /
NK109(dze)001:2120: ye shes kyi sku snang gsal zhing mi 'gyur ba'i ngos nas lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2122: da ni nang don bcu gnyis pa snang stong gnyis
NK109(dze)001:2123: med du bstan pa ni de dngos por snang ba'i
NK109(dze)001:2124: phugs stong pa rang grol du mthong na /
NK109(dze)001:2125: med pa stong pa nyid kyang ma sgrub par rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2127: da ni nang don bcu gsum pa de dag kyang
NK109(dze)001:2128: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don can du bstan
NK109(dze)001:2129: pa ni / chos nyid a'i don skye med rang grol du rtags na /
NK109(dze)001:2130: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid rig pa 'chi med
NK109(dze)001:2131: du rang grol bas don bzhi pa de ltar don
NK109(dze)001:2132: rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor bas snang ba thams cad la
NK109(dze)001:2133: gnas lugs kyi rgyas thebs par bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)001:2134: nang don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po dbyings dang /
NK109(dze)001:2135: rig pa'i yul du gyur bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2136: e ma ho ni snang ba ye shes kya rgyas btab pas ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2137: rang snang stong pa nyid kyi rgya ni /
NK109(dze)001:2139: stong 'byams ye shes sku'i rgya ni gsal stong dbyer med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2140: sna tshogs mtshan nyid rigs pa'i rgya ni bde stong dbyer med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2141: rnam dag gling yangs pa'i rgya ni /
NK109(dze)001:2143: mtshan ma dngos dag rig pa'i rgya ni dran pa la rig pa'i rgyas btab pas /
NK109(dze)001:2145: snang ba rang rdzogs dbyings kyi rgya ni 'byung snang
NK109(dze)001:2146: la dbyings kyi rgyas btab pas dbyings 'khor mar gsal
NK109(dze)001:2148: zhes bsdus don bzhi pa'i nang don bzhi pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2149: da ni nang don gnyis pa lta sgom sbyod pa
NK109(dze)001:2150: 'bras bu'i don gyis snang ba rang sar dag pa
NK109(dze)001:2151: rgyas thebs par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2152: spyod pa rmad byung rol pa'i rgya snang la dbang bsgyur /
NK109(dze)001:2153: bsgoms pa rmad 'byung pa nyin mtshan kha sbyar bas
NK109(dze)001:2154: sems la rgyas thebs pas khams gsum du mi ldog
NK109(dze)001:2155: lta ba rmad du byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:2156: mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun bcad pas /
NK109(dze)001:2157: rig pa dang nam mkhar 'brel pa'i rgyu 'bras bu
NK109(dze)001:2158: nyid kyang rgyur mi ldog pas rmad du byung ste
NK109(dze)001:2159: / brtson 'grus rab zag bcas mi snang /
NK109(dze)001:2160: 'bring bar ma do la tha ma tshe gcig la chag chad med du'o //
NK109(dze)001:2162: da ni nang don gsum pa dbyings rig pa 'du 'bral med par rgyas btab par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2164: rmad du byung bas stong pa zang thal du rtogs pas 'khor ba la rgyas thebs so //
NK109(dze)001:2165: gzhi ma bcos par rang snang bas chos nyid rmad du byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:2166: rol pas thams cad rang grol du rgyas btab pas /
NK109(dze)001:2167: ye shes rang na gsal lo /
NK109(dze)001:2168: rang rig lta ba'i gdengs kyis brtags pa rmad du byung ba ni rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:2169: shes rab kyis stong gsal ngo mnyam du rgyas thebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2170: de dag gi ngo bo rmad du byung rig pa
NK109(dze)001:2171: lu gu rgyud chad med par rang snang bas phyi
NK109(dze)001:2172: 'khrul pa'i yul la rgyas thebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2173: de ltar yang dag rig pa la dri ma med pas /
NK109(dze)001:2174: dbyings rig gang du yang ma phye pa'i rgya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2175: zhes de dag gis ni le'u gsum pa'i bsdus pa'i
NK109(dze)001:2176: don bzhi pa la gsum du byas nas bstan to
NK109(dze)001:2177: // da ni bsdus pa'i don lnga pa de'i phyir
NK109(dze)001:2178: rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di bla ma'i gdams ngag dang
NK109(dze)001:2180: nang don drug gis bstan pa'i dang po bla ma'i
NK109(dze)001:2181: gdams ngag snod khyad par dang ldan pa la gsum
NK109(dze)001:2183: lta ba gnyis med kyi don bstan gyis e ma
NK109(dze)001:2184: ho gsang ba'i bdag po chen po khyod nyon cig
NK109(dze)001:2185: ces gdam nas / de yang bskal pa dang ldan pa cig gis /
NK109(dze)001:2186: phyi spros bcas kyi dbang dang /
NK109(dze)001:2187: nang spros med kyi dbang dang /
NK109(dze)001:2188: gsang ba shin tu spros pa med pa'i dbang /
NK109(dze)001:2189: 'og nas 'byung ba ltar rdzogs par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:2190: de nas rab tu spros pa med pa'i dbang rdzogs par byas te /
NK109(dze)001:2191: de'i nye rgyur dam tshig la brten par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2192: de nas smin pa grol bar byed pa la /
NK109(dze)001:2193: snying po ni thabs khyad par can dril ba /
NK109(dze)001:2194: bcud ni sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:2195: dngos gzhi la brten nas 'khor ba'i g.yang sa bcad pa /
NK109(dze)001:2196: gdams pa snying gi snying la gnag pa /
NK109(dze)001:2197: ngag bla ma'i zhal nas byung pa 'di la rtag tu gnas na /
NK109(dze)001:2198: rig pa'i bcud snying po ste /
NK109(dze)001:2199: de nyid la nyams su blangs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2200: snying po snod khyad par can la bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:2201: 'bras bu la tshogs pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2203: da ni nang don gnyis pa de ltar bla ma'i
NK109(dze)001:2204: thabs la brten nas rgyud 'di'i mtha' 'di yin par
NK109(dze)001:2205: bstan pa ni / nges pa'i bcud /
NK109(dze)001:2206: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gsum dang 'brel bas /
NK109(dze)001:2207: 'bras bu khams gsum du ldog mi srid do //
NK109(dze)001:2208: rgyud gyi rtsol ba mthar thug pa ni 'di nyid yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2209: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na yang 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:2211: da ni nang don gsum pa de'i don go ba'i
NK109(dze)001:2212: dus na snang ba thams cad gnyis med du bstan
NK109(dze)001:2213: pa ni / don dam kun rdzob gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:2214: bden pa gcig pa dbyer med du rtogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2217: da ni nang don bzhi pa de ltar rtogs shing
NK109(dze)001:2218: go bas 'khrul pa ka nas dag par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:2219: ni / de yang gcig las 'das pas grangs zad /
NK109(dze)001:2221: gcig tsam du yang ma grub /
NK109(dze)001:2222: de ltar gcig dang du ma dang bral bas tha dad pa ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2223: de nyid rang thog tu grol bas gnyen po gzhan
NK109(dze)001:2224: la rag ma lus par rtogs pa'i dus na gnyis
NK109(dze)001:2225: su med pas gcig tu yang ma yin la /
NK109(dze)001:2226: gcig tu mi gnas pas gnyis su yang ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:2227: gsang ba snod med pa la /
NK109(dze)001:2229: thabs kyis rgyu'i theg pa rnams las khyad par 'phags te /
NK109(dze)001:2230: de'i tshad 'di yin bya bar bzung bar mi shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2231: de dang gnyis med du go ba'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:2232: thabs nyams gnyis su med pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2233: de yang sems can gyi snang bas 'khrul pa'i yul la sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK109(dze)001:2234: de nyid thabs kyis grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:2235: snang ba snang thog du grol ba'i gnad de yang don dam pa nyid la gcig las med de /
NK109(dze)001:2236: gal te kun rdzob dang gnyis su byung na /
NK109(dze)001:2237: gcig la brten pa'i grangs las 'das te /
NK109(dze)001:2238: zad pa med zhes nang don bzhi pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2239: da ni nang don lnga pa sna tshogs su snang yang de go na gcig du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2240: de'i phyir na snang ba gcer bzhag tu bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2242: nang 'dzin pa'i sems kyis ma bcad yul sems gcig med kyang /
NK109(dze)001:2243: de nyid shes pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:2244: thams cad rang gi 'bor grol ba'i nyams sna tshogs rang sar 'byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:2245: sna tshogs de nyid la zhen pa rang grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:2246: ma rig pa nyid ma rig pas grol ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:2247: de'i phyir chos nyid thams cad gnyis med du go bas /
NK109(dze)001:2248: gnyis med de'i ngang la dus thams cad du gnas na /
NK109(dze)001:2251: da ni nang don drug pa de ltar 'khrul pa
NK109(dze)001:2252: dag pas zhing khams 'di nyid la 'char bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:2253: pa ni / 'khrul snang gi yul snang shes tha dad pa rang log du rtsad chod na /
NK109(dze)001:2254: de nyid rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2255: de ltar gnyis su med na /
NK109(dze)001:2256: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa lhun gyis grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2257: zhes pa la sogs pa mtshan skabs su bstan /
NK109(dze)001:2258: le'u'i gzhung de la bsdus don lngar byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:2259: le'u'i mtshan 'khrul pa de ni ma yin la der 'dzin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2260: ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes la sbyor /
NK109(dze)001:2261: brda ba ni gzhung tshig dang yi ge la brten
NK109(dze)001:2262: nas 'khrul pa rang grol ba'i le'u la bsdus pa'i
NK109(dze)001:2263: don lnga la nang don yan lag gi don sum
NK109(dze)001:2265: zhes pa ni tshig don gsal ba bstan pa'o zhes le'u gsum pa'i mu tig gsal bar phye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2268: // grabadangi nya&atashah&a&a&a da ni 'bad pa med par rang grol
NK109(dze)001:2269: du bstan pa'i le'u mu tig gsal bar phye na
NK109(dze)001:2270: / le'u 'di la bsdus pa'i don dgu ste /
NK109(dze)001:2271: dang po chos nyid kyi rgyan du thams cad 'dus
NK109(dze)001:2272: par bstan pa la nang don lngas bstan pa'i dang
NK109(dze)001:2273: po / de dag gi grol lugs ji ltar yin zhus pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2274: de yang chos nyid kyi rgyan bstan pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:2275: de nas la sogs pa'i tshig lnga gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2276: da ni nang don gnyis pa lan bka' stsal pas ye shes dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2277: bcom ldan 'das la sogs pa'i tshig dgu gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2278: da ni nang don gsum pa rig pa skye med kyi snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2279: de yang rig pa nyid thog ma skye ma myong
NK109(dze)001:2280: bas da lta skye ba med pa snang ba ni
NK109(dze)001:2281: / skye bya blo'i rim pas rgyu med pas /
NK109(dze)001:2282: skye byed yul rkyen tha dad pa med /
NK109(dze)001:2283: de ltar rgyu rkyen gnas las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:2284: rig pa nyid dngos gang du yang ma grub pas /
NK109(dze)001:2287: shes rig ma bcos pas rig pa'i ngang 'khor 'das dus gcig la grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2288: rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid de la nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa zad pas /
NK109(dze)001:2289: 'bu tha'i thugs rjes kyang bcos su med do //
NK109(dze)001:2290: de dag thams cad bag chags las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:2291: gnyen po gzhan gyis kyang bar gcod du med do //
NK109(dze)001:2293: da ni nang don bzhi pa spros pa dang bral
NK109(dze)001:2294: ba'i dbyings su thig le dang lu gu rgyud kyis
NK109(dze)001:2296: chos nyid kyi thig le ni dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma'i rgyan bzang po 'od dang /
NK109(dze)001:2298: de las thig le'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:2299: gzhi thig le dbyings rang gi mdzod spu na gnas /
NK109(dze)001:2300: lam gyi ni sor bzhis ma reg 'bras bu'i ni dbyings kyi go ra las 'das mod /
NK109(dze)001:2301: bzang po'i thig le ni mthing ga mi 'gyur ba'i spros las mi 'da'/
NK109(dze)001:2302: bzang po'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i de las kha dog lngar gsal /
NK109(dze)001:2303: bzang po'i rtse mo'i thig le ni ljang gu bya
NK109(dze)001:2304: stsal dang bral ba'i mtha' skor ba thig le bdun
NK109(dze)001:2305: gyis rnam par sprel ba las /
NK109(dze)001:2307: de ltar thig le bdun 'dus pa'i dbyings rnam par
NK109(dze)001:2308: dag pa'i nang du sku gsum gyi ngo bo lu
NK109(dze)001:2309: gu rgyud / rgyun ma chad par gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:2310: 'bad pa med pa'i sangs rgyas gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:2311: de la brtson 'grus can gyis nyams su blangs na
NK109(dze)001:2312: ye shes kyi snang ba kha dog gi snang ba
NK109(dze)001:2320: gur khyim la sogs pa rang bzhin gyi 'od zer lnga ltar 'bar ro //
NK109(dze)001:2322: da ni nang don lnga pa de yang las kyi
NK109(dze)001:2323: rlung gis 'khor 'das mtshams sbyar ba bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2324: / sangs pa las dang nyon mongs pa rgyas pa thig le dang sku /
NK109(dze)001:2325: las kyi ni rig pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:2326: sku ni tshad la phebs pa /
NK109(dze)001:2328: nam mkha' la rang gsal ba /
NK109(dze)001:2329: gsang rgya kyi tshig gnyis gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2330: de dag gis bsdus pa'i don dang po chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:2331: kyi rgyan dang thams cad 'dus par bstan pa la
NK109(dze)001:2333: da ni bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa byung tshul bstan
NK109(dze)001:2334: pa la nang don lngas bstan pa'i dang po rang
NK109(dze)001:2335: gi rig pa'i pho brang bstan pa ni e ma
NK109(dze)001:2336: la sogs pa'i tshig lnga gzhung gis gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2337: nang don gnyis pa gzhi gnas kyi ye shes gsum gyi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2338: rang rig ye shes sku'i klong /
NK109(dze)001:2339: chos sku'i rang dag gi ye shes ngo bo ka nas dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2340: stong pa dngos med ye shes /
NK109(dze)001:2341: gsal ba mkha' nam mkha' rol pa sna tshogs lhun grub kyi ye shes gsum gyi /
NK109(dze)001:2344: ma 'gags pas ni rang bzhin ni lhun grub bo //
NK109(dze)001:2345: le'u gnyis pa'i bsdus don gnyis pa'i nang don gnyis pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2346: da ni nang don gsum pa ye shes kyi rlung
NK109(dze)001:2347: dang las kyi rlung gis tshad bzung ba bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:2348: ni / shes rab kyi rtsal skye pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:2349: ting nge 'dzin spang la me mched pa dang 'dra ba skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2351: nang du las kyi rlung zad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2352: de'i stobs kyis yang dag par rnam par rtog pa 'thor bas rlung dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:2353: mi skyod pa ni gzhi las ma g.yos bar rig pa bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2354: rnam rtog las kyi rlung zad de /
NK109(dze)001:2355: ye shes nyid thabs khyad par dang bcas pas /
NK109(dze)001:2356: kun tu bzang po'i ngang las ma g.yos pa'i ting 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2357: de nyid gsang zhi dpyad na chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i lus na 'od gsal gyi rgyan /
NK109(dze)001:2358: longs sku'i 'od lnga spras pa 'di nyid la kun bzang gi rang bzhin nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:2360: da ni nang don bzhi pa spyod pa'i rang bzhin g.yo ba med par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2361: chos sku'i spyod pa la sogs pa'i tshig bzhi gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2362: da ni nang don lnga pa dngos po'i lta ba
NK109(dze)001:2363: bla ma'i gdams ngag la rag ma lus par bstan
NK109(dze)001:2364: pa ni / lta ba'i ni yul gang la lta
NK109(dze)001:2365: na phyi nang sna tshogs su snang ba las lta
NK109(dze)001:2366: pa ni / la / ji ltar lta na 'og
NK109(dze)001:2367: nas 'byung ba ltar grol lugs lnga'am drug gis lta
NK109(dze)001:2368: pa ni / la / / dpe ji ltar na /
NK109(dze)001:2369: mgron po la rgal ba ltar dang /
NK109(dze)001:2370: sgeg mo me long la blta ba ltar lta'o /
NK109(dze)001:2371: bltas pa la dgos pa ci yod na khams gsum
NK109(dze)001:2372: las grol nas rang gi ngo bo'i sgo nas ye
NK109(dze)001:2373: shes cig char du shar ba de /
NK109(dze)001:2374: thabs ni gnad kyis grol ba la sogs pa la mkhas pas /
NK109(dze)001:2375: rig pa nyid gzhi las ma bskyod par grol te /
NK109(dze)001:2376: rdo rje rig pa'i ye shes la sems pas /
NK109(dze)001:2377: de las ma bcos pa'i ngang du grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:2378: zhes de dag gis bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa ye
NK109(dze)001:2379: shes kyi byung tshul bstan pa la nang don lngar
NK109(dze)001:2381: da ni bsdus pa'i don gsum pa de la rgyun
NK109(dze)001:2382: du spyod pa'i thabs bstan pa la nang don bzhis
NK109(dze)001:2383: bstan pa'i dang po gsang sngags mang yang dpe don
NK109(dze)001:2384: rtags gsum la yid ches par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2385: de yang phyi sna tshogs rol pa la bslab pas /
NK109(dze)001:2386: nang sems rig gnyis su don med pa'i don rang
NK109(dze)001:2387: la shar bas ye shes dngos su skye ba'i rgyu
NK109(dze)001:2388: bstan pa ni blo brdeg go /
NK109(dze)001:2389: de la bslabs pas 'brel chags shing bslabs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2390: rig pa nyid rgyun du snang zhing /
NK109(dze)001:2391: phyi nang gnyis med du rnam par grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:2394: lus kyi gnad shes pas grol ba'i dang /
NK109(dze)001:2395: thabs che bas gzhan la gsang ba tsam gyis 'grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2396: thabs kyi sgo mang bas gang la brten kyang grol ba'i gnad yod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2397: de yang dpes phyi la yid ches pas /
NK109(dze)001:2398: snang ba thams cad dpe don gyi man ngag tu shes /
NK109(dze)001:2399: nang rtags la yid ches pas /
NK109(dze)001:2400: rtsol bsgrub gzhan la bya mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:2401: gsang ba don la yid ches pas /
NK109(dze)001:2402: chos nyid mngon gsum las 'das pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2403: gsum gyis rab tu bstan pa'i bsdus don gsum pa'i nang don bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2404: da ni nang don gnyis pa rang rig pa'i ngo bo bsam pa las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2405: chos rnams kun gyi la sogs pa tshig lnga gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2406: da ni nang don gsum pa bag chags 'thug po
NK109(dze)001:2407: bla ma'i gdams ngag gis chod par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2408: / bag chags phung po snod 'dra ba la /
NK109(dze)001:2409: las dang nyon mongs pa dri ma dang 'dra ba chags pas /
NK109(dze)001:2410: sgo lnga las yul lnga'i 'dzin pa tha dad par byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:2411: de la mig rten la bslabs pas /
NK109(dze)001:2412: gzugs la sogs pa rnams chos kyi sku'i ngang las ma g.yos pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:2413: de'i phyir na gsang sngags thams cad kyi gnad thabs bla ma'i gdams ngag la rags las te /
NK109(dze)001:2414: sems kyi gnad kyis khams gsum las grol ba'i thabs bcu gcig dang /
NK109(dze)001:2415: rig pa'i gnad kyis grol ba dgu dang /
NK109(dze)001:2416: sku gsum gyi gnad kyis grol ba nyer gcig dang /
NK109(dze)001:2417: snang ba ma bu sbyor ba'i gnad nyer gcig dang /
NK109(dze)001:2418: de ltar bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la thug go /
NK109(dze)001:2419: de dag la brten nas chags pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:2420: yul de dag la bdag tu ma bzung pas ye
NK109(dze)001:2421: shes bla ma'i gsung la brten nas chos nyid kyi
NK109(dze)001:2423: de nyid ni lhun ma bcos pa la /
NK109(dze)001:2424: snang brtag thams cad yongs su rdzogs nas dper ri
NK109(dze)001:2425: rab kyi rtser phyin na gling bzhi dus gcig la
NK109(dze)001:2427: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba bya ba dang bral bas rtsol bsgrub med /
NK109(dze)001:2428: klong du gyur pas ci byas kyang ngo lta ba
NK109(dze)001:2429: med pas chen po yin pas gang gis kyang gtan
NK109(dze)001:2430: la mi phebs par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2432: da ni don bzhi pa thugs rje dang shes rab
NK109(dze)001:2433: kyis snang ba'i rtog pa gcod par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2434: // sangs rgyas kyi tshig gsum gzhung gsal lo /
NK109(dze)001:2435: zhes de dag gis ni le'u bzhi pa'i bsdus pa'i
NK109(dze)001:2436: don gsum pa de la rgyun du spyod pa'i thabs
NK109(dze)001:2437: bstan pa la nang don bzhir byas nas bstan to
NK109(dze)001:2438: // da ni bsdus pa'i don bzhi pa 'khrul pa'i
NK109(dze)001:2439: snang ba 'di dag kyang rang 'byung du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:2440: la don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:2441: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba rang gi rig par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2442: stong pa ni dngos po'i skyon med pas mtha' gang du yang ma lhung /
NK109(dze)001:2443: dag pa ni de dri ma'i nyams med pas khams gsum 'khor ba'i ming med /
NK109(dze)001:2444: ye shes ni ye nas gsal 'grib dang bral bas rgya gang dang yang ma chad /
NK109(dze)001:2445: rang ni gzhan la ltos pa dang bral bas ji ltar byas kyang chos nyid las 'gro sa med /
NK109(dze)001:2446: byung sa ni byas pa ma yin pas tha ma skye 'jig du ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2447: de lta bu'i chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba ni rang gi rig pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:2448: gsang sngags ni rig pa 'brel ma chad par gnas pa /
NK109(dze)001:2449: lu gu ye shes kyi rlung la brten nas 'gyu ba /
NK109(dze)001:2450: rgyud ni sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi 'brel /
NK109(dze)001:2451: ngang ni 'khor 'das thams cad de nyid las 'gro sa med pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:2453: da ni nang don gnyis pa de yang dbyings kyi
NK109(dze)001:2454: rgyas btab te nyams su blang pa bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2455: / chos ni nyams su blang bya /
NK109(dze)001:2457: dngos gzhi la bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2458: ma bu sbyar ba'i gnad kun gyi rang 'byung gi ye shes ni /
NK109(dze)001:2459: dbyings ni phyi'i nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba /
NK109(dze)001:2460: nang gi rnam par dag pa'i sgron mar rig pa bcug pas las kyi rlung dang bral nas /
NK109(dze)001:2461: rtog pa tha dad pa 'gags pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2462: dbyings rig 'du 'bral med par rtogs pas thabs kyi rgya sgron ma dang ma bral ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:2464: da ni nang don gsum pa de yang bla ma'i
NK109(dze)001:2465: gdams ngag gi gnad du 'gro bar bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2466: / de yang chos sku la sogs pa lam snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:2467: dngos po la ni rang gi dbang po'i spyod yul du snang /
NK109(dze)001:2468: de kho na ka dag lam rig pa'i dri ma dag pa'i ye shes ni /
NK109(dze)001:2469: rig pa thabs kyi go rar bcug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2470: stong pa ni rig pa mngon gsum du snang yang dngos po rdzas su ma grub /
NK109(dze)001:2471: yul gyi ni lus dngos po la rtsa stobs khyab pas /
NK109(dze)001:2473: rlung la brten nas rig pa 'gyu pas /
NK109(dze)001:2474: gnad du ni rtsa ltems pas rig pa'i yul snyed /
NK109(dze)001:2475: rtsa brtsir bas rig pa ma bu phrad /
NK109(dze)001:2476: rtsa bcud pas rig pa khungs su tshud /
NK109(dze)001:2477: rtsa mnyes pas rig pa dngos su 'thon pa ni sbyor ba rten gyi brdeg pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2479: de ltar byas pa ni man ngag gi rgyal po ste /
NK109(dze)001:2480: spyi bcings ni ngo bo gcig tu grol bas rnam
NK109(dze)001:2481: par rtog pa tha dad pa'i yul du ma bcings
NK109(dze)001:2482: pa'i ngang / chos nyid las ma 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2483: de ltar rtsa la brten pa'i bde ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:2484: rlung dang thig le la brten pa'i bde ba thams
NK109(dze)001:2485: cad rang snang lhun grub rig pa lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)001:2486: du rdzogs pa'o // nang don gsum pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2487: de dag gis ni bsdus don bzhi ba 'khrul pa'i
NK109(dze)001:2488: snang ba de dag kyang rang 'byung du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:2489: la gsum du byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:2490: da ni bsdus pa'i don lnga pa 'khrul pa de
NK109(dze)001:2491: yang rkyen kha nas bzlog par bstan pa la nang
NK109(dze)001:2492: don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:2493: rkyen de dag rang dag tu bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2495: rnal pa chos nyid la gang zag gi blo 'byor
NK109(dze)001:2496: ba ma sdug bsngal kun bde bar shar ba'i lta
NK109(dze)001:2497: ba ni / sems ni rta la las kyi rlung zhon nas /
NK109(dze)001:2498: phyi nang kun tu 'gro las kyis rtog pa tha dad pa'i gzhi byed /
NK109(dze)001:2499: de nyid dngos mus bsdud pa'i rtse las byed cing /
NK109(dze)001:2500: nyon mongs pa'i gzhi yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2501: de'i sgo sems dang ye shes kyi dbye ba'i man ngag gis /
NK109(dze)001:2502: byung tshor gyi rnam par rtog pa 'gags pas /
NK109(dze)001:2503: 'gyu ba las kyi rlung gcod pas /
NK109(dze)001:2504: rnam rtog rang sa dwangs pa chu'i rnyog ma rang dengs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:2505: 'byam pa ni gnyid dbyings kyi thigs su bsad pa /
NK109(dze)001:2506: yangs pa dbyings kyi sgron ma la gtad pas /
NK109(dze)001:2507: phug lta ba rang 'byung gi ye shes las kyi dbang du ma gyur pa /
NK109(dze)001:2508: btib pa ni rtogs pa rags pa'i mtha' rmi lam 'gags pa /
NK109(dze)001:2509: kun gyi man ngag ni gnyid dang rmi lam gyi thun mong ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2510: 'dod pa'i sgo ni dbang po rang yan pas tshogs drug gyi na d+har song pas /
NK109(dze)001:2511: chos nyid ma dang 'phrad pa'i gnad rlung nang du stibs pa las byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:2512: rlung phyi nang gi 'grul gcad nas ye shes snying gi nang du bcug ste /
NK109(dze)001:2513: a'i rgyas btab pas nang du gsal pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2514: chos nyid lam du 'khyer ba ni dag snang la gcer bzhag tu bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2515: ye shes kyi snang ba dag pa lhug par 'char ro //
NK109(dze)001:2516: kyi rkun ni yid nam mkha' la 'phangs pas lus sems kyi 'brel chad de /
NK109(dze)001:2517: mdor ni mig phyung pa ni nam mkha' la sbur bas /
NK109(dze)001:2518: dran med du rang grol bas rig pa'i ngo bo rang sar zin te /
NK109(dze)001:2519: mtshan ma ni dngos po thams cad stong par skyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:2520: rtog pa tha dad pa zil gyis mnan nas /
NK109(dze)001:2521: snang ba 'khrul pa rgya yis stab pas /
NK109(dze)001:2522: chos nyid la byan tshud pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2524: da ni bsdus don lnga pa'i nang don gnyis pa de nyid rkyen dang bral bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2525: ye shes gang nas kyang ma byung ma skyes /
NK109(dze)001:2526: 'gyur med rig pa nyid las 'gro sa gzhan med /
NK109(dze)001:2528: 'od lnga'i snang pas kun la khyab pa /
NK109(dze)001:2529: yangs pa dbyings gcig gi khongs las ma 'das pa /
NK109(dze)001:2530: kun tu rig pa nyid yul kun la khyab cing snang /
NK109(dze)001:2531: chub pa de nyid chos sku las 'gro sa med /
NK109(dze)001:2532: shes rab ni brjod bya thams cad kyi gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:2533: rang snang ni 'byung rkyen tha dad pa las 'das pa /
NK109(dze)001:2534: chos nyid ni de las ma bcos par bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2535: sgo lnga'i yul du ma'i rtog pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2536: de yang rgyu yis ma bskyed pa'i phyir rkyen dang
NK109(dze)001:2537: bral ba'i chos nyid kun bcud du dril bas snying
NK109(dze)001:2538: por gnas pa'o // 'khrul pa'i snang ba skad cig
NK109(dze)001:2539: chod pas rig pa nyid nam mkha' la rgyug pa'o
NK109(dze)001:2540: por gnas pa'o // // zhes de dag gis ni
NK109(dze)001:2541: bsdus pa'i don lnga pa 'khrul pa de yang rkyen
NK109(dze)001:2542: kha nas bzlog par bstan pa la yang gnyis su
NK109(dze)001:2544: da ni le'u bzhi pa'i bsdus pa'i don drug pa
NK109(dze)001:2545: 'khrul pa zhing khams su bstan pa la nang don
NK109(dze)001:2546: brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:2547: 'khor ba nyid kyi bzlog tshul bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2548: e ma ho zhes rang la rang ngo mtshar dang bcas pa'i tshig gis gsungs la /
NK109(dze)001:2549: rang rig pa'i ye shes dbyings rig 'du 'bral med
NK109(dze)001:2550: pa las ma g.yos pa'i ngang du ngo bo bsam
NK109(dze)001:2551: pa las 'das par zhog ces sngon byung du sdud
NK109(dze)001:2553: rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas slob ma la'o //
NK109(dze)001:2557: klong dbyings gcig rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i phyir na bskyal zhes bsdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2558: 'khor ba ye nas yod ma myong pas /
NK109(dze)001:2559: snang shes kun chos nyid du shar bas ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa gsum byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:2560: de las bzlog pa'i sku gsum du grol bas bya zhes gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2561: de yang bcos ma'i spyod pas spyod bya rtog dpyad
NK109(dze)001:2562: kyi yul du ma gyur pas gong du yang ma
NK109(dze)001:2563: phye ba de nyid yid dpyod ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2564: yul du ma las gzhal byar ma gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2566: da ni nang don gnyis pa sems dang yid la ye shes ngos bzung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2567: rtsa ba lnga ni gti mug ma spangs la gnas
NK109(dze)001:2568: lugs su dag pas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes
NK109(dze)001:2569: las 'bras bu rnam snang gi skur smin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2570: yang rgyu 'dod chags ma spangs la gnas su dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2571: lam so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las /
NK109(dze)001:2572: 'bras bu snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku smin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2573: zhe sdang ma spangs la gnas su dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:2574: lam me long lta bu'i ye shes su gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:2575: 'bras bu sku rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i skur smin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2577: lam gnyam pa nyid 'bras bu rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK109(dze)001:2578: rgyu phrag dog ma spangs gnas su dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:2579: lam bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su gsal par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:2580: 'bras bu don yod grub pa'i skur smin par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:2581: yid kyi dran byed 'gyu byed rang sar grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:2582: sangs pa'i rig pa la nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:2583: thams cad rig pa gcig pu yin par ngo shes pas na /
NK109(dze)001:2584: sems can kun gyi lam la /
NK109(dze)001:2585: sgron ma bzhi ltar rnam par snang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:2586: de yang gang na gnas na kun rang lus rtsa
NK109(dze)001:2587: ba'i d+r+wa ba 'dus pa gzhi rig pa'i ye shes
NK109(dze)001:2588: gnas pa / lus rtsa ba'i 'khor lo bzhi 'dus
NK109(dze)001:2589: pa'i nang na don dam gyi 'byung ba bzhi rnam
NK109(dze)001:2590: par dag pa'i ye shes bzhi gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2591: me long la bzhin bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:2592: snang yul du yod la bzung yul du med pas stong pa /
NK109(dze)001:2593: de'i gsal cha gzugs su snang pas rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:2594: de yang shes rig gzhan la ma ltos pas /
NK109(dze)001:2595: ye shes lnga'i rtsa la 'od lngar snang pas gsal pa'i bzhin gzugs su gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2596: bstan pa ni snang yul shar pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2597: de ltar gnas pas gzhan nas 'ong du re ba'i rtog pa chod pas byung /
NK109(dze)001:2598: zhes bya ba tsam du yang ma grub 'khrul pa'i gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:2599: ma grub pas ma 'khrul ba tsam du yang gnas pa min pas /
NK109(dze)001:2600: de nyid gnyis med du bskyal lo //
NK109(dze)001:2601: bsdus don drug pa'i nang don gnyis pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2602: da ni nang don gsum pa rang gi lus kyi
NK109(dze)001:2603: bya ba 'dzin med du grol par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2604: / phung po ni gzugs kyi phung po dngos med zal thal du shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2605: rdul dang rdul phran gyi zhen pa dang bral /
NK109(dze)001:2606: tshor ba bde sdug ngo mnyam du shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2607: myong reg tha dad pa'i zhen pa dang bral /
NK109(dze)001:2608: 'du shes rang snang rgya chen por shes pas rang
NK109(dze)001:2609: gzhan bdag tu 'du shes pa'i zhen pa dang bral
NK109(dze)001:2610: / rnam shes yul yul can las 'das par shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2611: gnyis snang myong ba'i zhen pa dang bral /
NK109(dze)001:2612: 'du byed rang grol gnyen po las 'das par shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:2614: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa'i zhen pa dang bral ba
NK109(dze)001:2615: lnga nyid kyang ye nas rang dag rgyu med du
NK109(dze)001:2616: shes pas / rang lus ye nas sangs rgyas yin par thag chod /
NK109(dze)001:2617: de chod pas 'khrul ba 'byung ba lnga las grub
NK109(dze)001:2618: pa'i lus ni mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so
NK109(dze)001:2619: // 'byung ba zhes gang nas byung na /
NK109(dze)001:2620: dngos po'i gnas lugs las byung bas na 'byung ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2621: phyis bag chags lus kyii gzhi byed pas na 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2622: lnga ni sas lus kyi gzhi 'dzin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2623: sha'i rgyu gti mug gis byas /
NK109(dze)001:2624: chus lus kyi gzungs sbrel bas /
NK109(dze)001:2625: khrag gi rgyu 'dod chags kyis byas /
NK109(dze)001:2626: mes lus kyi rtse 'byin pas drod kyi rgyu zhe sdang gis byas /
NK109(dze)001:2627: rlung gis lus kyi stobs skyed pas dbugs kyi rgyu nga rgyal gyis byas /
NK109(dze)001:2628: nam mkhas lus sems kyi 'brel byas /
NK109(dze)001:2629: yid kyi rgyu phrag dog gis byas so //
NK109(dze)001:2630: de dag rgyur cis 'gro zhe na 'dod chags khrag
NK109(dze)001:2631: yin pa'i rtags su 'dod chags drag po skyes pas
NK109(dze)001:2632: lus la rdul 'byung zhing ba spu gyen la ldang
NK109(dze)001:2633: / gti mug sha yin pa'i rtags su gti mug gi dbang du song ba'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:2635: zhe sdang me'i rgyu yin pa'i rtags su zhe sdang
NK109(dze)001:2636: skyes pa'i dus su lus la drod skye zhing sems
NK109(dze)001:2637: 'khor / nga rgyal rlung gi rgyu yin pas rtags
NK109(dze)001:2638: su nga rgyal skyes pa'i dus su dbugs kyis brgyangs
NK109(dze)001:2640: phrag dog nam mkha'i rgyu yin pa'i rtags su phrag dog skyes pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:2641: yid rab tu 'phro zhing 'gran sems khyad par can skye'o //
NK109(dze)001:2642: de dag chos nyid 'od gsal gyi ye gdangs yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2643: dag snang chen po la longs spyod /
NK109(dze)001:2644: de'i phyir na 'di ltar snang ba 'od gsal gyi
NK109(dze)001:2645: lus nyid du grol bas 'byung ba phra rags kyi
NK109(dze)001:2647: dbang po ni mig ga zugs la dbang bas de
NK109(dze)001:2648: nyid la gcer gyis bzhag pas gzugs stong par grol
NK109(dze)001:2649: la / stong pa nyid gzugs su grol ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:2650: rna ba sgra la dbang bas /
NK109(dze)001:2651: de nyid la gcer gyis bzhag pas sgra nyid gsal bar grol la /
NK109(dze)001:2652: gsal ba nyid sgrar grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:2653: de bzhin du dri nyid ris yal du grol la /
NK109(dze)001:2655: ro nyid rang snang du grol la /
NK109(dze)001:2657: lus nyid sems su grol la /
NK109(dze)001:2658: sems nyid lus su grol bas 'jug pa'i gzhi med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2659: 'dzin pa'i yul snang ba yul gyi gnad kyis gzugs rang gi sa rdul dang phra rab las grol /
NK109(dze)001:2660: brjod pa skur pa'i gnad kyis sgra'i rang sa /
NK109(dze)001:2662: mthong pa yul gyi gnad kyis dri'i rang sa /
NK109(dze)001:2663: snom byed mtha' yas su grol /
NK109(dze)001:2664: myong byed stong pa'i gnad kyis ro'i rang sar zhen
NK109(dze)001:2665: pa rang thad kyi mtha' las grol bas brten pa
NK109(dze)001:2666: rtsa'i gnad kyis rig gi rang sa bde sdug rang
NK109(dze)001:2667: sa las grol ba lnga de dang rang gi sar
NK109(dze)001:2668: grol ba ni / chos las 'das pa'i 'khrul gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2669: zhes nang don gsum pa rang gi lus kyi bya ba 'dzin med du grol bar bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:2670: da ni nang don bzhi pa lus las 'byung ba'i
NK109(dze)001:2671: nyon mongs pa nyid kyang rang grol du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:2672: ni / nyon mongs ni gti mug gis grol bas chu la chu bzhag pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2673: 'dod chags de nyid kyis grol bas mar la mar mnan pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2674: zhe sdang de nyid kyis grol bas nam mkha' la nam mkha' yal ba lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2675: nga rgyal de nyid kyis grol pas rlung la rlung thim pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:2676: phrag dog de nyid kyis grol bas me long la bzhin yal ba lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:2677: lnga nyid rang grol ba yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:2678: gzugs kyi khams nyid rdul phra rab la skyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:2681: shin tu 'phra ba las bskyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:2683: 'dod pa'i khams rang dang gzhan la bskyal bas brjod
NK109(dze)001:2684: pa ngag gi 'bras bu rul ba tsam nyid ni
NK109(dze)001:2685: ye nas rang grol yin pa'i phyir //
NK109(dze)001:2686: so so'i gzhi la ma bcos par skyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:2687: lus sems 'khor ba'i 'brel chad pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2688: mi rigs chos nyid rang la byung ye nas rig par gnas pa'i rgyu yin la /
NK109(dze)001:2689: 'khrul pa'i rgyu sku dang ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)001:2690: chos nyid ye nas rang la sangs te ye med du shes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:2696: gzhi ni de dag 'tshogs pa dang 'brel ba dang 'dus so //
NK109(dze)001:2697: de ltar chos du ma las skur byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:2698: rang lus chos skur gtan la dbab pa /
NK109(dze)001:2699: gnad 'dus bye brag pa'i man ngag gi blo rdeg go /
NK109(dze)001:2700: de nyid rang shar bas gsum po yang lam snang yin par yid ches so //
NK109(dze)001:2701: de ltar ches pas skye ba snga phyi lus kyi rgyud ba'i rtsa ba /
NK109(dze)001:2702: phyis lus mi len par rang lus chos skur gtan la phab pas gcad do //
NK109(dze)001:2703: yid gzhan la sogs pa'i tshig drug gzhung gi shes so //
NK109(dze)001:2705: da ni nang don lnga ba spyod pa ci byed
NK109(dze)001:2706: pa thams cad stong pa'i lta bar bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:2707: / yan lag ma skyod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:2708: sngon 'gro'i dus na rnal du 'bebs pa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:2709: rlung bsgom pa'i dus na lus kyi rtsa mdo rnams su zhim rtse'i thig le byas la /
NK109(dze)001:2710: zhag lngar gnyid spang pa la lus kyi yan lag ma skyod par gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:2711: des na ma song gnas su phyin pa ye shes 'od kyi sa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2712: de ltar lus kyi gnad bstun pas thar ba'i sar 'gro ba'i lam nyid ye nas bsgrod pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:2713: rang byung du gnas pa las gzhan du 'gro ba'i gnas med do //
NK109(dze)001:2714: smra ba'i ngag ni brjod med pas /
NK109(dze)001:2716: sngon 'gro'i dus na rnal du 'bebs pa'i cho ga zhag gsum brjod pas rgyun bcad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2717: lar nyams len gyi dus na ngag bcad pa gnad yin no //
NK109(dze)001:2718: dran stong ye grol gyi gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)001:2719: ma smras gzhi la bzhag pas brjod med nang du 'char zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2720: ye nas rig pa nyid la bsam du med pas smra brjod kyi gzhi stong ste /
NK109(dze)001:2721: bsam pa'i yul bdag tshig blo zad pas brjod pa las 'das pa'i don rgyud la 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:2723: zhes pa ni sngon 'gro'i dus na sems rnal du 'bebs pa'i cho ga'o //
NK109(dze)001:2724: rtsa ba'i bde ba bsgom pa'i dus na sems kyi 'phro 'dus bcad pa zhag gsum du bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:2725: de yang sems la ye nas dran pa med pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:2726: ci yang ma grub par gnas pas na /
NK109(dze)001:2727: ye nas rang bzhin gyi bsam gtan gdod ma nas gnas pa chen por gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:2728: bya med dang 'bad rtsol las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:2729: de ltar lus ngag sems kyi gnad bstun pas /
NK109(dze)001:2730: phyi lus 'byung ba'i dri ma rdul phra rab kyis bcing pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:2731: ngag tshig 'khrul pa'i dri ma dang /
NK109(dze)001:2732: gsang ba'i sems la nyon mongs pa'i dri ma rnams ni rang dag las /
NK109(dze)001:2733: lus sprul skur dri med zang thal /
NK109(dze)001:2735: sems chos skur dri med zang thal chen por gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:2737: da ni nang don drug pa de yang ye nyid nas rang grol bar bstan pa ni /
