NK109(dze)001:4094: de nyid gsal bar gnas pas chad mtha' las log /
NK109(dze)001:4095: de ltar rtag chad gnyis su med pas stong gsal rig pa'i snying po can du gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:4096: de yang 'jig rten pa'i grub mtha' ltar byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:4097: cir snang chos nyid kyi grogs su shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:4098: 'das pa'i grub mtha' ltar rdzogs pas de nyid las gzhan du brjod du med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4099: de ni sna tshogs thabs kyi sgo ma 'gags pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4100: thabs de bcud du dril bas ni rig ba'i rang gdangs de 'od gsal du shar bas so //
NK109(dze)001:4101: de ni lu gu rgyud rtag tu gzir ba'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4102: de ltar shar ba nyid gzhan gyis ma yin par
NK109(dze)001:4103: rang grol yin pas snang ba rang grol cog gis
NK109(dze)001:4104: bzhag pa ni / ngang kun tu bzang po chos nyid ma bcos pa las byung ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:4105: zhes nying lag gi don gnyis pa de nyid bla ma'i gdams ngag du mas rtogs par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:4106: da ni yan lag gi don gsum pa de yang
NK109(dze)001:4107: ye nas 'bad med rang grol yin par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:4108: ni / rig pa de nyid la 'khrul pa yod ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)001:4109: gzhi la log pa'i rig pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4110: thog ma yang rang las byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:4111: tha ma yang rang grol zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:4112: de yang 'di dag bcu ni 'khrul pa'i mtshan nyid bcu ste /
NK109(dze)001:4113: 'og gi dpe bcu bo go rim gyis 'di dag la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4114: de yang rig pa las dang nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i tshad zhen chags chung bas bzung /
NK109(dze)001:4115: khyab pa'i tshad snang bas mi gnod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4116: rig pa la dngos pos ma gos pas stong pa'i
NK109(dze)001:4117: tshad rang gi lus zang thal du mthong bas bzung
NK109(dze)001:4118: / rig pa phyi yul la shar ba'i tshad thig le sku dang bcas pas bzung /
NK109(dze)001:4119: rig pa 'khor ba'i chos las zang thal ba'i tshad nyin mtshan med pas bzung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:4120: rig pa 'khrul pa'i rnam pa las log pa'i tshad dag snang shar bas bzung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:4121: rig pa la rnam par rtog pa sangs pa'i tshad rlung gi 'gyu ba zad pas bzung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:4122: rig pa ma rig pa'i zla dang bral nas gcig
NK109(dze)001:4123: pur gnas pa'i tshad mthong snang grogs su shar bas
NK109(dze)001:4124: bzung ngo // rig pa de rgyur rtogs pa'i tshad
NK109(dze)001:4125: lus las 'byung ba'i gnod pa dang bral bas bzung
NK109(dze)001:4126: bzung ngo // ngo // rig pa de 'bras bus
NK109(dze)001:4127: grol ba'i tshad chos zad pas bzung ngo de dag
NK109(dze)001:4128: bcu ni pha rol tu phyin pa nas /
NK109(dze)001:4129: sa bcu la rtags dang yon tan bshad nas 'dug ste /
NK109(dze)001:4131: blo 'khrid pa tsam las ma gtogs te /
NK109(dze)001:4132: don sngon du skye ba med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4134: de ltar yang rnam dpyod dus la ltos pa rnams dus der 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:4136: 'di ni gsang sngags mngon gsum gyi sa bcu zhes /
NK109(dze)001:4137: da lta rgyud la skye nges pa las dus snga phyi la ltos pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4138: lhag ma ni gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:4139: dge bcu tshad la phebs pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:4140: snang ba 'di dag so so'i dpe ltar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:4141: 'di dag ni gsang sngags kyi lam skye ba'i rim pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4143: da ni nying lag gi don bzhi pa de ltar
NK109(dze)001:4144: gnas pa'i don dpes gong ma rnams kyi don go
NK109(dze)001:4146: sa bcu rang la rdzogs pa de lta bu'i sems
NK109(dze)001:4147: nyid rnam par rtog pa'i rlung brgyad kyis ma bslad
NK109(dze)001:4148: pa ni / grol ba'i dus na nor bu rin po che dang 'dra ba'i yon tan 'byung /
NK109(dze)001:4149: khyab pa'i dus na phyug po'i bang mdzod lta bu'i yon tan 'byung dpe 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4150: de dag nyams su blang bya dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)001:4151: nor bu rin po che mig ma phug pa la bslab pa la sogs blo rtag gi gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:4152: lhag ma ni gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:4153: yan lag gi don lnga pa'i nying don bzhi pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4154: da ni nying lag gi don lnga pa rig pa'i tshad de nyid kyis grol lugs bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4155: 'gag pa yul dang dbang po med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4156: phyi nang gnyis med du zang thal ba'i rig pa la /
NK109(dze)001:4157: gzhi med pa'i gnad kyis da 'khrul pa'i rgyu med
NK109(dze)001:4158: pas rtsa ba dang bral ba'i rig pa la lam
NK109(dze)001:4159: med pas rtogs pa med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4160: ye nas grol ba'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4161: de yang grol lugs lnga po 'di dag gi go ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4162: ye grol la skyar gzhi med pa'i gnad la brten
NK109(dze)001:4163: nas lta bsgom 'bad rtsol la rag ma lus par
NK109(dze)001:4164: bstan pa dang / rang grol gnyen po med pa'i
NK109(dze)001:4165: gnad la brten nas bla ma'i man ngag la rag
NK109(dze)001:4166: ma lus par bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4167: cer grol mthong yal gyi gnad la rgyud lung man ngag la rag ma lus par bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4168: mtha' grol ltos pa dang bral ba'i gnad la brten
NK109(dze)001:4169: nas ltos pa gang la yang mi 'cha' ba dang
NK109(dze)001:4170: / gcig grol la zla med pa'i gnad la brten
NK109(dze)001:4171: nas thabs dang shes rab la rag ma lus par
NK109(dze)001:4172: / bstan pa'o // de la ye nas grol ba'i go ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4175: tshig gi don dang bzhir shes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4176: gong ni glo bur ma yin par thog ma nas grol zin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4177: de skyar nas grol rgyu med pa'i gnad ni /
NK109(dze)001:4178: rig pa nyid 'khrul ma myong pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4179: ye nas grol bar 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4183: rig pa ni ye nyid nas rig pa nyid grol ba yin pa'i gnad ni /
NK109(dze)001:4184: rig pa la gzhi med pas ltos pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4185: rtsa ba med pas byung sa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4186: mtshan brgyad med pas gtan la mi phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4187: skye ba med pas grol rgyu med pas so //
NK109(dze)001:4188: de yang ye nas grol zin pa'i rtags dang /
NK109(dze)001:4189: bsgom bsgrub gang gis kyang mtshan nyid mthong ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:4190: de yang rgyu 'bras la rjes med pa'i rig pas 'thad do /
NK109(dze)001:4191: rig pa la rgyu med pas 'bras bu med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4192: las dang rnam smin yod mi srid do //
NK109(dze)001:4193: gzhan du yang bstan nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:4196: ye nas grol ba'i sems nyid ni //
NK109(dze)001:4197: phyi nas grol rkyen ga la srid /
NK109(dze)001:4200: gtan yal ba rang bzhag gi he dus 'grub ste /
NK109(dze)001:4201: gtad sa ye nas grol bas de nyid rang sar grol te /
NK109(dze)001:4202: ye nyid nas grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4203: de yang sems la byung ba med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4205: 'gro ba med pa'i gnad kyis ye nas grol bar shes so //
NK109(dze)001:4209: ma grol zhes tha snyad tsam du gdags su med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4210: ye nas grol zin pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4211: de la bskyar nas grol mi dgos pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4212: sems ye nas sangs rgyas pas so /
NK109(dze)001:4213: ye nas grol ba de la /
NK109(dze)001:4214: da grol rgyu med pas shes so /
NK109(dze)001:4216: ye zhes khyab pa spyir gtang pas /
NK109(dze)001:4217: bya ba dang bcos pa med pa'i don te /
NK109(dze)001:4220: gar yang gnas pa las 'gyur ba med pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)001:4221: grol zhes bkrol ba lta bu min pas lta bsgom gyis 'bad mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:4222: grol zhes rang lugs su gnas pa las bcas bcos med pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)001:4223: de ltar yin pas lus ngag yid rang shugs la lhod chags shing /
NK109(dze)001:4224: sems nyid rnal du 'bebs pa la grol zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4225: de yang gtan du de ltar gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:4226: theg pa thun mong las 'phags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4227: ye nas grol ba'i dpe ni a li ka li'i 'bras bu ye nas smin zin pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4228: da smin rgyu med pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:4229: rang grol la yang lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:4230: rang grol ba'i go ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4231: gnyen po med pa'i don te /
NK109(dze)001:4232: snang ba nyid snang sa nas rang grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:4233: snang ba las ma gtogs pa'i chos log pa gang yang med do //
NK109(dze)001:4234: de bzhin du stong pa la sogs pa de nyid grol ba la sogs pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4235: dper na chang nad can la chang gis 'joms pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4237: lcags kyis lcags gcod pa la sogs pa 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4238: nyon mongs pa de nyid kyis grol bas na rang grol zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4239: rang grol du 'joms pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4243: rig pa ni chos nyid kyi rig pas 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:4244: grol ba thams cad rang grol yin pa las gzhan
NK109(dze)001:4245: gyis bkrol ba lta bu ma yin par 'thad la
NK109(dze)001:4246: / gal te gzhan grol yin na dngos po gcig
NK109(dze)001:4247: la gzugs tha dad du snang pa mi srid pa
NK109(dze)001:4248: / bzhin no // dngos po'i mtshan nyid dngos pos gtan la phebs pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4249: lung ni sems sde las grol ba rang gzhan las min zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:4250: de la sogs te lung bgrangs na dpag tu med do //
NK109(dze)001:4252: rang grol chen po la rtsod gzhi med pa'i he dus 'grub cing 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:4253: 'di ltar snang ba rang grol ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4254: gnyen po gzhan la rag lus pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4256: rang gis rang grol ba ma gtogs pa gzhan ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4257: gzhung gzhan nas kyang 'dod chags can 'dod chags lam du byas pas grol ba bshad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4258: snang ba snang ba rang gi thog nas grol ba nyid snang ba las ma rtogs pa'i grol rgyu'am /
NK109(dze)001:4260: de nyid de nyid du grol bas gnas pa'i rten med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4261: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:4262: de nyid rang las ma rtogs pa ltos pa'i sa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4263: 'gro sa med pas skye ma myong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4264: gang nas byung ba'i sa med de /
NK109(dze)001:4265: de nyid rang ma yin pa'i chos log pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4268: dper na sprul gyi mdud pa sus kyang ma bkrol bar rang grol ba bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4270: 'di ltar snang grags kyi chos thams cad byung yang rang las byung la /
NK109(dze)001:4271: grol yang rang grol bas so //
NK109(dze)001:4272: dper na nam mkha' dang sprin bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4273: de ltar yin pas yul gzhan la rten pa'i bsgom pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4275: spyod pa rkyen can min pas na /
NK109(dze)001:4276: don gyi zhes bya ba chos zad pa la bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4277: gcer grol mthong yal la yang lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:4278: gcer grol gyi go ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4279: gcer gyis mthong ba tsam gyis de nyid mthong sar grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4280: skad gcig ma dang po rang la mthong pa'am thos pa'am /
NK109(dze)001:4281: rig pa tsam gyi grol bas te /
NK109(dze)001:4282: de ni chos nyid mngon sum gyis rtsis thebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4283: gcer grol tu 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4286: rig pa ni gtad yal gang du yang ma dmigs pas 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:4287: snang ba snang thog tu snang ba tsam gyis grol te /
NK109(dze)001:4290: gzugs yin pa tsam la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:4292: de bzhin du sgra la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4293: de grol ba cis shes na gzugs su mthong bas gzugs ma yin pa'i spros pa chod /
NK109(dze)001:4294: de gcer gcer bzhag pas de nyid grol te /
NK109(dze)001:4295: gzhan la 'jug pa'i shes pa mi skye bas so //
NK109(dze)001:4296: lung ni gser gyi snying po'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:4297: gcer grol chen po'i lta stangs kyis //
NK109(dze)001:4298: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis ka grol //
NK109(dze)001:4301: phyogs bral gcer bzhag gi he dus 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:4302: 'di ltar snang ba gcer grol yin /
NK109(dze)001:4303: de nyid gcer sar bzhag la bzhag sar grol la /
NK109(dze)001:4304: grol sar yal ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4306: chos can dum bu la bslabs pas dum bu gcer grol te /
NK109(dze)001:4307: gang du yang song ba med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4308: gang nas kyang 'ong ba med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4309: gang du 'gro yang 'gro ba med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4310: gar yang gnas pa las 'gyur ba med pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:4311: chos can spyi la bslabs pas snang ba thams cad gcer grol du song ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4312: dpe ni gzu bo'i blo can lha khang du phyin pa lta bu ste /
NK109(dze)001:4313: mthong pa la ris med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4314: tshig gi don ni gcer gyis mthong ba tsam gyis de nyid du grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4315: ma bu 'phrad pas grol ba yin pas snang ba de nyid blos ma bsgyur /
NK109(dze)001:4316: snang bas ma bcad par bzhag pas rang dag la 'gro ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:4317: mtha' grol la yang lnga ste /
NK109(dze)001:4322: stong pa'i mtha' gang la yang ltos pa mi 'cha' ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4323: don gyis 'di yin 'di min gyi rtsis las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4324: mtha' grol du 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4325: rig pa ltos bral ngo bo nyid kyi rig pas 'thad do //
NK109(dze)001:4326: gang la yang ma ltos par mtha' dang bral ba yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4327: dbus la yang gnas pa ma yin no /
NK109(dze)001:4328: de'i phyir na mtha' dang bral bas dbus ma dmigs pa'i lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4329: lung ni rtsal chen yon tan rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:4330: mtha' dang bral bas grol zhes bya //
NK109(dze)001:4332: he du ni gcig shes pas kun grol ba'i he dus 'thad do //
NK109(dze)001:4333: gcig mtha' dang bral bar shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:4334: 'di ltar snang btags thams cad las grol ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4335: ltas pa gang la yang gcar med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4336: grol lugs ni yod mtha' la mi gnas pas med mthar grol la /
NK109(dze)001:4337: med mtha' la mi gnas pas yod mthar grol la /
NK109(dze)001:4338: yod med gnyis ka la mi gnas pas gnyis kar grol /
NK109(dze)001:4339: gnyis ka ma yin pas gnyis ka yang yin par grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4340: de bzhin du snang shes kun la bsgres pas grol ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:4342: gcig gi mtha' las grol ba yin pas gnyis su mi gnas la /
NK109(dze)001:4343: gnyis las grol bas gcig tu yang mi gnas pas so //
NK109(dze)001:4344: de bzhin du gnyis ka dang /
NK109(dze)001:4345: gnyis ka ma yin pa la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4346: mu ni yod pa'i mu snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4347: med pa'i mi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4349: gnyis ka ma yin pa gzhan 'gags pa la grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4350: gcig grol ba la yang lnga ste //
NK109(dze)001:4351: gcig grol gyi go ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4352: grol ba de yang 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4353: rig pa gcig pur grol ba las ma gtogs pa gang yang med do //
NK109(dze)001:4354: des na rig pa ye nas grol ma grol gyi tha snyad las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4355: gcig grol du 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4356: gcig las gzhan med pas grol zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:4357: gcig pu ni rig pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:4358: rang rig pa gcig pu ma yin pa'i chos log pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4359: lung ni gser gyi snying po las /
NK109(dze)001:4360: gcig tu grol ba'i chos nyid ni /
NK109(dze)001:4361: du ma ro gcig yin pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4364: gcig shes kun grol kyis 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:4368: chos nyid du ngo shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:4370: dpe ni du ma ro gcig tu shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:4371: tsh+wa gcig gi ro gtan la phebs na /
NK109(dze)001:4372: tsh+wa kun gyi ro gtan la phebs pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4374: gcig ni rdzogs pa chen po thig le nyag gcig spros pa dang bral ba nyid de /
NK109(dze)001:4375: de'i ngang du grol ba yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4376: du ma grangs kyi mtha' thams cad stong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4377: de ltar grol lugs lnga po gang zag gcig gces pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4378: dbang po'i bye brag gis gang la gang mos kyis grol ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:4379: 'di dag ni gsang ba sgra rgyud nas kyang shin tu zhib par bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:4380: zhes nying don lnga pa rig pa'i tshad de nyid kyi grol lugs bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:4381: da ni yan lag gi don bzhi pa'i nying lag
NK109(dze)001:4382: gi don drug pa de yang gnyen po gzhan la
NK109(dze)001:4383: ma ltos par rang grol du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4384: de yang rkyen ngan pa rnams ye shes kyi grogs su shar ba rkyen gyis grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:4385: rang grol ba yin pa'i 'thad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4386: de yang 'dir ni grol lugs lnga po de ltos gzhi dang bral ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4387: rang grol yin pas dmigs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4389: spyod pa'i chos kyi ltos pa dang bral ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4390: ye grol la gzung 'dzin zung 'jug gi ltos pa dang bral ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4391: mtha' grol tha snyad kyi tshig la mi ltos pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4392: gcig grol byed blo la mi ltos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4393: tshig rnams ni gzhung du brtag go /
NK109(dze)001:4395: de ni nying lag gi don bdun pa de'i don dpe yis gtan la dbab pa bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:4396: de yang rang gis rang grol ba dper na dri
NK109(dze)001:4397: mas dri ma 'khrud bzhin te gzhan la rag ma
NK109(dze)001:4398: lus / de bzhin du dag pas dag pa grol te /
NK109(dze)001:4399: ka dag ka dag gis grol la /
NK109(dze)001:4400: rig pa rig pas grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4402: dug gis dug rnams bong nga dkar pos btsan dug 'joms pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4404: lcags kyis ni sa gdar dang /
NK109(dze)001:4405: rdzong so gis lcags rnams gshog pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4406: mtha' grol ni shing las me byung bas shing rnams sregs pa lta yod pa med mthar grol pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4408: dper na brtsol rdo yis rdo rnams gcog pa dang 'dra ste /
NK109(dze)001:4410: rdo yis rdo bcag rdo ma bcag kyang rdo las gzhan ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4411: de ltar rang rang dgra rang gis byed pa la ma gtogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:4412: gnyen po rigs mthun pas grol ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:4414: da ni nying lag gi don brgyad pa de yang
NK109(dze)001:4415: ye nyid nas rang la rdzogs par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:4416: / he du de'i phyir rang gi gzhi la gnas pa'i rig pa la /
NK109(dze)001:4417: rig pa nyid la 'khor 'das dus gcig tu rang
NK109(dze)001:4418: shar ba yin pa'i phyir na snang ba thams cad
NK109(dze)001:4420: thog ma nas rang las byung ba yin pa'i phyir gzhi rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4421: gzhan ltos kyis chos las rang grol ba yin pa'i
NK109(dze)001:4422: phyir 'khrul pa thams cad kyang rdzogs pa chen por
NK109(dze)001:4423: byung ba'o // dri ma rang dag pa yin pa'i phyir lam rdzogs pa chen por kyang byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4424: ye nas rang rig yin pa'i phyir shes bya rdzogs pa chen por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4425: rig pa nyid ye nas rang la khyab pa yin
NK109(dze)001:4426: pa'i phyir na 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen por byung
NK109(dze)001:4427: ba'o // gang nas kyang ma 'ongs pa'i rig pa
NK109(dze)001:4428: rang gis yin pa'i phyir rgyu rkyen rdzogs pa chen
NK109(dze)001:4429: ba'o // por byung ba'o // rkyen gzhan la rag
NK109(dze)001:4430: ma lus pa rig pa nyid rang gis rang rtogs
NK109(dze)001:4431: pa yin pa'i phyir chos nyid rdzogs pa chen por
NK109(dze)001:4432: ba'o // por byung ba'o // byung ba'o // 'bad
NK109(dze)001:4433: pa med par ye nas grol bar gnas pa'i rig
NK109(dze)001:4434: pa rang la log pa yin pa'i phyir 'khor 'das
NK109(dze)001:4435: rdzogs pa chen por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4436: tshig gi spros pa'i mtha' thams cad nye bar zhi
NK109(dze)001:4437: nas rang la gnas pa yin pa'i phyir rgyud lung
NK109(dze)001:4438: rdzogs pa chen po byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4439: thog ma nas ma skyed par rang la rdzogs pa
NK109(dze)001:4440: yin pa'i phyir dus gcig la rdzogs pa chen po
NK109(dze)001:4441: zhes bya'o // rang gis rtogs shing shes la gzhan
NK109(dze)001:4442: gyis ma bcos pa yin pa'i phyir na bla ma'i
NK109(dze)001:4443: gdams ngag rdzogs pa chen por byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4444: blos bsgyur ba ma yin par rang gi sar bzhag
NK109(dze)001:4445: pa yin pa'i phyir bsam gtan rdzogs pa chen po'o
NK109(dze)001:4446: // rang gis rang byas pas 'jig pa dang bral
NK109(dze)001:4447: ba'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir dbyings rdzogs pa chen
NK109(dze)001:4448: // po'o // de dag gis ni yan lag gi
NK109(dze)001:4449: don bzhi pa glo bur gyi 'khrul pa de'i ldog
NK109(dze)001:4450: tshul bstan pa la nying lag gi don brgyad du
NK109(dze)001:4452: da ni yan lag gi don lnga pa log nas
NK109(dze)001:4453: 'khrul pa ye shes ji lta bu yin par bstan
NK109(dze)001:4454: pa la nying lag gi don drug gis bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)001:4455: dang po / dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs kyi ngo bo ji lta bu yin par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4456: 'di dag ni le'u 'di'i 'gor sdud pa pos zhus
NK109(dze)001:4457: don bzhi pa ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes ji lta
NK109(dze)001:4458: bu zhes pa'i lan du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4460: gong du bstan pa de ltar rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don gyis chos kyi sku ni /
NK109(dze)001:4461: ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i ye shes su rang
NK109(dze)001:4462: snang bas blo dang dngos po dri ma zad pa
NK109(dze)001:4463: ni / rnal 'byor pa rkyen gyis mi gnod pa'i dus so //
NK109(dze)001:4464: thog mar nga rang byung gi ye shes yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4465: skye ba snga phyi'i rgyud pa zad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4466: grub pa'i mtha' zhig pa'i dus na'o //
NK109(dze)001:4467: de yang ma rig pa'i zla dang bral bas ni
NK109(dze)001:4468: rnal 'byor ba'i yin min gyi rtsis las 'das te
NK109(dze)001:4470: lus ngag yid la sdug bsngal rgyu med pa ni bde ba'i snang 'di nyid kyis 'dres pas /
NK109(dze)001:4471: lus la drod skyes pas lus ni bde ba chen po yin la /
NK109(dze)001:4472: ngag gtan gyi zung zad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4473: yid la byed pa dang bral ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:4474: tshig las 'das pa'i ye shes brjod pa'i rgyu med par brag cha ltar shes pa'i dus na //
NK109(dze)001:4476: nang du smra ba rgyun chad /
NK109(dze)001:4477: gsang par bsam pa'i 'phro 'du rgyun chad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4478: de dag ni ye thog ma nas rang la gnas pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:4479: de rang gi rnam par dag pa'i rtags su byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4480: de yang 'di nyid la brtson 'grus rab zag pa zad nas 'bu ba tha ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4481: gzugs su grub pa med pas lus zang thal du song ba'i sdes /
NK109(dze)001:4482: sa ni 'byung ba'i lus kyis sems sdes su bcug pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4483: de sems dang bcas pa ni min pas 'di nyid la grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4484: 'di'i dus na phyi lus kyi dngos po zad pas /
NK109(dze)001:4487: nang sems kyi byung tshor gyi mtshan ma'i dngos po zad pas rtog pa ngan pa mi rgyu /
NK109(dze)001:4488: gsang ba grub matha'i 'dzin pa'i dngos po zad pas chos las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4489: phyi nang kun stong par gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:4490: 'di'i dus dbyings rig pa'i 'phel zad pas /
NK109(dze)001:4492: du ma phye ba gang yang med pa ni ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4493: blo'i sgro 'dogs pas chos dang bral te /
NK109(dze)001:4494: nyams su blang bya'i stobs med pas thabs las 'das pa'i rtags su /
NK109(dze)001:4495: chos kyi tshig sna tshogs kha nas rang byung du 'ong ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4496: de'i dus na shes rig rang so na gsal bas
NK109(dze)001:4497: rtog pa med pa la phyi nang gi dngos po
NK109(dze)001:4498: gsal bas / rlung phyi nang du 'gyu ba sangs te /
NK109(dze)001:4499: gang sdod pa'i sar sar gyis 'gro ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4500: 'di'i dus na phyi nang gnyis su mi 'dzin pas sems snang ba med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4501: nang rig pa sar snang ba gnyis med pa'i tshe /
NK109(dze)001:4502: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK109(dze)001:4503: 'bras bu ye shes gnyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4504: ji ltar bsam pa'i dngos po bsgyur bar nus te /
NK109(dze)001:4505: 'gro ba la phan bdag tu 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:4506: 'di'i dus na rig pa nyid rang dag pas 'dres
NK109(dze)001:4507: pa'i zla ma rig pa med pa'i rtags su gang
NK109(dze)001:4508: gtad pa la lcog gis bzhag pas rang byung gi
NK109(dze)001:4510: de'i tshe tshig gzhan gyis bsgyur du mi btub ste /
NK109(dze)001:4511: gzhan gyis bcos pa'i tshig med pa ni 'brel ba
NK109(dze)001:4512: med pa'i gtam gyi tshig kun tu lus par byung
NK109(dze)001:4513: ngo / de ni brjod du med pas don khong du chud pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4514: snga bsam dang phyis bsam par byed pa'i sems med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4515: yid rtog pa'i dran pa 'dzin med rang grol du song bas /
NK109(dze)001:4516: gang yang ched du byed pa dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4518: da ni nying lag gi don gnyis pa de ltar
NK109(dze)001:4519: gnas pa'i gzhi de la gnyen po gzhan gyis bcos
NK109(dze)001:4520: su med par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4521: rig pa rang sa las ma g.yos pas so ma nyid yin la /
NK109(dze)001:4522: de nyid stong pa gzugs dang bral bas gnyug ma'i chos nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:4523: de la ma gos pas ngang zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4524: de yang lus ngag ma bcos pa'i gzhi brdal ba kun khyab nyid la brtan nas /
NK109(dze)001:4525: mchog gi dngos grub thob pa yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4526: de la gnyen po gzhan med la /
NK109(dze)001:4527: gsal 'grib dang bral bas rnal mar gnas pa'i gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:4528: de yang ngang rang bzhin bdag nyid chen po gsum du bzhugs pas bcos ma las grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4530: da ni nying lag gi don gsum pa de lta
NK109(dze)001:4531: bu'i de yang ye nas gnas par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:4532: / thog ma nas 'di kho na ltar gnas pas
NK109(dze)001:4533: da bcos mi dgos par shes bya ni gang dag
NK109(dze)001:4534: shes par bya ba'i yul yin zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:4535: blo bral dngos 'das kyi don de shes pa la
NK109(dze)001:4536: dgos pa ci yod na khams gsum du mi ldog
NK109(dze)001:4538: shes lugs ji ltar shes na blo dang bral bas yid dpyod du ma song /
NK109(dze)001:4539: dngos po las 'das pas zhe 'dod dang bral ba shes so //
NK109(dze)001:4540: de'i babs rang stobs kyis 'grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4541: de nyid sngon rgyu byung sa med pas 'das pa la mi ltos /
NK109(dze)001:4542: phyis nas 'byung du re ba med pas ma 'ongs pa la rten mi 'cha'/
NK109(dze)001:4543: gdod nas med pa'i phyir da lta snang ba la rten mi 'cha' bas /
NK109(dze)001:4544: dus gsum la snga phyi med pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4545: de'i phyir na 'gyur ba ma yin par gsang sngags kyi lam drang po la gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4546: de ltar sangs rgyas dang sems can yongs la khyab pa'i sems gcig po de ni /
NK109(dze)001:4548: de la sna tshogs sgyus mar grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4549: gcig po de la grub pa'i mtha' theg pa kun gyi spyi phung yin zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4550: de yang thog ma ste 'das pa'i dus na yang sems de rang /
NK109(dze)001:4551: bar dang ste da lta yang de rang las ma rtogs pa'i sems med la /
NK109(dze)001:4552: tha mar yang de nyid rang du grub pa las gzhan ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4553: de'i phyir na gcig shes pas kun grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4555: da ni yan lag gi don bzhi pa de yang
NK109(dze)001:4556: sems can la ji ltar gnas tshul bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:4557: / de ltar sems la gnas pa'i 'khrul pa med pa'i gzhi de ni /
NK109(dze)001:4558: de yang rang rig pa las byung pa'i ye shes mkhyen pa phyogs med du gsal /
NK109(dze)001:4559: ye shes las byung pa'i 'od de gsal ba ni kha dog lngar bris legs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4560: de yang chos sku las byung ba'i longs sku zhal phyag tu rdzogs la /
NK109(dze)001:4561: longs sku las byung pa'i sprul sku gzugs su rdzogs
NK109(dze)001:4562: pa gsum ni ye nas rang la ma bskyed rdzogs
NK109(dze)001:4563: pas gzhan nas brtsal mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)001:4564: bsgrub tu med pa'i 'bras bu ye nas rang la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:4565: de la chos kyis rtsol sgrub dang bcas pas ye nas bcos su med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4566: de nyid rang grol ba'i gnad kyis so //
NK109(dze)001:4567: dbu ma sems tsam la sogs pa'i grub mtha' mkhan
NK109(dze)001:4568: po rnams kyis ye nas gzhan 'dod dgag pa dang
NK109(dze)001:4569: / rang 'dod skyabs pa dang bral pa'i gzhi de
NK109(dze)001:4570: ni 'dod pa phyogs cha dang bral ba zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:4571: / // gzhi rig pa chos kyi sku de la
NK109(dze)001:4572: gti mug la sogs pa'i dug lngas ye nas gos
NK109(dze)001:4574: stong pa nyid kyi gzhi la las dang bag chags kyis mi gos pa'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:4575: de yang nyams su blang bya dang sbyar ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4576: gti mug can ni gti mug gi lam du zhugs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4577: de bzhin du chags pa can 'dod chags la lam du bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4578: zhe sdang can zhe sdang la lam du bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4579: de bzhin du nga rgyal du bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4580: phrag dog can phrag dog la lam du bya ba ni gzhan nas bstan nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:4581: de yang 'khor 'das gcig tu bsre ba stod bcud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4583: smad gdams pa'i man ngag gis 'du 'bral gang la yod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4584: snang ba thams cad de ltar 'gyur ba'i man ngag tu shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4586: da ni nying lag gi don lnga pa ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:4587: nyid de'i rgyan nam rol par thams cad 'byung bar
NK109(dze)001:4588: bstan pa ni / gsal ba ni mig nas sgron ma'o //
NK109(dze)001:4589: de yang da lta byas pa lta bu ma yin pas sngon nas gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4590: de nyams su blangs sngon du snang bas 'khor ba'i snang ba log pas brjid re che'o //
NK109(dze)001:4591: snang ba ni ma dag pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba bde sdug gi gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:4592: dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba chos nyid kyi
NK109(dze)001:4593: 'di dpung lhun te sangs dang mer bar snang ba
NK109(dze)001:4594: / ri sdug pa ni yid du 'ongs pa la chags pas /
NK109(dze)001:4595: thog ma yang khams gsum du khrid la /
NK109(dze)001:4596: de yang nyams kyi dga' bde la chags na khams gsum du 'khrid par byed do //
NK109(dze)001:4597: de yang dbang po rab la chos kyi sku la
NK109(dze)001:4598: ngo sprod pas brda' dang rten 'brel la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:4599: sprad pas / rang snang thig le'i dal la dang re spro'o //
NK109(dze)001:4600: dbang po 'bring pos longs sku la ngo sprod pas
NK109(dze)001:4601: gzugs dang ri mo la brten nas sprad pas 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:4602: snang zhing khams dang re spro /
NK109(dze)001:4603: dbang po tha mas sprul pa'i sku la ngo sprad
NK109(dze)001:4604: pas 'dra 'bag dang mar me la brten nas sprad
NK109(dze)001:4605: pas / rang lus 'od gsal du mthong ba dang re spro'o //
NK109(dze)001:4606: de yang phyi'i ngo sprod gsum dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)001:4607: sprul pa'i sku dpe man shel gyi mdangs la brten nas phrad do //
NK109(dze)001:4608: longs sku rtags byang chub sems kyi sgron ma la brten nas phrad /
NK109(dze)001:4609: chos sku don rang rig pa 'od gsal bde ba chen po la brten nas phrad do //
NK109(dze)001:4610: ngo bo ni ka nas dag pa'i ye shes so //
NK109(dze)001:4611: zang thal ni rig pa'i gseng lam ste spyi bo
NK109(dze)001:4612: tshangs pa'i bu ga ste rtsa stong pa sbubs re
NK109(dze)001:4613: yangs te snang srid 'khor 'das kun 'gyu bas so
NK109(dze)001:4614: // de yang rang bzhin du lhun grub rin po
NK109(dze)001:4615: che'i snang bas sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis ka
NK109(dze)001:4616: la kun tu khyab pas de la sus rtogs shing
NK109(dze)001:4617: khong du chud pa bdal re che ste /
NK109(dze)001:4618: phyogs med du rang shar la /
NK109(dze)001:4620: thugs rje ni bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i thugs rje mos pa dang ldan pa la 'char /
NK109(dze)001:4621: rkyen yul dang phrad pa'i thugs rje gang zag las sad pa la 'char /
NK109(dze)001:4622: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje sems can kun la
NK109(dze)001:4623: byung ba ni so so la skyed re che ste
NK109(dze)001:4624: / las sad pa'i 'gro ba skad cig la sangs rgya bar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:4626: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:4628: gzhi rig pa gang na yod pa na 'od yod de /
NK109(dze)001:4629: dper na nyi ma gang na yod pa na 'od yod pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:4630: de yang kun la khyab pas ste /
NK109(dze)001:4631: de yang ye nas chos nyid kyi gdangs snang ba'i bskrag re gsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4632: ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4633: gnas pa gzhi gnas lugs thog pa med pa shes
NK109(dze)001:4634: rab kyi rtsal gyis tshig don dbyer med du gcod
NK109(dze)001:4635: la bang mgyogs pa ni rlung gi 'gyu bar brten
NK109(dze)001:4636: nas myur du gcod cing 'khor 'das sdud pa dang
NK109(dze)001:4638: rig pa las byung ba'i ye shes kyi rtsal 'od kyi rang gdangs su byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:4639: phyi nang med pa 'od re gsal ba ni sgron ma mig nas 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4640: stong pa ni snang yul du yod la /
NK109(dze)001:4641: bzung yul du ma grub ste /
NK109(dze)001:4642: dper na me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar snang la
NK109(dze)001:4643: rang bzhin med pa la kun 'byung ba de ngo
NK109(dze)001:4644: mtshar che ste / snang la rang bzhin med pa las thams cad kyi ngo bor byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4645: bsgom pa'i gnad nyin mtshan kha sbyor du byung ba
NK109(dze)001:4646: de ma brtsal rang sar bzhag pas rgyun re ring
NK109(dze)001:4648: spyod pa'i gnad snang ba la dbang bsgyur nus pas
NK109(dze)001:4649: snang ba ma bkag rang las byung ba'i spyod pa
NK109(dze)001:4650: brdal re chags pa ni lus ngag yid tshi chad
NK109(dze)001:4652: lta ba'i gnad mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun gcod pa yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:4655: srid pa 'khor ba'i chos snang ba dang shes pas bsdus pa /
NK109(dze)001:4657: bzhengs pa rang gi blo thog du phung gis shar ba /
NK109(dze)001:4659: 'khor 'das las ma gtogs pa gzhan med pas de'i gong na lta ba gzhan med do //
NK109(dze)001:4660: 'bras bu'i gnad phyir mi ldog pa ye thob chen po'i rgyas thebs /
NK109(dze)001:4661: de la 'bad pa byar med pas rang gis rang grol bas te /
NK109(dze)001:4662: de su yis rtogs pa tsam gyis grol bas rgya re che'o //
NK109(dze)001:4663: ye nas rang thog tu rang grol ba rtogs pa'i gnad yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4664: rdzogs pa chen po blo dang bral ba'i don rgyud la skyes pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4665: rang la 'khor re mkhas pa ni nyams rgyud la brten pa las byung ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:4666: kha dog ni dkar ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4670: mthing ka dang lngar ldan pa ni ma 'dres pa
NK109(dze)001:4671: so so na gsal bas bri re legs te so
NK109(dze)001:4673: snang ba ni dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba /
NK109(dze)001:4674: srid pa lus can 'gro ba rnams /
NK109(dze)001:4675: rnam dag ni 'khrul snang ye shes su shar ba /
NK109(dze)001:4676: de ltar shar ba de khod re snyoms pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4680: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i gzhi ni rang
NK109(dze)001:4681: las byung ba'i 'od gsal gyi snang ba bkod re
NK109(dze)001:4682: legs pa ni / mu khyud kyi rwa bas kun nas mdzes par byas pa 'o //
NK109(dze)001:4683: gzhi nas ni ka nas dag pa'i rig pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4684: lam dus su dbyings rig pa 'du 'bral med pas chen po ste der ma 'dus pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4685: sangs rgyas dang sems can tsam gnas pas shong ba re che ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4686: 'khor 'das gnyis po gcig tu bsre ba'i man ngag
NK109(dze)001:4687: gis snang srid lto sbyar ba zhes bya ba ni
NK109(dze)001:4689: da gnyis snang mi srid pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4690: sku chos sku longs sku sprul sku /
NK109(dze)001:4693: lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi sgron ma dang ldan rtsegs
NK109(dze)001:4694: re legs pa ni ye shes dag pa'i sgron ma
NK109(dze)001:4695: dang bcas pa'o // zhes nying don lnga pa ngo
NK109(dze)001:4696: bo nyid de'i rgyan nam rol pa thams cad 'byung
NK109(dze)001:4697: dang bcas pa'o // bar bstan nas / da ni
NK109(dze)001:4698: nying lag gi don drug pa de yang sems can
NK109(dze)001:4699: la ji ltar gnas pa bstan nas de'i ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:4700: la gang gis kyang ma gos par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:4701: dang bcas pa'o // bar bstan nas / / rang ngo bo la /
NK109(dze)001:4703: de yang sems can la gnas pa'i ngo bo gang yin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4704: 'khor 'das gnyis med du 'dres pas sangs rgyu med pas las dang nyon mongs pa las grol /
NK109(dze)001:4705: rgyas rgyu med pas sku dang ye shes las grol /
NK109(dze)001:4706: sems can med lta bsgom spyod pa las grol /
NK109(dze)001:4707: ma rig med pas rgyu dang rkyen las grol /
NK109(dze)001:4708: 'khrul ba med pas bzung ba dang 'dzin pa las grol /
NK109(dze)001:4709: sems med pas ni bsam pa'i phugs ded pas las kyi rdos zad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4710: yul phyung pas slar ldog pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4711: rtsad bcad pas phyis skye ba'i rgyun chad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4712: rtse phab pas bzhugs pa'i rten med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4713: gnad de dag la brten nas khams gsum du mi ldog pa'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:4715: yid brtson du bzung bas 'gyu ba rgyun chad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4716: ngos bzung pas skyon yon tan du gyur pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4717: mdor phyung pas 'gro ba'i lam zad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4718: mkha' la sbur bas sems kyi rten bral ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:4719: rten lags pa med pa la sogs pa khams gsum 'khor ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4720: 'das pa sku gsum yod pa min no //
NK109(dze)001:4721: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rig pa la dgra med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4722: de las ltos pa'i bshes med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4723: dgra gnyen ngo mnyam pas chags sdang yang dag pa'i lam du bslongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:4724: 'di'i dus na ngo mnyam drug gis man ngag gis las kyi mtha' bsdu ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4725: 'di'i dus na zhen pa'i yul 'gag pas nyon mongs
NK109(dze)001:4726: pa med cing de la ngar 'dzin pa'i shes pa
NK109(dze)001:4728: sa rdo ngo mnyam pa'i dus so //
NK109(dze)001:4729: 'di'i dus na lus 'gro ba dang 'ong ba dang bral nas /
NK109(dze)001:4730: sa gcig tu 'dus pa las lus bya ba med pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:4731: rtsol med kyi don khong du chud pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4732: de ltar yang bya ba med pas grol bas grol zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4733: 'di'i dus na blo'i chos tshig dang yi ge las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:4734: khrig chags su smra ba med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4735: chos zad pa'i rtags yin te /
NK109(dze)001:4736: 'khrul pa dag pa'i snang ba tsam du yang med do //
NK109(dze)001:4737: thabs med pas bla ma'i man ngag dang bral /
NK109(dze)001:4738: shes rab med pas tshig las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4739: de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na phung po gzugs kyi
NK109(dze)001:4740: phung po rdul phra rab so so nas sil bur
NK109(dze)001:4741: 'gyur ba dang / tshor ba'i myong reg 'gags pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4743: rnam shes kyi grong mthor ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4744: 'du byed bya ba las grol ba dang med cing de lnga'i mtshan nyid mthong pas zad pas te /
NK109(dze)001:4745: khams dang rten 'brel gyi chos kyang zhig nas myong ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4747: 'di'i dus na yul lnga la zhen pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4748: de la 'dzin par bya ba tsam du yang med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4749: 'khor ba'i rdos zad pa'i rtags yin no //
NK109(dze)001:4750: 'di'i dus na mig gi dbang pos gzugs kyi mthong ba'i don 'gags pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4751: de bzhin du rna ba la sogs pas thos pa'i don 'gags pa med cing /
NK109(dze)001:4753: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul la sngon por zhen pa
NK109(dze)001:4754: sogs med pas rnal 'byor pas lus kyi ma bcing
NK109(dze)001:4756: yul la bzung pa 'di ltar bya /
NK109(dze)001:4758: mi bya zhes par yang med /
NK109(dze)001:4759: de la 'dzin pa med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4760: bdag tu rtog pa'i blo zad pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4761: de nyid rang rig pa yin pas de la cha sa sku longs sku sprul sku med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4762: de las byung ba'i ye shes la bdag tu 'dzin pa med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4763: 'das pa'i las ma nor ba rnyed pa'i rtags yin no //
NK109(dze)001:4764: shes pas bsdus pa'i ye shes med pas sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)001:4765: dang sems can gnyis med shes bya'i ye shes med
NK109(dze)001:4766: pas mkhyen pa kha phyir ma ltas te nang du
NK109(dze)001:4767: gsal / de la bdag tu 'dzin pa'i blo med
NK109(dze)001:4768: pas 'khor 'das gang du yang ma grub pa zhes
NK109(dze)001:4769: gsal / bya'o // de la nyams kyi 'phel zad pas 'od med pa /
NK109(dze)001:4770: de nyid rig pa la zhen pa med pas kha dog du yang yod pa ma yin no /
NK109(dze)001:4771: ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4772: de la sgra med pas mnyan bya'i yul med /
NK109(dze)001:4773: dri med pas snom bya'i yul med pa la sogs pa 'dod yon med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4774: thams cad ye shes kyi rol par shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4775: de la zhe'i 'dod pa med cing 'dod pa de la zhen pa tsam du yang med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4776: yul bdag tu ma bzung pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4777: de la phyi nang med pas dbyings med /
NK109(dze)001:4778: lha bskyed mi dgos pas gzhal yas khang yang med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4779: brten par bya ba'i gzhi med pa las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4780: rang rig rang gi lha yin pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4781: zhal phyag tu 'dzin pa'i lha med pas /
NK109(dze)001:4782: de la mched par bya ba'i yul las 'das ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4783: rang lus gzhal yas khang la /
NK109(dze)001:4784: rang sems lhar shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4785: zhes de dag gis ni yan lag gi don lnga
NK109(dze)001:4786: pa log nas 'khrul pa'i ye shes ji ltar bu
NK109(dze)001:4788: nying lag gi don drug tu byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:4789: da ni nying lag gi don drug pa de la
NK109(dze)001:4790: gnyis snang ji ltar yin bstan pa la nying lag
NK109(dze)001:4791: gis don bcus bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:4792: de yang rkyen gyis 'khrul te de la 'dzin pa'i rnam pa ji ltar byung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4793: de yang 'di dag ni sdud pa pos le'u 'di'i
NK109(dze)001:4794: 'go dod du zhus don lnga pa de la gnyis
NK109(dze)001:4795: snang ji ltar lags zhes dris pa'i lan du byung
NK109(dze)001:4796: ba'o // ston pas kye ma zhes nges par gsang
NK109(dze)001:4797: ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod nyon cig
NK109(dze)001:4799: rigs gsum gyi khro bo las khyad par du gsang sngags kyi bdag por dbang bskur bas na'o //
NK109(dze)001:4800: gzhan las khyad par chen po'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4801: ngo bo ka nas dag pas 'khrul rgyu dang /
NK109(dze)001:4802: 'khrul rkyen gang du yang ma grub la /
NK109(dze)001:4804: ji ltar yang shar cing snang du stub la /
NK109(dze)001:4805: thugs rje kun la khyab pas spang blang dang dgag sgrub gang du yang med pa'i gzhi de las /
NK109(dze)001:4806: yod ces dngos po'i chos dang /
NK109(dze)001:4807: med pa zhes stong pa'i chos gnyis byung bas te de'i gnad kyis 'khor 'das gnyis su byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4808: de ltar byung bas spyi pa'i gzhi ni lhun grub
NK109(dze)001:4809: sna tshogs su snang bas gang du yang ma 'gags
NK109(dze)001:4810: la / gar yang ma dmigs pas te /
NK109(dze)001:4811: gzhi zhes khyab pa spyir btang nas /
NK109(dze)001:4812: gzhi zhes 'dod pa rang shug pa bzhag ste shes
NK109(dze)001:4813: pa'i khyad par zhes 'khrul pa ma 'gags pa'i gzhir
NK109(dze)001:4814: bzhag pa ni / ngo bo ka nas dag pa
NK109(dze)001:4815: nyid 'khrul ma myong zhes bya ba brjod pa tshig
NK109(dze)001:4817: de nyid rang 'khrul bar song pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4818: dper na rab rib can gyis mig gis nam mkha' la skra shad par mthong pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:4819: nga ni ma 'khrul lo zhes brjod kyang 'khrul pa song pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:4820: don gyis ka nas dag zhes pa'am /
NK109(dze)001:4823: nges pa don gyi dngos gzhi pa yin zhes pas 'khrul pa song ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4824: de nyid ma rig pa gsum chos nyid yin zhes de dang sbags pa'i ni /
NK109(dze)001:4825: gzhi la lhun gyis grub zhes spang dka' ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:4826: de yang don gyi sems can ma 'khrul sangs rgyas 'khrul zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:4827: ma 'khrul ba 'dod pa nyid 'khrul par song pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4828: ming med ming du song ba lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:4829: de shes par bya ba'i yul ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi ka dag ste /
NK109(dze)001:4830: ming med ming du song ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:4831: rig pa zhes ma rig par song bas /
NK109(dze)001:4832: de nyid rang yang dri mar snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:4833: dper na lus yod pas grib ma yod la /
NK109(dze)001:4834: skyes bu glen pa zhig mtshan mo nya'i nub mo sngon du shar du phyin pas /
NK109(dze)001:4835: grib ma nag po de 'drer mthong nas bros pas /
NK109(dze)001:4836: phyi bzhin 'brong te rab tu bred pa lta bur dang /
NK109(dze)001:4837: de nas nub tu log pas sngon du zhugs nas song pas /
NK109(dze)001:4838: sdug bsngal gyis zin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:4839: de bzhin du sems la dran pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4840: bsam pa'i cha shar ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4841: lus las grib ma 'byung ba ma shes pa bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:4842: rig pa las ma rig par shes pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4843: ngo bo nyid ni ka nas dag kyang de'i rang gzhan grib ma ltar lhun grub tu byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4846: 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul par brtags pas gnyis su spags pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4847: rtog pa de yul du 'tshol byed kyi yid du song pas yul kun la 'jug par byed la /
NK109(dze)001:4848: de la zhen pas bdag dang gzhan du nga'i dang
NK109(dze)001:4849: kho'i gtan la phab pas gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid
NK109(dze)001:4850: du song la / de nyid la zhen la mthar thug dang bcas pa 'jug pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:4852: ma dang bu tsha la sogs pa nges pa can
NK109(dze)001:4853: du 'jog pas nges par 'jog pa'i yid du song
NK109(dze)001:4854: ngo // de la rang ma yin pa gzhan gyi sdug bsngal la rnam par rtog pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4855: yid kyi rnam par shes pa song ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4856: de dag la brten nas nyon mongs pa la spyod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4857: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang /
NK109(dze)001:4858: drug gi 'dzin pa yul dang shes pa gnyis la ma 'phags pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4859: rig pa chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid kyang bzung ba
NK109(dze)001:4860: yul tsam po dang bye brag pas bcings pa chos
NK109(dze)001:4861: nyid zang thal yin pa'o don rgyud la ma skyes
NK109(dze)001:4862: so // de nas cha med pa'i rdul 'phra rab
NK109(dze)001:4863: las byung ba'i lus sems dang bcas pa blang pa'i
NK109(dze)001:4864: so // phyir na / dang po'i rlung lnga'i yul
NK109(dze)001:4865: dag pa'i 'od lnga phyir shar ba de las 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:4866: so // phyir na / / 'od gsal nyid 'byung ba'i bag la chags nas /
NK109(dze)001:4867: phyir yul med pa la mngon gsum du snang ma nus so //
NK109(dze)001:4868: zhes nying don dang po bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:4869: da ni yan lag gi don gnyis pa de yang
NK109(dze)001:4870: rkyen gyis 'khrul te las 'dzin pa'i snang ba ji
NK109(dze)001:4872: de ltar rang las byung ba ngo ma shes pa
NK109(dze)001:4873: la rgyu'i rkyen lus yod na bzhin yod pa ltar
NK109(dze)001:4874: byung la / de la yang ma rig pa gsum 'dus pa las song pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4875: de nyid yul du mar shar bas dmigs pa'i rkyen
NK109(dze)001:4876: zhes bzhin yod pas me long gi nang du shar
NK109(dze)001:4878: de gnyis la btags pas nga'i dang bdag gir bzung pas /
NK109(dze)001:4879: bdag po'i rkyen zhes dang yul can du rtog pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4880: de ltar gsum 'dus pas 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid gsum du smin par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:4881: de ma dag pa'i rkyen zhes grib ma rang las
NK109(dze)001:4882: byung bar ma shes pas na ma dag pa ste
NK109(dze)001:4883: / 'khrul pa rang las byung bar ma shes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4885: rang byung du ma shes te /
NK109(dze)001:4886: gzhan snang du bzung pas ma dag pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:4887: lus sems kyi 'brel snang ba de nyid las du mar byung zhing shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:4888: 'gro ba so so la snang ba de nyid yid kyi 'gyu ba rang 'byung du byung pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:4889: yul mi 'dra ba so so la re re snang
NK109(dze)001:4890: ba'i phyir na 'khrul pa'i snang ba zhes gang du
NK109(dze)001:4893: da ni nying lag gi don gsum pa de las
NK109(dze)001:4894: dngos po phyi snod kyi 'jig rten ji ltar byung
NK109(dze)001:4896: de ltar 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid kyi sa bon gyi cha smin pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4897: dngos su med pa la sa nam mkha' stong pa'i dal du gzugs med pa'i khams zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:4898: rnam shes bzung pa'i lus can 'byung ba'i cha sa bon da nga bcas par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:4899: de'i dus na rnam par yid gdangs pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha'/
NK109(dze)001:4900: kha dog dkar ba dkar ba'i 'od dang ldan pa
NK109(dze)001:4901: shin tu dkar ba las gling bzhi ri rab dang
NK109(dze)001:4902: bcas pa stong gsum gyi stong 'jig rten gyi khams
NK109(dze)001:4903: gcig gi snod rten par byed pa'i sa bon e
NK109(dze)001:4904: gru gsum rnam par gdangs pa'i nam mkhar chags so
NK109(dze)001:4905: // de lta bu'i nam mkha' de las rnam par
NK109(dze)001:4906: srubs byed kyi rlung zhes bya ba byi ba khra
NK109(dze)001:4907: mo'i kha rlangs tsam rab tu sngo ba la 'bur
NK109(dze)001:4909: kun tu khyab byed kyi rlung gis phyogs kun bdal bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:4910: mkha' la na bun 'khrigs pa ltar 'khrigs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4911: rtsub 'gyur gyi rlung zhes pa'i rang sgra yam zhes pa phyogs kun nas grags pas /
NK109(dze)001:4912: na bun 'khrigs pa de lta bu rab tu zhib
NK109(dze)001:4913: ste nam mkha' la sprin gtor ba ltar dum bur
NK109(dze)001:4914: song ngo // de nas rnam par sdud zhes chu'i
NK109(dze)001:4915: rlung zhes bya ba gser gyi rdo rje gyen la
NK109(dze)001:4916: langs pa 'dra bas gser gyi sgra byung pas /
NK109(dze)001:4917: de dag gcig tu bsdus te rdo rje'i dbyibs dang
NK109(dze)001:4918: 'dra bas 'dra bas rgya chen zhing spang sdug pa
NK109(dze)001:4920: de las smin byed me'i rlung zhes bya ba kha dog dmar la gsal ba'i me mched nas /
NK109(dze)001:4921: de dag bsregs pa las yam gyi dal 'jam zhig khod snyoms par chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4922: de nas 'byed byed rlung gi rlung zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:4923: kha dog sna tshogs pa phyogs kun sbud pa phu ba dang 'dra ba /
NK109(dze)001:4924: 'ur sgra dang bcas pas langs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4925: yang de dag so so gtor ro //
NK109(dze)001:4926: de nas srub byed kyis bsrubs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4927: grang zhing gseng ba'i sgra'u byung pas /
NK109(dze)001:4928: rlung dang sna tshogs rdo rje dang 'dra ba /
NK109(dze)001:4929: bum pa la rlung gi lha mo bzhis rlung gi ba dan 'dzin pa /
NK109(dze)001:4930: kha dog sna tshogs par 'od 'bar ba las /
NK109(dze)001:4931: las kyi mtha' smin par byed pa la dgongs te /
NK109(dze)001:4932: kha dog ljang gu in+d+ra n+ai la'i rnam pa dang
NK109(dze)001:4933: 'dra ba rgya che la spangs sdug pa chags pa
NK109(dze)001:4934: ni / nam mkha'i rlung gis 'degs pa'i stobs byas /
NK109(dze)001:4935: de nas chu'i rlung gis gcig tu bsdus te /
NK109(dze)001:4936: yar la mi 'phar ba'i gzungs byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4937: rdo rje'i rtse mo bzhi nas 'thabs pa'i rtsal lcags kyi phag mo bzhi 'phyang du stong /
NK109(dze)001:4938: me'i rlung gis smin cing ma 'dres par byas /
NK109(dze)001:4939: de nas rlung gis khod mnyams shing phan tshun du 'chug med par bsdams /
NK109(dze)001:4940: de'i steng sa'i rlung rab tu gang stong byed pa
NK109(dze)001:4941: zhes bya bas mnan nas sra zhing 'khregs pa'i las
NK109(dze)001:4943: de yang 'phags pa rnams kyis ni rlung gi dal de dag lnga'i bar bar na /
NK109(dze)001:4944: stobs ldan gyi nam mkha' re re yod pas mthong la /
NK109(dze)001:4945: nyan thos rnams kyi rdul phra rab tu bkod legs par mthong la /
NK109(dze)001:4946: rang sangs rgyas rnams kyis rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i yan lag dang bcas par mthong la /
NK109(dze)001:4947: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis rnam pa
NK109(dze)001:4948: can gyi rang bzhin du ma grub par gzigs so
NK109(dze)001:4949: // de yang rlung de'i rngams su sa ya gcig stong phrag brgyad /
NK109(dze)001:4950: rgyar sa ya bzhi dang 'bum phrag drug tu chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4951: de yang las kyi rtogs pa rlung la bslabs pas chod do //
NK109(dze)001:4952: rlung ga yul las su rung pa las sa ya bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:4953: drug 'bum gyi las kyi mtha' stongs par byed pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4954: de nas rlung gi dal de'i bum pa la mthar
NK109(dze)001:4955: 'byed rags pa'i rlung zhes bya ba dngul gyi rnam
NK109(dze)001:4956: par dang 'dra ba steng gi nam mkha' la g.yas
NK109(dze)001:4957: g.yon gang du yang mi 'pho bar langs pas /
NK109(dze)001:4958: nam mkha' nas bdud rtsi dag byed kyi chu zhes
NK109(dze)001:4959: bya ba'i thig pa yang dang yang du phab pa
NK109(dze)001:4960: las / rlung rdo rje rgya gram gyi bum pa'i nang gang pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4961: zhi ba gsal dag gi chu zhes pa'i rang bzhin
NK109(dze)001:4962: du kham gi sa bon las rab tu 'phel te
NK109(dze)001:4963: 'o ma'i rgya mtsho lta bu chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4964: de nas las dkrug me'i chu zhes bya ba phyogs
NK109(dze)001:4965: kun nas rab tu ldab pa'i sgra dang bcas pa
NK109(dze)001:4966: byung ste / chu gong ma rnams dkrugs pa las khrag gi rgya mtsho dmar mer gyis song ngo //
NK109(dze)001:4967: de yang phyogs kun nas 'dar ba'i sgra dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4968: de nas chu'i chu rab 'khod zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:4969: nam mkha' nas lo bdun gyi bar du babs pas
NK109(dze)001:4970: de dag mar khol ma ltar rab tu spangs mtho
NK109(dze)001:4972: de'i dus na chu'i lha mo gar byed pa dpag tu med pa dang bcas par chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4973: de nas chu'i rlung rnam par skyod byed zhes bya ba'i song ba'i sgra dang bcas pa langs pas /
NK109(dze)001:4974: chu de dag kyang dum bur dum bur song ste /
NK109(dze)001:4975: dngul chu'i thig pa ltar gyur te de yang rab tu 'tsheg pa'i sgra byung bas /
NK109(dze)001:4976: de dag gcig tu 'dres shing kha dog dngul las byung ba'i mdog lta bur gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:4977: phyogs kun nas rgya mtsho 'khrug par byed pa'i rlabs
NK109(dze)001:4978: kyis dbus su spungs pas chu'i sa rab tu spangs
NK109(dze)001:4979: mthong ba spel legs par gyur te gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:4980: de nas sa'i chu nam mkha' nas gser gyi char sil ma zhag bdun du babs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4981: chu de dag mnyam po ste /
NK109(dze)001:4982: legs par 'khrigs par chags pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4983: chu de dag kyang g.yang dang bral ba'i gser gyi kha dog dang 'dra ba chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4984: phyogs thams cad du rab tu mnyam pa'i rang bzhin du 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:4985: de yang kha dog ser ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:4988: kha dog gsal zhing yang pa de lta bu la /
NK109(dze)001:4989: dbyibs rab tu bzlum po zla ba nya gang pa dang 'dra bar chags so //
NK109(dze)001:4990: de yang rngams su dpag tshad 'bum phrag bcu gcig dang /
NK109(dze)001:4991: stong phrag nyi shu bar gyi skal pa nyi shu'i bar du 'jig rten chags pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:4992: rgyar dpag tshad sa ya gsum dang stong phrag lnga yod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:4993: 'jig rten pa'i las kyi mtha' rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:4994: de nas yun 'ga' zhig gi bar la bya ba dang byed pa gang yang med par gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:4995: de nas bar gyi bskal ba gcig na rlung gi
NK109(dze)001:4996: dal gyi 'og nas bsrub byed kyi rlung zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:4997: ba / rab tu gzir pa'i sgra dang ldan pa gcig langs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:4998: 'og ma nam mkha'i sa bon gyi dal rten pa'i e de yang rnam par ldog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5002: 'thug pa'i sgra dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:5003: rlung de nyid gser gyi rdo rje dpag tshad gnyis
NK109(dze)001:5004: kyi rgya khyon yod pa'i dang ldan pa gcig tu
NK109(dze)001:5005: gyur te / chu'i dal gyi steng du thal gyis song pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5006: 'og rlung gi dal thams cad kyang rab tu g.yos te /
NK109(dze)001:5009: shar dma' na nub mtho ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5010: nub mtho na shar dma' ba la sogs par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:5011: de nas de nyid thur la phog pas thal gyis byung pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5012: rlung dang chu la sogs pa thams cad gcig tu 'dres so //
NK109(dze)001:5013: de nas yang steng du 'phar ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5014: de dag so so gnas gnas su gyur to //
NK109(dze)001:5015: rdo rje de ni dper na lag na rdo rjes
NK109(dze)001:5016: rdo rje shin tu stobs dang ldan par 'phang pas
NK109(dze)001:5017: / gang la yang thog pa med pa ltar ci
NK109(dze)001:5018: la phog kyang thogs pa med pa dang 'dra bar
NK109(dze)001:5019: / / gang la yang zang thal du 'gro ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5020: de lan bzhi pa la chu dang rlung gi bar
NK109(dze)001:5021: du yid 'byed pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' dpag
NK109(dze)001:5022: tshad lnga stong spangs du yod par phye'o //
NK109(dze)001:5023: de nas lan lnga pa chu'i dal de dag gi phyogs kun dkrugs pas /
NK109(dze)001:5024: khyab med chu'i chu zhes bya ba rab tu 'dar ba'i sgra dang ldan par byung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5025: chu'i steng du 'o ma las spris ma byung ba
NK109(dze)001:5026: ltar gser gyi sa gzhi dpag tshad lnga stong par
NK109(dze)001:5027: chags so // de nas chags pa'i sa zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:5028: ba rdul 'phra rab dpag tu med pa phyogs rab
NK109(dze)001:5030: de'i steng du sa'i rdul gcig la gcig brten na sa chags pas /
NK109(dze)001:5031: de'i steng du smin par byed pa'i me zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:5032: bar rab tu bslabs pa'i sgra dang bcas pa phyogs
NK109(dze)001:5033: kun nas rlung langs rnam par dang 'dra ba byung
NK109(dze)001:5034: pa las / skal pa'i me dang 'dra ba phyogs thams cad du rab tu 'bar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5035: de nyid 'bar bas gong ma rnams bsregs so //
NK109(dze)001:5036: de nas me'i rdul bag chags gcig la gcig chags pas dpag tshad 'bum phrag gnyis su chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5037: de nas 'byed pa'i rlung zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:5038: dper na rgya mtsho las rlangs pa byung pa ltar tu phyung pa dang ldan pa byung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5039: steng gi nam mkha' nas rlung gi rdul phra rab grangs med pa bas te /
NK109(dze)001:5040: dper na bar snang las kha ba babs pa'i rnam
NK109(dze)001:5041: pa dang 'dra ba gcig la gcig chags su babs
NK109(dze)001:5042: pas / sngar gyi rdul phran de dag kyang rab
NK109(dze)001:5043: tu 'khrugs shing g.yo ba dang ldan par gyur te
NK109(dze)001:5044: pas / / de nyid dpag tshad 'bum phrag gcig tu chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5045: de nas gseng byed pa'i nam mkha' zhes bya ba
NK109(dze)001:5046: sngo ba la g.yu'i barlangasa dang 'dra ba langs pa
NK109(dze)001:5047: las / nam mkha' nas nam mkha'i rdul phran dpag tu med pa bab pas /
NK109(dze)001:5048: sngar gyi rdul 'phra rab de dag rab tu 'khrugs te /
NK109(dze)001:5049: de dag gi bar bar du rdul re re shong ba'i nam mkhar byas so //
NK109(dze)001:5050: de nas gnod byed pa'i sa zhes bya ba 'brug sngon po gyen la langs dang 'dra ba'i dbyibs /
NK109(dze)001:5051: phyogs kun tu 'phar ba las de dag rab tu 'khrigs te /
NK109(dze)001:5052: rang bzhin gyi byed pa'i las kyi rgya mtsho la
NK109(dze)001:5053: dar chags pa dang 'dra ba dal zhing khod snyoms
NK109(dze)001:5054: pa / dbyibs gru bzhi pa 'bum phrag gcig tu chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5055: sa'i dal de dag ni dbyibs gru bzhi pa /
NK109(dze)001:5056: zur bzhi na sa'i lha mo gser gyi bum pa thogs pa bzhis bzung ba /
NK109(dze)001:5057: logs bzhi klu'i bu rab tu stobs dang ldan pa bzhis lag pas bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5058: sa'i las brtan pa dag g.yo bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5059: de yang dpang du rdul 'phra rab rnams 'bum phrag bzhi dang khri phrag gcig /
NK109(dze)001:5060: bar gyi nam mkha' la de snyed de 'bum phrag brgyad dang khri phrag gnyis so //
NK109(dze)001:5061: srid du ni sa ya gnyis dang stong phrag lngas srid pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5062: 'byung ba'i las so sor byed pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5063: 'byung ba'i dal de dag kyang mchod rten bang rim
NK109(dze)001:5064: dang 'dra bar gcig la gcig brten du chags so
NK109(dze)001:5065: // mdo nas ni de dag gi bar nas yang
NK109(dze)001:5066: gong ma'i dpag tshad gcig tsam yod pas bar mtshams
NK109(dze)001:5067: bcad nas yod par bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:5068: bkod pa chen po 'jig rten bkod pa'i le'u nas
NK109(dze)001:5069: chu dang sa'i bar na yang nam mkha' yid skyob
NK109(dze)001:5070: pa zhes bya ba dpag tshad lnga stong gis btegs
NK109(dze)001:5072: nam mkha' de'i dbus na me'i dal dpag tshad rngams
NK109(dze)001:5073: su stong phrag gcig pa srid du 'bum phrag lnga
NK109(dze)001:5074: pa gcig kha dog dmar ba'i 'od da nga ldan
NK109(dze)001:5075: pa gcig /'byung ba spyi mthun gyis smin par byed
NK109(dze)001:5076: pa'i las su yod par bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:5077: de yang sa'i chus khyab pa'i las byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5078: 'gro ba'i las kyi bye brag ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5079: sa'i mes smin par byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5080: 'gro ba'i lus kyi kha dog gsal pa yin /
NK109(dze)001:5081: sa'i rlung gis rdul 'phra rab tu byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5082: 'gro ba dbang po rdzogs par byed pa yin /
NK109(dze)001:5083: sa'i nam mkhas par phye ba'i las byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5084: 'gro ba'i sems gnas par byed pa yin /
NK109(dze)001:5085: sa'i sas gnas par byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5086: 'gro ba'i las bsod nams ston par byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5087: 'di dag kun la don rtags kyis bshad pa ni gzhan nas bstan pa yod do //
NK109(dze)001:5088: de nas snod kyi bcud la skyabs pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5089: de nas yang 'og nas smin pa las kyi rlung
NK109(dze)001:5090: zhes bya ba gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang
NK109(dze)001:5091: ldan pa rang bzhin myur pa'i stobs dang ldan pa
NK109(dze)001:5092: gcig gis sa dang chu'i dal thams cad dkrugs pa
NK109(dze)001:5093: las / dper na 'o ma'i zho bsrubs pas mar dang 'khrogs pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:5094: dngul gyi snyigs ma gser du 'gyur te lci bas
NK109(dze)001:5095: gting du song nas dwangs ma sa'i rdul la sogs
NK109(dze)001:5097: dbus kyi ri rab dpag tshad brgyad khri dang bzhi stong /
NK109(dze)001:5098: thur du sa'i dal la yang de snyed zug pa /
NK109(dze)001:5100: 'og ma rlung gi bang rim gi bang rim g.yu'i rdo rje can zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:5102: de'i steng la chu las grub pa'i bang rim pad+ma rnam par spungs pa zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:5103: shel las grub pa rang bzhin gyis 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5104: de'i steng ma'i bang rim 'khor lo rnam par brtsegs pa zhes bya ba gser las grub pa /
NK109(dze)001:5105: skabs su gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong pa rab
NK109(dze)001:5106: tu 'phra ba rdul 'phra rab dang 'dra ba 'phros
NK109(dze)001:5107: pas / 'gro ba rnams la bde ba dang mi
NK109(dze)001:5108: bde ba'i rnam pa rnams kyi las kyi bye brag
NK109(dze)001:5110: de'i steng na rin po che rab tu 'od 'bar
NK109(dze)001:5111: ba zhes bya ba'i bang rim 'byung ba me las
NK109(dze)001:5112: grub pa / bye ru'i rgyu las byung pa /
NK109(dze)001:5113: de las me'i 'od rab tu 'bar ba /
NK109(dze)001:5114: des ni 'gro ba'i char 'bab pa dang mi 'bab pa'i las kyi mtha' ston par byed pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:5115: de la gcog lnga yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5117: so so'i 'dod pa'i lha dang bcas pa /
NK109(dze)001:5119: gling phran brgyad de bcu gnyis dang /
NK109(dze)001:5120: bkod pa ni gling nyi shur bshad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5122: ro so so dang ldan pa'i mtsho bdun dang /
NK109(dze)001:5123: mtha' lcags ri nag po dang ldan pa chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5124: 'dzam bu gling gi byang phyogs na /
NK109(dze)001:5125: gnya' shing 'dzin la sogs pa'i ri bdun po de la /
NK109(dze)001:5126: gnod sbyin chen po gser rkang dang /
NK109(dze)001:5132: mchog srid dang bdun gyi khang bu so so'i 'khor dang bcas pa'i gnas yod de /
NK109(dze)001:5133: de dag rnams kyis 'dzam bu'i gling du mi'i nad dang /
NK109(dze)001:5137: mu ge la sogs pa'i legs nyes su byed pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5138: de dag gi 'khor na bsreg byed kyi ma mo bdun gnas pas byed do //
NK109(dze)001:5139: de dag gi bar gyi mtsho bdun po de'i nang
NK109(dze)001:5140: na klu chen po brgyad kyi pho brang rang rang
NK109(dze)001:5141: gi 'khor dang bcas pa gnas te /
NK109(dze)001:5142: 'dzam bu gling du char che ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5143: chung pa'i las kyi bye brag rnams ni klu'i rgyal po de dag gis byed pa yin no //
NK109(dze)001:5144: ri rab kyi bang rim gru bzhi ni 'degs dus
NK109(dze)001:5145: kyi gnod sbyin rab tu stobs dang ldan pa'i pho
NK109(dze)001:5146: brang gnas te / 'di dag gis ni dbyar dgun ston dpyid du 'byed pa'i las byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5147: rlung gi lha mo la sogs pa'i 'gro ba 'di dag ni /
NK109(dze)001:5148: srid pa las kyi 'gro ba zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:5149: snod kyi mtshan nyid nye bar ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5150: de yang gnas pa ni dang po chags pa dang mnyam zhing /
NK109(dze)001:5151: tha ma 'jig pa dang mnyam mo //
NK109(dze)001:5152: de ltar bar gyi skal ba nyi shu'i bar la chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5153: da ga nas pa yang de tsam mo //
NK109(dze)001:5154: 'jig pa la yang de snyed do //
NK109(dze)001:5155: de ltar bar gyi bskal pa drug cu la yun gyi bskal pa gcig go /
NK109(dze)001:5156: yun gyi bskal pa drug cu la dus matha'i gcig /
NK109(dze)001:5157: dus matha'i drug cu la bskal pa chen po gcig yin no //
NK109(dze)001:5158: de la bar gyi bskal pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5159: dang po 'gro ba'i tshe lo dpag tu med pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5160: lo brgya brgyas lo re mar bri ba'i rtsis kyis /
NK109(dze)001:5161: tha ma tshe lo bcu pa la thug pa de
NK109(dze)001:5162: las yang yar brgya brgyas lo re la yar 'phel
NK109(dze)001:5163: bas / dpag tu med pa la thug pa /
NK109(dze)001:5165: mar bri ba'i nyi shu bar gyi bskal pa gcig yin no //
NK109(dze)001:5166: de ni snod kyi 'jig rten gyi chags lugs te /
NK109(dze)001:5167: nang lus chags pa yang de dang sgo 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:5168: theg pa chung ngu nas de ltar ma yin par
NK109(dze)001:5169: bshad pa yang 'dug go /'di ltar ni dpag bsam
NK109(dze)001:5170: gyi ljon shing rgyas pa'i rgyud las zhib tu bshad
NK109(dze)001:5171: do // de dag dkyus dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)001:5172: mkha' la nam mkha' stong pa ci'i ngo bor yang
NK109(dze)001:5173: ma grub pa las rang bzhin du 'byung ba'i byed
NK109(dze)001:5174: pa'i las kyis e la sogs pa gong du bshad
NK109(dze)001:5175: / de steng du rlung zhes bya ba'i spyi'i chos bzhi 'og nas chags dang zhes pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:5177: 'byung bar byed pa'i dus na rdul 'phra rab brten cing chags pa'i las kyang rlung gis byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5178: chung phung po yang chags par byed do //
NK109(dze)001:5179: nang lus kyi dus na yang lus chags pa'i brten rlung gis byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5180: de la sems chags pa'i rten kyang /
NK109(dze)001:5182: tha ma lus 'jig pa'i dus na rlung la brten
NK109(dze)001:5183: pa'i nyams su myong ba sems la 'chags par byed
NK109(dze)001:5184: pa'o // de yang 'jig rten chags pa'i dus na 'byung ba rnams rlung gis sdud par byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5185: nang lus kyi dus na yang rgyu rkyen sems dang
NK109(dze)001:5186: bcas pa gcig tu bsdus nas 'gro bar grub par
NK109(dze)001:5188: dang po rlung gis nam mkha' skyod pa'i las byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5189: nang lus kyi dus na 'gro ba'i las kyi bye brag rnams 'phen pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5191: 'degs pa'o ni phyi'i dus na rdo rje rgya gram gyis chu 'degs la /
NK109(dze)001:5192: lus kyi dus na 'gro ba'i lus kyi stobs bskyed cing rtsa'i 'khor lo 'degs par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5193: de la gang brten na chu'i dal brten pa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:5194: nang lus kyang rlung la brten pa yin pas rlung
NK109(dze)001:5195: gi byed pa'i las 'gyur na phung po 'jig go
NK109(dze)001:5196: / phyi'i dus de la chu ni dbye na khyab pa ni rlung gi dal la khyab ste /
NK109(dze)001:5198: mchod rten gyi bang rim dang 'dra bar khyab po
NK109(dze)001:5199: lus kyi dus na khrag gis lus mgo 'jug tu
NK109(dze)001:5200: khyab pas lus kyi gzugs byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5201: 'dzin pa dang ni sa'i dal 'dzin pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5202: lcags kyu'i rnam pa dang 'dra bas bzung pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5203: lus kyi dus na khrag gis 'gro ba'i srog 'dzin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5204: smin byed dang ni gser gyi sa gzhi las gzugs rdul 'phra rab du bsdus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5205: lus kyi dus na khrag gis dwangs ma las dbang
NK109(dze)001:5206: po la sogs pa so sor smin par byas pa
NK109(dze)001:5208: 'bum phrag bcu gcig dag gis grangs bstan pa /
NK109(dze)001:5210: 'o ma las mar chags pa'i dpe bstan /
NK109(dze)001:5211: sa ni 'bum phrag gi grangs bstan gong ma'i rlung
NK109(dze)001:5212: rngams su ye shes dang 'bum phrag drug bstan theg
NK109(dze)001:5214: srid du grangs med pa bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:5215: gong ma ni blo'i bye brag las dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5216: sa ni bsgrub par byed pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5217: dang po gser gyi barlangasa pa tsam las gser gyi gzhi grub la /
NK109(dze)001:5218: lus kyi dus na shes gzugs kyi phung por bsgrub par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5219: 'phra ba dang ni phyi dus na rdul 'phra rab tu byed la /
NK109(dze)001:5220: nang gi dus na yang sha la brten nas shes pa'i rtsal sbyong bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5221: rag pa nyid dang ni ri rab la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:5222: rdul phra rab 'dus pa las gzugs kyi rnam par
NK109(dze)001:5223: phye la / nang gi dus na phung po lnga'i
NK109(dze)001:5224: chos 'tshogs pa la brten nas lus su grub cing
NK109(dze)001:5226: de gsum ni don gyis 'gro ba gcig gis lus la lus ngag yid gsum 'dus pa yin no //
NK109(dze)001:5227: bkrog nas mar log pa'i gling dang ri rab kyi chags lugs gzhan du bshad pas 'dir mi spro'o //
NK109(dze)001:5228: zhes nying don gsum pa de las dngos po phyi
NK109(dze)001:5229: snod kyi 'jig rten ji ltar byung ba bstan nas
NK109(dze)001:5230: / da ni nying don bzhi pa de la brten
NK109(dze)001:5231: nas nang bcud kyi sems can ji ltar chags pa
NK109(dze)001:5232: / bstan pa ni / de la gzugs med kyang zhes pa /
NK109(dze)001:5233: de ltar chags nas kyang bar gyi bskal pa gcig tu stong pa cang med pa /
NK109(dze)001:5234: ri dang ri phran rnams la shing rigs mi 'dra ba mang po yod pa /
NK109(dze)001:5235: lung pa so so rnams kyang shing nags dang ljag ma'i gling du yod par gnas pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5236: nam mkha' nas bdud rtsi'i char bab pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5238: rin po che'i shing sna tshogs pad+ma'i rang bzhin du smin par byas te /
NK109(dze)001:5239: de la gang gi 'jig rten srid pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa de dag gi yid zhugs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5240: pad+ma'i gsung sgra dbyangs phyogs kun tu 'phros pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5241: snang ba zang thal du 'gro ba rnam shes mtha' yas pa'i gzugs /
NK109(dze)001:5242: res yod pa ltar snang la /
NK109(dze)001:5243: res med pa ltar yang snang la /
NK109(dze)001:5245: 'gro ba de dag kyang pad+ma rnam par brtsegs pa'i nam mkha' la brten nas gnas te /
NK109(dze)001:5246: de dag las dpag tu med pa mched pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5247: yod min med min gyi skye mched zhes bya bar brtags so //
NK109(dze)001:5248: de yang nam mkha' la yid las skye la /
NK109(dze)001:5250: res med par mched pas yod min med min gyi skye mched du brtags so //
NK109(dze)001:5251: de nas 'gro ba de dag dga' ba de la longs spyod mtha' yas pa la spyod pas te /
NK109(dze)001:5252: sems dpa'i don du dpa' bar 'gro ba'i zhes bya'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5253: de'i 'og na yid rnam par rol pa'i 'khor lo can zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' la /
NK109(dze)001:5254: gser gyi rdo rje chen po gcig gyen la blangs te /
NK109(dze)001:5255: 'od zer brgya phrag du mas yongs su bskor ba can gcig yod do //
NK109(dze)001:5256: de shin tu mdzes par rab tu dpa' ba'i nyams dang ldan te /
NK109(dze)001:5257: gong ma'i 'gro ba de dag nam mkha' la ting nge 'dzin gyis btegs nas 'gro la /
NK109(dze)001:5258: de'i rjes la 'og ma'i rab tu dpa' ba'i rdo
NK109(dze)001:5259: rje mdzes shing sdug pa tsam du lta bas dpa'
NK109(dze)001:5260: bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5261: rdo rje de la yid rab tu g.yos pas /
NK109(dze)001:5262: 'gro ba de dag gi rnam pa tsam las skyes
NK109(dze)001:5263: pa'i 'gro ba de dag las 'ga' tsam theg pa
NK109(dze)001:5265: gong gi dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin yal
NK109(dze)001:5266: nas ci yang med do zhes brjod pa gong ma
NK109(dze)001:5267: bas 'du shes tsam du las gzhan mi byed par
NK109(dze)001:5268: gnas pa las 'gro ba dpag tu med par mched
NK109(dze)001:5269: de / ci yang med zhes kyang bya /
NK109(dze)001:5270: cung zad med zhes kyang bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:5271: gong ma bas lus bong chung zhing 'od mdangs kyang chung ba /
NK109(dze)001:5272: gong ma'i ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i stobs kyis nyon mongs
NK109(dze)001:5273: pa ni cung zad tsam las mi gnas pas cung
NK109(dze)001:5274: zad zhes bya / ci yang zhes bya ba med par gnas te /
NK109(dze)001:5275: gong ma las skyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5276: de las mched pas skye mched zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5277: 'gro ba de dag kyang nyon mongs pa ni bag la nyal ba tsam las med /
NK109(dze)001:5278: tshe lo la sogs pa ni klong drug pa'i skabs su ston no //
NK109(dze)001:5279: 'di dag ni rin po che za ma tog zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5280: de'i dus na de nas dpag tshad stong phrag sum cu'i 'og na /
NK109(dze)001:5281: yid byed rnam par rol pa zhes bya ba'i nam
NK109(dze)001:5282: mkha' 'khor lo dpag tu med pa 'phro zhing gcig
NK109(dze)001:5283: la gcig 'phrad pa'i sgra 'byung pa yod de /
NK109(dze)001:5284: der 'og ma'i 'gro ba de dag ting nge 'dzin
NK109(dze)001:5285: zhi gnas phyogs gcig tu song pa las 'og tu
NK109(dze)001:5287: gcig la gcig rnam par shes pa tsam las /
NK109(dze)001:5288: 'gyur ba yid kyi sbyor ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5289: 'gro ba de dag mang por mched pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5290: rnam pa yul 'khor la 'jig pa shes pa tsam las bdag tu rtog pa tsam /
NK109(dze)001:5291: mtha' shes pa tsam yas te /
NK109(dze)001:5292: bsdu ba'i dngos po med pa /
NK109(dze)001:5293: de dag las skyes nas 'gro ba'i gzugs mtha' yas par mched pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5294: rnam shes mtha' yas kyi skye mched zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5295: de dag kyang gong ma bas tshe tshad thung zhing /
NK109(dze)001:5296: lus bong chung zhing 'od mdangs mi gsal pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5297: bsod nams kyi stobs nyams pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:5298: de dag gi 'og dpag tshad stong phrag gnyis na
NK109(dze)001:5299: sprin chen po rnam par rol pa'i nam mkha' zhes
NK109(dze)001:5300: bya ba sprin kha dog sna tshogs pa'i dum bu
NK109(dze)001:5301: bar bar du brlabs pa yod de /
NK109(dze)001:5302: der gong ma'i 'gro ba de dag thig pa'i tshul du bab pa las //
NK109(dze)001:5303: yang nam mkha' sprin gyis dum bu dum bur song pa la shes pa mched pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5304: 'gro ba mang po dpag tu med par mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5305: de nas nam mkha' mtha' yas pa'i skye mched zhes bya bar btags so //
NK109(dze)001:5306: 'di dag bzhi yang snang ba 'od kyi gzugs med par rnam par shes pa tsam la gnas /
NK109(dze)001:5307: 'byung ba sha khrag gi lus med pas rnam shes tsam por gnas /
NK109(dze)001:5308: 'gyur ba yid kyi lus med pas shes pa nang du gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5309: myong reg sdug bsngal gyi lus med pas dga' ba dang bde bar gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5310: des na gzugs med pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5311: khams ni de dag rnams 'dus 'tshogs pa las so //
NK109(dze)001:5312: de dag las nam mkha' mtha' yas sems rnam par 'phros pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5313: de 'og dpag tshad stong phrag nyi shu na /
NK109(dze)001:5314: rin po che 'ching bu rnam par bkod pa'i sa gzhi la /
NK109(dze)001:5315: phyi nang med par zang thal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5316: phan tshun yan man yang rlung gis bskyod cing 'gro ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5317: der shes pa dum bur chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5318: snang ba 'od du snang ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5319: sngar gyi shes pa yas gcig tu gyur pa las
NK109(dze)001:5320: 'od kyi lus kha mig rna bar ldan pa kun
NK109(dze)001:5322: dpag tu med par mched de /
NK109(dze)001:5325: 'phyo ba la sogs pa yang 'od dang rlung gis byed do //
NK109(dze)001:5326: 'gro ba de dag gi gnas ni gong ma gzugs
NK109(dze)001:5327: med rnams las 'og tu gyur pa las 'og min
NK109(dze)001:5328: zhes bya ste / gong ma las 'og /
NK109(dze)001:5329: gzhan las gong du gyur pas mi zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5334: gzhal yas khang la sogs pa gzhan nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:5335: de yang gong rnam par shes pa tsam las lus med pa /
NK109(dze)001:5336: 'dir ni rnam par shes pa la phyi 'od kyi lus su grub pas gzugs so //
NK109(dze)001:5338: ri mo'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar yod pas na gzugs zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5339: de yang rgyu'i gzugs yod la /
NK109(dze)001:5340: 'bras bu'i gzugs bcu gcig la sogs pa dngos su med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5341: gong ma'i shes pa'i dbang gis so //
NK109(dze)001:5342: de'i 'og na rin po che 'thon mthing gi rnam par spras pa'i nam mkha' yod de /
NK109(dze)001:5343: der gong ma'i 'gro ba'i shes pa'i bag yal ba lhung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5344: de las 'gro ba dpag tu med par mched pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5345: shin tu mthong ba zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba /
NK109(dze)001:5346: gcig la gcig mthong na dga' ba yod pas mthong na dga' ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5349: tshe dang 'od la sogs pa chung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5350: de'i 'og tu rin po che rab mdzes kyi gzhi la /
NK109(dze)001:5351: gong ma las gya nom snang ba zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5352: 'di dag la yang gang las byung ba dang ci
NK109(dze)001:5353: las grub pa la sogs pa 'dug ste 'dir ma
NK109(dze)001:5354: bris so // de la gong ma la gya nom par 'dod pas gya nom pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5355: de'i 'og tu ring po che ze rmug gu'i nam mkha' las mi gdung ba'i 'gro bar 'byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5356: de'i 'og tu rin po che shel gyi khang bu
NK109(dze)001:5357: brtsegs ba'i nam mkha' la mi che ba zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:5358: bar 'gro ba dpag tu med par chags so //
NK109(dze)001:5359: gong ma'i mi gdung pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5360: snang ba dga' bde'i snang ba cir shar yang de
NK109(dze)001:5361: la gdung pa med pas na mi gdung ba zhes
NK109(dze)001:5362: bya'o // de las gdung ba mi che bas mi che ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5363: de'i 'og na rin po che rab mdzes kyis rnam par brdal ba na /
NK109(dze)001:5364: yang gong ma'i lha 'ga' lhung ba las 'bras bu
NK109(dze)001:5365: che ba zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med
NK109(dze)001:5367: 'di dag ni las dge ba'i 'bras bu che ba las byung pa sha stag go /
NK109(dze)001:5368: des 'bras bu che ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5369: de'i 'og na rin po che ka li mdog mdzes
NK109(dze)001:5370: kyis rnam par spras pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha'
NK109(dze)001:5371: yod de / der yang gong ma las thig pa'i rnam pa ltar 'gro ba 'ga' chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5372: bsod nams skyes zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba rnams byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5373: de dag ni sngar bsod nams kyi dpag tu med pa bsags pa las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5374: 'dis kyang bsod nams kyi tshogs dga' bde las skyes pa de bsod nams skyes zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5375: de'i 'og na rin po che sprin rnam par stug pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' yod do //
NK109(dze)001:5376: der gong ma'i 'gro ba rnams chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5377: sprin med 'od zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5378: de yang dal 'jam 'gro tshad dang ldan pa sprin
NK109(dze)001:5379: med pa'i nyi ma'i rnam pa dang 'dra bas na
NK109(dze)001:5382: de'i 'og na rin po che'i 'od rnam par 'byin
NK109(dze)001:5383: pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' la yang sprin med
NK109(dze)001:5385: tshad med dge ba zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5386: de dag ni dge ba'i rtsa ba tshad med la spyod pas tshad med dge zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5387: de'i 'og na rin po che in dra ni la
NK109(dze)001:5388: las grub pa'i rnam par spras pa zhes bya ba'i
NK109(dze)001:5389: nam mkha' la / yang tshad med dge ba'i 'gro
NK109(dze)001:5390: ba dge ba'i bag las yangs pa 'ga' chad pa
NK109(dze)001:5391: nam mkha' la / las / dge rgyas zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5392: 'di dag ni gong ma las dge ba rgyas pa
NK109(dze)001:5393: tsam la spyod la spyod pas na dge rgyas zhes
NK109(dze)001:5394: bya'o // de'i 'og na rin po che pa tang
NK109(dze)001:5395: ka ling gis rnam par spras pa'i nam mkha' la
NK109(dze)001:5396: bya'o // / dge ba rgyas pa'i bag yal ba'i 'gro ba 'ga' chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5397: dge chung zhes pa'i 'gro ba bsam gyis mi khyab par mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5398: de yang gong ma bas bag dge ba'i cha chung bas na dge chung zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5399: de'i 'og na nor bu ke ke ru las rnam
NK109(dze)001:5400: par spras pa'i nam mkha' la zhes bya ba las
NK109(dze)001:5401: / gong ma'i dge ba chung ngo snyam pa'i bar la 'gro ba 'ga' lhung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5402: tshad med 'od zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5403: 'di dag ni rang gi lus la 'od tshad med pa yod pas tshad med 'od zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5404: de'i 'og na rin po che dpal brtsegs pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' la /
NK109(dze)001:5405: gong ma'i 'od rnam par 'khrugs pa las 'gro ba 'ga' mched pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5406: 'od gsal zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5407: de yang 'od gsal ba 'ba' zhig la spyod pas 'od gsal zhes bya'o //
