NK109(dze)001:5408: de'i 'og na rin po che dpa' ba'i 'od ces bya ba'i nam mkha' la /
NK109(dze)001:5409: gong ma'i 'od gsal las 'gro ba 'ga' chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5410: 'od chung zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5411: gong ma bas 'od chung bas 'od chung zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5412: de'i 'og na rin po che ma ki zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' la /
NK109(dze)001:5413: gong ma'i 'od mdangs yal ba las 'ga' chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5414: tshangs pa 'dun na 'don zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med par mched /
NK109(dze)001:5415: de yang de dag re re'i 'dun na kha don
NK109(dze)001:5416: 'don pa re re yod pas 'dun na 'don zhes
NK109(dze)001:5417: bya'o // de'i 'og na rin po che rab tu si ka ta zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' la /
NK109(dze)001:5418: gong ma'i 'don pa'i rtsar 'gro ba 'ga' chad pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5419: tshangs pa zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med par mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5420: de yang dge ba la tshangs bar spyod pas na tshangs pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5421: 'di dag la lus kyi tshad dang /
NK109(dze)001:5425: gnas dang snang ba ji ltar snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5426: snga ma las ci las byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5427: phyi ma gang du skye ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5428: re re'i gzhal yas khang gi tshad la sogs pa ni gzhan na bstan nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:5429: de dag ni gzugs kyi khams zhes bya ste gzugs ni 'od dang gzugs la sogs spyod pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5430: khams na mang po 'tshogs shing 'dus pa la bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5431: gong mas ni 'od dang gzugs brnyan la mi spyod pas gzugs med ces bya la /
NK109(dze)001:5432: 'og rnams ni de nyid la spyod pas na gzugs kyi khams so //
NK109(dze)001:5433: 'di dag la rigs mi 'dra ba bcu bdun du byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5434: las kyi bsags pa'i khyad par las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5435: de la 'og tu 'dod pa'i khams zhes bya ba chags te /
NK109(dze)001:5436: de yang gong ma'i longs spyod la 'dod pas na 'dod khams zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5437: de ltar 'dod kyang las kyis bsags pa'i khyad kyis thob pa ni med la /
NK109(dze)001:5438: yid la 'dod pa ni 'di dag mngon par shes pa'i cha yod pas mthong ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5439: de'i 'og na dpag bsam gyi shing rin po che
NK109(dze)001:5440: rab tu rgyas pa las gong ma'i tshangs pa'i sems
NK109(dze)001:5442: sngon gyis bsags pa'i khyad kyis lhung ba las gzhan
NK109(dze)001:5443: 'phrul dbang byed zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu
NK109(dze)001:5445: de yang lus gzhan las sprul pa tsam las byung bas na /
NK109(dze)001:5446: gzhan 'phrul dbang gzhan la byed pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5447: 'di dag la tshe tshad la sogs pa gzhan nas bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:5448: de'i 'og na dpag bsam gyi shing mthong mdzes zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:5449: gong ma'i 'gro ba de dag 'ga' lhung pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5450: 'phrul dga' zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5451: de yang rang lus kyi 'od las bu stong ngam
NK109(dze)001:5452: bargya'am dpag tu med pa sprul pa las dga' bas
NK109(dze)001:5454: de'i 'og tu dpag bsam gyi shing dmigs mdzes zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:5455: gong ma'i 'gro ba de dag 'ga' lhung pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5456: dga' ldan zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5457: de yang dga' ba dang ldan pa 'ba' zhig la spyod pas na dga' ldan zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5458: de'i 'og tu dpag bsam gyi shing yid 'gyur ba zhes pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5460: 'thab bral zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med pa mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5461: de yang 'thab bral zhes bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5462: lha min dang 'thab pa med pas na 'thab bral zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5463: de'i 'og tu dpag bsam gyi shing yongs 'du sa btol zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:5464: mtha' bral gyi 'gro ba 'ga' ltung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5465: yang sum cu rtsa gsum pa zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5466: de yang sum cu rtsa gsum zhes bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5467: shing de la glang po che rab tu brtan zhes bya ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5468: gser zho sum cu rtsa gnyis g.yu gcig dang sum cu rtsa gsum yod pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5469: lha'i dbang po brgya byin zhes bya ba sras dang bcas pas na /
NK109(dze)001:5470: sum cu rtsa gsum pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5471: de'i 'og tu ri rab kyi steng du sna cog rnams la /
NK109(dze)001:5472: gong ma las ltung ba'i gnas su gyur pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5473: rgyal chen rigs bzhi zhes bya ba'i 'gro ba dpag tu med par mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5474: 'di dag ni 'og ma'i gling bzhi'i sa bon du gyur pas na /
NK109(dze)001:5475: mi las rgyal la rigs bzhi yod pas na /
NK109(dze)001:5476: rgyal chen rigs bzhi pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5477: de dag ni rigs drug las 'gro ba lha'i rigs zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5478: lha zhes bya ba ste mdzes shing 'od dang ldan pas na lha zhes bya ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5479: de yang khams gsum ga lha la tshang pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:5480: snga ma las lus ngag yid kyi dge ba brtson pa las byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5481: de nas de'i 'og tu bsod nams kyang bgas kyis
NK109(dze)001:5482: bri ste lus kyi 'od la sogs pa yang yang
NK109(dze)001:5484: tshe lo yang rim gyis bri nas /
NK109(dze)001:5485: 'dod pa khams kyi bye brag gong sa las dpag tshad stong bzhi khri'i 'og na /
NK109(dze)001:5486: dga' ldan brtsegs pa zhes bya ba'i yul na /
NK109(dze)001:5487: nyi ma dang zla ba la sogs pa'i snang ba ni med /
NK109(dze)001:5488: rang snang tsam las med do //
NK109(dze)001:5489: snang ba thams cad rab tu mdzes pa'i pad+mas spras pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5491: pad+ma las rdzus skyes kyi tshul du byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5492: gong ma'i 'od kyi mdangs yod pa'i bsod nams kyis /
NK109(dze)001:5493: 'od kyi snang ba rab tu gsal ba las spyod pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5494: de gnyis kyi yid rnam par g.yos pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5495: rdzus skyes kyi lha'i bu 'ga' tsam mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5496: de dag kyang mthong na dga' ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5497: 'gro ba bde ba tsam la spyod do //
NK109(dze)001:5498: 'gro ba de dag 'gro na nam mkha' la 'gro
NK109(dze)001:5499: ba ni gong ma'i lha gnas las skyes pas so
NK109(dze)001:5500: // 'dug na yang nam mkha' la 'dug pa ni lus 'od las byung bas so //
NK109(dze)001:5501: de nas 'gro ba de dag ni rang gi 'od la 'dus cing /
NK109(dze)001:5502: zas su dga' ba dang bde ba za ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5503: gong mar zas gos la longs spyod pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5504: 'gro bar 'dod kyang bsam pa tsam gyis phyin pa na /
NK109(dze)001:5505: gong ma'i ting nge 'dzin las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5506: tshe yang dpag tu med pa thub bo //
NK109(dze)001:5507: nyon mongs pa mngon du rgyu ni med /
NK109(dze)001:5508: bde ba la 'ba' zhig tu gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5509: 'di nang 'gro ba de dag 'dul ba'i ston pa
NK109(dze)001:5510: drug pa rdo rje 'chang khyad par las kyi stong
NK109(dze)001:5511: pa de gnas de nyid nas pad+ma rab du mdzes
NK109(dze)001:5512: pa 'dab ma stong dang ldan pa /
NK109(dze)001:5513: sbugs yang shing mdzes pa la rdzus nas skye ba'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5514: gzigs stangs gsum las byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:5515: 'gro ba de dag la 'gro ba 'dul ba'i spyan gyis gzigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:5516: gong ma'i lha'i bu de gnyis zla ba dri ma med par zhes bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5517: nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed pa zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:5518: ba byung ba ni thabs dang shes rab la brten
NK109(dze)001:5519: nas 'gro ba 'dul ba'i ston pa byung ba'i rtags
NK109(dze)001:5520: so // de nas snang ba 'dul byed kyi spyan gyis pad+ma la gzigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:5521: nam mkha' nas 'byung ba tsha grang gi rang sgra
NK109(dze)001:5522: la mi snang ngo zhes bya ba lan gsum du
NK109(dze)001:5523: byung bas / 'gro ba de kyang mi zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:5524: ba thog ma lus kyang 'byung ba sha khrag las
NK109(dze)001:5526: skabs su gong ma'i 'od la brten nas zang thal du snang la /
NK109(dze)001:5527: 'dod chags la sogs pa mngon du rgyu med pas dbang po lnga dang /
NK109(dze)001:5528: yan lag la sogs pa rab tu mdzes par ldan la /
NK109(dze)001:5529: pho mo'i dbang po'i sgo ni ma dod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5530: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis bstan pa la gzigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:5531: bstan pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba sgra thal 'gyur chen po zhes bya ba byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5532: de'i dus na nam mkha' la 'od kyi skar ma 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:5533: 'od kyi yang zhun bcu bdun dang bcas par snang ngo /
NK109(dze)001:5534: de nas 'gro ba yang mang du 'phel /
NK109(dze)001:5536: lus kya 'od la sogs pa yang yal /
NK109(dze)001:5537: bsod nams kyang chung du song /
NK109(dze)001:5538: sngon gyi las kyi dbang gis nyon mongs pa yang bgas kyis langs te /
NK109(dze)001:5539: bde ba'i dus na de dag las shar lus 'phags kyi gling du gnyis chad pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5540: lus 'phags gling pa'i 'gro ba rnams rdzus skyes la sogs pa nye bar mched do //
NK109(dze)001:5541: de la byang sgra mi snyan pa'i mi yang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5542: de nas ba glang spyod kyi mi rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:5543: de yang thog mar 'dzam bu gling nas chags shing mched pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5544: des na 'dzam bu gling pa'i sems can ni las
NK109(dze)001:5545: kyi sa pa zhes bsod nams che zhing bsgrub thag
NK109(dze)001:5546: nye'o // de nas 'gro ba de dag dga' ba dang bde ba'i bag la yengs pas /
NK109(dze)001:5547: tshe lo bye bar thung bar song /
NK109(dze)001:5548: 'gro ba de dag kyang sgo nga las skye bar song /
NK109(dze)001:5549: 'di'i dus na 'od ni bdun tshad du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5550: 'gro ba yang las kyi rlung gis nam mkha' la 'gro la /
NK109(dze)001:5551: zas su ni 'byung ba'i dwangs ma za'o //
NK109(dze)001:5552: gos su ni ci yang med pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5553: gcer bu la dreg pa chags pa las /
NK109(dze)001:5555: lha'i bu dri ma med pa'i dreg pa can zhes gcig la gcig bltas shing brjod do //
NK109(dze)001:5556: 'di'i dus na sngon gyi bsod nams kyi stobs kyis lus kyi dreg pa de 'khru ba'i ched du /
NK109(dze)001:5557: khrus kyi rdzing bu dal zhing 'jam la mthong na dga' ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5558: reg na bde ba byung zhing /
NK109(dze)001:5559: de'i nang na khrus dang gtsang sbra la gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5562: bstan pa la sogs pa ni 'dir ma bris te gzhan du blta'o //
NK109(dze)001:5563: rang bzhin gyi dge ba bcu la spyod do //
NK109(dze)001:5564: de nas sngon gyi las kyi stobs kyis tshe yang bgas kyis bri /
NK109(dze)001:5565: lus kyi 'od la sogs pa yang yal te /
NK109(dze)001:5566: 'byung ba tsha bas drod du byas grangs pa las rgyu rkyen du gyur nas /
NK109(dze)001:5567: drod gsher las skyes pa sha stag tu gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:5568: tshe lo yang 'bum pa la thug go /
NK109(dze)001:5569: der yang ljon shing zas su za ste /
NK109(dze)001:5570: mi re skyes pa dang shing re skye'o //
NK109(dze)001:5571: de'i 'bras bu zas su za ste /
NK109(dze)001:5572: khams kyi zas dgos pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5573: sngon 'dod srid rjes su chags pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5574: sngar gyi rang drod yal te /
NK109(dze)001:5575: gos kyi mgo zug pas shing lo ldeb po che gyon pa dag byung ngo /
NK109(dze)001:5576: de ni gti mug bag la nyal gyis gzhi chos nyid ma shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5577: 'di'i dus na 'gro ba de dag mo dang pho'i mtshan ma dod pa ni med de /
NK109(dze)001:5578: gcig la gcig mthong na dga' ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:5579: reg na bde ba tsam du byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5580: sngon gyi las kyis 'dod chags bag la nyal longs su nye ba'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:5581: de dag la bsod nams la sogs pa gong ltar rim gyis bri nas /
NK109(dze)001:5582: tshe lo yang brgyad khri la thug par gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:5583: 'gro ba 'di dag nyon mongs pa yang rim gyis langs pa'i mgo btsugs te /
NK109(dze)001:5584: sngon 'dod pa'i khams su lhung bas 'dod chags byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5585: de'i dus na las dang dbang po'i bye brag las /
NK109(dze)001:5586: pho mo'i dbang po'i sgo dod pa tsam byung la /
NK109(dze)001:5587: 'di'i dus na gcig la gcig bltas pas tshim pa
NK109(dze)001:5588: tsam gyi 'dod chags skyes nas 'gro ba mang du
NK109(dze)001:5589: mngal nas skyes pa las 'phel lo //
NK109(dze)001:5590: 'di'i dus 'od ni rang gsal ba tsam yod la /
NK109(dze)001:5591: gos su shing shun gyon no //
NK109(dze)001:5592: sngon gyi las kyi stobs kyis zas su 'dod 'jo'i ba ra byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5593: rang nam 'dod pa'i dus na ba zhos lus gso ba'i rkyen du byung la /
NK109(dze)001:5594: rlung gi rnam shes bag la nyal bas /
NK109(dze)001:5596: lus kyi stobs chung bas 'gro bar 'dod pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5597: cang shes kyi rtas gar 'gro bar 'dod par phyin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5598: de lta bu'i bsod nams kyi rkyen mang po byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5599: de las kyang rim gyis zhe sdang gi 'go byung bas gcig gi ba de bsad pas /
NK109(dze)001:5600: de'i dbang gis zhe sdang mngon du rgyu langs pa las de yang nub /
NK109(dze)001:5601: rta yang nub nas sor bzhi sa la ma reg par 'gro /
NK109(dze)001:5602: zas kyang sa'i tshil zhag bzang po sbrang rtsi'i ro dang 'dra ba gcig byung nas /
NK109(dze)001:5603: de la zas za zhing 'dug go /
NK109(dze)001:5604: gos ni shing las ras kyi bal 'jam po cig byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5605: de gyon cing 'dug go /'di'i dus na 'dod chags
NK109(dze)001:5606: kyi dbang gis gcig la gcig lta ba la sogs
NK109(dze)001:5607: pa byung ste / de'i dbang gis gcig la gcig
NK109(dze)001:5608: bltas shing bgad pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags byung ste
NK109(dze)001:5609: pa byung ste / / de la 'gro ba mang du mched de /
NK109(dze)001:5610: de las kyang nyon mongs pa skyes pa'i dbang gis
NK109(dze)001:5611: lus kyi 'od mog mog por song nas mi gsal
NK109(dze)001:5612: / sa tshil de sngar rang nam 'dod tsam na song zhing za ba las /
NK109(dze)001:5613: le lo can zhig gis nang ma 'ga' tsam blangs /
NK109(dze)001:5616: lo tsam gyi blangs pas de yang nub pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5617: de legs so zhes gzhan gyis kyang bslang shing zos pas /
NK109(dze)001:5618: le lo dang gsog 'jog gis de yang nub bo //
NK109(dze)001:5619: de nas bar der las kyi dbang gis gos dang
NK109(dze)001:5620: zas gnyis med pa yang lo mang du gnas so
NK109(dze)001:5621: // de nas 'gro ba de dag kyang rab tu rid pa /
NK109(dze)001:5623: 'od kyang yal nas mun par gnas pa ni gti mug gi dbang gis so //
NK109(dze)001:5624: de nas bsod nams kyi stobs kyis nam mkha' la nyi ma'i snang ba shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:5625: 'di ni nye ring du mi 'ong bar mar 'dug ces nyi mar btags so //
NK109(dze)001:5626: de nas zla ba shar bas 'di yang de'i zla bar 'dug zhes brjod bas zla bar btags so //
NK109(dze)001:5627: 'di yi dus na zla ba yang dus mtshan mo
NK109(dze)001:5628: tsam du 'char la drod dang ldan par yod pa
NK109(dze)001:5629: las / yang 'gro ba las 'di ltar gnyis dro
NK109(dze)001:5630: ba'i snang ba yal nas bsil bar gyur cig ces
NK109(dze)001:5631: las / brjod pas / sngon gyi smon lam gyi
NK109(dze)001:5632: dbang gis drod kyi stobs 'gags nas bsil bar gyur
NK109(dze)001:5633: las / brjod pas / to // de la la
NK109(dze)001:5634: las ha cang bsil drags so zhes byas pas de
NK109(dze)001:5635: rang yang yar skye mar 'grib tu song ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5636: de la bsod nams kyi stobs kyis 'bras sa lu bzang po gcig btab ma dgos par skye ste /
NK109(dze)001:5638: de yang nang rngas na nang rang skye /
NK109(dze)001:5639: nub rngas na nub rang skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5640: de'i mchog zos pas lus rab tu stobs dang ldan par gyur nas /
NK109(dze)001:5641: gos su ras bal de g.yog nas thags su byas nas gyon pas /
NK109(dze)001:5642: de'i dbang gis 'dod chags ni 'khyud pa'i 'dod chags
NK109(dze)001:5643: byung nas dbang po'i sgo ma sbyar na ma tshim
NK109(dze)001:5644: pas / dbang po'i sgo sbyar ba dag byung ngo /
NK109(dze)001:5645: de ltar dbang po'i sgo sbyar ba la gcig la gcig ltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:5646: ngo tsha ba'i 'du shes skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:5647: shing dang rdo la sogs pas so so'i khang bu byas te logs skyar ro //
NK109(dze)001:5648: de la nam mkha' nas bdud rtsi'i sil ma'i char bab pas 'jag mas bkab pas /
NK109(dze)001:5649: khyim la snga ba 'jag ma'i spyil po byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5650: de nas 'bras kyi zhing la nga rgyal can zhig gis 'di rnams dbang zhes ri mo byas te /
NK109(dze)001:5651: kun gyi bsgos nas byas so //
NK109(dze)001:5652: de nas 'dod chags kyi zla nga rgyal byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5653: de las las ngan pa rnams kyi zhing ngan pa las ma skyes pas ma sos /
NK109(dze)001:5654: las bzang po rnams kyi ni bzang du shes pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5655: ngan pa'i bdag pos brkus pas te /
NK109(dze)001:5656: brku 'phrog gi las zhe sdang gi dbang las byung bas de yang nub bo //
NK109(dze)001:5657: de nas shing gi thong pas ri la brkos te /
NK109(dze)001:5658: 'bru la snga ba so byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5659: de bag tsam btab cing za /
NK109(dze)001:5660: des kyang ma 'tsho nas rmo brko'i las byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5661: ri rtse mo la 'jag khyim byed cing yun 'ga' gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:5662: de nas rim gyis ri rked la sogs pa nas
NK109(dze)001:5663: tha ma khung du khyim la sogs pa'am so so'i
NK109(dze)001:5664: zhing la sogs par byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5665: de yang de dag rim gyis yal ba'i dbang gis
NK109(dze)001:5666: 'gro ba 'di dag ni nyon mogs pa rags su
NK109(dze)001:5667: song ste / spyod pa ngan pa la spyod pa
NK109(dze)001:5668: dpag tu med pa'i skal ba tha ma las byung
NK109(dze)001:5669: song ste / ngo // de ltar 'dod chags dang /
NK109(dze)001:5672: mi dge ba bcu la spyad pa'i dbang gis ngan
NK109(dze)001:5673: song gsum po'i skye gnas rnams kyang rim gyis chags
NK109(dze)001:5674: so // de dkyus dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)001:5675: 'dod dang zhes pa 'dod pa'i khams 'dod chags las byung la /
NK109(dze)001:5676: zhe sdang la gzugs dang zhes pas las gzugs kyi khams su byung /
NK109(dze)001:5677: gti mug las gzugs med kyi khams zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5678: de ltar khams ni 'dus pa dang 'tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:5679: gsum ni grangs te gong du bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:5680: de ni sa chu me rlung la bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5681: yod zhes res gzugs yod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5682: res ci yang med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5683: rnam pa ni yul shes pa ni rig pa tsam mo //
NK109(dze)001:5684: cung ni nam mkha'i rdul zad nas med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:5685: gzugs rdul phra rab tu med la /
NK109(dze)001:5686: khams ni shes byed mang po 'dus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5687: de las ni yod min med min las skyes te rnam par rig tsam mo //
NK109(dze)001:5688: gnas pa lha'i gnas gtsang ni sa rdo'o bag med
NK109(dze)001:5689: pa la sogs ni rigs kyi lha lnga la sogs
NK109(dze)001:5690: pa'o // gzugs kyi khams kyi lha 'od kyi lus can ni /
NK109(dze)001:5691: gong gzugs med pa nas 'og min gyi lha 'og
NK109(dze)001:5692: tu nam mkha' nas thig pa bab pa'i tshul du
NK109(dze)001:5693: mas chad pa'o // de'i 'og gzugs khams gnas rigs
NK109(dze)001:5694: bcu bdun min pa gzhan 'phrul dbang byed la sogs
NK109(dze)001:5695: pa 'dod pa khams lha rigs mi 'dra ba drug
NK109(dze)001:5697: lha dang zhes pa la gzugs med la skye mched mu bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:5698: gzugs kyi khams la gnas rigs bcu bdun dang /
NK109(dze)001:5699: 'dod pa'i khams la rigs drug ste nyer bdun ni lha'i rigs so //
NK109(dze)001:5700: de yang lha zhes bya ba khyad par du bzod
NK109(dze)001:5701: pa mchog dang ldan pa bsgoms pa las byung ba'o
NK109(dze)001:5702: // lha min ni gong ma'i lha min kyang 'dod
NK109(dze)001:5703: pa khams kyi lha rigs drug gi gsum man chad
NK109(dze)001:5704: la rtsod par byed pas lha min la /
NK109(dze)001:5705: de dag 'khor dang longs spyod mi mnyam pas min zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5706: 'di la yang stobs chen gnod sbyin gyi rigs dang /
NK109(dze)001:5709: gsod dga' srin po'i rigs la sogs pa lnga yod do //
NK109(dze)001:5710: mi zhes pa mngon par mthong ba'i khyad par gyis bsags pa bsod nams dang ldan pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5711: de yang nye bar mtshon pa gling bzhi la rigs mi 'dra ba bzhi ni /
NK109(dze)001:5712: khyad par gong ma rgyal chen rigs bzhi las chad bas so //
NK109(dze)001:5713: de las kyang lho'i 'dzam bu gling na mi bu rigs bzhi'i dbang byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5714: rgyal khams 'di na dang po 'di yod la /
NK109(dze)001:5715: bar du 'di tha ma tshe lo 'di la dbang byed do zhes bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5716: bkra shis mdzes ldan gyi skabs su bstan par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5717: de rnams ni mi'i 'jig rten zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5718: mngon mtho ni las dge ba bcu spyad pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5719: de nas ni mi la gnas dge bcu spyad pa'i dbang gis gling la /
NK109(dze)001:5723: gzugs med dang mtho ris gnas bcu'o //
NK109(dze)001:5724: gsum pa zhes pa mi dang /
NK109(dze)001:5726: de las mi las dge ba bcu las byol nas /
NK109(dze)001:5727: ngan song du song pa'i rigs bzhi 'am lnga ni /
NK109(dze)001:5728: mi dge ba bcu spyad pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5729: yid zhes yid kyi lus yod pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5730: de yang zas dang skom yid la btags pas na /
NK109(dze)001:5732: de ni byol song las mched pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5734: dmyal ba ni sdug bsngal dang ldan pa'i lus de yang yid btags las chad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5735: 'di la rigs nyer gcig tu bstan /
NK109(dze)001:5736: theg pa chung ngu nas bco brgyad bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:5737: de ltar 'gro ba rigs drug gi lus la sems dang ldan pas sems can zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:5738: khams gsum po de dag skyes pa ni thog ma bardzusa skyes dang /
NK109(dze)001:5739: de nas sgong nga las skyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5741: mngal skyes dang bzhi las skyes so //
NK109(dze)001:5742: da lta yang 'di dag ni mi la nye bar mtshon pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5743: 'gro ba rigs drug po de dag kyang skye ba bzhis bsdus te /
NK109(dze)001:5745: zhes nying don bzhi pa de la brten pa bcud kyi sems can ji ltar chags pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:5746: da ni nying lag gi don lnga pa de yang
NK109(dze)001:5747: khyad par du mi lus te skal pa dang po'i
NK109(dze)001:5748: mi'i bsod nams kyi tshad bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5749: de yang nye bar mtshon pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5750: bskal pa ni yun la brten pa /
NK109(dze)001:5751: des gang bskal na ye shes bskal pas na bskal pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5752: dang po ni tshe lo dpag tu med nas brgyad khri yan chod kyi mi /
NK109(dze)001:5753: gzugs ni khru tshad sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:5754: bzang zhing gzhon sha chags pa ni lang tsho //
NK109(dze)001:5755: dpe byad ni gong ma'i lha'i lus las gyur pas legs pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5756: rang las byung ba'i 'od kyis 'gro ba de dag gi lus khyab ste /
NK109(dze)001:5757: tshe lo 'bum pa'i dus na nam 'dod pa na 'jo ba'i ba byung /
NK109(dze)001:5758: de'i 'og tu brgyad khri pa'i thog bsod nams kyi zas sa tshil byung /
NK109(dze)001:5759: de'i 'og tu 'bras sa lu byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:5760: de dag kyang snga ma'i bsod nams las grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5761: dpag tu med pa las skye ba ni lus 'brel pa /
NK109(dze)001:5762: dga' ni khams gsum las dgu yod pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5764: de las lo brgya brgya na re re bri nas bye ba /
NK109(dze)001:5766: de las tshe lo yang brgyad khri'o //
NK109(dze)001:5767: de las rim gyis bri nas tha ma bcu pa la thug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5768: de'i dus tshe lo 'bum pa la pho dang mo'i
NK109(dze)001:5769: dbang po'i sgo dod pa la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK109(dze)001:5770: gong du bstan / zhes nying don lnga pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5771: da ni nying lag gi don drug pa de nas
NK109(dze)001:5772: de dag longs spyod la sogs pa bgas kyis bri
NK109(dze)001:5773: ste da lta'i lus 'di la thug bar du bstan
NK109(dze)001:5774: pa ni / de nas nyon mongs cher song bas 'khrul pa'i rgyu yul dang shes pa gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:5776: de la lus sems gnyis ka chags te /
NK109(dze)001:5777: tshe lo brgyad khri la bltas pas tshim pa la
NK109(dze)001:5778: sogs pa'i lus nyon mongs pa sems kyi las su
NK109(dze)001:5779: gyur pa na / bgas kyis ni je che la song pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5780: rags pa ni zhe sdang la sogs pa mngon du 'gyur ba nyid du 'gyur ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5781: de nas pho mo'i dbang po'i mtshan ma dod nas gcig la gcig bltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:5782: bltas pas tshim pa'i chags las sogs pa 'dod pa'i dbang gis byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:5783: 'gro ba de dag gi bsod pa las dang bag chags med pa /
NK109(dze)001:5785: de zad pa'i phyir lus kyi 'od la sogs zas dang /
NK109(dze)001:5787: de nas tshe lo brgyad khri pa'i 'og la gong
NK109(dze)001:5788: ma'i ljon shing la sogs pa rim gyis yal nas
NK109(dze)001:5789: / sa'i tshil zhag sbrang rtsi'i ro dang 'dra ba gcig byung nas de za /
NK109(dze)001:5790: de yang yal nas 'bras sa lu bzang po ma
NK109(dze)001:5791: btab par la zas su za ba la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:5792: zas de rnams la spyod do zhes nying don drug
NK109(dze)001:5793: pa'o // da ni nying lag gi don bdun pa
NK109(dze)001:5794: de ltar gyi gzugs de phung po dang nyon mongs
NK109(dze)001:5795: pa chos mthun gang dang ldan pa bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:5796: pa'o // / gong du bstan pa de ltar 'jig pa chu rten pa rlung la rten pa /
NK109(dze)001:5799: sa steng dang gsum po'i mi nyid ni /
NK109(dze)001:5802: rnam shes 'tshogs pa du ma 'dus pas phung po'o //
NK109(dze)001:5803: tshor ba myong reg sna tshogs 'dus pas phung po //
NK109(dze)001:5804: 'du shes gcig dang tha dad pa 'dus pas phung po /
NK109(dze)001:5805: 'du byed rtog dpyod sna tshogs pa 'dus pas na phung po ste lnga dang /
NK109(dze)001:5810: lus sna tshogs 'dus pa'i dbang po lnga'i /
NK109(dze)001:5811: de yang rigs lnga'i rgyu ma dag pa las byung la /
NK109(dze)001:5812: dbang po ni rigs kyi bdag po lnga ma dag pa las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5813: mgo la sogs pa yan lag lnga ye shes lnga'i rtsal ma dag pa las byung /
NK109(dze)001:5814: snying la sogs pa don snying lnga ni 'od lnga'i mtshan nyid ma dag pa las byung /
NK109(dze)001:5815: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul lnga dang ni 'od lnga'i
NK109(dze)001:5816: snang ba rang snang du ma shes pa las byung
NK109(dze)001:5817: ngo // 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa
NK109(dze)001:5818: lnga ni ye shes lnga ma dag pa las byung
NK109(dze)001:5819: ngo // / sna tshogs su sdud pa'i sems la sogs pa lnga ni /
NK109(dze)001:5820: chos nyid kyi gdangs lnga ma dag pa las byung /
NK109(dze)001:5821: kun du 'tshol byed la sogs pa lnga ni rlung lnga rnam par ma dag pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5822: bsam dran bas 'dzin pa'i bdag tu rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5823: yul du ma la bdag tu rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5824: 'gyu ba tha dad pa la bdag tu rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5825: shes pa rnam pa tsam la bdag tu rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5826: chos rnam par sems dpa' dang bcas pa la bdag
NK109(dze)001:5827: tu rtog pa ni lnga ni 'gyu ba mched pa
NK109(dze)001:5828: las byung ba'o // lus la 'tshogs pa'i chos de dag gis gzung ba yul dang /
NK109(dze)001:5829: 'dzin pa sems dang gnyis 'dus pas 'khor ba'i sems can nyid du grub bo //
NK109(dze)001:5830: 'khrul pa ni ma rig pa las byung ba gnyis
NK109(dze)001:5831: ni yul sems kyi snang ba de lta bu byung
NK109(dze)001:5832: ba'o // dper na zo chu'i 'khor lo ltar thur
NK109(dze)001:5833: du 'gro ba'i 'khor lo bzhin du gcig nas gcig
NK109(dze)001:5834: ba'o // tu 'khor ro // de yang gcig tu brgyud de /
NK109(dze)001:5835: lus mi 'dra ba tha dad pa blangs /
NK109(dze)001:5836: de nyid la chags pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba de
NK109(dze)001:5837: nyid la yun ring ba de nyid bskal pa dpag
NK109(dze)001:5838: tu med pa ring por gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5839: rang 'a byung gi ye shes rang la snang bar ma shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5840: zhes nying don bdun pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:5841: da ni nying don brgyad pa de ltar snod bcud
NK109(dze)001:5842: kyi 'khrul pa nyid rang grol yin par dpe'i sgo
NK109(dze)001:5843: nas gtan la phab ste bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5844: de ltar gang gi phung po dang khams la sogs
NK109(dze)001:5845: pa'i snang ba ni spyi pa'i gzhi la 'di ltar
NK109(dze)001:5846: ldog pa rgyas par bshad pa ni lus kyi 'tshogs
NK109(dze)001:5847: pa'i chos de dag la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:5853: dper na nam mkha' dag pa'i dus su sgor thon pas mig rab rib tu song ba'i dbang gis /
NK109(dze)001:5854: thag pa las ni sbrul du mthong bas rab tu basngangasa nas log ste /
NK109(dze)001:5855: rnam dag nas thag par mthong ba bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:5856: thag pa de sbrul ma yin pa la sbrul du bzung ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:5857: de yang phyi snod du 'dzin pa yang med pa nyid las yod par 'dzin pa'i shes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5858: nang bcud kyi sems gnyis su chags pa 'di yang mi bden pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5859: med pa'i don snang ba ste rmi lam gyi rnam pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5860: de yang dag par brtag na thag pa nyid du bden par shes pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:5861: rig pa nyid la ye nas snod bcud du grub ste /
NK109(dze)001:5862: ye nas stong pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:5863: zhes nying don brgyad pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:5864: da ni nying lag gi don dgu pa bden pa
NK109(dze)001:5865: gnyis kyi don dgag sgrub med par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:5866: / de yang brtags pas thag par bden pa ltar don dam pa'i chos su bden la /
NK109(dze)001:5867: 'di la yang ngo bo nges tshig dbye ba gsum
NK109(dze)001:5868: du gtan la phab pa 'dug ste 'dir mi spro'o
NK109(dze)001:5869: // kun rdzob snang tshad tsam du bden la /
NK109(dze)001:5870: yang dag par ma grub bo //
NK109(dze)001:5871: gzugs ni don dam par smra bsam brjod pa las 'das /
NK109(dze)001:5872: kun rdzob snang shes sna tshogs pa can du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5873: de yang dper na sbrul mthong pa'i dus sbrul du mthong ba tsam gyis bden pa bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:5874: kun rdzob snang tshad tsam du bden la /
NK109(dze)001:5875: thag pa mthong ba don dam pa yang dag pa nyid du bden pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5876: don dam pa'i chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:5877: de yang sems can zhes dper na mtho la bya chags pas /
NK109(dze)001:5878: mtho bya can zhes bya bar song pa /
NK109(dze)001:5879: lus dang sems 'dus pas sems can du song pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5880: bya 'phur bas 'tho dang bya la 'brel ba med
NK109(dze)001:5881: pa bzhin du lus sems gnyis la yang 'brel pa
NK109(dze)001:5882: med do // de yang bden pa gnyis kyang don dam pa'i ngos nas 'brel ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:5883: de rang bzhin gang du yang ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:5884: 'jig rten pa'i ngos nas kun rdzob tsam du bden pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5885: yang dag pa nyid la don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis la 'brel pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:5887: kun rdzob rnam pa dang yang 'khrul pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5888: don dam pa ma 'khrul pa yang dag pa yin pas so //
NK109(dze)001:5889: zhes nying don dgu pa bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:5890: da ni nying lag gi don bcu pa de ltar
NK109(dze)001:5891: snod bcud thams cad dag pa'i dbyings su ye nas
NK109(dze)001:5892: grol ba yin par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5893: rlung la sogs pa stong pa nyid kyi dbyings las ni /
NK109(dze)001:5894: ye nas stong pa las ma gtogs pa gang yang med pa /
NK109(dze)001:5895: de yang snod kyi 'jig rten ji ltar grol zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:5896: de'i ngo bo ye nas 'khrul ma myong pas ka
NK109(dze)001:5897: dag tu rtogs pas thams cad rang grol ba las
NK109(dze)001:5899: 'dod khams la sogs khams gsum ji ltar grol zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:5900: de yang rang gi rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:5901: ngos bzung med pas stong nyid du rang dag /
NK109(dze)001:5902: gzugs kyi khams 'od gsal du rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:5903: 'dod pa'i khams shes rig tu rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:5904: gzugs med pa'i khams stong pa nyid du rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:5905: gzugs kyi khams 'od gsal chen por rang grol ba ni chos nyid khyab che ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5906: de yang bcud kyi sems can de rnams snying po
NK109(dze)001:5907: sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan du grol te chos
NK109(dze)001:5908: nyid du dril ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5909: sems can gyi gzugs de dag ji ltar grol zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:5910: gong du bstan pa'i phung po lnga la sogs pa mi'i lus kyi mtshan nyid grol lugs ni /
NK109(dze)001:5911: de la 'gro ba'i lus la snying po byang chub kyi sems gnas pa de nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:5912: phung po lnga skur lngar grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5913: gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang mdzad du grol ba la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5914: dbang po lnga ye shes lngar grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5915: mig gi dbang po me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK109(dze)001:5916: su grol ba la sogs pa lnga dang ni zhes
NK109(dze)001:5917: bya'o // gzugs la sogs pa'i yul lnga 'od lngar grol /
NK109(dze)001:5918: don lnga kha dog rnam pa lngar grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5919: nyon mongs pa lnga chos ma bcos pa la sogs pa lngar grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:5920: yan lag lnga ye shes kyi rlung me dang mnyam pa la sogs pa lngar nyid du grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:5921: ngo bo sku lngar snod lngar grol /
NK109(dze)001:5922: rang bzhin 'od mdangs lngar 'byung ba lngar grol /
NK109(dze)001:5923: thugs rje ni rang bzhin shugs dang /
NK109(dze)001:5924: rkyen yul dang phrad pa'i dang /
NK109(dze)001:5925: bskul zhing gsol btab kyi dang /
NK109(dze)001:5926: mdzad pa sna tshogs pa'i dang /
NK109(dze)001:5927: gdul bya mos 'gyur gyi thugs rje dang lngar me lnga grol bas ni kun la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5928: de ltar grol ba'i chos nyid la dran pa med
NK109(dze)001:5929: pas yid kyi 'gyur ba nyid kyang med pa ni
NK109(dze)001:5930: / rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings kyi cho 'phrul la ma gtogs pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:5931: de yang ngo bo las rang bzhin gyi snang ba de las thugs rje byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5932: de yang rig pa yang rang bzhag pas thams cad grol ba de'i ngang ma bcos par 'du ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5933: de yang gcig rang ni chos sku stong pa /
NK109(dze)001:5934: de las byung ba'i 'khor 'das gnyis ni ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:5935: thig le nyag gcig las ma gtogs pa'i chos med
NK109(dze)001:5936: do // zhes yan lag gi don drug pa de
NK109(dze)001:5937: nyid la gnyis snang ji ltar yin par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:5938: la nying lag gi don bcur byas na bstan to
NK109(dze)001:5939: do // // zhes mu tig la sogs pa mtshan gyi skabs su bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:5940: le'u'i mtshan ni gnas lugs ni ngo bo ka nas dag pa la 'khrul rgyu med kyang /
NK109(dze)001:5941: de'i rang bzhin 'khrul ba rang rdzogs su bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5942: snang lugs kyi chos thams cad rdzogs par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5943: le'u gzhung gi mtshams phyed par byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:5944: le'u de la bsdus pa'i don gnyis su byas te /
NK109(dze)001:5945: yan lag gi don drug tu byas pa la /
NK109(dze)001:5946: nying lag gi don sum cu rtsa gnyis su byas
NK109(dze)001:5947: nas gzhung gi le'u tshig dang yi ger bcad nas
NK109(dze)001:5948: bstan pa'o // lnga pa ni gzhi las gzhan du gyur pa drug gi gong ma'o //
NK109(dze)001:5949: mu tig rin po che gsal bar 'byed par byed
NK109(dze)001:5950: pa las le'u lnga pa'i don rnams par phye ba'o
NK109(dze)001:5953: mathagapamme/&&& da ni le'u drug pa mu tig gsal bar dbye ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:5954: le'u drug pa sems can gyi snang thabs bstan pa'i le'u la bsdus pa'i don gsum gyis bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:5955: dang po dri ba dang bcas pa'i dgongs pa ngo bo nyid kyi gnas lugs bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5956: gnyis pa ngo bo nyid de 'ching byed kyi dri ma gang yin par bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5957: gsum pa sems can gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum ji ltar tshang par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:5958: dang po la nang don dgus bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:5959: dri ba mdor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5960: rdo ni chags pa rje ni de gcod par byed pa /
NK109(dze)001:5961: 'dzin pas chags pa gcod byed kyis sdud pa po zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5962: gsol ba ni ston pa la zhus pa /
NK109(dze)001:5963: kye zhes gsol ba btab pa'i tshul gyis bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:5964: rdo stong pa rje gsal ba /
NK109(dze)001:5965: 'chang ba gsal stong dbyer med pa'i ston pa chen po zhes bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:5966: gsang ba de'i don gsang ba tsam gyis dngos grub 'byung la /
NK109(dze)001:5967: de skal ldan gyi rna bar bsgrags pa tsam gyis nges shes bskyed par byed pa /
NK109(dze)001:5968: de nyid la dbang bskur bas bdag ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:5969: 'khor ba'i las dang nyon mongs pa sangs pas 'das pa'i sku dang ye shes su rgyas pa /
NK109(dze)001:5970: kun 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5971: da lta'i ye shes thams cad gcig tu bsdus pa nyid ci la gsung pa lags zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:5972: de nyid kyi ngo bo'i don nam gnas lugs sam dgongs pa ji ltar lags /
NK109(dze)001:5974: 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs lnga'i dri ma
NK109(dze)001:5975: yis khams gyi sems can ji ltar 'ching bar 'gyur
NK109(dze)001:5976: ba lags zhes / nyon mongs pa bcom pa'i ye
NK109(dze)001:5977: shes lnga ldan 'khor 'das kyi mtha' las 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)001:5978: bstan pas bdag sngar ma 'tshal bas 'di gnyis gsungs
NK109(dze)001:5979: ba lags zhes / dang dris so // zhes nang don dang po'o //
NK109(dze)001:5980: da ni nang don gnyis pa lan bka' stsal pa mdor bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:5981: bcom ldan 'das la sogs pa tshig bzhi 'og nas ston /
NK109(dze)001:5982: da ni nang don gsum pa ngo bor rang bzhin gyi don rgyas par bshad pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:5983: de yang ngo bo ni ka nas dag pa'i rig pa'i ye shes su rang snang la /
NK109(dze)001:5984: rang bzhin ni sems can thams cad la kun tu
NK109(dze)001:5985: khyab pa mi bskyod pa la sogs pa'i sku lnga
NK109(dze)001:5986: ldan ni / de'i 'bras bu spros pa thams cad
NK109(dze)001:5987: kyi mtha' nye bar zhi bas thig le las byung
NK109(dze)001:5988: ldan ni / ba / nyag de'i don rtogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:5989: gcig du ma tha dad bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5990: de'i snang ba chos nyid la zung 'jug yul dang ris med de /
NK109(dze)001:5991: de'i dngos po stong pa la rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:5992: rang grol gyi ngos nas stong pa'i ngo bo chos
NK109(dze)001:5993: nyid rtog pa dang bral ba las ni rtogs pa
NK109(dze)001:5995: de'i rigs kyi snang ba nyid la 'char lugs rim gyis so //
NK109(dze)001:5997: da ni nang don bzhi pa rig pa'i ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:5998: de nyid la khyab cing de nyid la thams cad
NK109(dze)001:5999: rdzogs pa ni dri ma'i mtha' gang gis kyang ma
NK109(dze)001:6001: rig pa'i ngo bo de yang chos nyid stong pa
NK109(dze)001:6002: sems can kun la khyab pa phyi rol pa mthar
NK109(dze)001:6003: 'dzin pa'i rdul dang mun pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6004: snying stobs dang bral ba'i chos nyid la de'i rang bzhin gyi snang ba ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)001:6005: ye shes las byung ba'i 'od du gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:6006: de ltar ngo bo rang bzhin gnyis thabs shes rab
NK109(dze)001:6007: du byung ba la ma rig 'khrul pa'i dri ma
NK109(dze)001:6008: dang bral ba'i chos nyid ni /
NK109(dze)001:6010: de yang mi 'gyur pa'i rig pa nyid chos skur byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6011: de nyid sgron ma la brten nas nyams su blang pas /
NK109(dze)001:6012: lus ngag la bde ba chen po'i drod rtags 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:6013: sa rdo ri brag gi dngos po'i mtha' rdul phra
NK109(dze)001:6014: rab rnams stong pa ni nyams su blang ba las
NK109(dze)001:6015: byung ba'o // de gzhan la ma brten pas rang
NK109(dze)001:6016: byung shes bya thams cad kyi mthar thug pa yin
NK109(dze)001:6018: mkhyen pa thams cad du gsal ba yin la /
NK109(dze)001:6019: mchog tu gyur pas rgyal po ste /
NK109(dze)001:6020: dge brtsegs gzhan la rag ma lus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6021: mtho dang thams cad rang byung yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:6022: dma' ba rang grol ba'i gnad yul thams cad rnam
NK109(dze)001:6023: par dang pas brjod pa las 'das pas tshig gi
NK109(dze)001:6026: da ni nying don lnga pa de ltar rtogs pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6027: rnal 'byor pas 'khor 'das thams cad de nyid las
NK109(dze)001:6028: byung zhing de nyid kyi rgyan nam rol par bstan
NK109(dze)001:6029: pa ni / gzhi gnas rang 'byung gi ngang rang
NK109(dze)001:6030: byung gi rig pa nyid lo ka'i bya ba dang
NK109(dze)001:6032: nyams dang rtogs pa rgyas pa'i dgongs pa ni ma bcos rang sar grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6033: rig pa nyid ye sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba yang nga rang 'byung gi ye shes las ma 'das /
NK109(dze)001:6034: de ltar na mya ngan 'das pa yang nga rang rig pa'i ye shes ma gtogs pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:6035: gzhi rig pa de nyid mtshon bya ltar snang bas chos 'khor ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6036: mya ngan las 'das pa yang nga rig pa'i yin la /
NK109(dze)001:6037: de ma yin pa'i nag po'i chos min pa rnams kyang nga rig pa'i ye shes nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:6038: de yang gdeng rnyed pa'i rnal 'byor pas dmyal ba
NK109(dze)001:6039: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal la ya nga zhing bag
NK109(dze)001:6041: rig pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa la 'khor ba ma grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6042: de la sogs pa las ngan pas sdug bsngal dang
NK109(dze)001:6043: ldan par song ba yang nga rang 'byung gi ye
NK109(dze)001:6044: shes las ma gtogs pa med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6045: rig pa la rgyu med par rtogs pa'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6046: dkyil rig pa 'khor ye shes la rang dbang du gyur pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6047: rang lus lha dang 'bral ba med par gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6048: rtsa ba khyab pa'i rang bzhin gyi kun tu bzang pos so //
NK109(dze)001:6049: rang bzhin rtsal gnas pa'i yi ge la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:6050: ngag tu ci brjod pa sngags kyi bzlas par song
NK109(dze)001:6051: pas / tshig tu ci brjod pa nyid kyang nga
NK109(dze)001:6052: rang 'byung gi ye shes ma gtogs pa med pa
NK109(dze)001:6053: pas / ni / rang lus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6054: de yang sangs rgyas dkon mchog gi dbye ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6060: sprul pa'i sku'i sangs rgyas dang gsum /
NK109(dze)001:6061: de la chos sku'i zhing khams dang /
NK109(dze)001:6062: rnam 'phrul gyi dbye ba la sogs pa gzhan na bstan nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:6064: las kyi bye brag sangs pas na sangs zhes bya ba la /
NK109(dze)001:6065: yang dag pa'i yon tan rnams kyis rgyas pas na rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6066: ngo bo yang spang bya las 'das nas bsgrib byed gang gis kyang ma bsgribs par bzhugs so //
NK109(dze)001:6068: 'khor 'das kyi rtog pa sangs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6069: rnam par byang ba'i yon tan gyis rgyas pas 'jig rten na dkon pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6070: de la gzhan gyis bskur bar 'os pas mchog yin no //
NK109(dze)001:6071: las bsags pa ni chos te /
NK109(dze)001:6072: dbye ba ni bsgrub pa'i chos yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:6073: lam gyi chos 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa /
NK109(dze)001:6074: don dam pa'i chos zhi ba mya ngan la 'das pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6075: theg pa chung ngu'i lugs so /
NK109(dze)001:6076: ngo bo ni brjod bya'i don phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6078: lus ngag yid khyad par gyis lam srol du 'jug pa yan chos so //
NK109(dze)001:6080: chos kyi yul chos nyid de 'dres par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:6081: khams gsum las dbugs 'byin par byed pas te /
NK109(dze)001:6082: de'i don chod pa 'jig rten na dkon pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6083: de las yar ldan du 'phel bas na mchog ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6085: theg pa chung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)001:6088: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun no //
NK109(dze)001:6089: ngo bo rtag par brten nas don nyid la sbyor ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6090: nges tshig ni dge ba la dus thams cad du 'dun pa skyed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6091: de ltar rtag tu byed pa dkon pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6092: de las 'bral ba med par ched du byed pa ni mchog yin no //
NK109(dze)001:6093: de dag gsum kyang nga rig pa las ma gtogs par log na med do //
NK109(dze)001:6094: rang byung shes rig gi rgyal po ston pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6095: rig pa las ma gtogs pa'i shes bya log na med pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)001:6096: sgo lnga'i yul rjes su 'gro ba ldog pa las
NK109(dze)001:6097: ma gtogs pa gzhan med pas 'khor du yang byung
NK109(dze)001:6098: la / de nyid la brten nas yul du rtog pa'i 'dzin pa dang bral bar byed pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6099: rtsa rlung thabs kyi bde ba la brten nas bu tha bas /
NK109(dze)001:6100: bstan pa yang nga gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa las ma gtogs pa gzhan na med do //
NK109(dze)001:6101: yul dang yul can rang dag tu shes pas rang
NK109(dze)001:6102: gi 'khor sdud par byed pa'i sdud pa po yang
NK109(dze)001:6104: rig pa de nyid thabs du ma ltar snang bas lta ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6105: de la ma yengs bar gnas pas sgom pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6106: de la dus rgyun du byed pas spyod pa yang nga rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:6107: de nyid la dbang spros bcas dang /
NK109(dze)001:6109: shin tu spros pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6110: rab tu spros pa med kyang rig pa dam tshig srung bya yul gyi dang /
NK109(dze)001:6111: srung mtshams las 'das pa rang bzhin gyi dam tshig
NK109(dze)001:6112: kyang nga rig pa de lus ngag yid kyi sdom
NK109(dze)001:6113: pa yang / rig pa nyid de /
NK109(dze)001:6114: mchod pa la sogs pa yang rig pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6115: tshig lnga gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:6116: zhes nang don drug pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:6117: da ni nang don bdu na pa de ltar shes
NK109(dze)001:6118: nas 'di ltar snang ba thams cad rang gi rig
NK109(dze)001:6119: pa yin par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6120: de la 'jig rten pa'i chos thams cad du yang rig pa'i ye shes byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:6121: de yang sdig dang zhes pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6122: rig pa nyid ye nas grol ba'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)001:6123: las dge sdig gi phan gnod dang bral ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:6124: ming la nges pa med pa gtan tshigs kyis /
NK109(dze)001:6125: rnam grangs ming 'gyur gyi las kyis dgag bsgrub kyi mtha' dbye ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:6126: de la 'dir sdig pa ni ming gi rnam grangs yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:6127: ming la nges pa med par dge ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:6128: zhes byas kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:6129: de yang thams cad ming las ma gtogs pa gang yang grub pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:6130: de ltar na gang ltar btags pa de ltar snang zhes so //
NK109(dze)001:6131: de la yang btags pa ming yin gyi gtan tshigs kyis gzhig pas /
NK109(dze)001:6132: ming la nges pa med do /
NK109(dze)001:6133: yang dag par de nyid yin pa'i rgyu med do //
NK109(dze)001:6134: ming gi mtshan nyid gtan la phebs pa med de /
NK109(dze)001:6135: dper na mi rgan po la mi gzhon nu 'gon zhes par btags pa bzhin te /
NK109(dze)001:6136: rgan po gzhon par mi 'gyur la de bzhin du
NK109(dze)001:6137: mi sdig can yin kyang don dge ba yin na
NK109(dze)001:6138: ci stong ste / nges pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:6139: sdig pa nyid nga yin pas las dang rnam par smin pas gos pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:6140: rgyu sdig pa mi bden pas 'bras bu rnam par smin pa yang mi bden no //
NK109(dze)001:6141: de yang rig pa rgyu 'bras rjes med kyi rig
NK109(dze)001:6142: pa las rnam par smin pa mi bden pa ni
NK109(dze)001:6143: / theg pa thun mong pa rnams rgyu sdig pa
NK109(dze)001:6144: mi dge ba spyad pas 'bras bu ngan song du
NK109(dze)001:6145: 'gro ba zhes zer ba 'di yang dag par bden
NK109(dze)001:6146: / pa min te / rig pa'i ye shes kyi cho 'phrul las ma gtogs pa med pas so //
NK109(dze)001:6147: de la sdig dang rnam par smin pa la 'brel ba med pas kyang mi bden te /
NK109(dze)001:6148: de gnyis rgyu mi gcig pas rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel ba yang med de /
NK109(dze)001:6149: rgyu srog bcad pas 'bras bu yang tshur la srog gcod lo bar yang mi 'thad de /
NK109(dze)001:6150: rgyu phar srog gcod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6151: 'bras bu tshur 'ong ba gnyis rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yang med de /
NK109(dze)001:6153: de las byung ba'i 'brel pa yang med do //
NK109(dze)001:6154: sdig pa las rnam par smin pa ma byung /
NK109(dze)001:6155: rnam par smin pa las sdig pa ma byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:6156: 'bras bu mi bden pa'i dbang gis /
NK109(dze)001:6157: 'bras bu ltar rgyu da lta srog gcod pas /
NK109(dze)001:6158: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na rang gi srog la 'ong na rnam smin phan tshun 'khor ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:6159: rgyu sdig spyad pa la 'bras bu mtho ris su 'gro ba yang nges pas 'gal ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:6160: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu bden na /
NK109(dze)001:6161: rgyu da lta bdag gis srog bcad pas /
NK109(dze)001:6162: ma 'ongs ba'i dus na yang pha rol gyi srog gcod pa 'ong dgos pas mi bden no //
NK109(dze)001:6163: de yang myong ba rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu mi bden /
NK109(dze)001:6164: 'di la myong ba'i phyi ma la mi myong ste /
NK109(dze)001:6165: 'di la dbul po phyi ma la dbul po 'ong bar mi srid pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6166: byed pa rgyu mthun pa da lta shan pa byed
NK109(dze)001:6167: pas phyi ma shan pa byed pa'i rgyu med pas
NK109(dze)001:6168: so // gtan tshigs lung gis kyang shes te /
NK109(dze)001:6169: sdig dang rnam smin dge ba'i grogs che ba zhes bya dang /
NK109(dze)001:6170: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang byang chub chen po'i lam las byung zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6171: des na rgyu 'bras la rjes med pas so //
NK109(dze)001:6172: gtan tshigs ni rgyu mtshan go bzlog gi gtan tshigs kyis 'grub ste /
NK109(dze)001:6173: rgyu sdig byas pas 'bras bu dge bar 'gro bar yin te /
NK109(dze)001:6174: rgyu dang mtshan nyid go bzlog phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:6175: de ltar mi bden pas las dang zhes pa de'i thog tu mi 'bab bo //
NK109(dze)001:6176: de'i rnam par smin pa yang rig pa nga yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:6177: de yang nga rang 'byung gi ye shes des 'jig rten brtan pa snod dang /
NK109(dze)001:6178: g.yo ba bcud kyi sems can kyang nga rig pa nyid yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:6179: spangs blang las 'das pa'i chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:6180: de'i phyir na g.yo ba bcud kyi 'gro ba sems
NK109(dze)001:6181: can dang mi 'gro ba brtan pa snod kyi 'jig
NK109(dze)001:6182: rten rig pa mi 'gyur ba dang ye shes kyi
NK109(dze)001:6183: rlung gis bskyod pas g.yo ba nga yin no //
NK109(dze)001:6184: rig pa las 'tshogs pa'i chos rnams 'byung ba'i lus su snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6185: ma dag pa'i dus na nyon mongs par snang bas rig pa nyid /
NK109(dze)001:6186: bla ma'i lung med pa rnams la dri ma las
NK109(dze)001:6187: dang nyon mongs pa ltar kyang nga rig pa las
NK109(dze)001:6188: byung ba'o // sgo las 'dzin pas dbang po gzung 'dzin las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:6189: gzugs la yang mig gis mthong ba'i dus na khyab pas /
NK109(dze)001:6190: de rnams kyang nga rig pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:6191: rig pa de'i yul sna tshogs su snang ba'i phung
NK109(dze)001:6192: po lnga yang spang du med pas rig pa de
NK109(dze)001:6193: nyid 'khor 'das kyi chos 'dus pas khams bco brgyad
NK109(dze)001:6195: de nyid sna tshogs par snang bas skye mched bcu
NK109(dze)001:6196: gnyis su byung ba nga rig pa de thams cad
NK109(dze)001:6197: sdud pas sha dang sa kun la khyab pas khrag
NK109(dze)001:6198: dang rigs mtshon cing gzhi la chags pas rus pa
NK109(dze)001:6200: de nyid brjod pa thams cad kyi gzhir 'gyur pas mig dang /
NK109(dze)001:6201: tshig gi bsgyur nus pas yi ge dang /
NK109(dze)001:6202: btags pa sna tshogs su byung bas sgra dang /
NK109(dze)001:6203: snang ba sna tshogs su shar bas gzugs su yang nga rig pa nyid du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6204: de nyid sems kyi rtog pa tha dad du byung bas gzung ba /
NK109(dze)001:6205: de la rtog cing dpyod pas 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6206: de nyid 'dzin pa med par rang grol bas yul dang /
NK109(dze)001:6207: de nyid bzhag pa tsam gyis grol bas bdag tu rtog pa yang /
NK109(dze)001:6208: de nyid bde ba dang sdug pa'i snang ba dus gcig tu rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:6211: de nyid kun la khyab pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6212: rgyu rkyen sna tshogs par byung bas 'khrul pa yang nga nyid /
NK109(dze)001:6213: de nyid kyi rgyan du snang ba thams cad shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:6214: sgra dang dri dang ro dang reg gi dmigs rten la brlabs pas /
NK109(dze)001:6215: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga lam du khyer nas 'bud tha ba yang rig pa /
NK109(dze)001:6216: de nyid sdug bsngal gyi mtha' zad pas /
NK109(dze)001:6217: dmyal ba tsha ba dang grang ba'i reg pa gnyis
NK109(dze)001:6218: lhan gcig tu nyams su myong ba'i shes pa 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:6219: nas / log par 'dzin pa yang nga rig pa nyid ye grol du ma shes pa las so //
NK109(dze)001:6220: de nyid zhe 'dod bral bas yi dwags bkres pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6221: sdug bsngal du sna nga ba yang nga rig pa
NK109(dze)001:6222: nyid zhen med rang grol du ma shes pa las
NK109(dze)001:6223: / byol song rmongs pa gti mug gi byed pa can du snang ba yang /
NK109(dze)001:6224: nga rang gsal spros pa dang bral bar ma shes pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6225: rig pa nyid mi rnams res bde ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6226: res sdug bsngal ba sems kyi rtog tshogs rang snang du ma shes pa las /
NK109(dze)001:6227: res btang snyoms su gnas pas nga rig pa rgyun chad su ma shes pa las so //
NK109(dze)001:6228: mdor na sems can la ji ltar snang yang /
NK109(dze)001:6229: rang 'byung gi ye shes las ma gtogs pa yang med par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6230: de dag ni don gyis rtogs pa chen po'i rnal
NK109(dze)001:6231: 'byor pas gang yang spang mi dgos pa la dgongs
NK109(dze)001:6232: pa'o // zhes nang don drug pa de ltar shes
NK109(dze)001:6233: pas 'di ltar snang ba thams cad rang gi rig
NK109(dze)001:6235: da ni nang don bdun pa de ltar byung bas
NK109(dze)001:6236: de nyid kyi gong na gzhan med par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:6237: ni / nga ni zhes 'gran pa'i zla med pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6238: rig pa ngan song gsum las mi 'pham pa gzhi
NK109(dze)001:6239: gnas kyi rig pa lhag mthong du bstan pas las
NK109(dze)001:6240: dang bag chags kun las rgyal ba'i zhes lta ba
NK109(dze)001:6242: nga ni btags pa rnam grangs kyi chos las 'das
NK109(dze)001:6243: pas bcos pa'i tshig byas pa las 'das pa'i phyir
NK109(dze)001:6244: / yid dpyod du med pas brjod byed kun la mngon gsum gnad kyis 'phags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6245: nga ni lta ba yin pa dang min pa las
NK109(dze)001:6246: 'das pas dngos po rdzas su grub med pas rtags
NK109(dze)001:6247: shes bya la grub pa med /
NK109(dze)001:6248: stong pa rang rgyud du ma song bas rang shes
NK109(dze)001:6249: rig tu gsal pas chad pa gnyis med la 'khor
NK109(dze)001:6250: 'das kun ltar zung 'jug gnyis snang 'das par 'jug
NK109(dze)001:6251: par yin no // nga ni yid dpyod kyis brtags shing dpyad kyang mthong ba'i yul med pas /
NK109(dze)001:6252: dngos po zad pa'i rig pa nyid gsal cha dang
NK109(dze)001:6253: bcas pa bla ma'i lung yod pa kun la mngon
NK109(dze)001:6255: nga ni sku dang ye shes thams cad gting nas
NK109(dze)001:6256: rdzogs so bas zab pa'i rig pa yul kun la
NK109(dze)001:6257: khyab pas brtan pa rnam grangs kyi chos las che
NK109(dze)001:6258: ba yin no // nga ni sa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6261: mthong ba'i lam la sogs pa gcig nas gcig tu
NK109(dze)001:6262: bgrod pa'i lam rig pa nyid du 'gyur ba med
NK109(dze)001:6263: pa'i / sa bcu la sogs pa kun las pha rol du zang thal chen por phyin pas /
NK109(dze)001:6264: rdzogs pa chen po sa gcig pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6266: rig pa gcig pu nyid yin pa la 'khor 'das
NK109(dze)001:6267: kun dang gnyis med zung 'jug tu 'brel ba yin
NK109(dze)001:6268: no // nga ni gang la yang mi gnas pa mngon gsum du snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:6269: gzhan du gnas pa med pa ni brtan g.yo kun la /
NK109(dze)001:6270: dngos med zang thal du brtan pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:6271: nga ni 'khrul ba zad pa'i rig pa rang gi
NK109(dze)001:6272: ngo bor dag pa las 'gran pa'i zla ma rig
NK109(dze)001:6273: pa med sangs rgyas sems can kun la rdzogs pa
NK109(dze)001:6274: chen po thig le nyag gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6275: da ni brtan g.yo la khyab pa'i rig pa'i ngo
NK109(dze)001:6276: bo gcig pu la bem po sa chu me rlung
NK109(dze)001:6277: la sogs pa rig pa shes pas bsdus pas gnyis
NK109(dze)001:6278: med pas / snang shes kun la til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa ltar khyab pa yin no //
NK109(dze)001:6279: nga ni mun pas gtum pa'i rig pa la gos
NK109(dze)001:6280: 'khor ba'i rtog pa tha dad pa gyon pas rtog
NK109(dze)001:6281: pa rnams kyi gzhi la nam mkha' la kun tu
NK109(dze)001:6282: zang thal mtha' yas pa'i 'od kyis snang ba ston
NK109(dze)001:6283: byed pa'o // zhes nang don bdun pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:6284: da ni nang don brgyad pa de ltar rang gi
NK109(dze)001:6285: rig pas rang gi don de nyid du go bar
NK109(dze)001:6286: bstan pa ni / nga yi shes rab kyi srid
NK109(dze)001:6287: pa gsum 'dus pa'i ri bo lus kyi rgyas rig
NK109(dze)001:6288: pa nyid 'thums pas theg pa'i stobs /
NK109(dze)001:6289: 'khor ba nyid du bzlog pas 'das pa'i stobs khams gsum du mi bzlog pas che ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6290: rgyun du brtags pa'i rig pa las dang bag chags
NK109(dze)001:6291: kyi rgya mtsho la rig pa mngon gsum gyi hub
NK109(dze)001:6292: kyis gnyis med du btab pas nyon mongs pa thams
NK109(dze)001:6293: cad dus gcig la zad de /
NK109(dze)001:6294: lto nyon mongs ye shes su 'gyur bas che'o //
NK109(dze)001:6295: nga yis ye shes rnam par dag pa'i ri bo
NK109(dze)001:6296: stong gsum gyi stong gi 'jig rten du khyab pa
NK109(dze)001:6297: nyid til 'bru mig chung bar rig pa bcud pas
NK109(dze)001:6298: med pa sum cu rtsa drug mthar phyin pas /
NK109(dze)001:6299: 'khor ba las bsgral bas che ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6300: nga yi ni 'khor 'das gnyis med du 'brel bas
NK109(dze)001:6301: mun pa'i go cha ni 'khor ba lta ba la
NK109(dze)001:6302: sbyar ba'o // de nyid chos nyid du khyer ba gyon pas /
NK109(dze)001:6303: zhes 'khor ba'i g.yul chos nyid du bzlog pas dpa' bo chen po zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6304: nga yir nyi shu ba rig pa'i skad cig ma
NK109(dze)001:6305: gsum la grol bas 'khor ba rang grol 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6306: don skad cig la mthong bas /
NK109(dze)001:6307: gom gcig chos nyid skad cig la rtogs pas 'khor
NK109(dze)001:6308: ba las mchongs pa ni mchongs pa lnga dang ldan
NK109(dze)001:6309: pas che ba'o // nga yis ni rig pa gzhi
NK109(dze)001:6310: gcig la 'khor 'das dus gcig la zil gyis gnon
NK109(dze)001:6311: pa ni sa dang po la sogs pa rnams 'di
NK109(dze)001:6312: nyid du dus skad cig la rtogs pa gzugs stong
NK109(dze)001:6313: par grol bas stong pa nyid gzugs su 'gyur ba'i
NK109(dze)001:6314: lcid 'gyur mthong ba'i rig pa che ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6315: nga yis ni shes rab nyi ma'i snang ba lus kyi chos stong nyid du rtogs la /
NK109(dze)001:6316: thabs zla ba'i snang ba lta bus lus ngag la bde ba dngos su skyes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:6317: de gnyis zung 'jug dbyer med pa'i bde chen rang
NK109(dze)001:6318: gnas rdzogs pa chen por bting bas 'od dang zer
NK109(dze)001:6320: bde stong zung du zhugs pas che'o //
NK109(dze)001:6322: da ni nang don dgu pa de ltar rtogs pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6323: gang zag gis chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i gdengs rnyed
NK109(dze)001:6325: nga la ni khyab che ba'i rig pa rtsol bsgrub las 'das pa /
NK109(dze)001:6326: 'khor 'das gnyis dus gcig la mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:6327: phyi lus ngag gi bya ba dang bral bas lus ngag yid rang snang cig par grol la /
NK109(dze)001:6328: nang rlung phyi nang du rgyu ba'i bya ba dang bral bas gzung 'dzin gyi ming med /
NK109(dze)001:6329: gsang pa rig pa'i bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:6330: rlung bskyod kyi 'gro 'ong dang bral bas da bzlog pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6331: nga brjod pa thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa'i rig
NK109(dze)001:6332: pa la yid kyi 'gyu ba med pas ma bcos
NK109(dze)001:6333: pa'i chos rnams rang byung bas thog ma'i byung khungs
NK109(dze)001:6335: nga rang shar ba'i rig pa la phyi nang gi
NK109(dze)001:6336: snang ba thogs pa med par shar bas byas pa
NK109(dze)001:6337: med pa'i rig pa rang la shar ba nyid do
NK109(dze)001:6338: // nga ye nas 'bud tha ba'i rig pa la rtog ces bya ba'am /
NK109(dze)001:6339: rig pa'i bzhag par rag lus pa med la /
NK109(dze)001:6340: ma rtogs zhes tha mal du song pa med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6341: dbang po la rno rtul med pa'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)001:6342: rig pa nyid ye sangs rgyas par ngos zin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6343: nga ma spyad ba'i rig pa la chos thams cad
NK109(dze)001:6344: dus gcig tu rdzogs pas 'bud thal re ba dang
NK109(dze)001:6345: / sems can la dog pa med pa'i phyir 'khor
NK109(dze)001:6346: ba dang 'das pa la dus la snga phyi med
NK109(dze)001:6347: / par / bya bral thig le nyag gcig du rdzogs so //
NK109(dze)001:6348: nga bag chags dang bral ba'i rig pa sdug bsngal
NK109(dze)001:6349: las grol pa la 'khor ba la ya nga ba
NK109(dze)001:6350: med / dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal la bag tsha ba med pas /
NK109(dze)001:6351: ngan song gsum gyi 'jigs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6352: rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6353: nyon mongs kun dang ye nas bral lo //
NK109(dze)001:6354: nga tshig las 'das pa'i rig pa bde brdal ba la /
NK109(dze)001:6355: lus ngag yid 'chos pa'i mkhan po yid kyi shes
NK109(dze)001:6356: pa med pas thog ma nas rang lta bu gnas
NK109(dze)001:6357: pa nyid do // nga yul sems las 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6358: rig pa gzhi gnas lugs su gnas pa la bzung
NK109(dze)001:6359: ba dang 'dzin pa'i yul du med pas thog ma
NK109(dze)001:6360: nas rang la gnas pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:6361: nga phyi nang las 'das pa'i rig pa gnyis su
NK109(dze)001:6362: med pa la snod dang nang bcud gnyis su med
NK109(dze)001:6363: pa 'di ltar snang ba thams cad nga rang byung
NK109(dze)001:6365: nga 'khrul pa rang dag pa'i rig pa'i ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:6366: gcig tu grol ba la chos can rnam grangs dang
NK109(dze)001:6367: / chos nyid rnam grangs ma yin pa med pas chos thams cad ngo bo gcig pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6368: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don dang po
NK109(dze)001:6369: dri ba dang bcas nga dgongs pa nyid kyi gnas
NK109(dze)001:6370: lugs bstan pa la nang don dgur byas nas bstan
NK109(dze)001:6371: to // da ni bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa ngo
NK109(dze)001:6372: bo nyid de la 'ching byed kyi dri ma gang
NK109(dze)001:6373: gis 'ching bar bya ba bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:6374: 'chang byed gyi dri ma dngos bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6375: de nyid 'bad med rang grol du bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6376: dang po la nying lag gi don bzhi'i bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6377: dang po de nyid gyi dri ba mdor bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:6378: ni / rdo rje ni ye shes lnga las grub pa /
NK109(dze)001:6379: de rtag tu 'dzin pas na sdud po'i khyad bar gyi chos so //
NK109(dze)001:6380: yang na mnan pa gsol pa ni ston pa la
NK109(dze)001:6381: gong du ston bas gsung pa de ltar 'jig pa
NK109(dze)001:6382: phyi snod de la nang bcud kyi sems can brten
NK109(dze)001:6384: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sku dang ye shes su gsung pa rnams /
NK109(dze)001:6385: thams cad ngo bo nyid kyi chos yin gsung sa pas na /
NK109(dze)001:6386: sems can 'di rnams 'bad pa med par grol ba lags sam /
NK109(dze)001:6387: 'og te gang gis 'a ching ba lags /
NK109(dze)001:6388: sngar gsung pa ltar na sems can de dag 'ching bar mi rigs lags na /
NK109(dze)001:6389: yang ni sems can kun gang gis kyang ma bcings pa de nyid rang don da lags sam /
NK109(dze)001:6390: 'on te snang grags 'khor 'das kyi chos 'di dag ma lags pa /
NK109(dze)001:6391: gzhan dag gis de rnams ma rtogs pas sems bcings pa lags pa /
NK109(dze)001:6392: sems rnams ni ma grol bar 'dug pas 'di dag bdag gis ma 'tshal na /
NK109(dze)001:6393: rtog pa tha dad pa'i tshogs bcom pa'i ston pa
NK109(dze)001:6394: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus pa dang ldan pa
NK109(dze)001:6395: / khams gsum las 'das pa nyid kyis bdag la gsungs dang zhes dris so //
NK109(dze)001:6396: yan lag gi don gnyis pa de yang glo bur
NK109(dze)001:6397: gyi dri ma de nyid kyis ngo bo la 'ching
NK109(dze)001:6398: byed dang bral ba bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:6399: 'khor ba'i nyes pa'i skyon bcom pa la legs pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa /
NK109(dze)001:6400: legs nyes las 'das pa'i ston pas bka' dngos su
NK109(dze)001:6401: sdud pa po lag na rdo rje'i rna ba'i dbang
NK109(dze)001:6402: por stsal pa / sems can thams cad la gnas
NK109(dze)001:6403: pa'i nyon mongs pa 'dod chags la sogs pa chos
NK109(dze)001:6405: 'dod chags la sogs pa ngo bo nyid kyis stong
NK109(dze)001:6406: pa'i phyir don dam pa la yod pa ma yin
NK109(dze)001:6407: te / dper na nam rig pa mkha' ye shes te /
NK109(dze)001:6408: phyi yi nam mkha' stong pa las sprin glo bur
NK109(dze)001:6409: du byung ba bzhin du sems can rnams la glo
NK109(dze)001:6410: bur du rgyu ma rig pa rkyen bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:6411: lus dang sems su bcas pas chos nyid bsgrib pa ltar snang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:6412: sprin de nyid nam mkha' nyid las gzhan gang nas kyang ma 'ongs te /
NK109(dze)001:6413: de rang las byung ba bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:6414: de bzhin du dang po yang nam mkha' las byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6415: bar du yang nam mkhar gnas la /
NK109(dze)001:6416: tha ma yang nam mkhar thim par shes na /
NK109(dze)001:6417: nam mkha' dang sprin pa dbyer med pas /
NK109(dze)001:6418: don gcig gi ngang du thim pa zhes bya ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:6419: de bzhin du nyon mongs pa'i dri ma chos nyid du rang grol nas /
NK109(dze)001:6420: sems can 'ching ba ga la 'gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:6421: de nyid rang grol ba'i gnad kyis so //
NK109(dze)001:6422: gal te nyon mongs pa de nyid la bden par bzung na /
NK109(dze)001:6423: de'i ngo bo nyid las byung ba'i phyir las dang nyon mongs pa sangs nas /
NK109(dze)001:6424: mkhyen pa'i ye shes su rgyas pa nyid kyang 'ching bar 'gyur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:6425: med par las yod par bzung pa'i rnam pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:6426: sems rnam par rtog pa du mas bsdus pa las
NK109(dze)001:6427: lus 'byung bas bskyed pa can rnams ni rang bden
NK109(dze)001:6429: cis mi 'ching ste med pa las yang dag tu bzung bas so //
NK109(dze)001:6430: de yang kun rdzob tsam du bden te don dam pa rang bzhin med par shes na /
NK109(dze)001:6431: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma rnams ni rang gi sar dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6432: dper na chu'i snyogs ma de ma brnyogs par bzhag rang sar dwangs pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:6433: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun don dam par rang bzhin med par gcig go /
NK109(dze)001:6434: zhes nying lag gi don gnyis pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6435: da ni nying lag gi don gsum pa chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:6436: stong pa nyid de ma shes pas de nyid kyi
NK109(dze)001:6437: 'ching byed kyi rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6438: gong du bstan pa de ltar dngos po med par ma shes na /
NK109(dze)001:6439: sems ca na rnams khams gsum du 'ching ste phung po la sogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6441: phung po khams dang skye mched ni /
NK109(dze)001:6442: rigs dang rigs kyi bdag por grol /
NK109(dze)001:6443: zhes pas rgyas par ston no //
NK109(dze)001:6445: da ni nying lag gi don bzhi pa dngos po
NK109(dze)001:6446: de dag gis 'ching byed rang gi ngo bo bstan
NK109(dze)001:6447: pa ni / khams gsum po'i khang pa ru zhes
NK109(dze)001:6448: pa 'og tu chos nyid gzhal yas kyis rgyas par
NK109(dze)001:6449: pa ni / bstan no // zhes nying lag gi don bzhi pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6450: de dag gi ni yan lag gi don dang po
NK109(dze)001:6451: 'chings byed dri ma dngos bstan pa la nying lag
NK109(dze)001:6452: don bzhir byas nas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:6453: da ni yan lag gi don gnyis pa de nyid
NK109(dze)001:6454: kyang 'bad med rang grol du bstan pa la nying
NK109(dze)001:6455: lag gi don lngas bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:6456: de nyid kyang thams cad mnyam pa ris med du rang grol bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6457: gsang ba'i bdag po la nye bar bskul nas /
NK109(dze)001:6458: rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po zhes bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:6459: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can khams gsum du
NK109(dze)001:6460: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal de dag ni gzhan las ma
NK109(dze)001:6461: byung bar rang gi rnam par rtog pa'i las kyis
NK109(dze)001:6463: rang bzhin du ma bcos pas grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:6464: gnad rnam pa bzhi la brten nas grol ba ste
NK109(dze)001:6465: de yang ye grol bskyar gzhi med pa'i gnad la
NK109(dze)001:6466: brten nas 'gro ba rnams 'bad rtsol med par grol
NK109(dze)001:6467: ba dang / rang grol la gnyen po med pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6468: gnad la brten nas las dang nyon mongs pa'i sas
NK109(dze)001:6469: ma bcings par rang grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6470: yongs grol la mtha' med pa'i gnad la brten nas gcig shes pas kun grol bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6471: cer grol mthong yal gyi gnad la brten nas 'phral gcer mthong du grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6472: de yang spyod pa cer grol gyis 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga chos nyid du 'gyur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:6473: goms stobs la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6475: goms stobs ni bslab bya'i yul du gyur pa de /
NK109(dze)001:6476: gzugs kyi dmigs rten la bslab pas gzugs chos nyid du grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6480: reg gi dmigs rten la bslab par rig chos nyid du grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6482: dbang po rang yan du bzhag pas tshogs drug gi brdar 'gyur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:6483: dbang po rang sar bzhag pa'i gnas brtsal pa gsum gyis yul sems ro mnyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6484: dbang po rang so'i 'phul gnyis kyis snang sems kyi dbyibs dbyung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6485: yan pa'i gags bzung ba drug gis 'gro ba drug gcer mthong du grol ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:6486: de ltar gnad bcu gcig gis /
NK109(dze)001:6487: snang ba snang thog tu grol ba bye'u khras khyer ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:6488: brtags dpyad blo las grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6489: de la brten nas shes pa 'gyus thog tu grol ba bar snang gi ser bu ltar /
NK109(dze)001:6490: ngos 'dzin blo'i rtog pa dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6491: de ltar na gcer bzhag gcer grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:6492: snang shes gnyis kyi rten zad /
NK109(dze)001:6493: gcer mthong gcer yal bas yul sems gnyis kyi gzhi stong /
NK109(dze)001:6494: gcer grol gcer dag pas lus sems gnyis kyi 'brel chad pas na /
NK109(dze)001:6495: spyod pa snang ba rang yan ba zhes bya ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6496: de la bsgom pa'i man ngag du yongs grol la mtha' med pa'i gnad de /
NK109(dze)001:6497: gcig shes kun grol ba'i 'gag 'gyu ba yul gtad pas /
NK109(dze)001:6498: byung tshor gyi rten nyams par byed pa'i gnad ni /
NK109(dze)001:6499: gcig rgyab kun la phog pa'i /
NK109(dze)001:6500: 'gags gnyis kyis 'khor 'das lto sbyar ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6501: kun brgyab gcig gsad ba'i mtshon drug gis 'khrul pa 'gags la gtad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6502: de gcig shes pas yongs grol ba mdud pa gcig
NK109(dze)001:6503: bkrol bas do thag brgya chad pa lta bu ste
NK109(dze)001:6504: / bem rig matha'i 'dzin pa las grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6505: de ltar bsgoms pa nyin mtshan kha sbyar bas /
NK109(dze)001:6507: yongs su grol ba zhes tha snyad du bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6508: rang grol la gnyen po med pa ni lta ba'i man ngag tu byung ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:6509: 'khrul pa nyid kyis 'khrul pa grol bas gzhan ma
NK109(dze)001:6510: 'khrul ba brtsal du ma rnyed pas 'khrul pa'i ming
NK109(dze)001:6511: med pa ste / de yang yongs drug gi gnad
NK109(dze)001:6512: la brten nas lus sems kyi 'brel gcad pas 'gro
NK109(dze)001:6513: ba drug rang sa nas grol ba bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:6514: med pa ste / / rang lugs gnyis kyi gnad
NK109(dze)001:6515: kyis 'gag bsdam pas 'khor 'das kyi lto bzlog pa'o
NK109(dze)001:6516: med pa ste / / // de yang snang ba
NK109(dze)001:6517: rang grol ba mkha' la 'ja' tshon yal ba lta
NK109(dze)001:6518: med pa ste / / // bu'o // shes pa
NK109(dze)001:6519: rang grol de mkha' la sprin dengs pa lta bur
NK109(dze)001:6520: rang byung rang grol ba la /
NK109(dze)001:6521: gong ma'i don snang rang yal la /
NK109(dze)001:6522: blo ma thog tu grol bas rtog pa rgyun chad /
NK109(dze)001:6523: de ltar chad pa de lta ba mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun chod pas khams gsum ming med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6524: de yang rang sems la rtsa ba med pas skye ba'i rgyu med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6525: gzhi med pas bzlog pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6526: dang po byung sa med pas 'gro ba'i lam stong pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6527: gnas pa'i sa med pas 'jug pa'i yul med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6528: 'gro ba'i sa med pas rgyu mtshan nyid du gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6529: brten med pas chags pa'i sa med pa'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)001:6530: grong khyer rgyun chad nas rang gis rang grol bas gnyen po gzhan med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6531: 'bras bu gnad du ye grol byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:6532: de sems kyi khang bu gzhig pa'i man ngag gis sems kyi ltos zad par khyab ste /
NK109(dze)001:6533: brdeg pa'i rdzong drug gi gnad kyis 'bram bsgyen pa rtsa ba bcad pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:6534: brdung pa'i tho chen bzhis la sogs bsgyon pa'i 'byung gzhi gnad la bor ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:6535: dbab pa'i thog chen gsum gyis thig bstims pas sems grangs gcod pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:6536: 'jug pa'i thabs gnyis kyi rtse rje phab pas dran shes 'gag la gtad pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:6537: 'gyogs byed kyi pho nya gnyis kyis bya ra ba
NK109(dze)001:6538: bsad pas 'gyu ba'i khungs 'gags pa'i man ngag ste
NK109(dze)001:6539: / de yang ye grol bas rgyas thebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6540: gtad pa'i 'ben med pas bskyar du med /
NK109(dze)001:6541: 'gyu ba'i ltos med pas dgags su med /
NK109(dze)001:6542: dran pa'i brtan nyams pas bslang du med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6543: des na rang bzhin rnam dag gi 'bras bu la grol ba'i sa med pas byung sa med /
NK109(dze)001:6544: rgyu med pas rkyen la rag ma lus /
NK109(dze)001:6545: 'bras bu med pas ye nas grol ba'i gnad med do //
NK109(dze)001:6546: des na 'gro ba rnams grol bar nges pa'i gdeng bzhi la brten nas grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:6548: chos kyi dbyings stong pa nyid du mnyam pa'i phyir na grol bar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:6549: zhes nying don dang po thams cad mnyam pa ris med du grol bar bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:6550: da ni nying lag gi don gnyis pa rgyu'i 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:6551: pa de dag rang snang du grol bar bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:6552: ni / gong du bstan pa'i grol lugs 'dir byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:6553: phung po gzugs kyi phung po phra ba dang rags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6554: phra ba ni rdul phra rab bdag tu med pa las byung bas na /
NK109(dze)001:6555: 'bru'i phung po spungs pa lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:6556: rags pa ni kha dog dang /
NK109(dze)001:6557: dbyibs te kha dog ni dkar po dang /
NK109(dze)001:6564: sngo sangs la sogs pa'i rigs rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:6565: dbyibs ni gru bzhi las gru yon dang /
NK109(dze)001:6567: gru lnga'am dgu la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6570: zlum po gru bzhi zla gam gru gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:6573: de yang rgyu'i gzugs rdul phra rab dang /
NK109(dze)001:6580: de ltar na brten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba la
NK109(dze)001:6581: sogs pa 'tshogs pa'i chos mang po 'dus pas na
NK109(dze)001:6582: 'bras bu'i phung po spungs pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:6583: tshor ba'i phung po gzugs la sogs pa myong reg nyams su myang ba sna tshogs te /
NK109(dze)001:6584: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis sdug pa nyams su myong ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6586: res btang snyoms su gnas pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:6587: de yang rtog pa rag pa mang po 'dus pas na phung po'o //
NK109(dze)001:6588: rnam pa shes pa'i phung po la rnam par shes
NK109(dze)001:6589: pa'i tshogs brgyad kyi yul rnams la rjes su 'gro
NK109(dze)001:6590: ba ldog du byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6591: mig gi rnam par shes pas yul gcod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6592: 'byed pa las sogs pa byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6593: de ltar shes pa 'dus pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6594: rnam par 'byed pa la sogs pa 'dus pa na phung po'o //
NK109(dze)001:6595: 'du shes ni rnam par rig byed dang rig byed ma yin pa la sogs pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6596: mig gi 'dus te reg ba'i rkyen gyis tshor ba'i
NK109(dze)001:6597: myong ba la sogs te mang po 'dus pas na
NK109(dze)001:6599: 'du byed kyi ni drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa
NK109(dze)001:6600: dang nyi shu nye ba'i dang lnga kun du 'gro
NK109(dze)001:6601: la sogs te 'du byed lnga bcu rtsa gnyis 'dus
NK109(dze)001:6603: de ltar phung po lnga 'gro ba bcings pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6604: gzugs la 'ching byed yod pas dngos po la 'jug pa'i sems su 'khrul pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:6605: de yang cha med pa'i rdul phra rab kyi bcings pas lus dang sems yang mi 'bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6606: tshor ba la 'ching byed yod pas /
NK109(dze)001:6607: bde sdug sna tshogs pas sems nyams su myong bas las bcings pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6608: rnam shes las 'ching byed yod pas yul dang shes
NK109(dze)001:6609: pa tha dad par ma yin pa sems rnam par
NK109(dze)001:6610: shes pa tsam du bcings pas sems kyi dran shes
NK109(dze)001:6613: sems byung tshor 'gag pa med par shar yang de nyid gtan la ma phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6614: 'du byed la 'ching byed yod pas sems mi dge ba sna tshogs su slong bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6615: de ltar la ni rigs lnga'i rgyas su grol te /
NK109(dze)001:6616: gzugs kyi phung po nyid rnam par snang mdzad du grol la /
NK109(dze)001:6617: rnam snang nyid gzugs su grol bas gnyis med spang blang las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:6618: de bzhin du tshor ba la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6619: khams ni mig gi khams dang /
NK109(dze)001:6620: mig gi rnam par shes pa'i khams dang /
NK109(dze)001:6624: rna ba'i rnam par shes pa'i khams la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:6625: bco brgyad kyis sems dpa' dang sems mar grol la
NK109(dze)001:6629: sgra la sogs pa bcu gnyis phyi'i lha mo brgyad
NK109(dze)001:6630: ni lha mo bzhi ste bcu gnyis su grol lo
NK109(dze)001:6632: zhes pa rigs lnga yab yum bcu la /
NK109(dze)001:6633: rigs kyi bdag po ni gtso bo lngar grongs pas de dang dbyer mi phyed do /
NK109(dze)001:6634: gong ma'i gzung ba ni yul tsam las 'khrul pa ma yin pa las yang dag par bzung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:6635: tsam po las 'khrul pas de ltar snang shes kyis bsdus pa'i don snang ba yin pas so //
NK109(dze)001:6636: bye brag pa ni dung dkar po las ser por bzung pa'o lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:6637: de la 'dzin pa'i sems kyis zhen pas chos can du snang bas 'khrul pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:6638: de yang thabs bla ma'i gdams pas lus ngag la
NK109(dze)001:6639: bde ba bskyed na 'dzin pa zhen pa rang rgyud
NK109(dze)001:6640: pa las grol bas 'dzin pa sems kyis 'khrul pa'i
NK109(dze)001:6641: ming med shes rab kyis stong par brtag pas bzung
NK109(dze)001:6642: ba yul gyi 'khrul pa stong par grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:6643: de ltar 'khor ba zhes bya ste yang gcig tu 'khor bas na 'khor ba zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:6646: de dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:6647: chos kyi dbyings stong pa mtha' dang dbus med pa
NK109(dze)001:6648: nyid du grol spang blang dang rtsol bsgrub las 'das
NK109(dze)001:6649: pa'o // zhes nying lag gi don gnyis pa rgyu'i 'khrul pa de dag rang grol du bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:6650: da ni nying lag gi don gsum pa nyon mongs
NK109(dze)001:6651: de dag kyang ye nas 'di ltar grol bar bstan
NK109(dze)001:6652: pa ni / gong du khams gsum po'i khang par zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:6653: de yang 'dod pa'i khams 'dod pa'o rgyu lnga las byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6654: gzugs kyi khams gzugs kyi 'du byed bcu gnyis las byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:6655: gzugs med pa'i khams med pa'i lam brgyad las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:6657: 'dod pa'i rgyu dngos dran pa la de la cher chags pas 'dod chags zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:6658: 'dod chags kyis 'bras bu srog gcod par byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6659: 'di'i gti mug ma byin par len par byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6660: de'i zhe sdang gi 'bras bu brdzun du byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:6661: de'i nga rgyal gyi 'bras bu'i nga'i snyam par byung /
NK109(dze)001:6662: de'i phrag dog gi 'bras bu gzhan sel ba byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:6663: gti mug gi lam la phyin ci log tu 'gyur /
NK109(dze)001:6664: de'i gti mug gi 'bras bu nyid du byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6665: de'i 'dod chags kyi 'bras bu mi tshangs par spyod pa byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6666: de'i zhe sdang gi 'bras bu rgol bar byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6667: de'i nga rgyal gyi 'bras bu khengs par byung la /
NK109(dze)001:6668: de'i phrag dog gi 'bras bu 'khon du 'dzin par byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:6669: yang de'i byed pa'i rgyu zhe sdang gis gzugs sna tshogs par byas la /
NK109(dze)001:6670: de'i zhe sdang gi 'bras bu phyir rgol bar byas la /
NK109(dze)001:6671: de'i gti mug gis rnam par rmugs byas /
NK109(dze)001:6672: de'i 'dod chags kyis rgyags par byas /
NK109(dze)001:6673: de'i nga rgyal gyis rgol par byas /
NK109(dze)001:6674: de'i phrag dog gis rnam par g.yeng bar byas so //
NK109(dze)001:6675: 'dzin pa'i rgyu nga rgyal gyis byas pas dbang po mi 'dra ba tha dad par byas te /
NK109(dze)001:6676: de'i nga rgyal gyis khro bar byas /
NK109(dze)001:6677: de'i gti mug gis bying bar byas /
NK109(dze)001:6678: de'i zhe sdang gis ma byin pa'i las su byas /
NK109(dze)001:6679: de'i 'dod chags kyis rnam par rengs par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:6680: de'i phrag dog gis khong khro bar byas /
NK109(dze)001:6681: de'i bsags pa'i rgyu ni phrag dog gis las tha dad par byas te /
