NK109(dze)001:7979: sems phyi ltar shar bas snang ba nang ltar shar bas stong pa /
NK109(dze)001:7980: gsang ba ltar shar bas rig pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:7981: dam tshig dang zhes pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:7982: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs dang /
NK109(dze)001:7983: yan lag grangs te sems 'khor 'das kyi rtsa ba yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:7984: de las yan lag gi chos kyi rnam grangs dpag tu med par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:7985: man ngag 'khor dang zhes pa ni lta ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:7988: sems de lta sgom gyi gzhir gyur pas so //
NK109(dze)001:7989: nyams myong dang ni shes pa'i nyams gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:7991: snang ba'i nyams gsal ba de /
NK109(dze)001:7992: sems nyid bde gsal gnyis su med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:7993: de bzhin du 'byung ba rim brtsegs nas lha so
NK109(dze)001:7994: so'i skur bzhengs pa'i bskyed pa'i rim pa dang zhes
NK109(dze)001:7995: pa ni rig pa nyid rim gyis rtogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:7996: chos thams cad gcig char du khong du chud pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:7997: zhes nang don gnyis pa sngags la 'jug par byed
NK109(dze)001:7998: pa rtsa ba'i chos rnams de nyid la rdzogs par
NK109(dze)001:7999: bstan nas / da ni nang don gsum pa lam
NK109(dze)001:8000: du spyad pa'i chos rnams de nyid la rdzogs par
NK109(dze)001:8001: bstan nas / bstan pa ni / thos dang ni sgro 'dogs gcod pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:8002: sems la brten nas phyi nang gi sgro 'dogs gcod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8003: bsam pa dang ni nyon mongs pa'i mgo sems kyis gnan nas ye shes su gsal bar byed do //
NK109(dze)001:8004: bsgom pa dang zhes pa sems kyi nyon mongs pa rtsa ba nas spong par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8005: rig pa ye sangs rgyas pas lta ba la re dogs med /
NK109(dze)001:8006: de la rgyun du spyod pas spyod pa la dgag bsgrub med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8007: de la gsal 'grib med pas sgom pa chu bo'i rlung chen yin /
NK109(dze)001:8011: shin tu gtong ba cha na po'o //
NK109(dze)001:8012: tshul khrims ni dge ba chos sdud /
NK109(dze)001:8013: sems can don byed bsdom pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK109(dze)001:8014: chos zab mo la nges par sems pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8015: sdug bsngal dang du len pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8016: cir mi snyam pa'i bzod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8020: yon tan mngon par 'byung ba'i bsam gtan dang /
NK109(dze)001:8021: ting nge 'dzin 'das pa chen po'i bsam gtan dang /
NK109(dze)001:8022: 'jig rten pa'i sems rnam par gdul ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8026: gzhan zil gyis gnon pa'i stobs dang /
NK109(dze)001:8029: dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i smon lam dang /
NK109(dze)001:8031: yid las 'das pa'i smon lam mo //
NK109(dze)001:8032: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)001:8033: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)001:8035: de bzhin du thams cad bsdud pa'i thabs dang /
NK109(dze)001:8036: gzhan la 'jug par 'gyur ba'i thabs dang /
NK109(dze)001:8038: de dag kyang rig pa'i rtsal las byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:8039: de kun gyi pha rol na chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8040: rig pa dngos gsum gyi chos nyid gnas so //
NK109(dze)001:8041: dge ba lus kyi gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:8043: sems kyi gsum ste bcu spyod pa la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:8044: dkar po'i chos spyod pa kun kyang lus dang sems
NK109(dze)001:8047: da ni nang don bzhi pa dngos po gshis kyi
NK109(dze)001:8048: chos nyid thams cad kyang de nyid la rdzogs par
NK109(dze)001:8049: bstan pa ni / rno ba'i thabs rgyu yod pa'i
NK109(dze)001:8050: lcags kyi ral gri la til mar gyi ngar gyis
NK109(dze)001:8052: sla ba'i thabs mig 'phrul gyi rol mo lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8053: che ba'i thabs dbus kyi ri rab kyi steng du phyin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8054: de yang bla ma'i gdams ngag la rag lus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8055: 'di ni lus la gnas pa dang sbyar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8056: sdud pa byed pa'i shes rab tsh+wa la dang gar spyin lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8057: 'gyed pa'i nam mkha' la sprin gtor ba lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8058: bsgrol ba'i ti pa ra'i bu sgrol byed kyi bu mtshon thog pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8059: bskyod pa'i dar po che rlung gis bskyod pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:8060: khyab byed kyi til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa lta bu /
NK109(dze)001:8061: rig pa rgya che bas dbyings dang /
NK109(dze)001:8062: gsal bas rig par snang ba dngos su bltar yod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8063: de ltar snang la rang bzhin med pas sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:8064: gsal la rtog pa med pas ye shes /
NK109(dze)001:8065: ngo bo ka nas dag pas rang gi 'dug tshul /
NK109(dze)001:8066: de gnas pa'i cha nas gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:8067: mngon du gyur pa'i cha nas lam dang /
NK109(dze)001:8068: mthar phyin pa'i ngos nas 'bras bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:8070: rang gi ngo bo'i cha nas rtogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8071: yul can la rtog pa'i cha nas rtogs tshul ltar byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8073: snang ba dngos yin pas kha dog dang /
NK109(dze)001:8074: mkhyen pa'i cha ma 'gags pas yul lnga nyid du yang snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8075: de dngos po las 'das te rdzas su grub pa ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:8076: stong pa nyid thams cad dang /
NK109(dze)001:8077: blo'i rnam par rtog pa ma yin pas spros pa med pa thams cad ltar byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8078: de nyid mi 'gyur ba'i ngos nas ngo bor byung /
NK109(dze)001:8079: snang ba'i cha nas rang bzhin du byung la kun
NK109(dze)001:8080: la khyab pa'i ngos nas thugs rje ltar yang byung
NK109(dze)001:8081: ba'o // de nyid ma bcos pas ngang /
NK109(dze)001:8082: rang gsal bas rang bzhin 'gyur ba ma yin pas bdag nyid chen po'o //
NK109(dze)001:8083: de thog ma'i gzhi yin pas ka dag nyid dang /
NK109(dze)001:8084: de'i bzhin snang lugs su shar bas lhun grub dang /
NK109(dze)001:8085: de nyid sna tshogs su shar bas lhun grub sgo brgyad ltar shar nas /
NK109(dze)001:8086: sangs rgyas dang sems spyi'i gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:8087: de nyid gzhi dang gzhi shes pa'i khyad par las shes bya kha phyir bltas pas 'khrul ba'i gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:8088: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don gsum pa
NK109(dze)001:8089: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i lus dang
NK109(dze)001:8090: sems la ji ltar tshang bar bstan pa la gzhir
NK109(dze)001:8092: da ni bsdus pa'i don bzhi pa dkon mchog gsum
NK109(dze)001:8093: rang gi lus la ji ltar rdzogs par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8094: la nang don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po dkon
NK109(dze)001:8095: mchog gsum gyi tshang lugs mdor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8096: e ma la sogs pa'i tshig gsum 'og nas rgyas pa ston /
NK109(dze)001:8098: da ni nang don gnyis pa dkon mchog gsum gyi don rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8099: de yang gong gi sangs rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:8100: dkon mchog gi don rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8104: de la chos kyi sku la ngo bo /
NK109(dze)001:8108: ngo bo de'i bzhugs tshul gang gis kyang ma gos bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8109: ka dag pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:8110: ngo bo de'i mtshan nyid stong pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8111: de'i rang bzhin gang dang yang ma 'dres pa /
NK109(dze)001:8112: de'i thugs rje 'byed pa med pa'i ngo bo de'i snang tshul gnyis su med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8113: nges tshig btags pa rnam grangs kyi chos las skur
NK109(dze)001:8114: smin pas mtshan nyid gang gis kyang gtan la mi
NK109(dze)001:8115: phebs / rnam grangs ma yin pa'i chos las skur
NK109(dze)001:8116: smin pas stong nyid gang du yang ma grub pas
NK109(dze)001:8117: na chos sku zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:8118: chos ni khyad par du gyur pa /
NK109(dze)001:8119: kyi ni chos dang skur 'brel ba /
NK109(dze)001:8120: sku ni zhal phyag tu med pa'i smin so tsam las skur ming du btags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8121: dbyer na dngos po'i mtshan nyid dang bral ba'i chos sku /
NK109(dze)001:8123: gdul byas snang tshul gyi chos sku'o //
NK109(dze)001:8124: dngos po'i mtshan nyid dang bral ba'i ni /
NK109(dze)001:8125: gang gis ngo bor yang ma grub la /
NK109(dze)001:8126: rgyu mtshan gang du yang med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8127: de la ltar med pas zhal phyag tu mi snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8128: byar med pas gzugs brnyan ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:8129: rgyu med pas rkyen gyis mi shigs /
NK109(dze)001:8130: skye ba med pas tha ma 'chi ba med mi gnas /
NK109(dze)001:8131: ldog med pas de las 'gres gzhan med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8132: gnas pa 'jug tshul gyi chos sku ni /
NK109(dze)001:8133: kun la khyab pas gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:8134: de nyid sna tshogs su snang bas lam yin la /
NK109(dze)001:8135: de nyid rang la smin pas 'bras bu ste /
NK109(dze)001:8136: sangs rgyas dang sems dbyer med du khyab pa'i sems so //
NK109(dze)001:8137: gdul bya snang tshul gyi chos sku ni /
NK109(dze)001:8138: theg pa'i yang sgo re re nas gtan la 'bebs lugs re /
NK109(dze)001:8139: gang la gang 'thad du byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8140: de la rnam par 'phrul pas phye na gdul bya'i dbang du pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8141: chos kyi sku chos sku'i zhing khams chos kyi dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8142: gnas bsam ngo las 'das pa'i chos nyid ting nge
NK109(dze)001:8143: 'dzin mi g.yo ba chen po 'khor sna tshogs rang
NK109(dze)001:8145: bstan pa brjod du med pa'i chos nyid dus gang du yang 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid /
NK109(dze)001:8146: de'i longs sku'i zhing khams rdul dang bral zhing dri ma med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8147: gnas dran pa yid kyi rtog pa chod pa /
NK109(dze)001:8148: ting nge 'dzin sems pa dang 'dun pa med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8149: 'khor stong pa rang bzhin gyi byed pa can /
NK109(dze)001:8150: bstan pa dmigs pa yongs su dag pa /
NK109(dze)001:8151: dus rtag pa ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8152: de'i sprul sku'i zhing khams stong nyid rgya ma chad pa /
NK109(dze)001:8154: ting nge 'dzin 'gag med kun tu gsal /
NK109(dze)001:8156: bstan pa rang bzhin ma bcos pa /
NK109(dze)001:8157: dus snying po mngon par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8158: longs sku'i ngo bo mtshan nyid rang gsal chen po la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8159: de'i bzhugs tshul rang bzhin las ma g.yos pa'i sku'o //
NK109(dze)001:8160: de nyid dngos thabs dang shes rab rang ngo na gsal ba las mi g.yo /
NK109(dze)001:8161: nges tshig ni longs snang ba la /
NK109(dze)001:8162: de nyid mkhyen pa ma 'gags par spyod pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8163: sku ni snang ba rang gsal bkod pa chen po'o //
NK109(dze)001:8164: dbye na 'byung ba ngo bo'i longs sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:8167: gdul bya snang tshul gyi longs sku dang bzhi'o //
NK109(dze)001:8168: 'byung ba'i ngo bo'i longs sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:8169: chos kyi sku las byung bas na /
NK109(dze)001:8173: sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad la 'od dang /
NK109(dze)001:8175: snang ba lam gyi ni chos nyid kyi bar ma do la'o //
NK109(dze)001:8182: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan du gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8183: gdul bya snang tshul gyi longs sku ni /
NK109(dze)001:8184: theg pa so so'i 'dod gzhung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:8185: de las rnam 'phrul gyis phye na /
NK109(dze)001:8186: gdul bya'i dbang du byas pa /
NK109(dze)001:8187: longs sku'i chos sku dpal rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho de'i bzhugs tshul lam mtshan nyid /
NK109(dze)001:8188: phyi nas bltas nas nang gsal /
NK109(dze)001:8189: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal /
NK109(dze)001:8190: mdun rgyab med pa zhal phyogs bcu kun du thal le ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8191: de'i zhing khams phyag gi mthil na 'jig rten gyi khams ni nyi ma gcig la mnga' mdzad /
NK109(dze)001:8192: gnas rnam dag stug po bkod pa /
NK109(dze)001:8193: 'khor nyid las mi gzhan pa bstan pa rang 'byung gi ye shes rang dbang ba /
NK109(dze)001:8194: dus rtag pa mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8195: de'i longs sku rigs kyi gtso bo /
NK109(dze)001:8196: de nyid kyi mtshan nyid ngo bo tha dad pa la rang bzhin gcig pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8197: zhing khams so so rigs kyi dkyil 'khor grangs med pa brgyad la dbang bsgyur /
NK109(dze)001:8200: bstan pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes lnga la 'jol nyog tu longs spyod /
NK109(dze)001:8201: dus ni snang ba 'du ba dang mched pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8202: de'i sprul pa'i sku ni rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas so so'i gtso 'khor ro //
NK109(dze)001:8203: de'i mtshan nyid snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8204: gsal la stong pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8205: de'i zhing khams lha dang lha mo 'bum bsam gyis mi khyab pa la longs spyod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8207: 'khor sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpag tu med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8208: dus rig pa rang snang ba'i dus so //
NK109(dze)001:8209: sprul pa sku'i ngo bo sna tshogs nges med /
NK109(dze)001:8210: de'i bzhugs tshul chags zhen las rnam par grol ba /
NK109(dze)001:8211: ting nge 'dzin mdzad pa'i thugs la mnyam par gnas /
NK109(dze)001:8212: nges tshig gang la gang 'dul du sprul pas na sprul /
NK109(dze)001:8213: de nyid gzugs phun sum tshogs pas na sku'o //
NK109(dze)001:8214: dbye na ma dag pa sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:8217: ma dag pa'i 'di ltar nges par smad 'tshong la
NK109(dze)001:8218: sogs pa la bu chos nyid mthong la 'byung bar
NK109(dze)001:8219: ma nges pa'o // rang bzhin bsgrangs pa'i 'og min no //
NK109(dze)001:8220: 'gro ba 'dul ba gang la gang 'dul gyi de'i gzugs su dang /
NK109(dze)001:8221: skad la sogs pa sprul pa thub drug go /
NK109(dze)001:8222: de'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i gdul bya'i dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)001:8223: sprul pa sku'i chos sku dpal rdo rje 'chang chen po'o //
NK109(dze)001:8224: de'i mtshan nyid skye ba bzhi'i lus su byung zhing
NK109(dze)001:8225: mdzad pa sum cu rtsa drug mthar phyin par zhal
NK109(dze)001:8226: gyis bzhes pa / de'i zhing khams stong gsum gyi
NK109(dze)001:8227: stong bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong grangs med pa
NK109(dze)001:8229: de'i gnas me tog pad+ma kha stong dang ldan pa /
NK109(dze)001:8230: 'khor skye ba bzhis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba /
NK109(dze)001:8231: bstan pa sdee snod kun gyi rtsa ba sgra thal 'gyur chen po /
NK109(dze)001:8232: dus tshe lo dpag du med pa thub pa'i dus na'o //
NK109(dze)001:8233: de'i longs sku dpal rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje
NK109(dze)001:8234: chen po'i rtags sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa
NK109(dze)001:8235: / de'i zhing khams stong gsum gyi bye ba phrag brgya gnas 'dul ngo dang sbyar ba /
NK109(dze)001:8236: 'khor sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8237: nges pa don gyi theg pa dus nges pa med
NK109(dze)001:8238: pa'o // de'i sprul pa'i sku sh+aakya thub pa /
NK109(dze)001:8239: de nyid khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung nas /
NK109(dze)001:8240: nyid kyi mdzad pa la longs spyod /
NK109(dze)001:8241: zhing khams 'dzam bu gling bye ba phrag brgya la mnga' mdzad /
NK109(dze)001:8242: gnas bya rgod kyi phung po'i ri /
NK109(dze)001:8244: bstan pa rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa sna tshogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:8245: dus ni nges pa chen po rnam par gcod pa'i dus so //
NK109(dze)001:8246: de dag ni sangs rgyas dkon mchog gi rang bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:8247: de yang dkon pas dpe bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:8249: mchog gi yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8250: sangs rgyas yongs pa phun sum 'tshogs pa la sogs
NK109(dze)001:8251: pa'i yon tan dpag tu med pa la sogs pa'i
NK109(dze)001:8252: mnga' brnyes pas na sangs rgyas so //
NK109(dze)001:8254: chos sku longs sku sprul pa'i sku gsum mo //
NK109(dze)001:8255: de la gong du chos dang zhes pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8256: mdo sde la drang ba don gyi dang /
NK109(dze)001:8258: 'dul ba ni lung shes gtso ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8259: dngos po gtso ba'i bca' gzhi mngon pa'i sde snod ni gzhi gtso ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8260: dngos po gtan la phab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8261: de yang kha che'i bye brag smra ba'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:8263: rtogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi chos dang /
NK109(dze)001:8264: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8266: ngo bo ni dge ba rnam par sems pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8267: gang zag gi bdag 'dzin spongs pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8268: nges tshig dge ba la 'dun pas dge 'dun zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8271: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun no //
NK109(dze)001:8272: nyan thos ni bye brag tu smra ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8274: nyan thos kyi gang zag ni spyir sde ba bco brgyad la /
NK109(dze)001:8275: 'dir ni rtsa ba'i sde pa bzhi ni phal chen la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8277: bden pa bzhi ni 'khor ba'i lam 'bras bur bcas pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8278: 'das pa'i lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8279: rang rgyal gyi dge 'dun ni zag pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8281: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun las 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8282: sa dang po la gnas pa la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8283: zhes bsdus pa'i don bzhi pa rang gi lus dang
NK109(dze)001:8284: sems la dkon mchog gsum tshang bar bstan pa la
NK109(dze)001:8285: gnyis su byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:8286: da ni bsdus pa'i don lnga pa dkar po'i chos
NK109(dze)001:8287: de dag rang gi lta ba'i ngo la ji ltar
NK109(dze)001:8288: tshang bar bstan pa la gnas don bcu gnyis kyis
NK109(dze)001:8289: bstan pa'i dang po rnal 'byor pa'i lus dang sems
NK109(dze)001:8290: la ji ltar rdzogs lugs zhus par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:8291: / rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs pa'i tshig bdun gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:8292: da ni nang don gnyis pa de dag kyang stong
NK109(dze)001:8293: pa nyid las ma grub kyang 'dir rdzogs par bstan
NK109(dze)001:8294: pa dngos ni / rdo rje ni bde ba dang stong pa dbyer med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8295: de la rgyun du gnas pas 'chang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8296: bka' de dag gi don la ma grub par rtsal to //
NK109(dze)001:8297: gzhis ni khyab pa'i gzhi 'gro ba kun la gnas pa'i ye shes /
NK109(dze)001:8298: gnas pa'i gzhi ka nas dag pas gang yang ma grub /
NK109(dze)001:8299: snang ba'i gzhi cir yang snang ba /
NK109(dze)001:8301: dngos po stong pa nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:8302: de yang gzhi dang gzhi shes pa'i khyad par las /
NK109(dze)001:8305: snang ba la sogs pa thams cad ngo bo ka dag pa'i chos tshig tsam ma yin pa /
NK109(dze)001:8306: dbyings stong zhing bdag med par dag go /
NK109(dze)001:8307: lus kyi sems la stong pa'i rgyas btab pas rang snang rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:8308: sems la lus rang bzhin stong pa nyid kyis rgyas btab pas /
NK109(dze)001:8309: phyi rol gyi lus kyi dngos po rdul phra rab
NK109(dze)001:8310: zag pa dang bcas pa rang grol ba ni de
NK109(dze)001:8311: nyid stong par shes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8314: 'di ltar snang bas bsdus pa'o chos rnams rang gi lus dang sems la rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8316: da ni nang don gsum pa gong du bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8317: de dag gi don rdzogs lugs rgyas par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8318: ni / gong du dkyil 'khor la sogs pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8319: tshom bu ni shar rdo rje rigs kyi tshom bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:8323: dbus na de bzhin bde gshegs rigs kyi tshom bu dang lnga ni /
NK109(dze)001:8324: ye nas rnam par dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:8325: rig pa gcig pu'i chos nyid dkyil dang /
NK109(dze)001:8326: zhes bya ba ye shes lnga 'khor du byung bas
NK109(dze)001:8327: dal spro mi dgos pas stsol bsgrub las 'das pa'o
NK109(dze)001:8328: // rang gi rig pa la rtag tu goms pa ni mchod pa'i gnas su gyur pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8329: rang sa'i ngo bo ka dag tu rtogs na lha ni rig pa rang che bas /
NK109(dze)001:8330: gzhan nas yi dam brtsal mi dgos pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8332: rig pa'i gnad la goms par byas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8334: de nyid la nyams su myong ba'i byi dor byas
NK109(dze)001:8335: pas ni rang la gnas pa'i mchod pa zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:8336: // rang gi dkyil rig pa 'khor ye shes de
NK109(dze)001:8337: nyid mngon sum du mthong pas na rang nyid mched
NK109(dze)001:8338: // pa'o // de la tshig med pas brjod cing
NK109(dze)001:8339: tshig gi rtog dpyod mi dgos smra ba'i rgyu med
NK109(dze)001:8340: pas chos nya da bsam pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8341: gzhal bya'i yul med pas brjod bya'i gzhi med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8342: rang gis smras pa thams cad rang gi rtsa gnas
NK109(dze)001:8343: kyi yi ge'i gnad kyis sngags tshig tu 'gro ba
NK109(dze)001:8344: ni / brjod pa yi ge'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8345: ched du lag pa'i phyag rgya bskyod cing sor mo /
NK109(dze)001:8346: bsgyur ba rang gi rig pa nyid yin pas yan
NK109(dze)001:8347: lag ma bsgyur bar bsgul bskyod ci byas tshad phyag
NK109(dze)001:8348: dngos po stong pa bzung la /
NK109(dze)001:8349: rgya stong pas ye shes la btab pas /
NK109(dze)001:8350: snang ba phyag rgya chen por rdzogs pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8351: las kyi phyag bsgyur byed la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:8352: phyag rgya chen po yod la mi byed pa'i don zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8353: sems brtag dpyad kyis bsam pas /
NK109(dze)001:8354: ngo bo stong pa nyid la rnam rtog rang sangs pas rtsol bsgrub dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)001:8355: rig pa nyid ma skyed ye nas rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8356: rgyu med pas ting nge 'dzin bsgom du med do //
NK109(dze)001:8357: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bzhi ye nas gzhi dngos po'i 'dug tshul la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:8359: dkyil 'khor dang la sogs pa lus tshi chad pa
NK109(dze)001:8360: las mi dgos par brda dang rten 'brel la brten
NK109(dze)001:8361: nas / shin tu spros pa med pa'idabanga ma bskur bar thob pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8362: sems la nges shes cig char du skyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8364: dam tshig ye nas gdengs dang ldan pas dam tshig
NK109(dze)001:8365: srung pa'i yul de rang dag pas 'di dang 'di'i
NK109(dze)001:8366: mtshams med de 'da' ba dang bral ba'i phyir ro
NK109(dze)001:8367: // tshig tu brjod pa'i rtsa ba yan lag gi
NK109(dze)001:8368: dam tshig srung bya'i yul las 'das pa'i phyir ro
NK109(dze)001:8369: // // phyi'i snang ba chos nyid du rang grol /
NK109(dze)001:8370: tshig gis mtshon pa'i man ngag gis 'bu mi tha ste /
NK109(dze)001:8371: rang gi rig pa zhes pa nas /
NK109(dze)001:8372: rig pa nyid so bslod pa tsam gyis grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:8374: 'bad med rang las byung las rang grol la /
NK109(dze)001:8375: gnyen po med pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8376: de nyid so bslod pas nyams su myong ba ye
NK109(dze)001:8377: nas gnas pa'i gding rang la skyes pas 'khor 'das
NK109(dze)001:8379: rang gi snying na chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum /
NK109(dze)001:8380: yi ge las ma bskyod par ye nas rang la
NK109(dze)001:8381: rdzogs pas bskyed pa'i rim pa rang las byung bas
NK109(dze)001:8382: na gzhan nas btsal mi dgos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8383: zhes nang don gsum pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:8384: da ni nang don bzhi pa 'di ltar snang ba'i
NK109(dze)001:8385: chos thams cad btags pas ma grub par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8386: ni // 'di ltar gyi tshig gnyis gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:8388: da ni nang don lnga pa de dag kyang thos bsam gyis blo las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8389: brjod pa sna tshogs snang ba'i sgra brjod pas thog tu mi phebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8391: brjod pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK109(dze)001:8392: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo brjod pa dang bral ba'i phyir na thos pa byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:8393: brjod du med pa'i don mi rnyed do //
NK109(dze)001:8394: tshig gcig gis rtogs pas na mang po brjod du
NK109(dze)001:8395: med pas rang rig pa bde ba chen po zhes
NK109(dze)001:8396: rang gi rgyud las skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:8398: de la rang gi rig pa'i ye shes brtag dpyad kyis mi grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:8399: bsam pas chos nyid ma mthong ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8400: phyi rol snang ba kun la snang pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8401: da bsam zhing brtags shing dpyad pa'i yul las 'das pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:8402: rang la shar ba'i don ni brtags pas mi mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:8403: rig pa'i ye shes nyid ye nas bsgoms pa dang bral bas te rang la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:8404: chos nyid la bsgoms par bya zhing lus ngag bcos pa'i tshig las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8405: de nyid las grol ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8406: bsgoms bsgrub la rag ma lus pa'i rig pa phyogs med du gsal ba zhes bya /
NK109(dze)001:8408: da ni nang don drug pa lta sgom spyod pa
NK109(dze)001:8409: nyid kyang rang gi ngo bo yin par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8410: ni / rig pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba ma rnyed /
NK109(dze)001:8411: de ma rnyed pas 'das pa'i ming med /
NK109(dze)001:8412: de ltar gnyis ni rang rig pa nyid la rdzogs
NK109(dze)001:8413: pas de la shes rig gi dngos po zad pas
NK109(dze)001:8414: stong pa ste / de la 'bad pa med pas
NK109(dze)001:8415: rang grol bas gzhan la rag lus pa med pas
NK109(dze)001:8416: stong pa ste / na / lta ba chen po zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8417: de'i gnad kyi phyi rol gyi snang ba rnams ni
NK109(dze)001:8418: 'du 'bral med par ting nge 'dzin rang gi sems
NK109(dze)001:8419: la gsal bas / de las yangs pa'i sa med
NK109(dze)001:8420: pas sgom nyin mtshan kha sbyor ba'i gdeng rnyed pas
NK109(dze)001:8421: la gsal bas / / cir snang nyams su myong bar 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8423: da ni nang don bdun pa pha rol tu phyin
NK109(dze)001:8424: pa bcu yang de nyid la rdzogs par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8425: ni / rig pa'i ngo bo yul dang yul can
NK109(dze)001:8426: du med pas dmigs pa gzhan la gtang ba dang
NK109(dze)001:8427: ni / / mi gtang pa med pas btang ba'i blo med pas 'bad mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:8428: bzhag pa'i zhen pa med pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8429: yul gzhan la dmigs pa med pas sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa rang la rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8430: rang rig pa nyid la ye nas rnam par rtog pa'i dri ma med pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8431: ye nas ka dag tu gnas pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8432: dri mas ma bsgribs pa'i tshul ye nas chos can las 'das pas khrims srung rgyu dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)001:8433: rang gi lus ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin no //
NK109(dze)001:8434: chos kyi sku la stong pa'i dri ma dang bral bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:8435: yul can gang du yang mi rtog pas /
NK109(dze)001:8436: bzod pa bsgom pa'i rgyu dgra med pas /
NK109(dze)001:8437: gnas lugs la rgyas thebs pa'i bzod pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:8438: de nyid bya ba dang byed pa'i 'bad pa las
NK109(dze)001:8439: 'das pas nyams dang rtogs pa 'bral ma myong ba'i
NK109(dze)001:8440: rig pa la mngon gsum gyi gnad bsdams pas 'gyur
NK109(dze)001:8441: ba med pa'i phyir na brtsam mi dgos pa'i brtson
NK109(dze)001:8442: pa nyams len dus thams cad du 'grub par byed
NK109(dze)001:8443: pas so // ye nas rig cing bsam du med pas dmigs gtad dang bral te /
NK109(dze)001:8444: skyon dag nas yon tan rang la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:8445: bsam pa'i 'gyu ba rang chad pas ma spangs la
NK109(dze)001:8446: yongs su rdzogs ba'i sems nyid chos nyid du bstan
NK109(dze)001:8447: pa'o // rig pa lu gu rgyud ni /
NK109(dze)001:8448: ye nas rlung la brten nas thogs pa med par dbyings la snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:8449: tshig gang la yang thogs pa med pa'i don dang
NK109(dze)001:8450: 'dres pa'i shes pa tha mal las log pas rab
NK109(dze)001:8452: gzhan gyis zil gyis mi gnon pa'i rig pa gleng
NK109(dze)001:8453: pa la chos sku nyid ye nas gzhi la yod
NK109(dze)001:8454: pa'i rang la rdzogs pa'i stobs dang ldan pas /
NK109(dze)001:8456: ye nas rang la yod ba'i bzhin /
NK109(dze)001:8457: dngos su lhun gyis grub pas sus kyang ma btab
NK109(dze)001:8458: par gzhan la smon rgyu med par rang la rdzogs
NK109(dze)001:8459: pa'i phyir gzhan 'jug pa'i smon pa khyad par can
NK109(dze)001:8460: gsang sngags kyi lam du 'gro ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:8461: dngos po med pa'i rig pa stong pa'i ye shes rang la gnas pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8462: yul la bdag tu ma bzung bas de la 'dzin
NK109(dze)001:8463: pa med pas mkhyen pa nang du gsal ba'i ye
NK109(dze)001:8464: shes rang byung gi las ma gtogs pa gzhan med
NK109(dze)001:8465: do // rig pa'i dbang du snang ba 'dus pas dngos po stong pa nyid du dbang bsgyur bas /
NK109(dze)001:8466: sems nyid ye nas mtshon du med pas /
NK109(dze)001:8467: ngo bo stong pa'i thabs dang ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8468: rig pa nyid sngar 'das pa'i gnas kyis bag chags
NK109(dze)001:8469: la mi gnas pa dge ba bcu yis skyabs du
NK109(dze)001:8470: med de / de'i gnad pha rol tu phyin pa
NK109(dze)001:8471: bcu las byung ba'i ye shes kyi ngo bo bcu
NK109(dze)001:8472: med de / ni / bya ba'i yul ma yin pas 'dus ma byas /
NK109(dze)001:8473: byed pa'i mkhan po med pas chos la ma brten par rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8475: da ni nang don brgyad pa dngos po gshis de
NK109(dze)001:8476: yang rang gi ngo la tshang lugs rgyas par bstan
NK109(dze)001:8477: pa ni / thabs ni ye nas rang la yod pa'i bla ma'i gdams ngag las te /
NK109(dze)001:8478: sems can kun la rang bzhin gyis gsang la /
NK109(dze)001:8479: de nyid rang grol du shes pa'i ye shes la
NK109(dze)001:8480: shes rab kyis dpyad pa'i yul du ma gyur pas
NK109(dze)001:8481: / mtshan nyid du grub pa med pas stong pa nyid /
NK109(dze)001:8482: de rgyu mtshan gang du yang ma grub pas ngos bzung ba'i sa med /
NK109(dze)001:8483: rten gang la yang mi 'cha' bas chags pa'i yul med pa'i rig pa'i sku ni /
NK109(dze)001:8484: brtags dpyad blo'i chos ma yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8485: de ltar yang shes rab kyis ni brtags na phung po'i gting mi rnyed zhes so //
NK109(dze)001:8486: de yang phyi'i snang ba thams cad kyi dbyings su
NK109(dze)001:8487: shar ba na khyab pa chen po'i ye shes kyi
NK109(dze)001:8489: gzugs su snang ba thams cad rag pa'i skur grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:8490: shes bya rang gi mtshan nyid kyi snang bar thams
NK109(dze)001:8491: cad grol bas rig pa zang thal ba zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:8492: // sku ni gsum mam lnga'i grangs las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:8493: grangs la bdag tu rtog pa sangs te /
NK109(dze)001:8494: ngo bo gnyis dbang du byas te /
NK109(dze)001:8495: nyag 'phra ba'i don khong du chud la gcig du ma cha shas las 'das pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)001:8496: ye nas gnas pa'i don da lta rtogs pas shes te /
NK109(dze)001:8501: ma 'dres pa lnga dang ldan pa nyid de /
NK109(dze)001:8502: ye thog ma nas de ltar gnas pas 'dug tshul la /
NK109(dze)001:8503: shes bya rang gi ngo bo la babs kyis grub pas da de las bcos mi dgos pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8504: gzhi zhes pa ni sangs rgyas dang sems can kun
NK109(dze)001:8505: gyi byung khungs nyid yin pas sangs rgyas pa'i gzhi
NK109(dze)001:8506: zhes bya'o // lam ni rang la snang ba chos
NK109(dze)001:8507: nyid kyi bar ma do la dbang po 'bring po
NK109(dze)001:8509: de'i 'bras bu de nyid sku gsum mam ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8510: rtogs pas 'khor 'das las ye shes zang thal nyid du shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8511: de rtogs pa'i tshul gzhi gnas kyi rig pa'i snang
NK109(dze)001:8512: ba 'od lnga'i gdangs gting nas rdzogs pas gang dang
NK109(dze)001:8514: 'di ni ye shes lnga las byung ba'i kha dog lnga'i mdangs ston par byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:8515: rtsal yon tan du shar ba 'o //
NK109(dze)001:8516: dngos po las log pas kha dog lnga nyid du byung la /
NK109(dze)001:8517: de nyid 'byung ba lngar dag pas sa chu me rlung rang dngos po /
NK109(dze)001:8518: yul ni rnam par dag pa las chos nyid stong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8519: de yang bem por 'dzin pa'i dngos po las log
NK109(dze)001:8520: nas stong nyid ngos bzung dang bral bar gnas so
NK109(dze)001:8521: // de nyid la tshig gi brjod pa stong pa'i
NK109(dze)001:8522: phyir na spros pa med pa'i ye shes su bzhugs
NK109(dze)001:8523: // so // dri ma med pa'i ngo bo ka
NK109(dze)001:8524: nas dag pas brjod pas tshig gi gzhi dang bral
NK109(dze)001:8525: ba'i gnad kyis da lta tshig gis 'bu mi tha'o
NK109(dze)001:8526: // so // / rang bzhin du lhun grub la
NK109(dze)001:8527: 'char bar byed pa'i sgo brgyad po yod pas cir
NK109(dze)001:8528: snang tshad rang la rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8529: sems can thugs rje kun la khyab pa ni rtsol ba ma yin par rang la shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8530: rang ni gong ma'i shugs chos nyid du gsal ba las byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:8531: rang bzhin snang ba ma bcos par bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)001:8533: bdag nyid chen po kun la khyab pa ma bslad
NK109(dze)001:8534: pa'i gzhi yul kun la brdal bas ma bcos pa'i
NK109(dze)001:8535: lam / kun la chub pas ma bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:8538: dri ma rig pa rang dag pas 'chad rtsol ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8539: lhun grub kyi gzhi las sna tshogs su byung ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8540: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med zhes lam gyi bcos su ga la yod ces pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8542: sangs rgyas la ma rig pa yod la sems can la ye shes yod pa'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:8543: de yang 'khrul pas ni ma rig pa gsum rkyen bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8544: zhes nang don brgyad pa dngos po gshis de yang
NK109(dze)001:8545: rang gi ngo bo la tshang lugs rgyas par bstan
NK109(dze)001:8546: nas / da ni nang don dgu pa de dag
NK109(dze)001:8547: gi 'jug pa don gzhan nas mi rnyed par bstan
NK109(dze)001:8548: nas / pa ni / 'di kun gyi don gzhi
NK109(dze)001:8549: la bcas kyis grub pa'i phyir na gnas pa'i mi
NK109(dze)001:8550: nas / pa ni / 'gyur ba / lugs ma bcos pa /
NK109(dze)001:8551: rang la rdzogs pas gzhan nas rtsal mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:8552: rang la gnas pas gzhan nas brtsal bas rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:8553: zhes bsdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8555: da ni nang don bcu pa sangs rgyas dang chos kyi don tshang lugs rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8556: de yang rang gi lus sprul skur gtan la dbab pa 'og nas ston no //
NK109(dze)001:8557: gong du mdor bstan skabs su bstan la /
NK109(dze)001:8558: sprul zhes gang las sprul na /
NK109(dze)001:8559: lus la sems sprul pas sprul zhes bya la /
NK109(dze)001:8560: sems las lus su grub pas sku ni rang gi lus la zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8562: sku rig par smin pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:8563: de yang rang gi rang rig pas na sems nyid stong pa ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8564: sgo lnga rang dag pas 'dod pa'i longs lnga la spyod pas /
NK109(dze)001:8565: sku sna tshogs su snang ba nyid 'od gsal du grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8566: mdo sems sde las bsam pa'i 'phro 'du dpag tu med pas te /
NK109(dze)001:8567: chos nyid rtog pa dang bral bas zab mo rtogs par dka' ba'i cha nas bzhag go /
NK109(dze)001:8569: rang gi snang ba de ma yin la der 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:8570: pa'i snang ba 'dul bas na 'dul ba zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:8571: // mngon pa ni rang gi sems nyid rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8573: da ni nang don bcu gcig pa dge 'dun dkon
NK109(dze)001:8574: mchog ji ltar tshang ba'i don rgyas par bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:8576: des rab tu byung bas chen po /
NK109(dze)001:8577: snang ba phyi nang rdzogs pas bcos su med /
NK109(dze)001:8578: gzhan ma yin par rang ngo shes pas rig pa de las 'gro pa'i yul gzhan med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8579: sems sna tshogs cig pas nyid ma bcos na gsal pa /
NK109(dze)001:8581: gzhi de la brtan pa gyur pa dngos /
NK109(dze)001:8582: thams cad rang gzhan yod par smra ba'i sde pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:8586: phyir gtan tshigs kun gyi mang po dang 'brel ba /
NK109(dze)001:8591: brtan khyab pa'i sde ba nyid do /
NK109(dze)001:8592: bde ba sdug bsngal las grol ba /
NK109(dze)001:8594: phyir gtan tshigs sdug pa lus /
NK109(dze)001:8599: rdzogs pas bskyar du med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8603: 'byung ba dus med mi snang ba /
NK109(dze)001:8604: lam chos nyid kyi bar ba do la sems can mi 'gro mi srid /
NK109(dze)001:8609: 'gog pa las dang nyon mongs pa 'gog par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8613: yin pa lus sems bral ba /
NK109(dze)001:8614: phyir gtan tshigs zag rdul phra rab bcas dang bskor ba bar dang bcas pa /
NK109(dze)001:8615: spros dang tshig bral ba med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8617: med pa cha med pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8620: sku so so'i grub matha'i 'dod pa /
NK109(dze)001:8628: dang bcas pa g.yo ba bo /
NK109(dze)001:8630: 'di ni phun sum 'tshogs pa lnga'i rgyas bshad de /
NK109(dze)001:8633: yin pa the tshom med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8641: khyad par gzhan las 'phags pa rtogs pa 'bras bu /
NK109(dze)001:8643: dus nges pa rkyang lhag pa /
NK109(dze)001:8645: zhes nang don bcu gcig pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8646: da ni nang don bcu gnyis pa de dag kyang
NK109(dze)001:8647: gnas nas 'tshol ba tshi chad pa'i skyon du bstan
NK109(dze)001:8648: pa ni / de ltar gong du bstan pa de
NK109(dze)001:8649: kun rig pa dang sems dang rang gi lus las
NK109(dze)001:8650: thams cad rdzogs pas brtsol bsgrub dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8651: de nyid rang la rdzogs pa 'i phyir na gzhan nas byung ba ni ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:8652: rtsol bas rnyed pa'i gnas med do //
NK109(dze)001:8653: zhes bsdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8654: zhes de dag gis le'u bdun pa'i bsdus pa'i don
NK109(dze)001:8655: lnga ba dkar po'i chos de dag rang gi lta
NK109(dze)001:8656: ba'i ngo la ji ltar tshang par bstan pa la
NK109(dze)001:8657: nang don bcu gnyis su byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:8658: da ni bsdus pa'i don drug pa sems dang ye
NK109(dze)001:8659: shes dbye ba dang kun gzhi dang chos sku gtan
NK109(dze)001:8660: la dbab pa dang 'byung ba dwangs snyigs dbye ba
NK109(dze)001:8661: bstan pa la don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK109(dze)001:8662: tshig dang yi ge 'di dag rang la tshang pas
NK109(dze)001:8663: gzhan la dgos pa med pas sems mi dgos te
NK109(dze)001:8664: / sems med na don byed mi nus pas de ji ltar lags zhus pas bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8665: gong du bstan pa'i de nas sems rnam par rtog
NK109(dze)001:8666: pa du mas bslad pa med pa'i rig pa yis
NK109(dze)001:8667: / brjod pas stong pa'i phyir chos med pa'i lus 'byung ba phra rags las grub pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8669: gsol pa ni rang gi rang bzhin du bstan pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)001:8670: 'di ltar 'khor ba dang 'das pa'i chos rnams kun /
NK109(dze)001:8671: rang la ni rig pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8674: ye nas rdzogs pas chos tshig dang ya ga brdar bkod pa'i rgyud dang lung dang /
NK109(dze)001:8675: man ngag gi chos la dgos pa yod pa ma
NK109(dze)001:8676: yin na zhes tshig las 'das pa'i ye shes ngos
NK109(dze)001:8678: de'i phyir na chos med pa'i lus 'di la /
NK109(dze)001:8679: lus la tshig med par gong du bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8680: lus la tshig med pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8681: sems la ni ji ltar dgos par 'gyur ba yin /
NK109(dze)001:8683: yang na bem po yin nam gal te bem po yin na ni 'gro ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8685: smra ba la sogs par nus pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8686: 'on te ma skyed na sprul pa'i skus kyang don rnams ji ltar 'byung ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8687: sems med pas don byed nus mi srid la /
NK109(dze)001:8688: des na lus de nyid la dran pa dang bsam pa dang bcas pa'i sems med na ni /
NK109(dze)001:8689: dur khrod ni nyid dang khyad par ci yod de /
NK109(dze)001:8692: smra ba la sogs pa nus pa med pa bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:8693: don yod pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:8694: gal te dngos po med pa yin na yang na
NK109(dze)001:8695: nam mkha'i stong pa ji bzhin du rig med stong
NK109(dze)001:8696: pa yin nam / de nyid yin na rang bzhin stong pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8697: sems can don la ji ltar 'byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:8698: thugs rjes gzhan don mi byed na sprul pa'i sku ma yin par thal lo //
NK109(dze)001:8699: de ltar na sems med pa'i lus gcig gis kyang don byed mi nus la /
NK109(dze)001:8700: lus med na sems gcig pus kyang don byed mi nus pas /
NK109(dze)001:8701: de nyid sngar gsung pa de rig pa la ma lags na /
NK109(dze)001:8702: 'di dag la the tshom du gyur pas /
NK109(dze)001:8703: bdag la 'gro ba rnams kyi gtso bos bka' rtsol cig zhes zhus so //
NK109(dze)001:8704: zhes bsdus don drug pa'i nang don dang po'o //
NK109(dze)001:8705: da ni nang don gnyis pa de kun thog ma
NK109(dze)001:8706: nas ma grub pas mi snang ba'i ston pa dang
NK109(dze)001:8708: de nas ni zhus pa'i de nas so //
NK109(dze)001:8709: sku la sogs pa'i lus med pa'i ye shes rnam par dag pa'i snang bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:8710: brtags pa rnam grangs kyi chos med pa'i gzhi la gang yang mi gnas pa'i ston pas /
NK109(dze)001:8711: brjod du med pa'i bka' spros pa thams cad dang bral bar brtsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:8712: sems rtog pa tha dad pa med pas dran pa blo'i rtog pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:8713: glo bur gyi rkyen sangs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8714: yul du ma la mi rtog pa'i 'khor gyis brjod du med pa'i don bstan pas /
NK109(dze)001:8715: ma skyes pa'i chos nyid ngos zin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8717: da ni nang don gsum pa sems dang ye shes kyi dbye ba mdor bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8718: sems ni las dang nyon mongs pa sdud par byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:8719: de yang lus 'tshogs pa'i chos sems kyis 'dus pas de la 'tshogs pa'i chos rten 'brel bcu gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:8725: 'byung ba 'tshogs pa'i chos dpag tu med pa /
NK109(dze)001:8727: bag chags snga phyi la sogs pa lus la sems kyis bsdus pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8728: de dag la brten nas las dang rnam par smin pas byung pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8729: sems kyi dri ma nyon mongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8731: shes bya nyid dang sems spags pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8732: da ltar 'tshang pas kun gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:8733: de dag gcig pu sdud pa'i sems kyis lus su grub par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:8734: de dag la sogs pa 'gyu ba byung tshor gyi sems dang /
NK109(dze)001:8735: 'jug pa tha dad pa'i sems kyi nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa 'phra rags brgya dang /
NK109(dze)001:8736: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis su byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:8737: dri ma'i grangs su gyur pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8739: bcas pas yul du ma'i rjes su 'jug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8740: spyod pa dang bcas pa'i sems kyis the tshom dang /
NK109(dze)001:8741: yid gnyis kyi gzhi 'dzin pa dang bcas pa'i sems kyi blo'i rtog pa sna tshogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8742: ye shes ni rtog pa med pas mtha' dang bral ba yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8743: 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang bral bas dran bsam las 'das so //
NK109(dze)001:8744: yod med du rtog pa med pas blo las 'das pa'am /
NK109(dze)001:8745: dbye ba ni bdag tu rtog pa'i blo med pas shes byed gzhan du ma gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8746: des na sems dang ye shes 'byed pa la mkhas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8747: sems rtog bcas kyi mtshan nyid shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:8748: ye shes rtog pa dang bral ba nyid shes pa rnams kyis ni shes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8750: da ni nang don bzhi pa sems de ma dag
NK109(dze)001:8751: pa'i dri ma dngos po yin par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:8752: / rnam shes dum bu ba'isemasa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8754: bag rdul dang 'dra ba chags pas las dang nyon mongs pa'i tshogs rnams su byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8755: de kun gyi gzhi yin pas na kun gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8756: lus ni 'byung ba sa chu me rlung bzhi las grub pas /
NK109(dze)001:8757: de yang sa zug pa'i dus na lus kyi nad 'du /
NK109(dze)001:8758: byer ba la khams rgyas bsnyams pa las dang nyon mongs pa'i gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:8759: chu zug pa las ye shes skye ba'i dus /
NK109(dze)001:8761: snyoms pa las phung po dang byang sems rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:8762: me zug pa las nad kyi gzhi 'dzin /
NK109(dze)001:8763: byer ba la thun mong ston /
NK109(dze)001:8764: snyoms pa las phung po 'jig go /
NK109(dze)001:8765: de yang sas ni rdul phra rab rdzogs pa'i las byas /
NK109(dze)001:8767: sems rdul smin pa'i las byas /
NK109(dze)001:8772: yang chus zug pas nad bad ka na tsha ba dang grang ba'i gzhi bzung /
NK109(dze)001:8773: byer bas bad kan gyis nad smin par byas /
NK109(dze)001:8774: snyoms pas snod rnams la gzhi nad du bskyed do //
NK109(dze)001:8775: yang sa zug pas 'dus pa tsha ba'i rkyen byas /
NK109(dze)001:8777: snyoms pas sna tshogs su 'khrugs par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:8779: rlung gis rlung gsum gyi byed pa'i las byas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8780: de yang rlung gis lus chags par byas so //
NK109(dze)001:8781: sas lus su grub par byas /
NK109(dze)001:8782: mes dbang po la sogs pa gsal bar byas /
NK109(dze)001:8783: rlung gis skra dang so dang sen mo la sogs pa bskyed pa byas pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8784: de ltar 'byung ba byed pa'i las 'tshogs pas lus
NK109(dze)001:8785: can rnams kyi dri ma ni lus kyi sems bskyed
NK109(dze)001:8786: / sems ma dag pa las khams gsum du khrid pas /
NK109(dze)001:8788: sems bzung ba'i yul yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:8789: phyi rol gyi rtog pa du ma'o //
NK109(dze)001:8790: 'dzin pa sems kyi rtog tshogs yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:8791: nang du rtogs pa tha dad par skye'o //
NK109(dze)001:8792: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na yang nas yang du 'khor ba'i chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:8793: de ltar na sems las 'das pa'i ye shes ngos gnas lugs la zin na /
NK109(dze)001:8794: rtog pa de dang bral na /
NK109(dze)001:8795: las dang rnam par rtog pa du ma las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:8796: sems rang rgyud du 'dzin pa sangs nas nang du chos nyid mngon sum gyi don rtogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8797: nyams rgyas pas sa mi 'gyur ba thob pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8798: de ltar rtogs pas lus 'byung pa'i kun gyi dri
NK109(dze)001:8799: ma sems zad pas 'bras bu sku gsum du grol
NK109(dze)001:8800: ba zhes bya'o // des na 'gro ba zhes sems
NK109(dze)001:8801: la brten nas 'gro bas na 'gro ba zhes bya
NK109(dze)001:8802: ba zhes bya'o // ste / sems kyi mtshan nyid shes pas /
NK109(dze)001:8803: khams gsum gyi rtog pa chod pa rnams ni /
NK109(dze)001:8804: dri ma dang bcas pa'i sems des /
NK109(dze)001:8806: sems de med na lus can kun gyis 'gro bar nus pa min te /
NK109(dze)001:8807: de'i phyir 'gro ba 'di dag rnams sems kyi 'khrul 'khor gyis gcig nas gcig tu 'khor te /
NK109(dze)001:8808: lus mi 'dra ba tha dad par byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:8809: sems kyi rtog pa mi 'dra ba las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8810: rnam pa dkar dmar la sogs pa snang ba'i rigs mi 'dra bar byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:8811: sems kyi yul mi 'dra ba las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8812: de bzhin du sems ma rtogs na 'khrul 'khor sna tshogs pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8813: rtogs na sangs rgyas pa yin pas so //
NK109(dze)001:8814: zhes nang don bzhi par bstan pa nas /
NK109(dze)001:8815: da ni nang don lnga pa ye shes kyi ngo
NK109(dze)001:8816: bo rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang bral bar
NK109(dze)001:8817: bstan pa ni / de yang 'bu tha'i thugs rjes 'gro bar byed pas na sems yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8818: de yang rnam par rtog pa las kyi rlung brgyad
NK109(dze)001:8819: kyis bskyod pas sgo lnga'i yul kun la 'jug pa
NK109(dze)001:8820: dang bral bas / ye shes de bem po lta bu ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8822: gzhi las grub shes pa snod por yod la /
NK109(dze)001:8823: de nyid rtog pa dang bral bas rig pa la mkhyen pa ma 'gogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8824: de'i gsal ba'i byed bas 'od du snang bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8825: rnam par yul du ma la rtog pa kun shes
NK109(dze)001:8826: rab rnam par dag pa'i mes bsregs te dngos po
NK109(dze)001:8827: las 'das pas rang snang stong pa chen por gnas
NK109(dze)001:8828: pa'o // de nas ye shes de nyid ni mes
NK109(dze)001:8829: bud shing la sogs pa bsregs pas thal ba dang
NK109(dze)001:8830: dngos po med par byed pa bzhin du /
NK109(dze)001:8831: sbur la sogs pa gang la rig pa bsreg pas za ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8832: zhes nang don lnga pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:8833: da ni nang don drug pa ye shes kyi ngo
NK109(dze)001:8834: bo stong pa'i yul las 'das par bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:8835: / nam mkha' ni chos nyid kyi nam mkha' stong pa ngos bzung pa las 'das pa /
NK109(dze)001:8836: nyams kyi nam mkha' tshad du med pa de'i nam mkha' stong pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:8837: de dang mtshungs bar rig med stong pa yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8838: de rdzas su med pas stong pa /
NK109(dze)001:8839: mkhyeen pa'i ye shees su gsal bas stong pa phyang chad pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:8840: mkhyen rig nang du gsal bas zag bcas ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:8841: de la ming du btags na stong gsal rig pa'i
NK109(dze)001:8842: snying po can zhes sku gsum lam du byas pa
NK109(dze)001:8843: las byung pa'o // de'i phyir na ye shes nyid las 'od kyis snang bar ston par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8844: de la rtsol bsgrub med par rang shar te /
NK109(dze)001:8845: dper na nyi ma dang nyi ma'i 'od bzhin du
NK109(dze)001:8846: 'byed pa med pa'i thugs rje phyogs med du rang
NK109(dze)001:8847: shar bas / sangs rgyas sems can thams cad la khyab cing /
NK109(dze)001:8849: spyi dang rang gi chos kun rang rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8850: spang blang las 'das pa'i chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:8851: dran pa yid de rang la gnas pas dran med /
NK109(dze)001:8852: yid byed pa med pas ye shes la 'dzin rtog med pas dran pa'i gzhi stong pas /
NK109(dze)001:8853: sems nyid la rtog dpyod med pas de dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8855: shes de'i don rtogs pas nyid ni 'di lta ste /
NK109(dze)001:8856: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes ni ngo bo ka dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)001:8857: rang bzhin lhun grub dang thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes so //
NK109(dze)001:8858: mtshan nyid ni me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis rdo rje rigs kyi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8859: de bzhin mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rin po che la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8860: de'i snang yul la khyab pa'i ye shes ni /
NK109(dze)001:8861: chos kyi dbyings kyi mthing gar khyab la /
NK109(dze)001:8864: so sor rtog pa dmar po /
NK109(dze)001:8865: bya grub ljang khur khyab pas ye shes lnga'i gdangs 'byung ba lnga la khyab pas /
NK109(dze)001:8866: 'khrul snang ye shes 'char ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:8868: da ni nang don bdun pa kun gzhi dang chos sku'i dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8876: ngo bo 'tshogs pas sdud par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8877: nges tshig kun mang pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8878: gzhi mang po 'dus bas las byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8879: dbye na ye don gyi kun gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:8883: des na kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin te /
NK109(dze)001:8884: rnam par byang pa'i gzhi ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:8886: ye don gyi kun gzhi ni /
NK109(dze)001:8889: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi ni /
NK109(dze)001:8891: gnyis sbyor bas na gzhi yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8892: bag chags lus kyi kun gzhi ni //
NK109(dze)001:8893: snga phyi 'dres pas na kun yin la /
NK109(dze)001:8894: dngos po 'dus pas gzhi yin no //
NK109(dze)001:8896: bag chags snga phyi'i rten byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8897: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8898: lus dang 'tshogs pa du ma'i rkyen byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8899: lus sems kyi mtshams sbyor ba byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8901: bag chags snga phyi'i nying mtshams dang /
NK109(dze)001:8902: las kyi rnam smin snga phyi sbrel ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8903: rgyu 'bras kyi bsdebs kun yin la /
NK109(dze)001:8904: de dag lhan gcig tu 'tshogs pa'i gzhi yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8906: de dag gi mtshan nyid nges par rtogs na sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8907: de nyid gdos pa lus sems kyis 'brel bsags pa'i phyir na'o //
NK109(dze)001:8909: lus kyi mtha' stong pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:8910: 'byung ba'i zag pa zad pa'i sa rdul dang rdul phran la mi gnas /
NK109(dze)001:8911: nyon mongs pa'i zag pa zad pas bzung 'dzin snga phyi'i bsdebs med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8912: bag chags snga phyi'i zag pa zad pas zhen pa rang thog tu grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8913: de lta bu de dngos po zad pas stong zhing thams cad kyi bdag nyid du byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8914: ye shes lnga'i gdangs yod pas gsal la /
NK109(dze)001:8915: bla ma'i man ngag yod pas gsal pa mngon sum
NK109(dze)001:8916: du snang bas de nyid cig char du rtogs la
NK109(dze)001:8917: bla ma'i lung med kyang kun la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8918: de yang dran bsam las 'das pa'i chos sku bde
NK109(dze)001:8919: ba chen por shar bas rnam par rtog pa tha
NK109(dze)001:8920: dad pas ma spags par rig pa rang ngo na
NK109(dze)001:8921: gsal la / glo bur gyi dran pa rnams sangs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8922: rang bzhin du spros pa med pa'i chos nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:8923: tshig gi spros pa nyid dang bral ba sgros btags su med /
NK109(dze)001:8924: blo'i spros pa dang bral bas 'byung ba rang rgyud pa thal byung du med /
NK109(dze)001:8925: dper na nam mkha' lta bur kun la khyab cing /
NK109(dze)001:8927: ngo bo de rang bzhin gyis dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:8928: thabs kyis mtshan pa'i brda dang /
NK109(dze)001:8929: byin rlabs la sogs pa kun dang bral bas gzhi gcig las ma g.yos pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:8930: chos sku de ltar gnas pa la /
NK109(dze)001:8931: kun gzhi la rgyu yod pas bzlog yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8932: rkyen dang bcas pas tha 'jig pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:8933: de lta bu'i kun gzhi la /
NK109(dze)001:8934: bag chags snga phyi thams cad sogs pa'i phyir na rdzing dang 'dra ste /
NK109(dze)001:8935: chu la sogs kun sdud pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:8936: kun gzhis kyang 'khor 'das kun sdud pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8937: chos kyi sku ni 'gyur ba med pas na /
NK109(dze)001:8938: bag chags snga phyi dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8939: kun gzhi ni yid drug dang /
NK109(dze)001:8940: sems bcu drug la sogs pa 'dus pa las kun gzhi ste /
NK109(dze)001:8941: de yang lus kun gyi gzhi du mar byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8942: chos sku yid la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa du ma bral bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:8943: 'byung ba phra rags la sogs pa'i du ma'i gzugs
NK109(dze)001:8944: kyi snang ba'i 'byung ba sha khrag gi lus med
NK109(dze)001:8945: pa'o // zhes nang don bdun pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8946: da ni nang don brgyad pa 'byung ba dwangs snyigs dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:8947: 'gro ba'i lus la 'byung ba chen po /
NK109(dze)001:8948: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' lnga bo rnam par snang bas na /
NK109(dze)001:8949: 'byung ba'i dwangs ma'i 'od dkar po dang /
NK109(dze)001:8953: mthing ga lnga po 'byung ba phra rags kyi dri mas bsgribs nas phyir snang ma nus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8958: ri bong gi rdul dang lnga /
NK109(dze)001:8959: rags pa sa chu me rlung dngos po lnga ni yul /
NK109(dze)001:8960: mig la sogs pa'i gzugs su snang ba kha dog dkar po chu rdul dang /
NK109(dze)001:8964: ljang gu ri bong gi rdul dang /
NK109(dze)001:8965: lnga yang 'od lnga 'grib pa'i rdul dang bcas pas lus kyi mtha' smin par byas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8966: 'byung ba sa'i 'od ser por grol la /
NK109(dze)001:8970: nam mkha' mthing gar grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:8971: lnga'i mdud pa lnga po de yang rang grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:8972: chen pos chen po la sogs pa lnga 'od kha dog lngar gsal bas na /
NK109(dze)001:8973: nang gi 'byung ba 'phra ba ni lcags rdul dang /
NK109(dze)001:8977: glang rdul rnams rang bzhin med par logs pas rang snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8978: rags pa ri dang khang khyim dang /
NK109(dze)001:8979: ljon shing la sogs pa'i ye shes kyi sku'i dri ma rnams rang sar dwangs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8980: rang gi ngo bor log pas kha ye shes lnga /
NK109(dze)001:8981: dog 'phra rags kyis ma bsgribs par 'od lnga po snang ba la ma 'dres par gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:8982: de nyid snang ba rang dag pas so so'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8983: rdul dang rdul phran gyi bag rdul stong par rang dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:8984: nam mkha' ni rang dwangs pas /
NK109(dze)001:8985: me long lta bu'i ye shes la sogs pa lnga ni 'od lnga nyid du shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:8986: 'khrul pa'i snang ba dus gcig la 'gag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:8987: gzugs la sogs so sor ma dmigs pa'i yul ni
NK109(dze)001:8988: sgo lnga'i shes pa rnams 'dzin med du rang grol
NK109(dze)001:8989: ba na / nang gi 'byung ba'i rtsal lnga ni /
NK109(dze)001:8990: 'chi ka'i dus su 'byung ba dwangs snyigs 'byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:8991: sa sa la thim pas lus lci /
NK109(dze)001:8992: chu chu la thim pas kha chu la la sogs
NK109(dze)001:8993: pa lan gcig phyir byung nas slar kha sna lag
NK109(dze)001:8994: pa skam / me me la thim pas lus kyi drod 'chor /
NK109(dze)001:8995: rlung rlung la thim pas dbugs yang nas yang du brtsegs /
NK109(dze)001:8996: rlung nam mkha' la thim pas shes pa mi gsal /
NK109(dze)001:8997: nam mkha' rnam par shes pa la thim pas dbugs 'chad /
NK109(dze)001:8998: rnam par shes pa 'od gsal chos nyid ma'i snang ba la thim pa'i tshe /
NK109(dze)001:8999: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i snang ba 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:9001: sgo lnga yul dang shes pa ni yid dang sems
NK109(dze)001:9002: las kyi rlung gis nam mkha' la rang yal bas
NK109(dze)001:9003: / lus rdul phra rab la sogs pas bcings pa las grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:9004: phyi'i 'byung ba sa 'od ser po la sogs pa'i
NK109(dze)001:9005: dwangs ma ni 'od lnga la bar do la thim
NK109(dze)001:9006: pas / rig pa 'od la 'jug pa'i dus te /
NK109(dze)001:9007: snang ba thams cad sku dang ye shes su shar ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9008: de'i phyir na 'byung ba lnga nang du dwangs ma 'od du gsal /
NK109(dze)001:9009: de'i 'byung ba snyigs ma 'dus gdos bcas bor bas dbye zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9010: de ltar byung ba ni thams cad 'byung bas na 'byung ba /
NK109(dze)001:9012: dus snga phyi thams cad du 'byung bas na 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9014: snyigs ma sa chu me rlung nam mkha' lnga /
NK109(dze)001:9015: 'byed pa'i thabs rig pa yul la 'byed pa'i dus 'chi ka'i bar do /
NK109(dze)001:9016: phyed pa'i tshad chos nyid kyi bar do /
NK109(dze)001:9017: zhes mu tig la sogs pa mtshan skabs su bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9020: nang bcud gnyis las gcig nas gcig tu 'khor bas na 'khor ba /
NK109(dze)001:9021: 'das kyi ni de dag las 'das pas na 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9022: chos ni 'khor ba'i chos dge ba dang mi dge
NK109(dze)001:9023: ba rnam pa dkar nag so so rang gi mtshan
NK109(dze)001:9025: phyi nang snod bcud kyis ba sdus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9027: nyams su blang bya sku dang ye shes kyis bsdus pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9028: de thams cad de dag thams cad rang rang gi rig pa la rdzogs par bstan pa'i le'u la /
NK109(dze)001:9029: bsdus pa'i don drug gis byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:9030: yan lag gi sum cu rtsa dgus le'u ni gzhung
NK109(dze)001:9031: gi sde tshan nges par ston pa ste bstan no
NK109(dze)001:9032: // bdun pa'o ni drug las gzhan du gyur pa grangs kyi bye brag go //
NK109(dze)001:9033: le'u bdun ni mu tig gsal bar phye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9036: ga&a&a&aratah da ni le'u brgyad pa'i mu tig gsal bar dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9037: le'u brgyad pa rgyud thams cad bsdams pa ste bstan pa'i le'u 'di la bsdus pa'i don bzhi ste /
NK109(dze)001:9038: thabs kyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9039: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9040: gsum pa tshig gi rgyud kyi don bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9041: bzhi pa rgyud gsum gyi don spyir bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9042: dang po thabs kyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa la
NK109(dze)001:9043: yan lag gi don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK109(dze)001:9044: don gyi rgyud kyi ji ltar lags zhu ba zhus
NK109(dze)001:9046: de nas la sogs pa'i tshig drug gzhung gsal lo //
NK109(dze)001:9048: da ni nang don gnyis pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9049: ston pa ni yon tan khyad par can mnga' bas /
NK109(dze)001:9050: sdud pa po la thabs kyi rgyud kyi dbye ba gsung pas /
NK109(dze)001:9051: gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po zhes bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:9052: sngar sangs rgyas pa kun kyang sngar thabs la brten nas sangs rgyas pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9054: gzhi ka nas dag pa gcig tu gnas pa'i ngo bo khyad par rtsal du mar snang ba las /
NK109(dze)001:9055: rang la gnas pa'i gzhi de mtshon par byed pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9056: mtshon bya tshig la brten nas thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:9057: de mtshon par byed pa'i man ngag rgyud la brten nas grol bar byed pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9058: mtshon byed thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:9059: zhes nang don gnyis pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi dbye ba bstan pa nas /
NK109(dze)001:9060: da ni nang don gsum pa mtshon bya thabs kyi
NK109(dze)001:9061: rgyud kyi khyab ba gtan la phab pa bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:9062: ni / de yang mtshon bya'i ngo bo shes bya'i yul du gyur pa /
NK109(dze)001:9063: nges tshig gang gis mtshon na /
NK109(dze)001:9065: de'i dgongs pa tshig don gnyis med du rtogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9066: de yang mtshon bya mthong ba'i shes pa /
NK109(dze)001:9067: bya ba thabs la brten nas go ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9068: de'i rgyu ni lus can kun la khyab pas na gcig zhes pa ngo bo la khyad med do //
NK109(dze)001:9069: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad de'i rjes su /
NK109(dze)001:9070: de 'brengs nas 'khor ba las logs te 'das pa dngos so //
NK109(dze)001:9071: theg pa thams cad kyi de'i rjes su 'brongs kyang rtogs par dka' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:9072: lus can la khyab pa ci'i phyir na khyab zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9073: lus can kun la rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK109(dze)001:9074: rig pa nyid dngos po med par stong pas khyab pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9075: mu stegs rtag pa ltar rdzas grub tu ni ma yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9076: stong nyid ngo bo ngos bzung las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9077: de yang gsal ba 'od lnga'i rang gdangs kyis khyab zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9078: chad par lta ba bar chad pa lta bu ma yin pas shes reg rang ngo na gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9079: zhes nang don gsum pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9080: da ni nang don bzhi pa de nyid la stong pa nyid khyab byed bsgrub pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9081: sems nyid de zag pa zad pas stong pa nyid du rgyu gcig pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9082: sems nyid la rgyu med pas 'bras bu tha dad pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:9083: de nyid ngo bor gcig pas sems nyid la grangs kyi mtha' zad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9084: de nyid lus kyi bsdod pa las 'das pas dngos po rdzas su grub par med pas /
NK109(dze)001:9085: stong nyid blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9086: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na sems nyid stong pa las dang bag chags kyi rten med pas /
NK109(dze)001:9087: gang gis kyang gos pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9088: de yang dngos po ni 'byung ba'i dngos po phra rags la bdag tu rtog pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:9090: las dang mtshan ma'i dngos po 'brel dang lus sems la bdag du rtog pa'i blo med pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9091: 'du shes tha dad pa'i dngos po kun gyi chos bdag gir 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9095: yod med la sogs pa las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9096: de dag las 'das pa de nyid rig pa dngos yin te /
NK109(dze)001:9097: bla ma'i man ngag med pa la mngon sum du snang bar med do //
NK109(dze)001:9098: 'o na med pa rang ma yin nam zhe na yod pas sems can kun la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9099: de yang lus tha dad pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:9100: de nyid kyang tha dad do zhe na ma yin te ngo bo gcig pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9101: sems nyid gcig gi mtshan nyid gtan la phebs na /
NK109(dze)001:9102: sems dang sems kyis bsdus pa thams cad gtan la phebs par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9103: de na 'bu tha dad sems can kun gyi gzhir gyur pas na bcos mi dgos la /
NK109(dze)001:9104: ngo bo gcig yin pas gang la yang rag ma lus pas /
NK109(dze)001:9105: spang blang dang dgag sgrub tu med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9106: de sems can la khyab pas yeng du med /
NK109(dze)001:9107: rig pa'i bdag nyid du gyur pas 'ub kyis sems la 'dus /
NK109(dze)001:9108: de yang dbyings su 'dus pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9109: rig par chub bo zhes pa bsdam bya'i yul las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:9110: chos sku rig pas skye ba med pas slar ldog pa'i sa dran pa zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:9111: de yang ka nas dag pa'i ngo bo la ma
NK109(dze)001:9112: rig pa ye nas zad pas gnas pa las gzhan
NK109(dze)001:9114: chos nyid mthong ba'i khyad par las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9115: de nyid la med pa'i phyogs nas bltas pas stong
NK109(dze)001:9116: zhing thams cad la snang bas dngos por ma song
NK109(dze)001:9117: pas na / phyir snang zhing de la ngos bzung med bas stong pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:9118: rig pa lu gu rgyud dngos yin pas mthong du yod la /
NK109(dze)001:9119: bzung ba'i yul du ma grub pas dngos po med
NK109(dze)001:9120: pa'i chos nyid tha mal pa'i spyod yul du ma
NK109(dze)001:9122: 'byung ba'i rkyen lus zad pa'i phyir sems de ye
NK109(dze)001:9123: nas chos kyi sku nyid ni stong par sems can
NK109(dze)001:9125: de yang rgyu lus sems la mtshan nyid ma rnyed pas /
NK109(dze)001:9127: de stong zhing bdag tu med pas 'khrul pa min /
NK109(dze)001:9128: 'dus pa tha dad pa ma yin pas bzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i dbang du ma song ba'i /
NK109(dze)001:9129: de nyid 'khor 'das rkyen las 'byung ba phra rags ni bsdams rags pas bcings pa dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)001:9130: de ma bsgribs par zang thal bas lus sems stong
NK109(dze)001:9131: pa'i yul bas ngo dang bral bas 'gyu ba ma
NK109(dze)001:9132: brten / 'dzin pa med pas rang snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9133: de nyid 'khor 'das kun la khyab pas gnyen po med /
NK109(dze)001:9134: snang ba la bde bar brdar pas rdzogs pa chen po blo las 'das /
NK109(dze)001:9135: de la bzung pas ma rnyed pas dngos po med /
NK109(dze)001:9136: de nyid kyi ngo bor cir yang shar ba la /
NK109(dze)001:9137: shar ba nyid na stong par grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9138: de la 'byung ba phra rags kyi dri ma med pas 'od lngar gsal /
NK109(dze)001:9139: nyon mongs phra rags kyi dri ma med pas rig pa mngon sum du mthong /
NK109(dze)001:9140: de nyid kha dog lnga las ma 'das pas rigs lnga'i gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9141: de la 'khor 'das dus gcig la rdzogs pas thams cad chos nyid du grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9142: de la dran pa glo bur ba med pas rtog pa med /
NK109(dze)001:9143: dngos po rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i mtha' zad pas
NK109(dze)001:9144: stong pa'i byung khung de nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK109(dze)001:9145: gsal bas sgrib byed dang bral ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:9146: rang gi yul la chos nyid stong pas khyab pa'i
NK109(dze)001:9147: phyir na rang rgyud dri ma med pa zhes bya'o
NK109(dze)001:9148: // zhes nang don bzhi pa de nyid la stong pa nyid kyi khyab byed bsgrub pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9149: da ni nang don lnga pa'o na phyams chad pa
NK109(dze)001:9150: ma yin te gsal ba'i khyab byed du grub pa
NK109(dze)001:9151: bstan pa ni / de yang rang sems nyid 'od
NK109(dze)001:9152: lngar gsal te chos kyi rang bzhin ma 'gags pas
NK109(dze)001:9153: bstan pa ni / na / don dam pa'i 'byung ba bzhi las bskyed pa /
NK109(dze)001:9154: sgron ma bzhir smin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9155: thig le stong pa'i sgron mas 'od kyi mdangs byed la /
NK109(dze)001:9156: shes rab rang 'byung gis tshig don dbyer med du byed /
NK109(dze)001:9157: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i rig pas rig pa'i gzhi 'dzin par byed /
NK109(dze)001:9158: rgyang zhags chu'i sgron mas ni /
NK109(dze)001:9159: 'khor 'das kyi gzugs sdud pa dang snang bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9160: kun la gsal bas khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9161: de yang ngo bo ji ltar bus khyab zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9162: gsal ba dkar pos khyab pas sems la dri ma med /
NK109(dze)001:9163: dri dang dmar pos khyab pas /
NK109(dze)001:9164: rig pa nyid bya rtsal las 'das /
NK109(dze)001:9165: bsil ba dang zhes ser po khyab pas rig pa nyid yon tan kun gyi byung khung /
NK109(dze)001:9166: yang zhing zhes mthing khas khyab pas cir snang zhing
NK109(dze)001:9167: shar kyang rig pa'i ngo bo las 'gyur ba med
NK109(dze)001:9168: / g.yo ba'i zhes pa ljang khus khyab pas thams
NK109(dze)001:9169: cad du rdzogs shing gang dang yang ma 'dres pa'o
NK109(dze)001:9170: / // de dag gi bdag nyid 'dzin pas na rig pa nyid las byung ba'i 'od do //
NK109(dze)001:9171: de yang phyi snang ba las khyab pa byung ba lnga 'od du grol /
NK109(dze)001:9172: nang lus la khyab pas phung po lnga 'od lngar grol /
NK109(dze)001:9173: gsang ba rig pa la khyab pas ye nas yod pa'i gdangs lnga rang la gsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9174: sems nyid rang grol bar byed pa'i 'byung ba'i lus sku gsum du smin pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:9175: rgyud kyi sa bon lus la gnas pa las byung ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:9176: rig med stong pa las rang log pa'i phyir na rang bzhin gyis gsal bas khyab pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9177: dbang po rab gcig char du skad cig ma dang po la 'khrul snang 'gags la /
NK109(dze)001:9178: gnyis pa la nang dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba 'char la /
NK109(dze)001:9179: gsum pa la de dag las grol bar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9180: 'bring la sogs pa la rang gi rig pa nyid mngon sum du mthong pas bar do dang /
NK109(dze)001:9181: dbugs phyung nas grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9182: snang ba nyid rnam par dag pas rang la shar te phyi'i yul la gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:9183: rang ni lus dang 'a bral bas na gzhan nas brtsal mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)001:9184: nyon mongs pa'i dri ma mkha' la sprin dengs pa lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:9185: las kyi dri ma sbrul skogs pa bor ba lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:9186: shes bya'i dri ma rin po che g.ya' dang bral
NK109(dze)001:9187: ba lta bu de la dang de kun kyang so
NK109(dze)001:9188: sor chu'i rnyog ma rang dengs pa ltar dwangs pa'o
NK109(dze)001:9189: // de yang sgo lnga'i yul 'dzin pa med par
NK109(dze)001:9190: rang gsal ba'i rig pa yul la snang pa la
NK109(dze)001:9191: // / sgo lnga'i shes pa 'dzin pa med par
NK109(dze)001:9192: yul so so la snang yang zhen pa med par
NK109(dze)001:9193: rang gsal du rdzogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9194: de yang rang gi lus la 'od lngas gsal bas
NK109(dze)001:9195: khyab pa dang 'brel chags pa'i phyir na rgyun zhes
NK109(dze)001:9196: bya'o // zhes nang don lnga pa 'o na phyams
NK109(dze)001:9197: chad pa ma yin te gsal ba'i khyab byed grub
NK109(dze)001:9198: bya'o // pa bstan / da ni nang don drug
NK109(dze)001:9199: pa mtshon byed thabs kyis rgyud kyi dbye ba bstan
NK109(dze)001:9200: bya'o // pa bstan / pa ni / gong du
NK109(dze)001:9201: bstan pa de dag mngon gsum du nyams su blang
NK109(dze)001:9202: pa'i man ngag gis rtogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9203: de las thabs khyad par can zhes bya ba bla mas bstan pa'i gdams ngag nyid kyang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9204: de yang gang zag blo 'bring gi bye brag gis
NK109(dze)001:9205: rig pa rang grol du nyams su blang ba dang
NK109(dze)001:9208: cer bzhag la sogs pa ji ltar bshad par bya ba rnams ni /
NK109(dze)001:9209: dbang po'i rim pas bstan pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9210: 'dir ni dbang po gcig char ba rnams 'bad rtsol med par rang grol bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9211: blo rim gyis pa rnams 'bad pa dang bcas te nyams su blang bya gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:9212: 'bad pa med pa 'byung ba khyad par gyi lus can ni /
NK109(dze)001:9213: las khyad par can sad pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9214: rtog ba cig char can skyes pa rnams na 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:9215: ba'i snang ba rang sar dag nas sangs rgya ba
NK109(dze)001:9216: yin no // zhes nang don drug pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9217: da ni nang don bdun pa de nyid rtogs par byed pa'i man ngag dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9218: gnad ni ces pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:9219: skabs 'dir gnad kyi man ngag 'di lta bu zhig brtsam ste /
NK109(dze)001:9220: de la rten gyi gang zag 'khor ba las blo log nas /
NK109(dze)001:9221: 'jig rten 'di'i zhen pa dang bral nas /
NK109(dze)001:9222: chos nyid kyi don gcig char thob par 'dod pa cig gis /
NK109(dze)001:9223: thog mar bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa cig las /
NK109(dze)001:9224: dbang bskur rdzogs par byas te /
NK109(dze)001:9225: de la sngon du phyi spros bcas kyi dbang dkyil
NK109(dze)001:9226: 'khor dang bum pa la brten nas lus la bskur
NK109(dze)001:9227: bas / lus yi dam lha'i skur rang gis dbang thob pas /
NK109(dze)001:9228: phyi snod kyi gzhal yas khang du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9229: nang lus lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba dag 'byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9230: de nas rnal 'byor pa lus rgya las grol bar byed pa'i man ngag go /
NK109(dze)001:9231: de nas nang spros pa med pa'i dbang dal dang
NK109(dze)001:9232: bum pa la brten nas ngag la dbang bskur bas
NK109(dze)001:9233: ngag gi yi dam lha'i bzlas par gsal ba dang
NK109(dze)001:9234: / nang du brjod med kyi don nyams su myong ba skyes ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9235: yi ge a'i brjod pa la brten nas skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9236: gsang ba shin tu spros pa med pa'i dbang brda'
NK109(dze)001:9237: dang rten 'brel la brten nas sems la bskur bas
NK109(dze)001:9238: / sems dngos po gshis kyi steng du phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9239: sems 'od gsal chen po'i don nyams su myong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9240: de nas gsang ba bla na med pa'i rab tu
NK109(dze)001:9241: spros pa med pa'i dbang lus kyi 'dug stangs dang
NK109(dze)001:9242: lta stangs la brten nas lus ngag yid gsum la
NK109(dze)001:9243: bskur bas lus bzhugs stangs kyi gnad la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:9244: sku gsum gyi bzhag lugs su grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9245: ngag smra ba bcad pa la brten nas sgra'i nus
NK109(dze)001:9246: pa nyams pas brjod du med pa'i don khong du
NK109(dze)001:9247: chud pa dang / sems byin rlabs bskul ba brda'i gdan la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:9248: 'od gsal stong pa ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub par grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9249: gsang sngags kyi lam smin pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9250: de ltar na lus kyi smin pa rdzogs pas bskyed rim cig char du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9251: ngag gi smin pa rdzogs pas nus pa thun mong ma yin pa skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9252: sems kyi smin pa rdzogs pas rdzogs pa'i rim pa rtag tshad la phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9253: lus ngag yid sems kyi smin pa rdzogs pas chos
NK109(dze)001:9254: nyid mngon gsum gyi nyams su myong pa mngon par
NK109(dze)001:9255: rdzogs pa'o // de ltar smin par byed pa'i rten /
NK109(dze)001:9256: dam tshig rgyud la brten pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9257: spyir dam tshig gi rtsa ba bla ma yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9258: don gyi dngos grub 'dod pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9259: bla ma mnyes par byas pa la dngos grub 'byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9260: de ltar yang mkha' 'gro ma d+r+wa ba stong ldan las //
NK109(dze)001:9261: dngos grub 'dod pas bla ma la /
NK109(dze)001:9262: dus matha'i bar du mchod par bya /
NK109(dze)001:9264: de yang lus ngag yid gsum las mi 'da' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:9265: lus kyi spyod lam la sogs pas bla ma gnyes par bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9271: mthong phyag la sogs pa bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9272: de yang lus kyi gtong pa rnam par dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:9273: dbang bskur ba'i 'og tu yon dbul ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9274: rang gi 'byor pa ji ltar yod pas phul la mnyes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9275: gzhan yang lus kyi bya bas bla ma mnyes par bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9276: srog la sogs pas kyang bla ma mnyes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9277: ngag gi brjod pas kyang bla ma mnyes par bya
NK109(dze)001:9278: ba ni bla ma'i skyon ma yin pa yon tan
NK109(dze)001:9279: la gsal zhing khyad par gyi tshig rnams brjod par
NK109(dze)001:9280: bya'o // yid dang shes pas mnyes par bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9281: bla ma'i mdzad spyod brten pas bla ma mnyes te /
NK109(dze)001:9282: gzhan 'jug pa la dgod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9283: gzhan ci nas kyang bla ma la dad pas 'jug par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9285: mkhas pas tshig don la lhag chad med par bla
NK109(dze)001:9286: mas thugs kyi dgongs pa ni ji lta ba bzhin
NK109(dze)001:9287: du nyams su len pa las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9288: de ltar yang dam tshig chen po'i rgyud las //
NK109(dze)001:9289: ji ltar bla ma'i bya ba las //
NK109(dze)001:9290: lus dang ngag dang yid dag gis //
NK109(dze)001:9291: bla ma mchog la gus pa'i mi //
NK109(dze)001:9295: dngos grub 'dod pa'i dad pa can //
NK109(dze)001:9296: bla ma mnyes pa las byung ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9297: gal te bla ma ma mnyes na //
NK109(dze)001:9298: rtag tu 'khor ba'i kha mtha' rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:9300: de yang dbang bskur ba'i dus su yon dbul ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9301: dga' ston bya ba la sogs pas bla ma mnyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9303: 'gro ba gzhan la sogs pa yang mnyes shing mgu bar bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9304: de ltar byas pas gsang sngags kyi dam tshig tu 'gro zhing /
NK109(dze)001:9305: byin rlabs 'jug pa'i rten khyad par can du 'gro ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9306: de ltar yang 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK109(dze)001:9307: snying rje chen po dga' ston che /
NK109(dze)001:9309: de ltar lus ngag yid kyi gzhi ma smin pa smin par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:9310: da smin pa de grol bar byed pa la bla ma'i man ngag gal che ste /
NK109(dze)001:9313: de la sngon 'gro ni lam sel bar byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9314: dper na 'jigs bcas kyi lam du nyul ba lta bu ste sngon 'gro la lugs mang ste /
NK109(dze)001:9315: khyad par du sku gsum bsgrub par byed pa sku
NK109(dze)001:9316: gsum gyi sna khrid par byed pa 'byung bzhi'i rnal
NK109(dze)001:9317: 'byor ni / lus ngag gi rtags btsan thabs su skye bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9318: sems kyi sna khrid par byed pa lus ngag yid kyi bya ba'i rim pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9319: 'dis ni lus ngag yid 'du bar byed pa'i cho ga'o //
NK109(dze)001:9320: rig pa'i sna khrid par byed pa 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9321: de la lus ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa lus kyi bya ba'i 'khor lo ste /
NK109(dze)001:9322: 'di nyid du ji ltar byas pa tsam gyis ma
NK109(dze)001:9323: 'ongs pa'i dus na de nyid du 'jug par mi
NK109(dze)001:9324: 'gyur ro // de ltar yang bkod pa chen po'i
NK109(dze)001:9325: le'u sum cu pa nas gang gis ru shan 'byed
NK109(dze)001:9326: 'gyur ro // 'dod pas // lus kyi bya ba rang log phyir //
NK109(dze)001:9327: da lta gang du spyad pa'i don //
NK109(dze)001:9328: phyi nas de ltar ma yin te //
NK109(dze)001:9329: de nyid bzlog pas lus la yang //
NK109(dze)001:9330: gnas pa med pas khams gsum du //
NK109(dze)001:9331: lus kyang 'jug pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:9333: de nyid dgongs pa dang bcas pas na spyod par 'gro ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:9334: lus kyi bya ba la brten pas 'bras bu yang
NK109(dze)001:9335: de nyid kyis 'khor lor 'jug par mi 'gyur la
NK109(dze)001:9337: de ltar yang lung grangs ni dpag tu med do //
NK109(dze)001:9338: de nas lus sbun pa'i rnal 'byor du bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9339: de ltar nyi ma bdun nam bcu gcig gam /
NK109(dze)001:9340: zla ba phyed du byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:9341: phyir lus kyi zhen pa rang log pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9342: nang du 'dus zhing dul ba la sogs pa'i rtags kyang 'byung nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9343: dgos ched ni gzhan na bstan nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:9344: de yang lus la sems gnas pas lus kyi bya
NK109(dze)001:9345: bar rnam par bkod pas sems bag la tshud pa'i
NK109(dze)001:9347: de nas de'i 'og tu rnal la 'bebs pa zhes bya ba'i cho ga bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9348: 'di ni snga phyi bya la sogs pa tshi 'chad pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9350: bya ba la mi gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9351: lus kyi gnad du rtsa ltem pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK109(dze)001:9352: 'di'i dus na rtsa rnams 'phar ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9354: gal pa la sogs pa 'ong ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9355: de ni rlung rang sor tshud pa'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:9356: de ltar yang gser gyi snying po'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:9358: lus kyi byar med dal ba brten //
NK109(dze)001:9359: 'di'i ni sangs rgyas sku dang reg /
NK109(dze)001:9360: khyad par mchog tu gsang bas 'grub //
NK109(dze)001:9362: de la zhag gsum mam bdun nam /
NK109(dze)001:9364: de'i 'og tu ngag ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9365: ngag 'di ni ngag gi brjod bya tha dad pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:9366: khams gsum 'khor ba rgyun 'chad par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9367: 'dir ci dang ci brjod pa phyis de nyid du byed par 'gyur mi srid do //
NK109(dze)001:9368: des dbang bskur mchog gi rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:9369: skal dang ldan pas rigs drug skad //
NK109(dze)001:9370: rang dang mthun par brjod pa yis //
NK109(dze)001:9374: ji skad smra ba de bzhin byed /
NK109(dze)001:9376: 'di ltar yang gong ma tsam du las dag pa dang ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9377: brtson 'grus kyi khyad par gyis byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:9378: ngag gi brjod pa nyams pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9379: de nyid la zhen pa rang log pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9380: de la gtan ka ci 'dug snyam pa skye'o //
NK109(dze)001:9381: de'i 'og tu ngag rnal du 'bebs pa'i cho ga nyi ma gong tsam zhig byas pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9382: ngag gsong po byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9383: rdzun gyi tshig rgyun 'chad pa la sogs pa 'gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:9384: de'i 'og tu ngag gi bya ba las ngal gso ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9385: de'i 'og tu sems ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9386: nyi ma gong du bstan pa tsam zhig byas pas /
NK109(dze)001:9387: yang ji ltar bsam pa tsam zhig gis phyis de nyid du mi 'jug par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9388: de yang dper na sngar gyi bya bas sgyid lugs mis phyis mi byed pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:9389: de ltar rdo rje khang bu brtsegs pa las //
NK109(dze)001:9390: gang gis bsam pa'i 'khor lo nyid //
NK109(dze)001:9391: su yis bskor bar nus pa la //
NK109(dze)001:9394: yang dpag bsam ljon shing las /
NK109(dze)001:9395: bsam pas brtags la slar bzlog med /
NK109(dze)001:9397: 'di ni bag chags kyi mtshams 'byed par byed pa'i gnad yang dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9398: de'i 'og tu sems rnal 'bebs pa'i chos bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9399: 'di ni sngar gyi sems 'phro 'dus g.yengs nas ngal ba nyid phyis ngal gso zhing sor 'jug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9401: 'du shes gcod pas lung sgo 'gag zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)001:9402: de ltar dbang nye bar rtog pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9403: gang gis ru shan phye ba nyid //
NK109(dze)001:9404: khams gsum nyid du ldog pa min //
NK109(dze)001:9405: de la rnal du phabs pas brtan /
