NK109(dze)001:9408: de ltar sngon du 'gro ba rdzogs nas da dngos
NK109(dze)001:9409: gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes nyid nyams su
NK109(dze)001:9410: blangs ba la chos tshan bzhis bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9411: dpal ri bo brtsegs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9412: mngon sum gnad la goms 'dod pas //
NK109(dze)001:9413: gnad ni bzhi sde'i yis phye //
NK109(dze)001:9415: 'di dag ni gzhan gyis lung gis yid ches par byas pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9416: 'di nyid kyi lung grangs na brjod kyis mi langs te /
NK109(dze)001:9417: gzhan gyis lung yang bar 'grongs par 'ong ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9418: de la sngon du lus ngag gi gnad gzir bas ye shes gnas nas gdon pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9419: lus kyi gnad du sku gsum gyi bzhugs stangs byas pa tsam la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:9420: sku gsum gyi dgongs pa las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9421: 'o na 'byung ba'i lus kyi 'dug stangs chos sku'i bzhugs stangs su 'gro ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9422: chos sku sgyu ma lta bu la /
NK109(dze)001:9423: chos nyid sgyu ma'i skur bzhengs nas /
NK109(dze)001:9424: 'gro ba'i don la byon pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9425: de ltar yang gser gyi mkha' lding las /
NK109(dze)001:9426: rang gis chos sku'i bzhugs pa'i tshul //
NK109(dze)001:9427: gang zag gang gis lus kyi gnad //
NK109(dze)001:9428: de dang mthun par sus shes pas //
NK109(dze)001:9429: 'di ni chos sku bde chen la //
NK109(dze)001:9432: 'dir ni chos lus 'byung ba 'tshogs pa de dag las grol bar byed pa la /
NK109(dze)001:9433: sku ni de dag rnam par dag pa las sgyu ma'i sku nyid dus thams cad du gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9434: bzhugs pa ni ting nge 'dzin gnas pa las ma 'da' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:9435: stangs ni 'khor ba las thar ba byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9436: de dag las longs ni 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga rnam par dag par byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:9437: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i khams la 'jug par byed pa nyid la /
NK109(dze)001:9438: chos nyid mngon gsum gyi gnad la /
NK109(dze)001:9439: mig gi dbang pos spyod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9440: rdzogs pas ni lus kyi 'tshogs pa'i chos ma lus
NK109(dze)001:9441: pa 'od gsal du grol bar byed pa'i thabs so
NK109(dze)001:9442: // sku ni de dag tu smin pas 'khor ba las grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9443: de nyid gnad bstun pas gang zag de dus rtag
NK109(dze)001:9444: tu chos nyid mngon gsum la longs spyod rdzogs pa
NK109(dze)001:9445: bya'o // bzhugs pa ni ting nge 'dzin la gnas par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9446: stangs ni khams gsum las 'da' ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:9447: de ltar yang gser gyi mkha' lding las //
NK109(dze)001:9448: chos kyi dbyings la longs spyod phyir //
NK109(dze)001:9449: longs sku'i bzhugs stangs bstun byas pas //
NK109(dze)001:9450: 'dis ni sku gsum zhing la spyod //
NK109(dze)001:9451: des na mchog tu lus kyi gnad //
NK109(dze)001:9455: lus la 'byung ba la sogs pa'i byed las sna tshogs par sprul pa dag par byed la /
NK109(dze)001:9456: de dag las sgyu ma'i skur smin par byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9457: bzhugs pa gnas pa rgyud la brten par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9458: stangs ni brten pas khams gsum mi ltos par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9459: de ltar yang de nyid las /
NK109(dze)001:9460: lus kyis tshogs pa dag byed pa //
NK109(dze)001:9461: sprul pa sku yi bzhugs stangs nyid //
NK109(dze)001:9462: su yis shis pas gnad de bstun //
NK109(dze)001:9463: de nyid las grol sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9465: de ltar bzhugs stangs gsum kho nar nges la /
NK109(dze)001:9468: yang na brgya stong la sogs par byung na ci'i stangs zhes pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9469: 'dir ni 'gro ba rnams nyon mongs pa gsum gyis
NK109(dze)001:9470: khams gsum du khrid pa de las grol bar byed
NK109(dze)001:9471: pas na yang gsum du nges la /
NK109(dze)001:9472: nyon mongs pa gsum las lus ngag yid gsum du smin pas kyang gsum du nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9473: de yang thog ma srid pa las kyi 'khor lo las /
NK109(dze)001:9474: 'dod chags ma dag pa las gzugs su smin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9476: bya ba dang byed pa la rtsol bas /
NK109(dze)001:9477: de las 'gro ba dag gtso che ba las grub ste /
NK109(dze)001:9478: gsum 'dus kyang ngag smin gyi lus can zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9479: lus su smin pa'i dus na yang smra ba la dga' zhing /
NK109(dze)001:9480: brjod byed la brtson par byed cing /
NK109(dze)001:9481: 'dod pa che la 'dod chags la dga' ba gcig 'ong ste /
NK109(dze)001:9482: de nyid rnam dag gi lam du 'dzud pa'i phyir longs sku'i bzhugs stangs bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:9483: 'gro ba de lta bu'i ni mchog tu longs sku'i bzhugs stangs rtag tu byas na /
NK109(dze)001:9484: chos nyid kyi don la mchog tu mkhas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9485: de yang srid pa'i 'khor lo las gti mug ma dag pa las gzugs su smin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9487: de nyid bag la nyal ba slong bar byed pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9488: 'gro ba yid gtso che ba'i gzugs su smin pas /
NK109(dze)001:9489: 'di'i gzugs su smin pa'i dus na sems kyi 'gyu ba ma zhi /
NK109(dze)001:9491: brjod pa la mi dga' la /
NK109(dze)001:9492: rtag tu gnyid la dga' bar 'ong /
NK109(dze)001:9493: des ni chos sku'i bzhugs stangs la rtag tu gnas na /
NK109(dze)001:9494: chos nyid la dus thams cad du gnas par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9495: yang thog ma zhe sdang ma dag pa las gzugs su smin pa las sprul du smin pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9496: lus kyi byed pa gtso che ba'i gzugs su byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:9497: 'di nyid gzugs su smin pa'i dus na yang lus kyi bya ba la dga' zhing 'gro 'dod /
NK109(dze)001:9498: lus stobs che la lus bong rags la /
NK109(dze)001:9499: lus kyi byi dor la dga' ba'i lus su byung pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9500: 'dis ni sprul pa'i sku bzhugs stangs la rtag tu gnas na sangs rgyas par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9501: de dag la lus grangs ni dpag tu med de /
NK109(dze)001:9502: 'dir yi ge mang bas ma bris so //
NK109(dze)001:9503: des 'dod chags can so thar gyi lam du 'dzud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9504: zhe sdang can sngags kyi lam du bzud pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9505: gti mug can sngags kyi lam du bzud pa'i phyir bzhugs stangs gsum du nges pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9506: 'gro ba'i smin so lus ngag yid gsum du byung
NK109(dze)001:9507: nas de dag gi bcings pa las grol bar byed
NK109(dze)001:9508: pas na yang / gsum kho nar nges la /
NK109(dze)001:9509: des las mang na mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:9510: de las nyung na mi tshang pas gsum kho nar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9511: ngag gi gnad du smra ba bcad pas brjod du med pa'i don rgyud la skyes pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9512: 'gro ba gzhan dang tshig ma 'dren pas lus 'byongs pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9513: lus 'byongs pas lus sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK109(dze)001:9514: mkha' spyod kyi mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK109(dze)001:9515: lus sgyu ma'i skur 'gro ba'i de nas brjod bya bkag pas gang 'byongs te /
NK109(dze)001:9516: de 'byongs pa'i rtags su mi ma yin rnams dang brda 'phrod cing gtam zer ba dag 'ong ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9517: ngag gi yang brjod pa dka' bas yid 'byongs te /
NK109(dze)001:9518: de'i rtags su sngon du mi ma yin pa'i gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9519: de nas mngon par shes pa dum bu pa 'char ro //
NK109(dze)001:9520: sems kyi gnad du rig pa nyid gtad sa las ma 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:9521: chos nyid mngon gsum du shar nas snang ba bzhi mthar phyin par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9522: de ltar yang rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9523: lus dang ngag dang yid kyi gnad shes shing bstun pas 'khor ba las grol /
NK109(dze)001:9525: de nas gnad rnam pa gsum la brten nas mngon gsum rang thog tu dbab pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9528: rlung gi gnad dang gsum ste /
NK109(dze)001:9529: sgo ni gzigs stangs gsum las mi 'da' bar byas te /
NK109(dze)001:9530: de ltar dpal nam mkha' mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK109(dze)001:9531: chos kyi sku yi gzigs stangs kyis //
NK109(dze)001:9533: longs skus srid pa'i gzhi ma 'jig /
NK109(dze)001:9534: sprul skus sangs rgyas zhing du bsgrol /
NK109(dze)001:9536: de yang gzigs stangs gsum kho nar nges par cis zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9537: 'di ni gang zag gsum la gzigs pa yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9538: le lo can la longs sku'o //
NK109(dze)001:9539: brtson 'grus can la sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK109(dze)001:9540: btang snyoms can la chos sku'i gzigs stangs shis pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9542: de yang gzigs ni chos nyid la gzigs pas rnam dag bsgrib pa zad pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:9543: stangs kyi 'khor ba las grol bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9544: yul ni phyii'i yul nam mkha' stong pa sprin dang bral ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9545: nang ni dbyings rnam par dag pa mdzod spu nas drangs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9546: phyi ni rig pa 'char ba'i yul la /
NK109(dze)001:9547: nang ni nyams 'phel ba'i yul lo //
NK109(dze)001:9548: de ltar rig pa dang mnyam gnyis gnyis su med pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9551: rlung dal ba brten pas bya ba dang bral ba'i don rgyud la skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9552: rig pa lu gu rgyud ar la gtad pas rnam par rtog pa'i khung zad nas /
NK109(dze)001:9553: 'khrul pa gzhi la log nas ye shes ma bu 'phrad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9554: de la rig pa rlung dang bral nas 'gro 'ong med pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9555: rig pa la byan tshud pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9556: de yang khrid kyi lugs su slob na /
NK109(dze)001:9557: lus kyi gnad bstun pa la nyi ma lnga drug tu bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9558: de nas sgo sbyang pa la de tsam zhig /
NK109(dze)001:9559: de nas yul brtsal ba la nyi ma drug nas bdun du byas nas /
NK109(dze)001:9560: de mngon gsum rang thog tu phab nas /
NK109(dze)001:9561: de nas dus thams cad du nyams su blang pa las snang ba bzhi 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9564: mngon pa ni yul dngos su snang ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9567: rig pa gsum las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9568: snang ba ni yid kyis spyad pa ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9569: de las nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba 'char ba ni nyams ni snang ba'i nyams dang shes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9570: rig pa ni ci mi snyam du 'gyur ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9571: mngon pa shes pa drug 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9572: 'gro ba drug gi rtog pa khongs su chud pa la sogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9573: snang ba'i nyams ni ye shes lnga yi kha dog gi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9575: 'phel ba ni gong nas gong du mi 'dra ba 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9576: de yang ye shes lnga'i kha dog gi snang ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9577: rdo rje'i rigs rnam par dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:9578: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi kha dog dkar ba'i snam bur 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9579: de nyid rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i gdangs dkar la 'tsher bar 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9580: de'i 'og tu de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs rnam par dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:9581: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi kha dog mthing ga'i snam bur 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9582: rnam snang gi gdangs mthing ba la gnas par 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9583: rin po che'i rigs rnam par dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9584: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kha dog ser po'i snam bur dang /
NK109(dze)001:9585: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi gdangs ser ba las gser lta bur 'char ro //
NK109(dze)001:9586: pad+ma'i rigs rnam par dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9587: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi kha dog dmar po'i snam bu dang /
NK109(dze)001:9588: snang ba mtha' yas kyi gdangs dmar ba la rab
NK109(dze)001:9589: tu dmar ba la byi ru'i mdog lta bu 'char
NK109(dze)001:9590: ro // las kyi rigs rnam par dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9591: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi kha dog ljang khu'i rnam par 'char /
NK109(dze)001:9592: don yod grub pa'i ye shes ljang khu'i rnam par 'char /
NK109(dze)001:9593: don yod grub pa'i gdangs rab tu ljang ba las in+d+ra ni la'i rnam pa ltar 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9594: de dag gi phyi rim mthing ga rdo rje'i ra bas kun nas bskor ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9595: ye shes de dag tha dad pa ma yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9597: so so'i gtso bos byas pa'i kha dog lnga lngar gsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9598: rigs dang rigs kyi khyad par las snang ba'o /
NK109(dze)001:9599: de nas ye shes kyi rlung rnam par dag pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9600: me long lta bu gyen 'greng du snang ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9601: de la brten nas nyams kyi 'phel ba 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9602: mnyam pa nyid kyi rtsibs shar du snang ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9603: 'khrul pa'i snang ba zad du nye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9604: de nas so sor rtogs pa'i gru chad du snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9606: bya ba grub pa'i re lde'i rnam par tsam du snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9607: ye shes kyi rang gdangs so sor gsal ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9608: de nas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes yul gru
NK109(dze)001:9609: tsam du snang ba ni rtog pa rags pa 'gags
NK109(dze)001:9611: de dag la ma skyes pa'i rim pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9612: brtson 'grus rab rnams la rab tu zhag lnga lnga'o //
NK109(dze)001:9614: tha ma rnams la nyer gcig na gong ma'i snang ba 'gags nas /
NK109(dze)001:9615: yang 'og ma'i snang ba de dag rnam ba de dag rnam par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9616: kha dog dang dbyibs kyi bar 'dir ni //
NK109(dze)001:9617: thang gcig tu gnas pa dag pa 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9618: de nas de dag nub nas yang ye shes lnga'i dbyings kyi snang ba 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:9619: me long lta bu'i dbyibs mig tshags kyi rnam par dang 'dra ba 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:9620: de ni kha dog rab tu spel legs pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9621: de la goms pa las mig mngas ris su 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:9622: 'di ni sngon du 'gro ba tshad du phyin pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9623: de nas mnyam pa nyid d+r+wa ba phyed pa ltar 'char te /
NK109(dze)001:9624: de ni rlung gi sbyangs ba dag pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9625: de las d+r+wa bar snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9626: sngon 'gro dag cing tshar chod pa las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9627: de nas so sor rtog pa'i me tog gi tshom bur 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9628: gzigs stangs ma 'grus pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9629: de las pad+ma stong ldan du 'phar ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9631: bya ba grub pa'i mtshon cha lta bu ni /
NK109(dze)001:9632: rang bzhin ma bcos pa las grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9633: de las 'khor lo la sogs pa sna tshogs su snang ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9635: de nas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mkhar thabs su snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9636: rig pa mig nas drangs pa las byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9637: de ni za 'og gi gur khyim lta bu ni /
NK109(dze)001:9638: sngon 'gro dag par sbyangs pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9639: de dag kyang brtson 'grus kyi khyad kyis zhag gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:9642: bcu bzhi na gcig skye gcig 'gag go /
NK109(dze)001:9643: de phan chad ni nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:9644: 'di dag ni sems kyi sngon 'gro'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:9645: rtog pa tha dad pa bslang pa de 'gags pa'i rtags yin no //
NK109(dze)001:9646: de nas rig pa rang gi ngo bo'i snang ba
NK109(dze)001:9647: 'char te 'od de dag thig ler 'char ba ni
NK109(dze)001:9648: / lu gu rgyud gcig tu 'dus pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9649: de nas thig le gnyis sbrel du snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9650: thabs dang shes rab rnam pa dag pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9651: de nas thig le lnga la byan tshud pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9652: de nas thig le ye shes lnga las byan tshud pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9653: de nas thig le re re la sku phyed ma re snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9654: sprul pa'i sku sbyang pa rnam par dag pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9655: de nas sku rang rkyang ba re snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9656: sprul sku'i snang ba chos nyid mngon gsum mthong ba las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9657: de nas sku de dag yab yum lnga lngar snang gyur ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9658: longs sku'i ye shes tshad du phyin pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:9659: de nas so so'i tshom bu dkyil 'khor dang bcas par snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9660: de nyid mu khyud kyi ra ba dang so so'i gtso 'khor du snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9661: chos sku'i sbyang ba rnam par dag pa las tshad du phyin pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9662: 'di ni rig pa tshad phebs kyi snang ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:9663: sngon 'gro'i dus na lus kyi bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9664: byed pa de dag gi 'brel chad de /
NK109(dze)001:9665: phyis mi skye ba'i rtags so //
NK109(dze)001:9666: de la rig pa ni gzhi la gnas pa'i rig pa mngon du gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:9667: lam srog tu tshud pas sku snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9668: lam zad du nye bas dal rdzogs pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:9669: tshad ni sku yi dal rdzogs pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)001:9670: phebs pa ni de las 'das pa med pas rnam par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9671: de dag ni zla ba nya gang ba'i rnam pa dang 'dra ste /
NK109(dze)001:9672: yar gyi 'phel zad pas rang ngo la bcos su med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9673: de nas zla ba mar bri ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:9674: yang sku de yal nas thig le la thug pa la sogs pa /
NK109(dze)001:9675: dang po'i sa la nges par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9676: de ni dang po phyi snod kyi chags lugs zhig pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9677: nang bcud kyi sems can rnams kyi tshe'i tshad yar
NK109(dze)001:9678: skye ba dang mar 'grib pa zad pa'i rtags so
NK109(dze)001:9679: // de dag ma zad na bdag khams gsum las mi grol bas so //
NK109(dze)001:9680: de ltar phyi snod kyi 'jig rten zad pas brten sa med pas bzlog sa med pa'i gnad /
NK109(dze)001:9681: nang bcud kyi sems can zad pas skye ba rgyun
NK109(dze)001:9682: chad pas da rig pa nyid 'chi ba dang bral
NK109(dze)001:9683: ba'o // de nas snang ba ci'i ngo bor yang grub pa med de /
NK109(dze)001:9684: 'di yin 'di min gyi brjod par dka' bas /
NK109(dze)001:9685: chos nyid zad pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9687: 'bras bus ni gang zag gis 'di yin 'di min gyi brjod par dka' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:9688: 'di'i dus na chos tsam du yang dmigs pa med pa na chos zad pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9689: zad lugs ni rim gyis zad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9690: snang ba bzhi tshad du phyin pa'i lugs so //
NK109(dze)001:9691: chos nyid mngon gsum mthong nas goms par byas pa
NK109(dze)001:9692: las nyams la sogs pa'i snang ba ma skyes par
NK109(dze)001:9694: 'di ni blo mchog tu gcig pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9695: de las mtha' rten gyi man ngag ni sa zin
NK109(dze)001:9696: med de gong ma rnams kyi zla la yar sdud
NK109(dze)001:9697: pa ste / gong ma'i nan cag tu byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9698: 'di ni skabs nas shes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9699: sngon 'gro la sogs pa lhag ma kha skong ba las shes /
NK109(dze)001:9700: dngos gzhi de gzhung nas sbyar nas tshig gi don ni //
NK109(dze)001:9701: gnad ni skyes pa'i snying la mdas zin pa'i mod la 'chi ba dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)001:9702: chos nyid mngon gsum gyi gnad bstan pa tsam gyis grol bar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9706: de gang du bstan pa'i don ni chos nyid /
NK109(dze)001:9707: nyams ni goms par byed pa /
NK109(dze)001:9708: blang pa ni dngos grub kyi don no //
NK109(dze)001:9709: lus ni 'byung ba 'phra rags las grub pas de dag pa'i don du 'dug stangs la bslab bo //
NK109(dze)001:9710: sgo ni ye shes 'char ba'i sgo mig 'khor ba'i gzugs 'dzin pas //
NK109(dze)001:9711: de dag par byed pa'i don du gzigs stangs la bslab bo //
NK109(dze)001:9712: lus ni 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga tha dad du
NK109(dze)001:9713: 'dzin pa'i khams gsum du khrid par byed pa ste
NK109(dze)001:9714: / de dag par byed pa'i don du nam mkha'
NK109(dze)001:9715: stong pa gang gis kyang ma gos pa la btang
NK109(dze)001:9716: / ngo // nyid ni de dag las ma 'das par bzhag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9717: de ni de dag byas nas sangs rgyas nges so zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9718: de la gang gi lus kyi rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9719: gnad ni lus bcun pas ye shes 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9720: mthongs phye bas nam mkha' gsal pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:9721: rnam pa ni 'jug par byed pa la /
NK109(dze)001:9723: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum gyi 'og tu dpe gsum las sbyor ba 'og nas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:9724: seng ge ni rtsa gnad la phab pas 'bras bu nye bar thob pa'i dgos pa yod do /
NK109(dze)001:9725: tshul dang mi khyi tshugs su 'dug pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9726: lag mthil gnyis sa la gcar bas bzung ba las kyi rlung ldog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9727: de log pas phyir ye shes kyi snang ba mthong la /
NK109(dze)001:9728: nang bzung ba yul gyi rtog pa rgyun chad do //
NK109(dze)001:9729: rkang mthil sa la mnyam par phab ste lus khyi tshugs su 'dug pa ni //
NK109(dze)001:9730: khyab pa las kyi rlung bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9731: de log pas phyir snang ba sdod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9732: nang du zhen pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:9733: ro stod bsrong sa la bor nas mjing pa bslang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9734: 'phen pa las kyi rlung ldog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9735: de log pas phyi ru ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba sdod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9736: nang du nyon mongs pa'i rgyun dum bur 'gag par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:9737: glang chen ni stobs che ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9738: khyad par che ba la tshul ni kha sbub pa ni zil gyis gnon la /
NK109(dze)001:9739: rkang lag bzhi sa la rkang pa'i the bong sa la btsugs pa phyir phul ba ni //
NK109(dze)001:9740: rtog pa du ma'i las kyi rlung ldog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9741: de log pas phyir 'khrul snang 'gag la /
NK109(dze)001:9742: nang du lus sems la drod skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9743: lag pa'i mthil sa la bcar ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9744: 'gyu ba las kyi rlung bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9745: de log pas phyir thig le dang thig phran du 'char la /
NK109(dze)001:9746: nang du nyin mtshan med pa'i nyams 'byung /
NK109(dze)001:9747: mjing pa yid tsam dbye ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9748: 'dzin pa las kyi rlung bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9749: de log pas phyir sku'i snang ba mthong la /
NK109(dze)001:9750: nang du rlung gi 'gyu ba zad par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:9751: drang srong ni lus ma 'khrul pas rtsa drangs por 'gyur la /
NK109(dze)001:9752: de srong pa'i thabs byas pas rlung dbu mar byung
NK109(dze)001:9753: pas rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa 'gag pa'o
NK109(dze)001:9754: // lta bu ni dpe shes par bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9755: lus pus brang la sbyar te tsog pur 'dug pas /
NK109(dze)001:9756: 'phra ba las kyi rlung bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9757: de log pas phyir sku sna tshogs par snang la /
NK109(dze)001:9758: nang du sems gang du yang sdod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9759: rkang pa'i mthil sa la mnan pas srog rtsol las kyi rlung ldog /
NK109(dze)001:9760: de log pas phyir drod skye /
NK109(dze)001:9761: nang du chos nyid skye ba med pa'i nyams skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9762: lag pa mjing pa la 'khyud de bsrang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9763: 'debs pa las kyi rlung bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK109(dze)001:9764: de log pas rtog pa du ma 'gag /
NK109(dze)001:9765: phyir ye shes kyi mthong ba rnam par dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9766: sgo ni mig gi gzigs stangs las mi 'da'/
NK109(dze)001:9767: de nyid ni mig ma 'gul bas lus ma 'gul /
NK109(dze)001:9770: de ma mgul bas rtog pa 'gags nges so //
NK109(dze)001:9771: gsal byed gzugs snang bar byed la /
NK109(dze)001:9772: rnam pa ni mig gnyis ma 'gul bas dbyings rig pa gnyis rang bzhin gyis dal ba rnyed do //
NK109(dze)001:9773: gong ma'i yul phyi'i nam ma 'gyur ba /
NK109(dze)001:9775: nyid sprin dang bag rdul gyis ma sgrib pa /
NK109(dze)001:9776: 'gul ba yin pa sgo dang 'brel ba med par bsdad pa /
NK109(dze)001:9780: gsum phyi nang gsang ba de ltar bstun pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9781: dag pa'i dri ma med pa /
NK109(dze)001:9786: bzhin chos nyid rig pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:9787: sdod pa goms pas phyi'i snang ba sku dang ye shes su shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:9788: 'khrul ba rang bzhin gyis thams cad sdod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9789: rgyu sems can la 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9790: de la yid ma 'gyus pas rig pa brtson du zin pa'i man ngag ni /
NK109(dze)001:9791: rlung gi 'gyu ba med pas 'gyu ba rang sor gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9792: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa 'o //
NK109(dze)001:9793: bsam pa dang bral ba'i sems ni rlung gis ma bskyod pas /
NK109(dze)001:9795: glo bur gyi dran pa sangs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9796: ye nas blo dang bral bas so //
NK109(dze)001:9797: de nyid rang ngo la gnas pas rig pa la /
NK109(dze)001:9798: de nyid dbugs dang bral bas mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)001:9799: 'bras bu sku gsum du rang gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:9800: rang las byung ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:9801: yid kyi dal bas yul la bdag tu ma bzung
NK109(dze)001:9802: bas rnam rtog las kyi rlung 'gag de 'gag pas
NK109(dze)001:9803: cir snang chos nyid du 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9804: sems rang sor bzhag nas dal bas yid kyi rtog pa rang logs te /
NK109(dze)001:9805: dran pa glo bur ba'i rgyun 'gags pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9806: phyi nang gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so //
NK109(dze)001:9807: rig pa lu gu rgyud brtson du zin pas /
NK109(dze)001:9808: rlung gi dal ba rnyed pas snang ba thams cad /
NK109(dze)001:9809: sku lnga lngar shar bas 'khrul pa'i snang ba dus gcig la 'gags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9810: de ni rig pa nam mkha' la shar bas 'byung
NK109(dze)001:9811: ba 'phra rags kyi snang bas bsgrib pa'i rkyen rdul
NK109(dze)001:9813: phyi yul gyi snang ba la dbyings kyi sgron ma
NK109(dze)001:9814: dmigs na 'od lnga rang shar bas phra ba rdul
NK109(dze)001:9816: rags pa sa chu me rlung gi 'byung ba rnams mthar gyis 'phrar song pas /
NK109(dze)001:9817: snang ba 'od gsal du shar bas phyi 'byung ba 'gags /
NK109(dze)001:9818: nang du nyon mongs pa rags pa rnams mthar gyis phra ba bag la nyal thim pas /
NK109(dze)001:9820: de ltar nyams su blang pas dbyings kyi go rar
NK109(dze)001:9821: rig pa tshud pas 'khrul snang chos nyid du shar
NK109(dze)001:9822: bas / yul lnga la bzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i sems 'gags pas 'khrul pa rgyun chad pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9823: zhes nang don bdun pa de nyid rtogs par byed pa'i man ngag bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9824: da ni nang don brgyad pa de nyid rang gi nges tshig bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9825: de ltar ni gong du bstan pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9826: mtshon byed ni rang gazhi'am sa bon mtshon par byed
NK109(dze)001:9827: pa'i thabs kyi man ngag ston par byed pa'i rgyud
NK109(dze)001:9828: ni / so so rang rang gi rgyud la ye
NK109(dze)001:9829: nas ma skyed par rdzogs par gnas pas rgyud ces
NK109(dze)001:9830: ni / bya'o // de nyid mtshon par byed pa'i thabs zhes bya ba yin no //
NK109(dze)001:9831: de rang gi lus la rgyun du gnas pas rgyud ces bya ba yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9832: mtshon byed thabs kyi rgyud kyi nges tshig go /
NK109(dze)001:9833: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don dang po
NK109(dze)001:9834: thabs kyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa las yan lag
NK109(dze)001:9835: gi don brgyad du byas nas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:9836: da ni bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi
NK109(dze)001:9837: rgyud kyi don bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK109(dze)001:9838: drug gis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)001:9839: rang bzhin gyi rgyud rang gi ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9840: de gong ma bzhin lam gshegs pa'i shes bya rang
NK109(dze)001:9841: thog tu gnas pa'i rang bzhin ni ma bcos lhug
NK109(dze)001:9843: rgyud kyi snying po ni rig pa'i gnas lugs /
NK109(dze)001:9844: de yang shes rab kyis phye na 'khor ba'i chos
NK109(dze)001:9845: dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gang gis kyang
NK109(dze)001:9847: yid dpyod kyis 'di nyid shes pa ma yin te de'i don brjod par dka' bas mi 'byed /
NK109(dze)001:9848: de nyid sra zhing brtan pas rdo rje /
NK109(dze)001:9849: de'i rang bzhin lhun grub tu gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:9850: lus can kun gyi gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9851: rang gzhan rnam par gcad pa rgyud rang gi lus
NK109(dze)001:9852: yod pa'i don de mtshon pa'i gzhi sangs rgyas dang
NK109(dze)001:9853: sems can kun la khyad med du ngo bor gcig
NK109(dze)001:9854: pa'i phyir na / de'i rang bzhin cis zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9855: stong pa nyid ngo bo ngos bzung las 'das par gcig pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9856: gzhi sangs rgyas dang sems can du gcig pas /
NK109(dze)001:9857: gang yang ma rdzogs pa med pas spang du med la /
NK109(dze)001:9858: de la phra rags bdag tu 'dzin pa'i dri ma sangs pas bslang rgyu med la /
NK109(dze)001:9859: de nyid rang bzhin gnyug mas rgyas pas dgag sgrub kyi mtha' las log pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:9860: de bskyed pas na yul zhes gdags su btub bo //
NK109(dze)001:9861: rgyud breng chags pa kyi ni de dang gang zag tu 'brel pa /
NK109(dze)001:9864: bcud kyi rgyud gsum gcig tu dril pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9865: b+hud+d+ha dang sems can gzhi gcig pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9866: zhes nang don dang po rang bzhin gyi rgyud rang gi ngo bo bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9867: da ni nang don gnyis pa dbye ba dang gzhi
NK109(dze)001:9868: rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi gnas lugs bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:9870: rgyud ni lus can dang 'brel ba /
NK109(dze)001:9871: 'di lta ste ni bshad par bya'o zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9872: gzhi thog ma dang tha ma'i rig pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9873: de ni sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad la khyab pas gzhi rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:9875: lu gu rgyud rang ngo na gsal ba /
NK109(dze)001:9876: bcud kyi rgyud rig pa'i dwangs pa 'od du gsal ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:9877: de la gzhi rgyud bshad na ni /
NK109(dze)001:9878: ngo bo ni ka nas dag pas ma rig pa'i ming med pas /
NK109(dze)001:9879: 'khrul pas btags pa tsam du yang yod ma myong /
NK109(dze)001:9880: de ltar yod ma myong pas da lta 'khrul pa zhes tha snyad tshig tsam du yang med /
NK109(dze)001:9881: de med pas phyis 'khrul par 'gro ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9884: rang bzhin ni lhun grub gyi rtsal sna tshogs su
NK109(dze)001:9885: snang bas dgag bsgrub pa'i rig pa phyogs med du
NK109(dze)001:9886: shar bas / thams cad la ma khyab pa med cing /
NK109(dze)001:9887: thams cad du byung zhing thams cad du snang bas /
NK109(dze)001:9888: lhun grub sa bon gyi tshul du bzhugs pa las
NK109(dze)001:9889: 'bras bu tha dad par byung bar thams cad dgag
NK109(dze)001:9891: thugs rje ni kun la khyab dgag tu ma btub la /
NK109(dze)001:9892: thams cad du gsal zhing 'byed pa med pas snang
NK109(dze)001:9893: cha sna tshogs su byung ba'i rig pa rang snang
NK109(dze)001:9894: ba'o // 'char byed ma 'gags pas gong ltar yang snang /
NK109(dze)001:9896: yang ngo bo la ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes su shar bas 'khrul pa'i ming med /
NK109(dze)001:9897: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi ye shes su shar pas 'gag med kyi rig pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9898: thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes su shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:9899: snang stong tha dad pa'i bdag nyid du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9900: de ltar gsum gyi bdag nyid du da lta'i dus
NK109(dze)001:9901: na lus can kun la yang gnas pas sangs rgyar
NK109(dze)001:9902: btub pa'o // de yang ngo bo ye nas ma
NK109(dze)001:9903: rig pa'i dri ma ka ni thog mar mtshon pa'am
NK109(dze)001:9905: dag pa ni byas pa'am 'bad pa lta bu min te /
NK109(dze)001:9909: de ltar 'gro 'ong med pa'i nyag gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9910: las kyi mthar sangs pas khams gsum rgyun chad /
NK109(dze)001:9911: rtogs pa sngon du rgyas pas nyon mongs kyi gzhi stongs /
NK109(dze)001:9912: rang bzhin la lhun gyis grub pa rnams kyis mi shes pas gsang ba yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:9913: bla ma'i man ngag med pa rnams kyis mi shes pa chen po yin no //
NK109(dze)001:9914: zhes nang don gnyis pa dbye ba dang gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi gnas lugs bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9915: da ni nang don gsum pa snying po rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9916: de yang sku gsum ni rig pa nyid sku gsum
NK109(dze)001:9917: ye shes lnga'i snying por rdzogs pa'i rig pa ni
NK109(dze)001:9918: / rig pa stong du gnas pas sku'i rgyud ni stong pa yin pas dngos po las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9919: de kun khyab pas lus can rnams rang grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9922: rig pa las byung ba'i ye shes /
NK109(dze)001:9923: ye shes dang ye shes las byung ba'i 'od rang snang ngo //
NK109(dze)001:9924: de yang bzung yul du med pas mi snang yul
NK109(dze)001:9925: snang yul du yod pas gsal ba'i de nyid ma
NK109(dze)001:9926: bcos pas rang bzhin can zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9927: de thams cad kyi snying po shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:9928: rig pa nyid kyi nang thams cad kyi rang bzhin rdzogs pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:9929: rang bzhin gyi rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9930: de'i phyir na 'di ltar snang ba thams cad rgyud yin te thams cad 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:9931: da lta gnyis 'brel zhing breng chags pas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:9932: de'i rang bzhin sems can kun gyi tsi ta'i dkyil
NK109(dze)001:9933: du sku ye shes sum rtsegs kyi rang bzhin du
NK109(dze)001:9934: gnas pa'o // de sus kyang ma bskyed par ye nas rdzogs pa'i snying po yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9935: gang gis kyang bcos ma las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9936: gong du bstan pa de'i phyir na gcig tu dril bas snying po'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9937: 'khor 'das kun gyi srog 'dzin par 'gyur ba'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)001:9938: snying po'i rgyud ces 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi rnam par bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:9939: zhes nang don gsum pa snying po rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:9940: da ni nang don bzhi pa bcud rang bzhin gyi rgyud don rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9941: 'das pa'i las bag chags 'gron po la brgal ba ltar sangs la /
NK109(dze)001:9942: ma 'ongs pa la dran pa'i las la 'jug pa ma skyes pa ltar sangs la /
NK109(dze)001:9943: da ltar gyi rtog pa rdo tshan la kha ba bab pa ltar sangs so //
NK109(dze)001:9944: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba sa bon la lo 'dab rgyas pa ltar rgyas la /
NK109(dze)001:9945: ma 'ongs pa gser dang ser po rang chas pa ltar rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:9946: da lta'i btab pa'i lo thog dus su smin pa ltar rgyas so //
NK109(dze)001:9947: de dag thams cad gcig tu sdud pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:9949: ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i rig pa'i snying po
NK109(dze)001:9950: las 'das ma thams cad du bcud phyung ba ni
NK109(dze)001:9951: / nyams su myong pa'i don rang rgyud la skyes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9952: don dper na mar gyi snying po dril ba lta bur /
NK109(dze)001:9953: bsdus pas bcud zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9954: de stong pa yin pas mtshan ma ris can du ma song la /
NK109(dze)001:9955: de yang rtag pa mthar 'dzin pas rdzas su grub pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:9956: de nyid stong pa'i rang ngo gsal bar shar bas chad pa phyam chad pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:9957: stong pa dang gsal bar dbyer mi phyed /
NK109(dze)001:9958: de nyid rig pa'i mkhyen pa phyogs med du gsal bas /
NK109(dze)001:9959: stong pa phyam chad pa ma yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9960: gsal ba ris can du ma yin la /
NK109(dze)001:9961: rang gi don dam ma yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:9962: gsum dbyer med pas rtag chad gnyis ka dang /
NK109(dze)001:9963: gnyis ka ma yin pa log pas /
NK109(dze)001:9964: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9965: de'i bcud du rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud du dril ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:9966: 'di'i dus na rnam rtog tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK109(dze)001:9967: dri ma gnas mi srid pas sangs zhes bya la
NK109(dze)001:9968: / de nyid rig pa'i 'phel rgyas pas lus ngag
NK109(dze)001:9969: yid kun gyi bde ba thabs kyis bskyed pa ni
NK109(dze)001:9970: / / bla ma'i lung med pa la rang bzhin gyis gsang bas de'i don mi mthong ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:9971: gdams pa chen po yod pa la tshegs med par mthong ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:9972: khong du chud pa dus mnyam /
NK109(dze)001:9973: de chud pa dang nyams dang rtogs pa 'char bar dus mnyam mo //
NK109(dze)001:9974: de shar ba dang bud+d+ha pa dus mnyam pas na /
NK109(dze)001:9975: mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' dang bral ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9976: de yang gang las byung zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:9977: gzhi ma bcos par rang sar bzhag pa /
NK109(dze)001:9978: snying po mig mi 'gyur bar lta ba /
NK109(dze)001:9979: me tog de nyid la brten nas gsal ba 'gag pa med pa'i yul can zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9980: de gzhan la ma brten par rang gis rig pas /
NK109(dze)001:9981: de la chos rnams kyi ngo bo nyid snang ba rnam par dag pa mthong ba zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:9982: de nyid mthong ba tsam gyis ma rig 'khrul pa'i gzhi stongs /
NK109(dze)001:9983: de nyid pas khams du 'jug pa'i khung sgo chod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9984: de ni rdzogs pas gzhan la rag ma lus pas
NK109(dze)001:9985: chen po lta ba kun las khyad par du 'phags
NK109(dze)001:9986: pa / bcud dbyings rig pa 'bral med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:9987: de yang rgyud gzhan gser gyi me tog gi snying po las /
NK109(dze)001:9988: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bcud bsdus nas //
NK109(dze)001:9989: 'gro ba kun gyi snying la bcug /
NK109(dze)001:9990: de yi snying po lu gu rgyud //
NK109(dze)001:9991: dwangs ma bsdus pas bcud zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:9993: yang brtson pa don ldan las /
NK109(dze)001:9994: bstan pa kun gyi yang bcud ni //
NK109(dze)001:9995: chos nyid mngon sum lam zhes bya //
NK109(dze)001:9997: yang rdo rje nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las /
NK109(dze)001:9998: gzhi dang snying po'i me tog ni //
NK109(dze)001:9999: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin rgyud //
NK109(dze)001:10000: khyad par gsang mchog bcud du dril //
NK109(dze)001:10002: skyes bus mda' 'phangs ji bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:10004: yang mdo sde gser 'od dam pa las /
NK109(dze)001:10005: gzhi dang rang bzhin thabs dag las //
NK109(dze)001:10006: brten nas sa ngas rgyas zhing du yang //
NK109(dze)001:10007: tshegs med sla phyir rgyud du bzhag /
NK109(dze)001:10008: ces pa la sogs te lung bgrangs na brjod kyis mi lang ngo /
NK109(dze)001:10009: de lta gzhan las kyang rab tu grags pa'i gnad 'di ni /
NK109(dze)001:10010: theg pa thun mong pas mi shes pas gsang ba'i don la /
NK109(dze)001:10011: rgyud 'od nas ston pas na rig pa dang ye shes gnyis su rnam par bshad par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10012: zhes zhal gyis kyang bzhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10013: nges pas ni tshad ma yin zhing bstan du yod pas /
NK109(dze)001:10014: lung de dag ni bzung du yod pa'i phyir na lung yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10015: de'i rang bzhin stong par gnas kyang kun la khyab pas rgyud du bzhag tu btub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10016: zhes nang don bzhi pa bcud rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don rgyas par bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10017: da ni nang don lnga pa bcud rang bzhin de
NK109(dze)001:10018: dngos po las 'das te dbye ba bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:10019: / de yang ni gong ma las nye bar bsdus
NK109(dze)001:10020: pa bcud kyi rang bzhin ni don gdams ngag tu
NK109(dze)001:10021: dril ba snying po ni rig pa bsdus pa ni
NK109(dze)001:10025: ye shes kyi sku dang gsum ni /
NK109(dze)001:10026: phyi yul la snang ba'i dus na rig pa la skur gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10028: nam mkha' la dbyings rig 'du 'bral med par gsal ba gsum dang /
NK109(dze)001:10029: de nyid shes pas lta ba la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10030: de ltar shar nas yid ches pa lta ba'i gdeng dang /
NK109(dze)001:10031: dag snang zin pa yul gyi gdeng dang /
NK109(dze)001:10032: 'khrul pa 'gags pa thag chod pa'i gdeng dang gsum skyes pas /
NK109(dze)001:10033: 'khor ba nyid ye nas sangs rgyas su shes pas
NK109(dze)001:10034: rig pa la rgyu med pas mi ldog rig pa'i
NK109(dze)001:10035: sku mngon par snang bas 'khrul snang dag snang du
NK109(dze)001:10036: grol bas snang ba mi ldog chos nyid de sna
NK109(dze)001:10037: tshogs su snang bas rtogs pa'i gdeng rnyed pas mi
NK109(dze)001:10038: ldog pa dang gsum gyis ni /
NK109(dze)001:10039: ngo bo bcud du dril bas de las mi 'gyur
NK109(dze)001:10040: nges pa'i sa thob pas slar ldog rgyu med pas
NK109(dze)001:10041: ldog rten med de med pas ldog rkyen rang dag
NK109(dze)001:10042: / de dag pas ldog pa'i 'bras bu ye grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10043: de ltar grol bas 'khrul pa'i snang ba rang dag pas 'khor rgyu med /
NK109(dze)001:10044: de nyid dag pa'i snang ba rang shar bas 'khor rkyen rang 'gags /
NK109(dze)001:10045: 'dir ma chod kyang chos nyid kyi bar do'i snang
NK109(dze)001:10046: bar chod pas 'khor 'bras rang yal ba dang gsum
NK109(dze)001:10047: dang ni / 'di'i dus na rig pa la zla med pas 'khrul pa stong pa /
NK109(dze)001:10048: sems la rkyen med pas rnam rtog dri ma stong
NK109(dze)001:10049: 'od la 'gro med pas 'byung ba'i rkyen stong pa
NK109(dze)001:10050: dang gsum ni rig pa nyid bcu da du dril
NK109(dze)001:10051: ba'i rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i rgyun du gtan
NK109(dze)001:10052: la phab pa'o // de la ming 'dogs kyi dbang du byas na mi 'gyur bas gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:10053: de nyid drang por gnas pas lam dang /
NK109(dze)001:10055: de yang bzung bar ni bltar yod pa'i don tshad mas nges pas /
NK109(dze)001:10056: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10057: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na rang la gtan la bab
NK109(dze)001:10058: pas rgyud ces bya bar sems dang 'brel bas grub
NK109(dze)001:10059: pa'o // de yang shes bya stong ba'i rang bzhin la babs kyis grub pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10060: de'i don gsal ba'i cha ma 'gags pas sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)001:10061: sems can 'khor 'das gong ltar yang shar bas rang
NK109(dze)001:10063: zhes nang don lnga pa bcud rang bzhin gyi rgyud de dngos las 'das te dbye ba bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10064: da ni nang don drug pa rgyud de dag kyang
NK109(dze)001:10065: don so so ma yin par dpe don dang bcas
NK109(dze)001:10067: de yang sangs rgyas sems can gnyis ni gzhi gcig
NK109(dze)001:10068: yin pa las ngo bo'i khyad par las sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)001:10069: yon tan rnams kyis spras pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10070: shes rab rnon po gzhi nas 'phags pa las byung la /
NK109(dze)001:10071: sems can gyis shes rab nyid shes rab tu ma shes pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10072: da de las bzlog pa'i thabs bla ma'i man ngag gis mtshon byed tshig tsam la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10073: don tshig gis 'bud tha bar rtogs te /
NK109(dze)001:10074: de'i rang bzhin mtshan nyid du ma grub pas /
NK109(dze)001:10075: rang rgyud las bcos su med pas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10076: chos nyid kyi don de brjod pa las 'das pas
NK109(dze)001:10077: kyang brtag pa tsam du tshig gis mtshon pa de
NK109(dze)001:10078: ltar snang ngo // der snang yang de'i ngo bo
NK109(dze)001:10079: la tha snyad du dgags su med pas gzhi gcig
NK109(dze)001:10080: ltar snang ngo // yin par rtogs / de'i rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10081: de nyid stong pa blo'i spyod yul ma yin pas rtag pa rnam grangs kyi chos las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10082: de'i ngo bo zang thal bas tha dad pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)001:10083: rang bzhin gcig tu gnas pas 'gyur ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:10084: dper na skyes pa'am bud med gang rung ba zhig la /
NK109(dze)001:10085: ming mang po yod par gyur pa la /
NK109(dze)001:10086: ming gang nas bos kyang a zer ba ltar /
NK109(dze)001:10087: ming tha dad pa bzhin du lus tha dad ma yin te /
NK109(dze)001:10088: de ltar snang ba ltar chos nyid 'gyur ba med don kyang gang ltar brtags kyang mi stong ste /
NK109(dze)001:10089: ming gcig nas bos pas a zer 'ong ba dang
NK109(dze)001:10090: 'dra bar tshig gis don gtan la phebs pa ste
NK109(dze)001:10091: / don gyi ngo bo gtan la phebs te /
NK109(dze)001:10092: chos thams cad du ma ro gcig tu go ba tsh+wa gcig gi ro gtan la phebs nas /
NK109(dze)001:10093: tsh+wa thams cad kyi ro gtan la phebs pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:10094: de'i phyir na gang ltar brtags pa de ltar snang /
NK109(dze)001:10096: zhes de dag gi bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa rang
NK109(dze)001:10097: bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don bstan pa la yan lag
NK109(dze)001:10098: gi don drug tu byas nas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:10099: da ni bsdus pa'i don gsum pa tshig gi rgyud
NK109(dze)001:10100: bstan pa la yan lag gi don drug gis bstan
NK109(dze)001:10101: pa'i dang po / tshig gi rgyud ces bya ba
NK109(dze)001:10102: gang lags zhes rdo rje 'dzin pas zhus pa bstan
NK109(dze)001:10103: pa'i dang po / pa ni / de nas zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:10104: tshig dgus gzhung gis shes so //
NK109(dze)001:10105: da ni yan lag gi don gnyis pa de'i lan
NK109(dze)001:10106: tshig gi rgyud gnyis su gtan la phab pa bstan
NK109(dze)001:10107: pa ni / de nas rdo rje 'chang chen la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)001:10108: de nas rgyud kyi ston pa drug pa rdo rje
NK109(dze)001:10109: 'chang chen po des rgyud rnams ni tshig gi rgyud
NK109(dze)001:10110: rab tu 'byed pa'i gting zab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10111: de gsal ba 'dzin gsang pa'i de'i don mi gtong
NK109(dze)001:10112: pa las bzhengs ba sku'i 'dug stangs sna tshogs pas
NK109(dze)001:10113: gzigs na ni / sdud pa po lag na rdo
NK109(dze)001:10114: rje can la bos nas tshig 'di skad du gsungs
NK109(dze)001:10115: gzigs na ni / so // e ma ho zhes ngo mtshar ba dang bcas bas /
NK109(dze)001:10116: rdo rje sems dpa' 'dun pa 'dzin pa rtag tu gnas pa /
NK109(dze)001:10117: lus dang dbang po la sogs pa phyin ci ma log bar nyon cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10118: de nyid ni tshig gi rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par bshad par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10120: don ni rang bzhin dang thabs kyi rgyud dang ni zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10122: brjod bya log pa dang ma log pa'i khyad par gyi chos so //
NK109(dze)001:10123: rgyud ni bskyed pa'i rim pa gtsor bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10124: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtsor ston pa gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:10125: 'di dag ni rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso cher ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10126: de yang don ni sngar bstan pa'i rim pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10127: zhes nang don gnyis pa lan tshig rgyud kyi ganya sa su gtan la phab pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10128: da ni nang don gsum pa rgyud kyi mtshan sngon
NK109(dze)001:10129: du 'gro bas dbye ba bstan pa ni sngon du
NK109(dze)001:10131: rjes la skye ba'i rim pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10138: ngo bo ni mnan pa dang spre bar mi btub cing chod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10140: rigs mtshon pa'i phyir na rgyud de /
NK109(dze)001:10141: gang dang gang gis rigs su skye bar byed pas na rgyud de /
NK109(dze)001:10142: thang chod cing breng chags pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10143: dbye na tshig gi rgyud la btags pa'i dang /
NK109(dze)001:10146: sems nyid rnam par rtog pa'i dri ma med pa la bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:10147: des sangs rgyas pa'i mtshan nyid 'dzin par byed pas
NK109(dze)001:10148: na rgyud la sangs rgyas kyi rigs mtshon bar byed
NK109(dze)001:10150: btags pa po la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:10151: ming dang ming don ldan gyis rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10152: ming ni gang la ming yod pa la bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10153: ming don ldan ni bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso che bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10154: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10155: ldang tshad ni bskyed rim gtso bo la bcu'o //
NK109(dze)001:10160: ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:10161: phrin las dang lta ba gnyis te bcu tshang na
NK109(dze)001:10162: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso ba'i rgyud kyi ldang tshad
NK109(dze)001:10163: do // rdzogs pa la brgyad ste /
NK109(dze)001:10165: spyod pa dang sgom pa gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:10167: nyams dang gdams pa gnyis te brgyad po de tshang na /
NK109(dze)001:10168: rdzogs rim gtso ba'i ldang tshad do //
NK109(dze)001:10171: rgyu spun mang po la brten nas ras yug du longs ba lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:10172: de ltar tshig tha dad pa la brten nas don gcig tu slong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10173: 'thad pa ni rang la gnas pa'i rgyud de mtshon par byed pas na rgyud du 'thad do //
NK109(dze)001:10174: de yang tshig gi 'thad pa la brten nas don
NK109(dze)001:10175: phyin ci ma log par byed pas na rgyud do
NK109(dze)001:10176: // de yi rim pa gsal bar dbye /
NK109(dze)001:10178: tshig gi spros pa gcod pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i don rnams /
NK109(dze)001:10180: rgya mtsho lta bur brjod bya mang pas rig pa rang shar gyi rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:10182: spyod pa'i don rgya mtsho ltar ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10183: nyi ma lta bur gsal par ston par byed pa rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long /
NK109(dze)001:10184: theg pa gzhan gyi chos zil gyis manonapa'i chos ston pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10185: seng ge lta bu'i rgyud seng ge rtsal rdzogs dang ni /
NK109(dze)001:10186: mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid ston pa ri rgyal lta bu'i rgyud dpal yi ge med pa /
NK109(dze)001:10187: 'khrul pa'i 'khor lo gcod par ston pas 'khor lo lta bu'i rgyud bkra shis mdzes ldan /
NK109(dze)001:10188: sde snod kun gyi sgo 'byed par ston pa'i lde mig lta bu'i rgyud thal 'gyur gyis rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:10189: gol sa gcod par ston pa ral gri lta bu'i
NK109(dze)001:10190: rgyud kun tu bzang po thugs kyi me long dang
NK109(dze)001:10191: snang ba'i sgron ma ston par byed pa gsal shing
NK109(dze)001:10192: lta bu'i sgron ma 'bar ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10193: tshig don gser la g.yu spras pa lta bur ston
NK109(dze)001:10194: pa gser zhun ma lta bu'i rgyud nor bu 'phra
NK109(dze)001:10195: bkod / yid ches nges pa'i tshig ston par /
NK109(dze)001:10196: bar do la 'debs pa ma bu 'brel pa lta bu'i rgyud nyi zla kha sbyor /
NK109(dze)001:10197: me long gi nang du gzugs brnyan lta bur dpe
NK109(dze)001:10198: dang sbyar te ston par byed pa'i rgyud ngo sprod
NK109(dze)001:10200: mu tig gi 'phreng ba rgyu legs pa ltar man
NK109(dze)001:10201: ngag gi khrigs chags su ston pa mu tig phreng
NK109(dze)001:10202: ba'i rgyud dang / sbrul gyi mdud pa lta bur
NK109(dze)001:10203: gzhung tshig rang grol du ston par rig pa rang
NK109(dze)001:10205: khyung chen po nam mkha' la brtsol ba dang grub
NK109(dze)001:10206: pa med par thang gcad nas 'gro ba lta bu'i
NK109(dze)001:10207: rgyud kun tu bzang po klong drug pa'i rgyud dang
NK109(dze)001:10208: / chu bo'i rgyun 'bab pa lta bur dbang dang
NK109(dze)001:10209: byin rlabs ston par byed la rdzogs pa rang byung
NK109(dze)001:10210: / gi rgyud dang / spu gri tsha ngar dang
NK109(dze)001:10211: ldan pas gang reg pa gcod pa lta bu'i rgyud
NK109(dze)001:10212: dpal nag mo khros ma'i rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:10213: rgyal po'i gdung mi 'gyur bar rang sa zin pa
NK109(dze)001:10214: lta bur bstan pa'i rgyud sku gdung 'bar ba'i rgyud
NK109(dze)001:10215: dang / phyugs po'i bang mdzod na dgos pa la
NK109(dze)001:10216: spyod pa lta bu'i rgyud rin po che spungs pa
NK109(dze)001:10218: gsang chen nges pa chos nyid kyi don gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i rgyud bcu bdun dang /
NK109(dze)001:10219: bstan pa srung ba'i rgyud dpal nag mo khroms ma'i rgyud dang bco brgyad ni /
NK109(dze)001:10220: rang bzhin gtan la 'beb pa'i gnad ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10221: de ltar rgyud bco ba rgyad du rnam par phye bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10222: tshig gi rgyud kyi rim pa gsal bar phye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10223: tshig rgyud kyi don rnam par phye bas /
NK109(dze)001:10224: rang gi gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyang tshig rgyud la brten nas mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:10225: zhes nang don gsum pa rgyud kyi mtshon dpe dang sbyar ba'i dbye ba la bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10226: da ni nang don bzhi pa rgyud de dag gi che ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10227: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod nges par zungs shig /
NK109(dze)001:10228: zhes nyan par rna ba gtad cing bskul nas /
NK109(dze)001:10229: de la rgyud kyi snying po ni rig pa rang shar dang /
NK109(dze)001:10231: dpal yi ge med pa dang gsum shes na /
NK109(dze)001:10232: rgyal pos dmangs la dbang bsgyur ba dang 'dra ba
NK109(dze)001:10233: yi ge med pas rgyud spyi'i man ngag ston no
NK109(dze)001:10234: // de la blon pos kha lo bsgyur ba dang
NK109(dze)001:10235: 'dra bar rang shar gyis lta sgom spyod pa'i gzhi
NK109(dze)001:10236: 'dzin cing rang shar gyi dmigs ston /
NK109(dze)001:10237: rang grol ni dmangs kyi g.yog la sogs pa'i dmag dang khral la sogs pa byed pa ltar /
NK109(dze)001:10239: de gsum 'dzom pas rgyal khams la dbang bsgyur ba
NK109(dze)001:10240: dang 'dra ba sde snod kun la dbang bsgyur ba'o
NK109(dze)001:10241: // rgyud kyi dwangs ma ni me long gnyis dang nor bu 'phra bkod gsum shes na /
NK109(dze)001:10242: dper na ri gsum 'dus pa'i rtse mor phyin pas thams cad mthong ba dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)001:10243: 'di gsum shes pas chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid mthong ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10244: rgyud kyi me tog mu tig 'phreng ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10246: seng ge rtsal rdzogs gsum shes na nam mkha' la
NK109(dze)001:10247: nyi ma gsum dus gcig la shar ba dang 'dra'o
NK109(dze)001:10248: // rgyud kun gyi gdams pa gzhi la ma smin
NK109(dze)001:10249: pa smin par byed pa rdzogs pa rang byung gi
NK109(dze)001:10250: rgyud gcig tu shes pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10251: mkhar mthon po bslang pa'i 'gram rdo legs par tshud
NK109(dze)001:10252: bas rtse mor bslang du btub pa dang 'dra bar
NK109(dze)001:10253: de la brten nas rgyud gzhan nyan du btub pa
NK109(dze)001:10254: dang / bshad du rung ba thob pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10255: snang ba ni 'od lnga ting ni rang lus la /
NK109(dze)001:10256: rdzogs pa ni dmigs rdzogs pa'i ngo sprod pa'i rgyud spras pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10257: rtse mo 'byong pa'i mkhar la gzhan gyi dmag gis mi tshugs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10258: ye shes ni chos nyid kyi bar ma do /
NK109(dze)001:10259: gsum ni 'khrul ba las dag snang du bzlog par byed pa'i rgyud nyi zla kha sbyor shes na /
NK109(dze)001:10260: mkhar la phyogs bzhir dkar khung btod pas nang du snang ba gsal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10261: yan lag ni rkang pa gnyis med na 'gro ba'i don po med pa ltar dang /
NK109(dze)001:10262: rkang pa gnyis yod pas gong du 'gro ba'i sar
NK109(dze)001:10263: phyin pa dang 'dra ba'i rgyud chen po rin po
NK109(dze)001:10264: che spungs pa dang 'dra bar sku gdung 'bar ba
NK109(dze)001:10265: gnyis shes na / mkhar de la logs bzhi'i ba gam btags pa rab tu mdzes pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10267: de ltar lus sems gnyis 'grol bar byed pa'i rgyud sgron ma 'bar ba shes na /
NK109(dze)001:10268: rgyal po bsod nams dang ldan pa mkhar gyi rtser bzhag pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10269: snying po yod pas lus dang dbang po la sogs pa don byed pa dang 'dra ba'i rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:10270: kun tu bzang po klong drug pa shes na /
NK109(dze)001:10271: de la sgo mo dam po legs par bsgrigs pas
NK109(dze)001:10272: dgra dang rkun ma la sogs pas glags mi rnyed
NK109(dze)001:10273: pa dang 'dra'o // theg pa gzhan du gsang pa
NK109(dze)001:10274: la rang gi gzhung na dgos 'dod gzhan la rag
NK109(dze)001:10275: ma lus par ston par byed pa'i rgyud sgra thal
NK109(dze)001:10276: pa dang 'dra'o // 'gyur shes na / mkhar gyi
NK109(dze)001:10277: mtha' la lcags ris bskor bas dmag la sogs pa
NK109(dze)001:10278: pha rol gyi gnod pas mi tshugs pa dang 'dra'o
NK109(dze)001:10279: pa dang 'dra'o // 'gyur shes na / // mtshon cha rnon pos rang gi lus srung zhing /
NK109(dze)001:10280: pha rol gyi dmag dpung bzlog par byed pa dang
NK109(dze)001:10281: 'dra ba'i rgyud dpal nag mo khros ma shes na
NK109(dze)001:10282: / skyes pa gyad go zhub ldan pas mkhar gyi
NK109(dze)001:10283: sgo srung pas nang du sus kyang mi thar ba
NK109(dze)001:10284: / dang 'dra'o // zhes nang don bzhi pa rgyud de dag gi che ba bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10285: da ni yan lag gi don ston pa de'i don
NK109(dze)001:10286: rgyud brgyad du bsdus pa'i ngo bo bshad pa bstan
NK109(dze)001:10287: pa ni / e ma ni rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK109(dze)001:10288: don cig char du gtan la phebs pa'i gsang ba
NK109(dze)001:10289: snying dang 'dra ba de ltar bco brgyad las mchog
NK109(dze)001:10290: tu gsang chen nges pa'i rgyud bcu bdun ni gzhan
NK109(dze)001:10291: du bstan pa med pas ngo mtshar mchog tu che
NK109(dze)001:10292: pa ni / bas na / de'i don kun rtsa
NK109(dze)001:10293: ba dang yan lag gi rnam pa ltar bshad na
NK109(dze)001:10294: pa ni / bas na / / de yang rgyud kyi rim pa brgyad du bsdu na ni /
NK109(dze)001:10296: rdzogs pa rang byung la rtsa ba'i lung brgyad la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10297: phyi spros bcas kyi dbang gis 'gro ba spros pa
NK109(dze)001:10298: la dga' ba rnams yongs su smin par byed pa'o
NK109(dze)001:10299: // yi ge med pa'i rgyud le'u drug pa la
NK109(dze)001:10300: brten nas smin pa de grol bar byed pa'i man
NK109(dze)001:10301: ngag gi gnad rdzogs par bstan pa dang gnyis kyi
NK109(dze)001:10302: // ni / chos kun du ma ro gcig pas
NK109(dze)001:10303: dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa chos nyid la 'bras
NK109(dze)001:10304: bu med par bshad pa dang cig bshad pa'i rgyud
NK109(dze)001:10305: rig pa rang shar le'u brgyad cu rtsa drug pa
NK109(dze)001:10306: // ni / la brten nas / lta ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10308: spyod pa 'bras bu bzhi'i brjod bya khyad par du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10309: rig pa rang grol le'u dgu la brten nas ma'i
NK109(dze)001:10310: so gcod kyi dmigs gsal bar 'byed pa'i bu dang
NK109(dze)001:10311: gnyis kyis ni / dbyar gyi shing la lo 'dab
NK109(dze)001:10312: rgyas pa ltar brjod bya tha dad pa gtan la
NK109(dze)001:10313: phab nas snang tshul dang shar tshul du bshad pa
NK109(dze)001:10314: gnyis kyis ni / dang gnyis / yan lag gi
NK109(dze)001:10315: rgyud ni rin po che spungs pa le'u lnga la
NK109(dze)001:10316: brten nas yon tan rang rdzogs su bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:10317: gnyis kyis ni / dang gnyis / / sku gdung
NK109(dze)001:10318: 'bar ba le'u gsum la brten nas snga phyi da
NK109(dze)001:10319: lta'i lus ngag yid kyi rtags bstan pa dang gnyis
NK109(dze)001:10320: gnyis kyis ni / dang gnyis / / dag gis
NK109(dze)001:10321: ni / rgya mtsho la gza' skar shar ba bzhin
NK109(dze)001:10322: du gsal ba gting rdzogs par bshad pa dang gsum
NK109(dze)001:10323: gnyis kyis ni / dang gnyis / / dag gis ni / / lung rig gsal ba'i rgyud /
NK109(dze)001:10324: sgra thal 'gyur le'u drug la brten nas sde snod thams cad kyi rtsa bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10325: bkra shis mdzes ldan le'u bdun la brten nas 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:10326: ba'i dus la sogs pa ngos bzung ba dang gnyis
NK109(dze)001:10327: kyis me tog pad+ma kha phye bas phyis de las
NK109(dze)001:10328: skyed med pa ltar bshad pa dang bzhi /
NK109(dze)001:10329: man ngag gi rgyud rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi
NK109(dze)001:10330: me long le'u brgyad pa la brten nas ngo sprad
NK109(dze)001:10332: dbang dang dam tshig la sogs pa bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10333: kun tu bzang po thugs kyi me long le'u bdun pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10334: grol sgrib shan 'byed par bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10335: ngo sprod spras pa le'u gsum la brten nas snga
NK109(dze)001:10336: phyi da lta'i dpe don rtags la yid ches par
NK109(dze)001:10337: bstan pa dang / mu tig 'phreng ba'i le'u brgyad
NK109(dze)001:10338: la brten nas man ngag tha dad pa la brten
NK109(dze)001:10339: nas 'bu tha bar byed pa dang ste bzhi yis
NK109(dze)001:10340: bstan pa dang / ni / shing de la shing
NK109(dze)001:10341: thog smin pas 'bras bu gzhan med par smin pa
NK109(dze)001:10342: phyis mi ldog pa'i tshul du bshad pa dang lnga
NK109(dze)001:10343: bstan pa dang / ni / / dgongs pa rang
NK109(dze)001:10344: la gnas pa'i rgyud klong drug pa klong drug la
NK109(dze)001:10345: brten nas rigs drug gi skye gnas dag pa ra
NK109(dze)001:10346: byas pas khams gsum dong sprugs par bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:10347: bstan pa dang / ni / / / sgron ma
NK109(dze)001:10348: 'bar ba'i le'u bzhi la brten nas sgron ma bzhi
NK109(dze)001:10350: nyi zla kha sbyor le'u bzhi la brten nas bar
NK109(dze)001:10351: ma do bzhi lam du khyer bar bstan pa dang
NK109(dze)001:10353: da mig phye bas snang ba thams cad mthong bar
NK109(dze)001:10354: byed pa'i mig gis tshul du bshad pa dang drug
NK109(dze)001:10355: 'jug par rang grol ba'i rgyud seng ge rtsal rdzogs
NK109(dze)001:10356: le'u bcu gsum la brten nas lta ba'i dbyings byung
NK109(dze)001:10358: nor bu 'dra bkod le'u bcu bzhi pa la brten
NK109(dze)001:10359: nas rnal 'byor pa'i lam srol du zhugs par bstan
NK109(dze)001:10361: dran pa'i gzhi snying dang ldan pas gang byas pa
NK109(dze)001:10362: la thogs pa med pa'i tshul du bshad ba dang
NK109(dze)001:10363: bdun / mkhas pa cho ga'i rgyud dpal nag mo
NK109(dze)001:10364: 'khros pa'i rgyud le'u brgya rtsa brgyad pa la brten
NK109(dze)001:10365: nas bstan pa la gnod par sems pa drungs gdon
NK109(dze)001:10367: dper na grong gcig na khyim bzang po gcig gis
NK109(dze)001:10368: mel tshe byas pas rkun mas glags mi rnyed pa
NK109(dze)001:10369: ltar bshad de / de ltar brgyad du 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10370: de la rtsa ba'i rgyud gnyis med na /
NK109(dze)001:10371: sdong po rtsa ba rul ba la yal ga 'byung mi srid pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10372: bshad pa'i rgyud ma bu gnyis med na de la
NK109(dze)001:10373: lo ma med pas me tog 'ong mi srid pa
NK109(dze)001:10374: dang 'dra'o // yan lag gi rgyu gnyis med na
NK109(dze)001:10375: yan lag med pa'i mi lag rdum brag la 'dzeg
NK109(dze)001:10376: pas kyang lam med sar rang lhung pa dang 'dra'o
NK109(dze)001:10377: dang 'dra'o // // 'jug pa rang grol gyi rgyud gnyis med na /
NK109(dze)001:10378: snying med pa'i ros gzhan gyi don byed mi nus pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10379: lung rig gsal ba'i rgyud gnyis med na me tog
NK109(dze)001:10380: med pas 'bras bu dus su mi smin pa dang
NK109(dze)001:10381: 'dra'o // man ngag gi rgyud sde bzhi med na
NK109(dze)001:10382: 'bras bu med pas so nam byas pas god mod
NK109(dze)001:10383: 'dra'o // pa dang 'dra'o // dgongs pa rang gnas kyi rgyud gsum med na /
NK109(dze)001:10384: mig med pa'i mis las yang mi shes pas grong khyer du 'jug par mi nus pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10385: mkhas ba'i cho ga'i rgyu med na mel tshe byed
NK109(dze)001:10386: pa'i khyim med na nor rkun ba'i 'chor bar dang
NK109(dze)001:10387: 'dra'o // de ltar brgyad po de med na ni
NK109(dze)001:10388: bstan pa gcig gi cha rkyen ma rdzogs pas brgyad
NK109(dze)001:10389: du nges shing brgyad du 'thad la /
NK109(dze)001:10390: de las mang na mi dgos pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10391: de yang zug pa rtsa ba ltar bshad pas /
NK109(dze)001:10392: rtsa ba sems 'du ba la dgongs /
NK109(dze)001:10393: bshad pa ni rgyas pa lo 'dab ltar bshad pas /
NK109(dze)001:10394: tshig don 'bri ba la dgongs la /
NK109(dze)001:10395: yan lag gi dril ba sdong po ltar bshad pas /
NK109(dze)001:10396: dbyings rig gnyis su med pa la dgongs la /
NK109(dze)001:10397: lung rig ni gsal ba me long ltar bshad pas
NK109(dze)001:10398: sgron ma'i rang ngo 'dzin cing mngon sum du bstan
NK109(dze)001:10399: du yod pa la dgongs la /
NK109(dze)001:10400: man ngag gi smin pa 'bras bu ltar bshad pas /
NK109(dze)001:10401: sku gsum lam du byed pa la dgongs la /
NK109(dze)001:10402: dgongs pa rang gnas grol lam mthong byed ltar bshad pas /
NK109(dze)001:10403: 'bras bu lam du byed pa la dgongs la /
NK109(dze)001:10404: 'jug pa rang grol ni dran rig lam du slong
NK109(dze)001:10405: ba skyes bus snying stobs dang ldan pa ltar bshad
NK109(dze)001:10406: pas / sgron ma nyid ngo sprod pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10407: mkhas pa cho ga dmag gi dpung rdzogs pa ltar bshad pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10408: bstan pa nyid bsrungs nas yun ring du gnas pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10409: de dag gi 'bras bu ni rtsa ba zhes /
NK109(dze)001:10410: chos kyi rtsa ba sems la 'dus la /
NK109(dze)001:10411: sems kyi rtsa ba stong pa ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10412: rgyud ni de bzung pas sems dang ngo 'phrad /
NK109(dze)001:10413: bcings pas ting nge 'dzin rang la gnas /
NK109(dze)001:10414: blangs pas brjod bya'i don mthar thug pa sems la 'char /
NK109(dze)001:10415: bshad pas mchog gi dngos grub thun mong du thob /
NK109(dze)001:10416: bsgoms pas 'khor ba dong sprugs bsnyen pas gnas skabs kyi ye shes la longs spyod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10417: man ngag gi spros pa tshig gi man ngag tshig tu 'gro la don rang la mi phebs /
NK109(dze)001:10418: gnad 'dus don gyi man ngag gis tshig la ma brten par sangs rgyas so //
NK109(dze)001:10419: man ngag sems brjod bya la brten nas brjod du med pa'i don sems la skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10420: bshad pa'i tshig ni tshig gi spros pa la brten nas don spros med kyi ye shes mtshon pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10421: dgongs pa ni thun mtshams las 'das pa'i ye shes la bar med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10422: de yang rang la gnas pas gnas pa nas byung ba med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10423: lung ni mi 'gyur zhing bstan pa la yid ches skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10424: rigs pa'i ni de'i don la brten nas rig pas sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10425: gsal ba shes pa gsal bas gang du ma 'gags /
NK109(dze)001:10426: dbang po gsal bas chos dang chos ma yin par rnam par phyed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10428: de la yan dbang po lnga rang yan du bzhag pas tshogs drug gyi na d+har 'gyur ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10429: lag ni bzung ba tsam gyis khams gsum las 'da' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:10430: 'jug pa stong pa snang ba la zhugs pas snang sems kha sbyor /
NK109(dze)001:10431: snang bas stong pa la zhugs pas yul sems gnyis su med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10432: de las rang grol bas bcos su med ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10433: mkhas pa ni ma mo'i dus na rnal pa la
NK109(dze)001:10434: mkhas pas bsam pa tsam gyis bsgrub bya nyams par
NK109(dze)001:10435: byed pa dang / las dang 'od ka la mkhas
NK109(dze)001:10436: pas mnan pa tsam gyis sngags dang ting nge 'dzin
NK109(dze)001:10437: mi dgongs par bsgrub bya'i srog chom pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10438: ma mo'i sngags dang ting nge 'dzin la mkhas pas lha nye zhing dngos grub myur ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10439: ma mo'i bsnyen bsgrub las sbyor la mkhas pas rang gi 'dod pa'i don 'grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10440: rdzas dang mchod pa la mkha' 'gro ma'i las kyi 'gyur brtse zhing bya ba 'grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10441: cho ga rdzogs pa la brten nas lha zhing dngos ma'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10442: cho ga thor bu ba la brten nas gnas skabs kyi las nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10443: cho ga phra mo la brten nas mkha' 'gro ma'i las kyi 'gyur brtse ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10444: zhes nang don lnga pa de dag kyang rgyud brgyad du bsdus pa'i ngo bo bshad pa bstan nas /
NK109(dze)001:10445: da ni yan lag gi don drug pa tshig gi
NK109(dze)001:10446: rgyud dag gi bshad pa'i dgos pa bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)001:10447: / don ni rgyud kun gyi thams cad kyi ni don brgyad du 'dus la /
NK109(dze)001:10448: de yang gong du rab tu gsal bar bshad do //
NK109(dze)001:10449: de dag bsdam pa las rgyud de dag gi ngo bo rnam par phye bas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10450: de dag kun gang zag gcig la 'tshogs pas 'khor
NK109(dze)001:10451: ba'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad dus gcig tu
NK109(dze)001:10452: sangs nas / 'bras bu stong pa'i ci'i ngo bor
NK109(dze)001:10453: yang ma yin par rgyas pas kun gyi rang bzhin
NK109(dze)001:10454: sems bzhin rtogs pa thob nas khams gsum las 'da'
NK109(dze)001:10456: de'i phyir gong du bstan pa de ltar tshig gi rgyud rnam par phye ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10457: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don gsum pa
NK109(dze)001:10458: tshig gi rgyud bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK109(dze)001:10459: drug tu byas nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:10460: da ni bsdus pa'i don bzhi pa rgyud gsum gyi
NK109(dze)001:10461: don spyir bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis
NK109(dze)001:10462: kyis bstan pa'i nang don dang po /
NK109(dze)001:10463: de dag gi don ji ltar yin pa zhu ba
NK109(dze)001:10464: sngon du 'gro bas gzhan don phun sum 'tshogs par
NK109(dze)001:10465: bstan pa ni / de ltar gsungs pa'i de nas sdud pa'o rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10467: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'khor rnams bstan pa gzhan
NK109(dze)001:10468: du ma bshad par rab tu gsang ba'i rgyud ni
NK109(dze)001:10469: dngos po'i gnas lugs la gzhi'i rgyud ces bstan pa
NK109(dze)001:10470: ste / de rgyud du cis 'gro na sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)001:10471: sems can tsam gyi rgyud de las skyes pas na
NK109(dze)001:10472: ste / rgyud yin no // de'i rtogs pas sangs rgyas kyi rgyud snyegs la /
NK109(dze)001:10473: de nyid la rtogs pas sems can gyis rgyud snyegs pas rgyud yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10474: rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni snying po rang bzhin gyi
NK109(dze)001:10475: rgyud rigs pas te rig pa'i chos nyid mngon gsum
NK109(dze)001:10476: du mthong pas 'das pa'i rgyud 'dzin pas rgyud yin
NK109(dze)001:10477: la / bla ma'i man ngag med cing ma mthong bas 'khor ba'i rgyud 'dzin pas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10478: me tog rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni /
NK109(dze)001:10479: sgron ma sus mthong pa chos nyid mngon sum gyi rigs pa yin pas na rgyud yin la /
NK109(dze)001:10480: de ma mthong ba las dang nyon mongs pa'i rigs yin pas rgyud yin la /
NK109(dze)001:10481: bcud rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni /
NK109(dze)001:10482: de nyid nyams su blangs ba las snying po bcud du dril ba zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)001:10483: ye shes lnga yi kha dog gi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10484: dbyibs kyi snang ba mthong bas khams gsum du mi 'jug pa'i rgyud yin pas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10485: thabs kyi rgyud la mtshon bya gzhi yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:10486: gzhi sems la ma brten pa'i sangs rgyas sems can gang yang med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10487: gnyis kyi rgyud 'dzin pas na rgyud la /
NK109(dze)001:10488: de mtshon pa tsam la brten nas khong du chod pa ni don yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:10489: don rtogs pa tsam gyis sangs rgya bas na /
NK109(dze)001:10490: sangs rgyas kyi rgyud yin pas rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10491: mtshon byed thabs kyi rgyud de /
NK109(dze)001:10492: mtshon byed bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas mngon du 'gyur te /
NK109(dze)001:10493: de mngon du gyur pa las sangs rgyas la yang med las /
NK109(dze)001:10494: de nyid rang rgyud pa la brten nas mngon gsum du mthong bas /
NK109(dze)001:10495: yang dag pa'i yon tan mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud yin pas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10496: de dag don gyi rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10497: don la rgyud med do zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:10498: don nyid rgyud yin pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10499: don las ma gtogs pa'i rgyud log pa rtsal du mi rnyed pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10501: rgyud du rtogs pas na de las gzhan med pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10502: de yang don chos nyid kyi rigs yin pas na rgyud do //
NK109(dze)001:10503: de ltar don gyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:10504: tshig gi rgyud rnam par phye nas bstan pas 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10505: 'jig rten pa'i 'khor de dag lus dga' ngag mgu sems rangs pa'i sems kyi bde ba skyes te /
NK109(dze)001:10506: lus ngag yid la bde ba khyad par can skyes pas rang la rang ngo mtshar ba skyes te /
NK109(dze)001:10507: 'di gang las byung na ston pa'i drin yin par mthong nas /
NK109(dze)001:10508: rdo rig pa rje ye shes rig pa dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pas 'chang pa /
NK109(dze)001:10511: lag na rdo rje tshig 'di skad shes rab kyis btags nas gsol ba btab bo //
NK109(dze)001:10512: kye ma zhes nges pa kho nas bos nas /
NK109(dze)001:10513: drug pa ni phyir 'gro ba rigs drug la gzigs nas /
NK109(dze)001:10514: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje tshad du phyin pa las /
NK109(dze)001:10515: thub pa drug gi skur sprul nas /
NK109(dze)001:10516: 'gro ba drug gis rtog pa gcod la /
NK109(dze)001:10517: nang du nyon mongs pa drug la gzigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:10518: mkhyen pa'i ye shes drug la longs spyod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10519: gsang ba yul la gzigs pas 'bras bu sku drug du smin pas na'o //
NK109(dze)001:10520: bla na med pa'i ting nge 'dzin drug la gzigs pas /
NK109(dze)001:10521: nang du chos nyid drug la dbang thob pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10522: des na drug pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10523: rdo rje dus thams cad du sems can gyi don las mi 'da' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:10524: 'chang ba ni thog ma sems bskyed pa'i dus na 'gro ba'i don bya'o bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10525: tshig dang don gyi rgyud rnams kyi rim pa de ltar lags na /
NK109(dze)001:10526: sdud pa po des gzhan don du gsol ba btab pa /
NK109(dze)001:10527: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'byung ba phra rags las sems rnam rtog tha dad pas bslad pas can /
NK109(dze)001:10528: dug gsum gyis gzir ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10530: yang na dbang po ma tshang zhing /
NK109(dze)001:10531: yan lag ma tshang pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10533: yang las bzang po bsags pa rnams kyang rung ste /
NK109(dze)001:10534: gang rung pa yang dag pa'i lta ba rgyud kun
NK109(dze)001:10535: gyi gnad hril gyis dril nas gdams pas gang zag
NK109(dze)001:10536: dad pa dang ldan pa gcig gis nyams su blangs
NK109(dze)001:10537: pas ye shes mngon sum du gyur pa'i rang gi
NK109(dze)001:10538: rig pa la / snying po thams cad gcig tu
NK109(dze)001:10539: dril nas ni bdag gis ma 'ongs pa'i 'gyu ba
NK109(dze)001:10540: tha dad pa'i sems can rnams la /
NK109(dze)001:10541: bsdus pa'i nyams su len pa de ji bstan par bgyi /
NK109(dze)001:10543: de nyid ston pa rdo rje 'chang gis skye 'gro'i
NK109(dze)001:10544: sems can thams cad bsgrol bar zhal gyis bzhes pas
NK109(dze)001:10545: na / bdag gis sems can gyi don mthar phyin
NK109(dze)001:10546: par bgyi bas thugs la 'khrul pa med par gsungs
NK109(dze)001:10547: shig ces zhu ba phul zhing gsol ba btab pa'o
NK109(dze)001:10548: na / // zhes bsdus pa'i don tha ma'i nang
NK109(dze)001:10549: don dang po de dag gis don ji ltar yin
NK109(dze)001:10550: pa zhu ba sngon du 'gro ba gzhan don phun
NK109(dze)001:10552: da ni yan lag gi don gnyis pa ston pas
NK109(dze)001:10553: lan du rgyud de dag gi tshig mtha' yas kyang
NK109(dze)001:10556: de nas ni gsol ba btab pa'i de nas ston
NK109(dze)001:10557: pa ni yon tan khyad par dang ldan pa la
NK109(dze)001:10558: dmigs pa'o // bka' ni bcos ma ma yin pa /
NK109(dze)001:10559: stsal pa ni sngon 'byung du sdud pa po'i rna ba'i dbang po la bstsal /
NK109(dze)001:10560: rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas slob ma'i rna ba'i dbang po la stsal /
NK109(dze)001:10561: stsal lugs ji ltar stsal na /
NK109(dze)001:10562: 'o ma las ni mar lta bur bsdu ba la dgongs pa nas bka' stsal te /
NK109(dze)001:10563: tshig rgyud bcu bdun tsam du bsdus na 'di ltar yin zhes bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10564: tshig gi brjod bya ji ltar brjod /
NK109(dze)001:10567: rim gyis dril nas bstan na /
NK109(dze)001:10568: tshig gi spros pa kun bsgrangs pa tsam du zad
NK109(dze)001:10569: mod kyang ni 'di ltar blo'i tshu rol gyi rtog
NK109(dze)001:10571: bcos ma blo'i rtog pa yin pa las ma rtogs pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10572: rgyud bcu bdun po'i mdo ni ngag don dril nas bstan na /
NK109(dze)001:10573: zab mo 'dus pa ni tshig don bcu gcig tu don thams cad bsdu ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10574: 'dir tshig don bcu gcig bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:10575: thog ma rtogs te sangs rgyas ma byung ma rtogs
NK109(dze)001:10576: sems can ma byung ba'i sngon rol na gzhi ji
NK109(dze)001:10577: ltar gnas pa'i tshig don dang po ni /
NK109(dze)001:10578: gnas pa gzhi yin la lugs bdun te /
NK109(dze)001:10582: nges pa don gyi dngos gzhi bar 'dod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10583: cir yang bsgyur du btub par 'dod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10584: cir yang khas blang du btub pa 'dod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10585: gzhi sna tshogs khra bor 'dod pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10586: 'di la gang zag rnam pa gnyis kyi dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)001:10587: grub pa'i mtha' rjes su 'dzin pa'i gang zag dang /
NK109(dze)001:10588: lam rjes su 'dzin pa dang gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:10590: drug po skyon can yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:10591: skyon can ngos bzung ba dang gcig po skyon med
NK109(dze)001:10592: yin pas skyon med gtan la dbab pa gnyis las
NK109(dze)001:10593: / de yang skyon can phyogs gcig tu bzhag nas dor ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:10594: lhun grub skyon can yin pas gzhi mi btub pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10595: rgyu lhun gyis grub par 'dod na ni gzhi mi btub ste /
NK109(dze)001:10596: gzhi la rgyu'i ming gis btags pas brjod bya nyams la /
NK109(dze)001:10597: gal te grub par 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10598: rgyu de la 'bras bu grub bam ma grub /
NK109(dze)001:10599: grub na ni 'bras bu ldog pa dang bcas pa'i skyon spang bar mi nus /
NK109(dze)001:10600: res rgyu yin la de las 'bras bu yang grub la /
NK109(dze)001:10601: 'bras bu las rgyu grub pas na thug med kyi skyon dang /
NK109(dze)001:10602: yang na rgyu 'bras gcig pa'i skyon spang bar mi nus so //
NK109(dze)001:10603: gcig par 'dod na ni las rgyu 'bras kyi brjod bya nyams so //
NK109(dze)001:10604: gal te tha dad par 'dod na ni rgyu lhun grub kyi 'dod pa nyams so //
NK109(dze)001:10605: gal te 'bras bu la rgyu grub par 'dod na ni /
NK109(dze)001:10606: 'bras bu rgyur thal ba mi khegs so //
NK109(dze)001:10607: des na 'bras bu dang rgyur btags pa la nges
NK109(dze)001:10608: pa med pas na rgyu 'bras kyi 'brel ba brtags
NK109(dze)001:10611: 'bras bu las rgyu bskyed pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:10612: yang na thams cad nas thams cad du lhun grub tu 'dod na /
NK109(dze)001:10613: mi 'dod pa dgag tu mi btub pas rang 'dod
NK109(dze)001:10614: pa'i don mi 'grub pas lhun grub la dgos pa
NK109(dze)001:10617: mi mthun pa'i phyogs mi 'grub pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10619: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'dod pa nyams so //
NK109(dze)001:10620: gal te gnyis med du lhun gyis grub bo zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:10621: rgyu dang 'bras bu la sogs pa gnyis su med
NK109(dze)001:10622: na ni yang lhun grub kyi 'dod pa nyams shing
NK109(dze)001:10624: de yang rgyu lhun gyis grub pa'i dus na 'bras
NK109(dze)001:10625: bu med pa la sogs pa'i rigs pas gnod de
NK109(dze)001:10626: / de la sogs pa'i rigs pas spros na mngas te 'dir ma spros so //
NK109(dze)001:10627: des na lhun grub skyon can du ngos bzung bas dor bya /
NK109(dze)001:10628: 'di la thugs rje'i cha nas kun khyab tu 'dod pas /
NK109(dze)001:10629: lhun grub tu khas blangs mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)001:10630: nges med du 'dod pas yang skyon can te /
NK109(dze)001:10631: ming la nges pa med pa yin tsam na /
NK109(dze)001:10632: ming tha dad pas nges pa yod med kyi rtsis med /
NK109(dze)001:10633: ming yang dag par ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:10634: don la nges par med na ni /
NK109(dze)001:10635: don 'gyur ba'i ngos nas med dam /
NK109(dze)001:10636: mi 'gyur kyang med 'gyur ba don ma btub /
NK109(dze)001:10637: mi 'gyur na nges pa med pa mi btub bo //
NK109(dze)001:10638: de bzhin yod pas nges pa med na /
NK109(dze)001:10639: mngon sum la bsnyon du mi btub /
NK109(dze)001:10640: med pas nges pa med na /
NK109(dze)001:10641: med pa la nges pa yod med kyi brtag pa mi rnyed /
NK109(dze)001:10642: de bzhin du snang stong kun la basgre'o //
NK109(dze)001:10643: des na nges med skyon can yin pas dor bya /
NK109(dze)001:10644: 'di ni thugs rje'i cha nas sna tshogs su shar
NK109(dze)001:10645: bas nges pa med pa'i don brtag mi dgos la
NK109(dze)001:10646: / nges pa don gyi dngos gzhi pa yang skyon can te /
NK109(dze)001:10647: ming la nges pa yod na /
NK109(dze)001:10648: ming la nges par med par tshig yin pas /
NK109(dze)001:10649: gdags bya ming tsam du yang ma grub la 'dogs byed tshig tsam du yang ma grub pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10651: don la nges par brtag pa yod dam /
NK109(dze)001:10653: phyi rol rtag par smra ba dang khyad med la /
NK109(dze)001:10654: mi rtag pa yod pa'i sgra mi 'jug pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10655: de rtag pas 'khor bar 'khor bar yod par nges pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10657: sems can gyis 'bad pa la dgongs pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:10658: des na nges pa skyon can yin par dor bya /
NK109(dze)001:10659: 'di ni ka nas dag pas yod med rtag chad gang du yang mi 'dod pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10660: cir yang khas blang du btub pa yang skyo na can yin te /
NK109(dze)001:10661: de yang yod par khas len na ni /
NK109(dze)001:10662: yod pa la med pas khyab bam ma khyab /
NK109(dze)001:10663: khyab na ni yod pa mi btub la /
NK109(dze)001:10664: ma khyab na ni ltos rigs mi khegs te /
NK109(dze)001:10665: yod pa la ltos pas med pas te /
NK109(dze)001:10666: de bzhin du snang shes kun la bsgres pas chog go /
NK109(dze)001:10667: med par khas len na yang snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)001:10668: yang na med pa la khas len yod mi srid do //
NK109(dze)001:10669: dper na cir yang khas blang du btub pa yang skyon can yin pas dor bya /
NK109(dze)001:10670: 'dir ni cir yang khas blangs mi dgos te /
NK109(dze)001:10671: rang bzhin las kun 'byung bas rtag gzhi gang du yang mi 'cha' 'o //
NK109(dze)001:10672: gzhi cir yang bsgyur du btub pa yang skyon can yin te /
NK109(dze)001:10673: yod pa las med par bsgyur du btub na ni mngon gsum du gsal la /
NK109(dze)001:10674: de bzhin du rgyu las 'bras bu bsgyur du mi btub la /
NK109(dze)001:10675: 'bras bu las rgyur bsgyur du btub pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10676: de bzhin du snang stong rtag chad thams cad la'o //
NK109(dze)001:10677: des na 'di yang skyon can yin pas dor bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10678: 'di ni thugs rje phyogs med du shar bas gang yang dgag tu ma btub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10679: gzhi sna tshogs su 'dod pa yang skyon can te /
NK109(dze)001:10680: dkar por snang ba'i dus na yang ser po la sogs pas khyab bam ma khyab /
NK109(dze)001:10681: khyab na ni dkar po zhes pa'i tshig gi nyams la /
NK109(dze)001:10682: ma khyab na ni sna tshogs kyi 'dod pa nyams so //
NK109(dze)001:10683: yang na dkar po yang yin la ser po yang yin zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:10684: dkar por snang ba'i dus na ser po ma grub la /
NK109(dze)001:10685: ser por snang ba'i dus na dkar po ma grub pas so //
