NK109(dze)001:10686: sna tshogs dus gcig la snang na ni gzhi tha dad du 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:10687: de yang mig gi rnam par shes pa la sngon por snang ba'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:10688: dkar po la sogs pa snang mi srid pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10689: yang sngon po dang dkar po gnyis phan tshun 'gal bas te /
NK109(dze)001:10690: de ltar yang tsha reg dang grang reg gnyis lhan gcig tu mi gnas pa bzhin no //
NK109(dze)001:10691: des na sna tshogs pa yang skyon can yin pas dpang bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10692: 'di ni rang bzhin la bcos ma med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10693: sna tshogs su shar yang ngo bo ka nas dag pas so //
NK109(dze)001:10694: de ltar yang bsam gyis mi khyab kyang drug po de skyon can yin pas gzhi mi btub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10695: 'di ni ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i ye shes su shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:10696: gzhi la 'khrul bya ba tsam du yang ma grub pas ka dag la /
NK109(dze)001:10697: ma 'khrul zhes bya ba yang ma grub pas na kun khyab bo //
NK109(dze)001:10698: don gyis khas len gang yang med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10699: rang bzhin kun snang gi ye shes su bzhugs pa las /
NK109(dze)001:10700: 'khrul pa zhes tha snyad du brtags kyang 'gal ba med /
NK109(dze)001:10701: ma 'khrul zhes btags kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:10702: de'i phyir na 'khrul gzhi la med pas tha snyad brtags pas stong pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10703: 'khrul pa gzhi la ma grub pas /
NK109(dze)001:10704: 'khrul ma 'khrul gang du yang mi gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10705: thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes kyi rnam pa gsum ni /
NK109(dze)001:10706: thugs rje phyogs med du shar bas yod med rtag
NK109(dze)001:10707: chad gang la brten med cing phyogs med du shar
NK109(dze)001:10708: ba'o // de yang ngo bo ka dag gi cha nas thog ma 'khrul ma myong pas /
NK109(dze)001:10709: sangs rgyas sems can gyi ming med da lta 'khrul pa la mi gnas /
NK109(dze)001:10710: rig pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas /
NK109(dze)001:10711: phyis 'khrul mi srid pas gzhi zhes kyang 'khrul pa med do //
NK109(dze)001:10712: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi cha nas sna tshogs dgag tu ma btub pas /
NK109(dze)001:10713: ji ltar snang yang mi stong /
NK109(dze)001:10714: ngo bo la gos pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)001:10715: thugs rje kun la khyab pa'i cha nas /
NK109(dze)001:10717: 'khor ji ltar shar yang de nyid de nyid kyis grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10718: de yang tha snyad kyi dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)001:10719: sku gsum du snang la gang du yang gtan la dbab tu btub pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10720: de yang snang ba sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK109(dze)001:10722: min gang yang ma yin yang /
NK109(dze)001:10723: shar thams cad du shar la /
NK109(dze)001:10726: grol ba de yang rang thog tu grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:10727: gnas pa las gzhan du 'gyur ba med do //
NK109(dze)001:10728: de ka la ming du btags na /
NK109(dze)001:10731: de nyid gang du 'gro ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:10732: de ltar gnas pas shar la /
NK109(dze)001:10735: stong pa de ngos bzung las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)001:10737: dus thams cad la rgya ma chad pa /
NK109(dze)001:10739: rtag par bzhugs pa'i ye shes so //
NK109(dze)001:10740: gnas lugs ni gsum las mi 'da' bar ka dag gi yi ge nas bstan pa yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10741: 'khrul zhes sna tshogs 'khrul pa yod pa la smos te /
NK109(dze)001:10742: de las khyad kyang gzhi rnam gnyis te /
NK109(dze)001:10746: bkra shis mdzes ldan nas bcu gnyis su bshad de
NK109(dze)001:10747: ma sa rtsa ba dang yan lag tu bcas pa
NK109(dze)001:10748: las 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas 'khrul ba'i gzhi
NK109(dze)001:10750: 'du byed rtsa ba dang yan lag du bcas pa'i
NK109(dze)001:10751: 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas 'khrul pa'i las gtan
NK109(dze)001:10753: rnam par shes pa ming gis rnam grangs las 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10754: rnam grangs du ma brtsi ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10755: ming 'jug pa sna tshogs pa las 'khrul pa'i lugs
NK109(dze)001:10756: la brten nas 'khrul pa'i rgyu gtan la dbab pa
NK109(dze)001:10757: dang / gzugs rdul dang rdul phran las 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10758: 'khrul pa'i dus gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10759: skye mched drug grangs nges pa la brten nas las 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10760: 'khrul pa'i 'bras bu gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10761: reg pa myong bas 'khor ba'i 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10762: 'khrul ba'i rtags gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10763: tshor ba rten sna tshogs pa las 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10764: 'khrul pa'i tshad gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10765: srid pa 'jug pa tha dad pa la brten nas 'khrul pa'i las so sor brtag pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10766: len pa gnyis 'dus pas 'khrul pa'i lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10767: lus sems bzlog pa'i 'khrul pa gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10768: srid pa chags pa rgyu'i 'khrul lugs la brten nas
NK109(dze)001:10769: phyi nang gi 'khrul pa'i nges pa khyad par gyi
NK109(dze)001:10771: skye ba 'gyu ba las kyi 'khrul lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10772: smin so tha dad pa'i 'khrul lugs gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10773: rga shi mtha' sna tshogs pa'i 'khrul lugs la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10774: 'khrul pa'i rkyen dang 'bras bu gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10775: de yang ming gzugs su grub pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10777: ming rdul dang rdul phran las zhugs pas na gzugs su grub pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10778: de gnyis gcig tu brtsis pas na /
NK109(dze)001:10779: 'khrul pa'i lugs bcu gnyis kyi 'khor lo gtan la dbab pas ni /
NK109(dze)001:10780: 'gro ba'i smin so lo bcu gnyis su byung la /
NK109(dze)001:10781: gnas pa'i dus na 'gro ba gcig gi lus la
NK109(dze)001:10782: yang 'byung ba'i byer zug snyoms pa'i las bcu gnyis
NK109(dze)001:10783: su gnas pa'o // de ltar 'khrul pa'i rtags su /
NK109(dze)001:10784: phyi rol zla ba bcu gnyis kyis lo gcig tu rtsi ba byung ste /
NK109(dze)001:10785: de ltar 'khrul gzhi gsal ba'i me long la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10786: 'khrul ba'i brtsis ma nor bar ded pas /
NK109(dze)001:10788: bzlog pa dang 'khrul lugs la sogs pa nges pa la phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10789: de yang theg pa thun mong pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10791: lus gcig la tha ma rga shi la thug par 'dod de /
NK109(dze)001:10793: 'di dag tha dad pa ste rga shi nyer bstan
NK109(dze)001:10794: gyi dbang du brtsi ba rang la yang lugs mi
NK109(dze)001:10795: mthun pa lnga u rgyan gyi yul na yod do
NK109(dze)001:10796: // 'khrul lugs tha dad pa'i phyir na 'gro ba'i lus kyang tha dad par byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10797: nang yang rtog pa tha dad par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10798: 'di dag ni bkra shis mdzes ldan gyi skabs nas rgyas par ston no //
NK109(dze)001:10799: shin tu zhib par 'khrul gzhi gsal ba'i me long nas bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:10800: de ltar rnam pa mang bar bshad kyang de dag re re la gnyis gnyis su 'dus te /
NK109(dze)001:10801: rga shi lhun gyis grub pa'i dus na ni /
NK109(dze)001:10802: 'khrul pa gnas pa'i dus brtsi ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:10803: 'gyu ba las kyi rtog pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10804: ye shes kyi tshad rnams gtan la phebs so //
NK109(dze)001:10805: rga shi thugs rje'i dus na lus dang las kyi bye brag dang /
NK109(dze)001:10806: dbang po la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10807: 'khrul pa bzlog pa'i mtshan nyid gtan la phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10808: de ltar gnyis gnyis su rtsis pas don gyis 'khrul pa'i 'khor lo nyer bzhis bskor bas /
NK109(dze)001:10809: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad gtan la phebs par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:10810: des na 'khrul gzhi rtsis la thug pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10811: de'i gnad ni lhun grub kyi dus na gzhi dang zhes khyab pa gtan la dbab /
NK109(dze)001:10812: thugs rje'i dus na gzhi shes kyi khyad par gtan la phab pas /
NK109(dze)001:10813: 'khor ba smin pa'i rgyu rkyen thams cad nges par gtan la phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10814: de ltar gnyis kyi bye brag las lus su smin
NK109(dze)001:10815: pa'i dus na rtags nges par gtan la phebs pa
NK109(dze)001:10816: ste / 'dis ni yid ches par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10817: de ltar 'khrul nas rang gi lus la gnas pa'i gazhi'am sa bon ni /
NK109(dze)001:10824: lnga tshan du gnas pa ni 'khrul lugs re re na gnyis gnyis te gnyis po la rgyu dang /
NK109(dze)001:10826: bye brag pa'i las dang lnga lngar byung ba las /
NK109(dze)001:10827: 'dir 'khrul zin nas kyang lnga tshan du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10828: de ltar lnga tshan du byung bas phung po lnga
NK109(dze)001:10829: la sogs pa lus la yang lnga tshan du byung
NK109(dze)001:10830: ba'o // de dag gi don rtags gzhan nas zhi ba bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:10831: de ltar gnas pa de'i gnas pa rang gang na
NK109(dze)001:10832: gnas pa ngos bzung pa'i tshig don bzhi pa ni
NK109(dze)001:10833: / gzhi'i de gnas pa lus kyi dkyil rtsa thams cad 'dus pa'i gnas na /
NK109(dze)001:10834: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rnam par dag pa'i ye shes bzhugs pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10835: brtsi zhes 'khrul ba rtsis kyi yan lag las byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)001:10836: snying po rin po che'i rtsa bzhi la /
NK109(dze)001:10837: 'byung ba gnyis gnyis pa'i rtsa bzhi ste brgyad /
NK109(dze)001:10838: 'byung ba'i byed pa gsum brtsis pa'i rtsa bzhi ste
NK109(dze)001:10839: bcu gnyis 'khor los bskor ba ni 'khrul pa'i 'khor
NK109(dze)001:10840: lo bcu gnyis kyi gnad do //
NK109(dze)001:10841: 'di la ngo bo skur gnas pas sku gsum 'di nyid du gtan la phebs la /
NK109(dze)001:10842: rang bzhin thig ler gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:10843: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma dngos su 'char ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10844: thugs rje 'od du gnas pas snang ba'i dus na dngos su snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10845: de ltar gnas pa lus la brten nas sangs rgya ba'i dgongs pa yod do //
NK109(dze)001:10846: de'i dkyil na gnas pas na gnas zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10847: de lam gang nas byung pa'i tshig don lnga pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10848: dang po lus ma'i mngal du chags pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)001:10849: bskyed byed du 'byung ba bzhi'i rtsa re re chags pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10850: shar du chu'i rtsa chags pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:10851: zug pa'i 'byung ba'i bsdeb bu byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10852: lhor sa'i las byed pa'i las /
NK109(dze)001:10853: nub tu me'i rtsa las snyoms pa'i las byang du
NK109(dze)001:10854: rlung gi rtsa las 'khrul pa'i lus su smin pa'i
NK109(dze)001:10856: 'khrul pa'i rgyu zug pas byas rkyen byer las /
NK109(dze)001:10858: tha dad pa'i las 'khrugs pas byas so //
NK109(dze)001:10859: de yang 'byung ba me'i rgyu las kun rdzob kyi rgyu /
NK109(dze)001:10861: de las kun rdzob las lus bskyed la /
NK109(dze)001:10862: don dam las ye shes bskyed do //
NK109(dze)001:10863: de'i smin so kun rdzob kyis lus kyi phung po dang khams dang /
NK109(dze)001:10865: dbang po la sogs pa rnams su byas so //
NK109(dze)001:10866: don dam las sgron ma bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)001:10867: ye shes kyi kha dog dang /
NK109(dze)001:10868: dbyibs la sogs pa rnams su byas so //
NK109(dze)001:10869: de bzhin las bskyed byed dus 'dus pas sra ba
NK109(dze)001:10870: sha'i byed par byas dran par chu 'dus pas gsher
NK109(dze)001:10872: mgrin pa ste ro rnams su me'i 'byung ba 'dus pas mched pa drod kyi las byas /
NK109(dze)001:10873: rtsa mang du rlung gi 'byung ba 'dus pas yang dbugs kyi las byas /
NK109(dze)001:10874: de dag gi dbus na yar rtsa gsum ka ba'i tshul du drang por yod do //
NK109(dze)001:10875: g.yas nas kun rdzob kyi thig ler 'gyu la /
NK109(dze)001:10876: g.yon na rang bzhin gyi dbus nas don dam pa'i thig ler 'gyu ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10877: de yang lam na rtsa ste lus kyi 'byung ba 'dus pa khyad par gyi las so //
NK109(dze)001:10878: gzhi zhes 'dir 'byung ba bzhi la dgongs pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:10879: yang na dang po'i chags pa las brtsis la /
NK109(dze)001:10880: de yang gong ma'i rtsa'i ngo bo yin la 'di ni dpe yin te /
NK109(dze)001:10881: ka ti gser lta bu las sa'i bdag nyid /
NK109(dze)001:10882: bu gu shel lta bu las chu'i bdag nyid /
NK109(dze)001:10883: 'phra 'khril dar dkar gyi snal ma lta bu las me'i bdag nyid /
NK109(dze)001:10884: dbang po yul las 'char bar byed pa ba men
NK109(dze)001:10885: gyi rwa lta bu las rlung gi bdag nyid do
NK109(dze)001:10886: // yang rtsa'i ngo bo gsum nas /
NK109(dze)001:10887: g.yas pa nas bzung ba las kyi rlung gi 'byung ba dang bcas 'gyu la /
NK109(dze)001:10888: g.yon pa nas 'dzin pa las kyi rlung dang bcas nas 'gyu ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10889: dbus rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rlung bzung ba dang /
NK109(dze)001:10890: 'dzin pa ma yin pa'i 'gyu byed rang dag pa'i rlung ni /
NK109(dze)001:10891: rnam par rtog pa gang gis kyang ma phye bas /
NK109(dze)001:10892: rtog 'dzin matha'i dri ma kun zad par 'gyur bas /
NK109(dze)001:10894: da ni drug pa sgo gang las 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:10895: de yang 'byung ba bzhi'i dwangs ma 'dus pa las /
NK109(dze)001:10896: 'byung ba khyad par gyi smin pa'i sa 'char bar
NK109(dze)001:10897: byed pa'i sgo ni 'dir sgron ma bzhi la dgongs
NK109(dze)001:10898: pa ste / de ltar bzhi zhes pa ni smin so'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:10899: mig gnyis su ye shes kyi ngo bo smin la /
NK109(dze)001:10900: rna ba gnyis la ye shes kyi rlung smin la /
NK109(dze)001:10901: spyi bo'i gtsug tu rig pa nyid smin pa la dgongs pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:10902: de dag gi rtags su mig nas thig le stong pa'i sgron ma dngos su 'char la /
NK109(dze)001:10903: de yang lag pa'i mtheb mdzub kyis rtsa bltems pa las 'char ro //
NK109(dze)001:10904: rna ba gnyis kyi mdun gyi gzhong bu na /
NK109(dze)001:10905: gser ldan gyi rtsa yod de /
NK109(dze)001:10906: de bltems pas rlung gi sgra 'ong ngo //
NK109(dze)001:10907: spyi bor na shar na rgya mtsho'i steng ga yod pa la /
NK109(dze)001:10908: nub na brtsig pa la sogs pa'i gtad yod pa'i bar du /
NK109(dze)001:10909: nyi ma shar ma thag tu 'dug ste /
NK109(dze)001:10910: rang kha nub tu bltas te /
NK109(dze)001:10911: de nyid las ma yengs par bltas pas /
NK109(dze)001:10912: spyi bo nas barlangasa pa sngo dmar du 'ong ba mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)001:10913: 'di ni mig gnyis nas thig le stong pa'i sgron ma dang /
NK109(dze)001:10914: dbyings rnam par dag pa gnyis su 'char la /
NK109(dze)001:10915: sna nas shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma 'char la /
NK109(dze)001:10916: mig dngos rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10917: da ni bdun pa sgo las shar ba'i rig pa de yul gang la snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:10918: de yang nam rig pa dngos la mkha' dbyings rkyen sprin pa dang na bun dang /
NK109(dze)001:10919: char la sogs pa dang bral ba sngo sang nge 'dug pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10920: rig pa 'char ba'i yul yin no //
NK109(dze)001:10921: de yang yul der chos nyid thams cad 'du ba rlung /
NK109(dze)001:10922: de nyid du 'dus pa rig pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:10923: brgyad pa nyams su ji ltar blang pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10924: dmigs pa yul can gyi blo can dang /
NK109(dze)001:10925: rig pa rang snang gi blo can gnyis las /
NK109(dze)001:10926: 'dir ni rig pa rang snang gi blo can gyi nyams su blangs pa ste 'di la'ang gnyis la /
NK109(dze)001:10927: khregs chod du nyams su blangs pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10928: thod rgal du nyams su blang pa la /
NK109(dze)001:10929: de la khregs chod du nyams su blang pa ni 'di nyid la snang ba dang ma 'dres par /
NK109(dze)001:10930: gcig char du man ngag bstan pa tsam gyis grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10931: dper na skyes bu'i snying la mdas zin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)001:10932: thod rgal nyams su blang pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10933: sngon du 'gro ba sna sel bar byed pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)001:10934: dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes rang gi rgyud la ji ltar bstan pa gnyis so //
NK109(dze)001:10935: 'di dag ni gong du bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:10936: dgu pa nyams su long pa'i tshad ni dmyal ba
NK109(dze)001:10937: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal yang zhing bag tsha ba
NK109(dze)001:10939: sangs rgyas la brod pa bskyed pa med pa'i ngang /
NK109(dze)001:10940: 'khor bar ltung gis dogs pa'i sdug bsngal med pa dang /
NK109(dze)001:10941: mya ngan las 'das pa la re ba med pa'i gding bzhi'i steng /
NK109(dze)001:10942: rig pa nyid ye sangs rgyas pa'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:10943: de nyid bde ba chen por grol ba'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:10944: 'khor ba nyid 'das pa yin pa'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:10945: 'das pa zhes shes bya la ma grub pa'i gnad dang /
NK109(dze)001:10946: bzhi gdeng rnyed pas chos nyid rnams su phebs pas /
NK109(dze)001:10947: chos dang sems can du 'byor pas nyid ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10948: bcu pa bar ma do la ji ltar 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)001:10949: gzhan ma yin te 'dir ni chos nyid kyi bar do la smos pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:10950: chos nyid ma'i snang ba la rig pa bu yi snang ba shar bas /
NK109(dze)001:10951: 'gyu ba phra rags kyi gdos pa med pas /
NK109(dze)001:10952: 'od dang 'od khyim du shar ba la rang snang
NK109(dze)001:10953: du ngo shes pas grol ba la sogs pa gzhan
NK109(dze)001:10954: nas rgyas par bshad nas yod do //
NK109(dze)001:10955: de ltar gnyis rig pa dang chos nyid sbyor ba'i sa ni //
NK109(dze)001:10956: de nyid rang bzhin du gnas pa las chos nyid du 'gyur ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10957: de nyid du gdeng rnyed pa'i dus na rjes su dran pa drug dang /
NK109(dze)001:10958: rang bzhin gyi bsam gtan dang /
NK109(dze)001:10960: mngon par shes pa drug phrag drug la sogs pa'i
NK109(dze)001:10961: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan dpag tu med pa thob
NK109(dze)001:10963: 'di dag gtan pa thob pa nyid las so //
NK109(dze)001:10964: rgyas par nyi zla kha sbyor gyi skabs su bstan par bya'o //
NK109(dze)001:10965: bcu gcig pa grol sa gang yin pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)001:10966: de ka nas dag pa'i chos nyid ngo bo rang
NK109(dze)001:10967: bzhin thugs rje gsum ma phyed mi 'byed mi g.yo
NK109(dze)001:10971: de yang thog ma'i gzhi blo'i rtags dpyod kyi yul ma yin pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)001:10972: de yang nam mkha' la nam mkha' thim pa lta bur mnyam pa ris med la /
NK109(dze)001:10973: ngo bo phyogs bral du sangs rgyas so //
NK109(dze)001:10974: de dag gis ni rgyud kun bsdams pa la yan lag gi don gnyis su byas nas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:10975: mu ni yod pa'i mu chos nyid stong par grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10976: med pa'i mu rang byung 'od gsal du grol /
NK109(dze)001:10977: gnyis ka'i mu stong gsal dbyer med du grol /
NK109(dze)001:10978: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i rang bzhin rnam dag tu grol /
NK109(dze)001:10979: rtag pa'i mu gang dang yang 'brel ba med pas grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10980: chad pa'i mu rgyu med pas grol ba gnyis ka'i mu rgyu 'bras rjes med pas grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:10981: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu mtha' gang du yang mi rtog pas grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:10982: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i rang bzhin /
NK109(dze)001:10983: snang ba'i mu dmigs pa rang dag pas grol la
NK109(dze)001:10984: stong pa'i mu sku gsum lam du snang bas grol
NK109(dze)001:10985: la / gnyis ka'i mu snang stong dbyer med pas grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10986: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu rgyu rkyen ltos zad pas grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:10987: shes pa'i mu gnas lugs la brjod du med pas grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10988: mi shes pa'i mu rig pa rang shar bas grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10989: gnyis ka'i mu gnas lugs la tshig med pas grol la /
NK109(dze)001:10990: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu shes bya la mtha' med pas grol lo //
NK109(dze)001:10991: de ltar snang shes kun la bsgres pas grol bas na /
NK109(dze)001:10992: rgyud 'di la brten nas 'gro ba rnams nges par grol bar byung pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:10993: de dag las grol ba'i rig de gang zhe na /
NK109(dze)001:10994: chos nyid mngon sum du mthong bas 'khrul pa rang
NK109(dze)001:10995: rgyud du 'dzin pa tig la phab pas yid dpyod
NK109(dze)001:10997: rnam par rtog pa skye ba'i rgyun 'gags pas ye
NK109(dze)001:10998: shes rang sa na gsal ba'i ting cir snang 'od
NK109(dze)001:10999: du shar bas / 'byung ba bzhi'i dngos por lta ba sel lo //
NK109(dze)001:11000: de yang 'khrul pa tig la phab pas 'khrul med rang dag /
NK109(dze)001:11001: nyon mongs tig la phab pas ye shes su rang shar ba la sogs pa'o /
NK109(dze)001:11003: dang po dbang gi khrid la brten nas /
NK109(dze)001:11004: gzhi ma smin pa smin par byas pas snod sbyangs pa'i 'phreng ba'o //
NK109(dze)001:11005: de nas man ngag sngon 'gro dang /
NK109(dze)001:11006: dngos gzhi gnyis kyi khrid la brten nas smin pa
NK109(dze)001:11007: de rang grol ba'i 'phreng bas khams gsum las grol
NK109(dze)001:11008: ba'o // rgyud ni de 'das pa'i sangs rgyas dang rgyud ma chad pas /
NK109(dze)001:11009: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dngos su ston pa la /
NK109(dze)001:11010: da lta'i 'bu tha'i rgyud la gnas pas /
NK109(dze)001:11011: nyams su blang pas da lta dngos su snang la /
NK109(dze)001:11012: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas su rgyud dag pas /
NK109(dze)001:11013: dgongs pa dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:11014: rgyud ni gong du bstan pa'i gzhi /
NK109(dze)001:11015: rang bzhin thabs kyi rgyud thams cad gcig tu bsdoms te bstan pa la bsdus pa'i don bzhi la /
NK109(dze)001:11016: yan lag gi don nyi shu le'u dum bu nges pa'i don //
NK109(dze)001:11017: brgyad pa grangs nges par byas nas bstan no //
NK109(dze)001:11018: brgyad ni de las mang na 'chol bar 'gro ba /
NK109(dze)001:11019: nyung na dgongs pa'i don ma tshang pas brgyad kho nar nges so //
NK109(dze)001:11021: dang po ma gleng na gzhi med pas gleng gzhi bstan la /
NK109(dze)001:11022: gnyis pa 'khrul pa gzhi la ldog pa'i le'u ma bstan na /
NK109(dze)001:11023: gleng ba la gegs med pas gnyis pa 'khrul pa gzhi la ldog par byung /
NK109(dze)001:11024: de ltar ldog kyang de'i gnad 'khrul pa das su brdas na mi grol bas /
NK109(dze)001:11025: gsum pa 'khrul pa das su brda' bar byung la /
NK109(dze)001:11026: de ltar 'khrul pa das su brdas pas las 'gro
NK109(dze)001:11027: ba rnams 'bad pa med par grol bas na bzhi
NK109(dze)001:11028: pa'o // de ltar 'bad pa med pa'i phyir gnas
NK109(dze)001:11029: lugs la 'khrul pa rang rdzogs su bstan pas lnga
NK109(dze)001:11030: pa'o // pa'o // de ltar gnas lugs la 'khrul
NK109(dze)001:11031: pa rang rdzogs pa de nyid sems can gyi snang
NK109(dze)001:11032: thabs yin par bstan pas na drug pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:11033: de ltar sems can gyi snang thabs de nyid 'khor
NK109(dze)001:11034: 'das kyi chos thams cad rang la rdzogs pas na
NK109(dze)001:11035: bdun pa'o // de ltar rdzogs pas rang gi rgyud
NK109(dze)001:11036: sangs rgya bas na rgyud thams cad rang rgyud du
NK109(dze)001:11037: bsdoms nas bstan par nges so //
NK109(dze)001:11038: de skad du rang gi rig pa dang rang shes
NK109(dze)001:11039: rig gi rgyal pos bka' bsdu ba'i don du stsal
NK109(dze)001:11040: pa dang / rang gi ngo bo'i 'khor rig pa ni rang las byung zhing /
NK109(dze)001:11041: rnon po ni shes rab khyad par can gyi rtogs pa ste /
NK109(dze)001:11042: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)001:11043: rig pa rang snang la sogs pa ni lnga dang /
NK109(dze)001:11044: dkar po la sogs pa nang snang ba'i 'khor dang /
NK109(dze)001:11045: phyi yul gyi 'khor rdo rje'i rigs la sogs pa rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang /
NK109(dze)001:11046: lag na rdo rje la sogs pa ste rigs gsum gyi khro bo dang /
NK109(dze)001:11047: dkon mchog rang bzhin gyi 'khor sangs rgyas chos sku dang /
NK109(dze)001:11054: byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bo /
NK109(dze)001:11055: 'jig rten pa'i 'khor sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la dga' ba'i lha dang /
NK109(dze)001:11056: lha ma yin gyi rgyal po thags bzang ris dang /
NK109(dze)001:11057: shes rab kyi 'khor mkha' 'gro ma brtse ba'i blo
NK109(dze)001:11058: gros la sogs pa dpag tu med pa rnams dang
NK109(dze)001:11059: / dri za'i rgyal po zur phud lnga pa dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten dang 'das pa'i 'khor rnams /
NK109(dze)001:11060: de skad gsungs pa'i rjes su yid rangs te /
NK109(dze)001:11061: bcom ldan 'das kyi gsungs pa la mgrin gcig tu mngon par bstod nas /
NK109(dze)001:11062: 'khor de dag gis kyang chos nyid mngon sum gyi
NK109(dze)001:11063: snang ba mthong nas rdzogs pa chen po'i chos nyid
NK109(dze)001:11065: mu tig phreng ba la sogs pa'i mtshan gyi skabs su bstan to //
NK109(dze)001:11066: rang bzhin ni khyad par 'phags pa chen po yid rtsol las 'das pa'i don /
NK109(dze)001:11067: rang la rdzogs pas gzhan nas brtsal mi dgos /
NK109(dze)001:11068: gzhan rang la rdzogs pas spang blang med do //
NK109(dze)001:11069: chen po ni de'i gong na gzhan med pas /
NK109(dze)001:11070: lta bas khyad par du 'phags pas mtha' bral yongs rdzogs bsgoms pa 'dod yon lam khyer /
NK109(dze)001:11071: spyod pa snang shes zung 'jug gis ni khyad par 'phags pa chen po yin la /
NK109(dze)001:11072: rgyud ni ming du thogs pa'i rgyud khri phrag phyed dag gnyis /
NK109(dze)001:11073: shwa lo ka ni 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi
NK109(dze)001:11074: mu tig phreng ba'i rgyud 'di la le'u brgyad du
NK109(dze)001:11075: bkod nas khyad par de dag gi nang nas byung
NK109(dze)001:11076: ba'o // rdzogs sdom ni lhag pa dang chad pa med cing /
NK109(dze)001:11077: dgongs pa'i don gzhan kha rags ma lus par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)001:11078: mu tig rin po che gsal par byed pa zhes bya ba /
NK109(dze)001:11079: mun chung gi sgron me dang 'dra ba /
NK109(dze)001:11080: rgya gar mkhas pa b+hi ma la mi tras mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK109(dze)001:11081: dpal sngags srung gi rgyal mo smug nag khros pa'i rgyal mo la gtad do //
NK109(dze)001:11083: 'di lta bu'i bstan pa zab mo 'di lta bu ni /
NK109(dze)001:11084: 'dzam bu gling gzhan na med par yid ches so //
NK109(dze)001:11085: des na skal ldan gyi snying la 'changs shig sa ma ya /
NK109(dze)001:11087: 'gro ba'i don du dge bar bsngo //
NK109(dze)001:11088: byang chub snying por myur du thob par shog /'og min gnas 'dra bsgoms la dgon pa ru //
NK109(dze)001:11089: rdo rje 'chang 'dra gu ru jo 'ber las //
NK109(dze)001:11090: gsang bdag dang mtshungs gru gu'i jo 'bum ngas //
NK109(dze)001:11091: chos nyid rang ngo sprod pa mu tig 'phreng ba zhus //
NK109(dze)001:11092: dge bas 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal du gyur //
NK109(dze)001:11093: chos nyid 'khrul snang zad nas grol gyur cig /
